NK027(sha)002:1: // 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dbang chog rin chen phreng ba zhes bya ba /
NK027(sha)002:2: gdod nas rnam dag khyab brdal gnyug ma'i ngang //
NK027(sha)002:3: phyogs dus kun khyab rgyal ba zhi khro'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:4: ston gsal 'bral med 'gro ba rtag tu bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:5: kun gyi bla ma mchod par gus phyag 'tshal //
NK027(sha)002:6: de'i bsgrub thabs dbang gi lag len rnams //
NK027(sha)002:7: rtsa rgyud rig 'dzin bla ma'i gsung bzhin du //
NK027(sha)002:8: rang bzo spang ste du mar 'thor ba rnams //
NK027(sha)002:9: gzhan phan bsam pas phyogs gcig 'dir bkod bya //
NK027(sha)002:10: 'dir 'dus pa chen po mdo yi bsgrub dbang la don gsum ste /
NK027(sha)002:11: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:12: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis las gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:13: rjes don brgyad kyi mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:20: dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:21: dgongs 'dus las slob dpon mtshan nyid brtag pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:22: ye shes snying po khyod nyon cig /
NK027(sha)002:23: rten cing dam la g.yo rgyu med //
NK027(sha)002:24: gsang sngags rgyud kyi sbyor shes pas //
NK027(sha)002:25: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i las la mkhas //
NK027(sha)002:26: de nyid bcu ni yongs shes shing //
NK027(sha)002:27: sems can rnams la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK027(sha)002:28: theg pa che la rtag dga' ba //
NK027(sha)002:29: de ni slob dpon yin par gsungs //
NK027(sha)002:32: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:33: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK027(sha)002:36: mtshan nyid de dag dang ldan pa ni bla ma'o //
NK027(sha)002:37: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:39: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mang dang //
NK027(sha)002:40: chu bo bzhin du ma bo zhing //
NK027(sha)002:41: mnyam zhing 'og kha'i chu ltar dwangs //
NK027(sha)002:42: nyi ma bzhin du gnas pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:43: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid shes par bya //
NK027(sha)002:44: mtho dang 'dus pa nub byang yin //
NK027(sha)002:45: shar lho gzhol zhing mnyam pa la //
NK027(sha)002:46: tho sgro grog do chu sna po //
NK027(sha)002:47: dal dbang dgra 'tshams brtag par bya //
NK027(sha)002:48: lhun sdug ri bo nags tshal ldan //
NK027(sha)002:49: rab tu mnyam zhing snum bag can //
NK027(sha)002:50: chu bo dbang gi phyogs yin te //
NK027(sha)002:51: rlung zad kyi na rlung nyung zhing //
NK027(sha)002:52: me tog shing tshal bya skad brtag /
NK027(sha)002:53: lo rgyus shis pa mchog tu bshad //
NK027(sha)002:56: sde dpung chen po'i mi tshugs shing //
NK027(sha)002:57: sa dang bar snang shes pa la //
NK027(sha)002:58: lo rgyus rnam gnyis ldan pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:59: yid 'ong sa btsal rgyas par bya //
NK027(sha)002:60: 'khor khang phyi nang bar ldan pa //
NK027(sha)002:61: rin chen byug pas bsrung bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:62: rin chen spras pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK027(sha)002:63: zhes pa gnas dang khang pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK027(sha)002:69: bsgrub dang bsgom la dga' ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:70: rtag tu bla ma la gus shing //
NK027(sha)002:71: dus gsum bla ma mchod byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:72: yon tan dad ldan slob ma yin //
NK027(sha)002:73: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:74: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:76: yo byad dka' ba kun bsdus nas //
NK027(sha)002:77: khyad par tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:78: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:79: ces pas sku'i rten tsaka li dang /
NK027(sha)002:80: bris sku lugs ma la sogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:81: gsung gi rten glegs bam dang /
NK027(sha)002:82: thugs kyis rten phyag mtshan du ma dang /
NK027(sha)002:83: dbang gi rdzas bum pa bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:84: bsgrub pa'i rdzas k+aa p+aa la /
NK027(sha)002:85: sman raka phyi nang gtor ma la sogs dang /
NK027(sha)002:86: mchod pa'i rdzas me tog la sogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:87: bgegs bzlog pa'i phur pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:91: dgra rkyen bzlog pa'i go mtshon dang /
NK027(sha)002:94: sil snyan la sogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:98: bla re yol ba la sogs pa nye bar mkho ba du ma dang /
NK027(sha)002:99: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad kyang /
NK027(sha)002:109: rdo rje kun tu rgyu dang /
NK027(sha)002:110: rdo rje ka ra ti la sogs pa dgos pa thams cad sta gon bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:111: dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:112: ston pa gnas 'khor yo byad de dag 'dzoms pa'i dus yin la /
NK027(sha)002:113: bye brag tu bsgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus ni /
NK027(sha)002:115: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK027(sha)002:116: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK027(sha)002:117: byang chub spyod pa cher spyad bya //
NK027(sha)002:118: snga dro'i dus su dkyil 'khor bri //
NK027(sha)002:120: gnyis pa bsgrub gzhi gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:122: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK027(sha)002:123: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK027(sha)002:125: dbang thob pa nod pa'i rdo rje slob dpon la /
NK027(sha)002:126: dbang gi zhu ba phul nas /
NK027(sha)002:128: bla ma thugs dam la bzhugs nas sta gon yan chad bsnyen pa /
NK027(sha)002:129: zhag tu byed pa'i phyed nye bsnyen /
NK027(sha)002:130: nub tha ma ma gtogs pa'i dbang du tshogs bzhi tshogs sam drug tshogs su byed pa bsgrub pa /
NK027(sha)002:131: nub tha ma la rtags dang mtshan ma bzang po
NK027(sha)002:132: byung nas dngos grub len kha la bsgrub pa chen
NK027(sha)002:134: gnas mtshan nyid dang ldan pas /
NK027(sha)002:135: sngon 'gro'i chos rnams rdzogs par byas la /
NK027(sha)002:136: lta ba dbyings ye shes dbyer med rtags pa'i ngang
NK027(sha)002:137: las b+hee ba don dang yi ge'i rjes su 'jug
NK027(sha)002:138: pas yi dam la brten pa ma thob kyi bar
NK027(sha)002:139: la bsnyen pa bskyal ba smin par slob ma'o //
NK027(sha)002:140: mos slob gnyis la sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:142: dang po ni bla mas gang ltar lha grangs kyis bsnyen pa ci 'grub bskyal lo //
NK027(sha)002:143: gnyis pa las rim la gnyis te /
NK027(sha)002:144: bsnyen sgrub kyi skabs su dkyil 'khor bya ba'i las rim dang /
NK027(sha)002:145: bsgrub pa chen po bsgrub dus su dngos grub thob nas dbang gi las rim mo //
NK027(sha)002:147: sa gzhi mnyam dang thig tshon ldan //
NK027(sha)002:148: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:149: rab gnas sbyin bsregs 'jug pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:150: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas bshad bya //
NK027(sha)002:153: dang po sa gzhi yongs su bzung //
NK027(sha)002:154: gnyis pa sta gon la gnas te //
NK027(sha)002:155: nub gsum pa la 'jug bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:156: spyi dbang chen po dbang bskur ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:157: dang po phun sum tshogs ldan nas //
NK027(sha)002:158: tshad phyin rab 'byams slob dpon gyi //
NK027(sha)002:159: snod dang ldan pa'i 'khor bsdus nas //
NK027(sha)002:160: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas dag tu //
NK027(sha)002:161: sa chog rdzogs byas da la ldan //
NK027(sha)002:162: ces pa dang po sa chog la don brgyad kyi spyir brtag pa gong du bstan /
NK027(sha)002:163: gnyis pa bye brag tu brtag pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:165: thad kar sog le lta bu dang /
NK027(sha)002:166: dma' dang dbo ba'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK027(sha)002:167: tsh+wa sgo zug rdo ru spal dang //
NK027(sha)002:168: gram pa thang shing sol dum dang //
NK027(sha)002:169: gyo mo rus pa gseg ma sogs //
NK027(sha)002:170: 'dod pa ma yin sbyang spo bya //
NK027(sha)002:172: bkra shis rtsa dang me tog shing //
NK027(sha)002:173: gnag dang kha dog ldan pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:174: gseg ma rus pa rab nyung zhing //
NK027(sha)002:175: lhag par gyur pa rab tu bshad //
NK027(sha)002:176: ces bzang po'i sa brtag go //
NK027(sha)002:178: mngon pa mi la bslang ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:180: blon po'am sa'i bdag po gang yin la /
NK027(sha)002:182: gnyis pa mi mngon pa la sangs rgyas dang sa'i lha mo gnyis las /
NK027(sha)002:183: dang po gnas der man+dala gru gang ba gcig byas la /
NK027(sha)002:185: tsan dan gyi chus chag chag gdab /
NK027(sha)002:186: de'i steng du mchod pa lnga dang /
NK027(sha)002:189: rang chos gos dkar po dang ldan pas stan la 'dug ste /
NK027(sha)002:190: +aa big+nana ta krid ta h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:191: ces pas rang bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bskyed la /
NK027(sha)002:192: mchod pa rnam pa lnga byin gyis brlabs /
NK027(sha)002:193: gtor ma bdud rtsi thal sbyor gyi sngags kyi bdud
NK027(sha)002:194: rtsi dang gser skyems btags pa gsum re brlab la
NK027(sha)002:195: / zhi thung lugs su 'dzab yan chad bya /
NK027(sha)002:196: de nas sa gzhi ye nas sangs rgyas spyan gyi rang bzhin de ltar b+hee la /
NK027(sha)002:198: ces pas sa gser gyi sa gzhir bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:199: sa yi lha mo la slang ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:200: dkyil 'khor du lam ser po bsam ste /
NK027(sha)002:201: lam rat+na pa sham sid+d+hi ku ru h'u sa m+aa ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:202: zhes pas sa'i lha mo sku mdog ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma /
NK027(sha)002:203: g.yas pa sa gnon g.yon rin po che yi bum pa bsnam pa /
NK027(sha)002:204: phag gi khri la bzhugs pa /
NK027(sha)002:205: 'od lnga dang ldan pa rnam snang gi dbu brgyan pa'i sku gsung thugs byin brlab la /
NK027(sha)002:206: badz+ra sa m+aa dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK027(sha)002:207: rdo rje dril bu thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:208: dam can gser gyi sa la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK027(sha)002:209: yid du 'ong ba'i pho brang dbus na bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:210: nyi zla skar ma dag gi rab brgyan te //
NK027(sha)002:211: byams thugs brtse phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:212: e h+yi'i spyan drangs ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:215: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)002:216: rgyal ba rgyal mtsho ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)002:217: srid pa rgyal mtsho mtha' yas kyi //
NK027(sha)002:218: spyod pa rgyal mtsho thams cad kun //
NK027(sha)002:219: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK027(sha)002:220: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo b+hi shwa mu
NK027(sha)002:221: she b+h+ya sarba tad kham ud ga te s+pha ra
NK027(sha)002:222: na e mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:223: yang dag nyid du dag mod kyang //
NK027(sha)002:224: 'jig rten sri zhu'i tshul gyi ni //
NK027(sha)002:225: 'gro ba yongs kyis don slad du //
NK027(sha)002:226: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsel nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:227: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:228: a ha ra a ha ra sarba big ta ra pu tsa te /
NK027(sha)002:229: na mahs man+ta bu ta nan /
NK027(sha)002:230: ga ga na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:232: pe nu su ra to hoh ti pu pa ra mu /
NK027(sha)002:233: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si h'u sa ma spo tha /
NK027(sha)002:234: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:235: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga du pe d+hu /
NK027(sha)002:237: pe nu su ra to ho //
NK027(sha)002:239: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si h+aum sa ma spo tha /
NK027(sha)002:240: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:241: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga du pe du /
NK027(sha)002:245: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si h'u sa ma spo tha /
NK027(sha)002:246: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:247: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga a lo ke h+r+aih pa na pem /
NK027(sha)002:248: pe nu su ra to ho /
NK027(sha)002:250: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si h'u sa ma spo tha /
NK027(sha)002:251: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:252: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga g+hen+d+he g+han /
NK027(sha)002:254: be nu su ra to hoh te pu pa ra mu /
NK027(sha)002:255: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si h'u sa ma spo tha /
NK027(sha)002:256: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:257: badz+ra r+aa ga nee be te +aah pe na pem /
NK027(sha)002:258: pe nu su ra to hoh te bu pa ra mu /
NK027(sha)002:259: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si h'u sa ma spo tha /
NK027(sha)002:260: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:261: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga shab+ta h'u /
NK027(sha)002:262: skyobs pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)002:263: spyod pa'i tshul dang khyad par las //
NK027(sha)002:264: sa dang pha rol phyin pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:265: lha mo khyod ni dbang du gyur //
NK027(sha)002:267: g.yas tri shu li'i phyag rgya sa la bsnun cing /
NK027(sha)002:268: a hi b+ha wa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:269: zhes pas sa'i lha mo sku lte ba yan chad thon te bzhugs par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:270: de nas mgron spyan drangs pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:272: 'dzam gling spyir na mthu chen dbang bsgyur ma //
NK027(sha)002:273: nam zla dus bzhi dbyar dgun ston dpyid nas //
NK027(sha)002:274: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs ston cing kun la 'tshe //
NK027(sha)002:275: sa bdag gtsang kun gnas nas 'khor ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:276: sa bdag ham phan dang ni the se dang //
NK027(sha)002:277: bi'u sna lag can sa bdag gnyan chen rnams //
NK027(sha)002:278: mchod sbyin gtor ma'i mgron du spyan 'dren na //
NK027(sha)002:279: thugs dam brtse phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:280: yul 'di'i sa la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:281: gangs ri g.ya' ri brag ri spang ri dang //
NK027(sha)002:282: bye rigs sa gnas sa bdag 'khor dang bcas //
NK027(sha)002:283: khyad par sa 'di'i bdag po 'khor dang bcas //
NK027(sha)002:284: rigs dang kha dog mi mthun bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK027(sha)002:285: mchod sbyin gtor ma'i mgron du spyan 'dren na //
NK027(sha)002:286: 'dir gshegs bka' yi gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:287: zhes pas mdun du byon par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:290: rgyas par bshams pa'i mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di //
NK027(sha)002:291: gser dngul la sogs rin chen sna lngas brgyan //
NK027(sha)002:292: sa bdag 'khor dang bcas la mchod pa 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:293: nor dbyigs grangs mang grangs su bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:294: rin chen 'bru sna ma lus zas kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:295: rang lus lhu tshig nyams pa bskang slad du //
NK027(sha)002:296: chags med stobs ldan sems kyi 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)002:297: bzhes nas lhu tshigs nad rnams bral bar mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:298: bu ram sbrang rtsi ka ra 'o ma dang //
NK027(sha)002:299: dug gsum sems la zhugs pa'i nad rnams la //
NK027(sha)002:300: khro gtum drag po'i nad rnams bsal slad du //
NK027(sha)002:301: zhi dul mnyes te mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:302: na ga ge sar la sogs sman sna brgyad //
NK027(sha)002:303: chags nyams nad 'bral ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:304: sa bdag sku bsnyung rkyen ngan sbyangs pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:305: rkang gnyis dkon pa'i don du brtsal dgos te //
NK027(sha)002:306: dbang chen sa bdag 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK027(sha)002:307: nyes skyon gdung sob gdan du 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)002:308: yun du skyid cing bde ba'i sems nyid kyi //
NK027(sha)002:309: dam rdzas bdud rtsi gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:310: zhes brjod la gtong ma dang dkar gsum mngar gsum
NK027(sha)002:311: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs la
NK027(sha)002:312: / gang bcol bka' nyan par bsam ste /
NK027(sha)002:314: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi rab tu 'bar //
NK027(sha)002:315: kun dag'i bdag po dbang byed chen por 'bar //
NK027(sha)002:316: kun tu sa yi lha mo brtan ma 'bar //
NK027(sha)002:317: sa bdag mthu chen 'khor gyi gnas rnams su //
NK027(sha)002:318: mchod sbyin dam pa'i gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas //
NK027(sha)002:319: so so'i 'khor gyi re ba bskangs gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:320: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:324: lcags ri gser ri dngul gyi ri //
NK027(sha)002:325: shel ri gangs ri khyung 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)002:326: mi la nor gyi dbyig 'byung zhing //
NK027(sha)002:327: chos bzang gnas lugs spyod pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:328: mthu chen lha 'am sman la sogs //
NK027(sha)002:329: sa bdag gnyan po 'khor bcas la //
NK027(sha)002:330: kun sbyangs dri sbyar 'bru yi skyems //
NK027(sha)002:331: rin chen sa le sbram gyi spras //
NK027(sha)002:332: rgyu bshams mchod sbyin gser skyems 'di //
NK027(sha)002:334: ces brjod de nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang phyag
NK027(sha)002:335: rgyas gser skyems phyogs bcu kun tu gtor la gnod
NK027(sha)002:338: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:339: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:340: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:341: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis bdag cag gi
NK027(sha)002:342: mos blos byas te sbyar ba'i mchod sbyin gyi gtor
NK027(sha)002:344: 'dzam bu'i gling na gnas pa'i sa bdag ma lus pa rnams dang /
NK027(sha)002:346: sa bdag klu chen gyi tshogs /
NK027(sha)002:349: bu smad dang g.yog 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul lo //
NK027(sha)002:351: de dag rnams kyis spyan lam du gnas kyi khyad par longs spyod kyi rten /
NK027(sha)002:352: sman gyi grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:353: gzhan yang gling bzhi gling phran brgyad nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun /
NK027(sha)002:356: tsan dan gyi skyed mos tshal /
NK027(sha)002:363: rin po che'i phung po la sogs pa yid mthun pa'i gnas su gyur nas /
NK027(sha)002:367: dbang po lag pa la sogs pa sman sna tshogs
NK027(sha)002:368: kyis sa bdag rnams 'od dang gzi brjid ldan par
NK027(sha)002:369: gyur cig / sa phyogs 'dir mnyes shing 'dus pa
NK027(sha)002:370: chen po'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs su gsol bas cho ga
NK027(sha)002:371: ma 'grub bar du gzhan du song zhig /
NK027(sha)002:372: ces brjod pas gzhan du song bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:373: de nas mdzub mo gnyis smin mtshams su bsnol te /
NK027(sha)002:374: a ho be ka kra ma ya /
NK027(sha)002:375: zhes pas lha mo nam mkha' la dpang por bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:377: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dzah zhes pa'i dbang po'i lha rnams spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:378: h'u bzhis dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:379: cad kyi byin rlabs bsdus nas bdag la thim pas
NK027(sha)002:380: / bdag gi lus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK027(sha)002:382: zhes pas rang bzhin zhe sdang rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag /
NK027(sha)002:383: g.yas rdo rje g.yon sdig mdzub gdengs ba /
NK027(sha)002:384: 'jigs pa'i sdang mig gi bgegs la bltas pas /
NK027(sha)002:385: rdo rje gsor zhing mi 'gro ba'i bgegs la bka' basgo'o //
NK027(sha)002:386: su ma b+ha ni bzlas shing yungs kar bgegs la
NK027(sha)002:387: gtor bas khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang nas
NK027(sha)002:389: tshur 'dus pas khro bo'i gur du bsam /
NK027(sha)002:390: spyan las me byung bas me'i gur du gyur par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:391: de nas rang gi gnas su lha mo'i mdun du 'dug ste /
NK027(sha)002:392: ci ltar che mchog rdo rje yi //
NK027(sha)002:393: ru tra bdud sde btul ba ltar //
NK027(sha)002:394: chos kyi rgyal srid dpung btsug pas //
NK027(sha)002:395: de bzhin tu ni bdag gis kyang //
NK027(sha)002:396: rgyal bar bya phyir dkyil 'khor bri //
NK027(sha)002:397: sa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:398: rat+na pa sham sid+d+hi ku ru sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:400: phyag rgya sa la bsnun pas /
NK027(sha)002:401: sa'i lha mo dgyes shing sa la thim pas sa
NK027(sha)002:402: rin po che sna tshogs pa'i rang bzhin du bsam
NK027(sha)002:403: mo // sa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:404: zangs sam shing dmar po la phur pa rtse mo zla gcig byas la /
NK027(sha)002:405: bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las pad+ma k+ai la ya
NK027(sha)002:406: phata dzah zhes brjod pas khro bo zhal gcig phyag
NK027(sha)002:407: bzhi pa sku mdog dmar po g.yas g.yon dang po
NK027(sha)002:408: gnyis pad+ma zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK027(sha)002:409: 'og ma gnyis phur bu dril ba /
NK027(sha)002:410: sku smad phur pa can gcig byung nas phur pa la bstim /
NK027(sha)002:411: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs te /
NK027(sha)002:412: pad+ma dbang gi khro mchog chags pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)002:413: ma lus dbang du bsdus pa'i las mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:414: 'dzam bu gling gi ye shes pa 'di dag /
NK027(sha)002:415: bdag gi byang chub grogs su gyur par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:416: pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya p+aa sham ma na ye w+aa shang ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:417: zhes pas phur pa dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su gdab pa de las 'od 'phros /
NK027(sha)002:418: sa la thim pas sa gzhi bdag gi dbang du gyur par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:419: sa sbyangs pa la bzhi'i byas pa sbyangs pa'i dang po lto 'phye brtag pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:420: phyogs bzhi thig dgu bcu'i byang shar nas /
NK027(sha)002:427: dgun gsum phag byi glang ste /
NK027(sha)002:428: zla ba gang shar mgo de'i bdun zur du 'jug ma la gnas so //
NK027(sha)002:429: des gling khams thams cad khyab nas 'od sa gcig tu bsdu /
NK027(sha)002:430: de'i g.yas rin po che bzung ba'i thad lto ba nas brus pas dngos grub thob bo //
NK027(sha)002:431: de las gzhan mgo la bla ma /
NK027(sha)002:435: de'ang bdag lto 'phye la mchod gtor phul nas /
NK027(sha)002:436: de'i lus lte ba'i thad du bsdu ste /
NK027(sha)002:437: de nam mkha' la bteg la /
NK027(sha)002:440: bden pa brdar la de'i lte ba'i thad du dong
NK027(sha)002:441: cung zad brus la gnas kun tu gtor bar bya'o
NK027(sha)002:442: // der rgya ci tsam 'dod pa rkos la gang ltar ngan pa byung na spang /
NK027(sha)002:443: bzang po byung zhing sngar bas lhag pa ni sa sas brtags pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:444: sa rkos pa'i nang du chu blug la gom pa
NK027(sha)002:445: brgya phyin nas 'ong ba'i 'grib tshab che na ngan
NK027(sha)002:446: / ma 'grib bar ri mo legs po'i gzugs bzang po ni chus brtags pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:447: des rdza bum nang du bum rdzas nyer lnga bcug nas sbas te /
NK027(sha)002:449: tram las rin po che'i mchod sdong /
NK027(sha)002:450: rang gi dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung bar bsgom mo //
NK027(sha)002:451: de nas ci tsam 'dod pa'i stegs bu byas la
NK027(sha)002:452: rdzas nyer lnga ba byung lnga dang sbyar bas byug
NK027(sha)002:453: cing me long gi ngos ltar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:454: mtshan ma gang byung yang skabs 'dir zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya ste /
NK027(sha)002:456: sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:457: de nas rang khro bor gsal ba'i g.yas kyi sor
NK027(sha)002:458: mo lnga la nyi ma'i dal re la h'u re
NK027(sha)002:459: bsam / de las 'od 'phros 'dus pa las rdo rje rtse lnga pa re re bsam la /
NK027(sha)002:460: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:462: lan gsum brdab pas nyes skyon thams cad dag par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:463: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyangs ba ni gnyis las mtshan med ni /
NK027(sha)002:464: ma h+aa shu nyee ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ha /
NK027(sha)002:465: chos kun rang bzhin dag pas na /
NK027(sha)002:466: bdag kyang rang bzhin rnam par dag /
NK027(sha)002:467: ces pas skye med stong pa nyid do //
NK027(sha)002:469: skad cig ma las rang gi rig pa h'u du gyur par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:470: de'i 'og tu 'byung ba rim brtsegs las khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bskyed la /
NK027(sha)002:471: sa dang sa 'dzin gyi rtog pa kun rdzob lha'i rang bzhin gyi sbyangs ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:472: drug pas byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:474: dkyil 'khor sta gon gyi skabs su bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:476: de yang cha rkyen bsdu zhing slob ma rnams nang du 'dus la gleng gzhi bshad /
NK027(sha)002:477: gag brgyad bshad la thugs dam bskangs //
NK027(sha)002:479: zhes gsungs pas thog mar cha rkyen bsdu ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:481: 'byor pa'i yo byad tshang ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:482: bde ba chen po'i tshogs su bshad //
NK027(sha)002:484: khyu byug rol pa'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK027(sha)002:485: kun tu rgyu dang gal phye dang //
NK027(sha)002:486: zla rgyas zla phrom lnga gsum rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:487: bsgrub pa tshogs kyis rdzas su bshad //
NK027(sha)002:490: mda' dang dar dang ral gri dang //
NK027(sha)002:491: thugs rje'i rgyun thag phur bu dang //
NK027(sha)002:492: phan dang bla re rgyal mtshan dang //
NK027(sha)002:493: do shal rdzas rnams bsdus te bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:494: ces gsungs pas gzhung nas 'byung ba bzhin bsham ste /
NK027(sha)002:496: las bum dang phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas rnams tshang
NK027(sha)002:497: bar bsags la phyi'i 'jig rten pa'i thugs dam bskangs
NK027(sha)002:498: ba ni / dar phyar rol mo'i sgra bsgrag /
NK027(sha)002:499: byin gyis brlabs la gser skyems rgyas pa btang /
NK027(sha)002:500: khyad par gzhi bdag la gser skyems dang gtor ma byin la sdong grogs bcol lo //
NK027(sha)002:501: gtsang ris kyi dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa lnga la gtor ma cha gsum btang la thugs dam bskang /
NK027(sha)002:502: 'jig rten gyi lha 'dre thams cad la phud gtor byin la /
NK027(sha)002:503: bsgrub pa chen po 'di la zhugs nas ma thon
NK027(sha)002:504: gyi bar la bar chad ma byed par bka' bsgo
NK027(sha)002:505: / khyad par du mgon po dang ma mo la bsgrub pa'i sdong grogs zhu /
NK027(sha)002:506: dkon mchog gsum la gsol ba drag tu btab bo //
NK027(sha)002:507: nang gi thugs dam bskangs ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:508: cha gsum dri chab khyer la tshogs las bya /
NK027(sha)002:509: mchod pa zlos kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs la phyi cha
NK027(sha)002:510: mthun sprul pa'i ma mo gzhung bzhin mchod la thugs
NK027(sha)002:511: dam bskul / nang ting nge 'dzin gyi ma mo'i
NK027(sha)002:512: yig 'bru sgo nas bskyed la ye shes pa spyan
NK027(sha)002:513: dam bskul / drangs la bstim / mchod bstod /
NK027(sha)002:514: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab po gsang ba'i
NK027(sha)002:515: thig le'i ma mo tsan d+ha li gnad kyi rtsa
NK027(sha)002:516: rlung gcun / rang bzhin lhun grub kyis ma mo
NK027(sha)002:517: mkha' klong gnyis su med pa'i ngang du la bzla
NK027(sha)002:518: rlung gcun / / bsrung ma thugs dam can la bar chad bsrung bar bka' bsgo bya /
NK027(sha)002:519: ma 'dres pa bsre ba'i cho ga bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:520: de nas zab cing rgya che ba'i chos bshad do //
NK027(sha)002:521: de yang 'o skol 'khor ba rnams khrag gi rgya mtsho lta bu'i nang nas /
NK027(sha)002:522: sdug bsngal gyi rba klong dpag tu med pa la longs spyod cing zhen /
NK027(sha)002:523: bya ba ma yin pa la mngon par zhen pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:525: 'dod yon la mngon par chags pa ni lan tsh+wa'i chu dang 'dra /
NK027(sha)002:526: ci byas sdug bsngal la spyod pa ni rgyal mtsho'i gzan dang 'dra ste /
NK027(sha)002:527: de ltar 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin la bde ba skad cig kyang med de /
NK027(sha)002:529: mi gtsang ba la dri zhim med //
NK027(sha)002:530: 'gro lnga dag la bde ba med //
NK027(sha)002:533: 'gro ba 'di dag ming dang gzugs kyis 'dam la chags /
NK027(sha)002:534: rlung gi srid pas 'khor bar 'khor lo lta bur 'khyams la /
NK027(sha)002:536: 'khor ba'i gnas nas thams cad sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'bras la longs spyod de /
NK027(sha)002:539: dud 'gro la gcig la gcig za /
NK027(sha)002:543: de thams cad la thun mong du skye 'chi'i sdug bsngal bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK027(sha)002:544: 'khor ba'i sems can gyi tshogs de dag la bsam na /
NK027(sha)002:545: sems can tsam po'i lus mthong nas //
NK027(sha)002:546: mi lus thob pa med pa tsam //
NK027(sha)002:547: kha 'thor pa yi tshogs mthong na //
NK027(sha)002:548: mi lus thob pa srid pa tsam //
NK027(sha)002:551: gang tshe dge spyod skal ldan yang //
NK027(sha)002:552: dge ba bdag gi ma byas na //
NK027(sha)002:553: ngan song sdug bsngal kun rmongs la //
NK027(sha)002:554: de tshe bdag gi ci byar yod //
NK027(sha)002:555: dge ba dag kyang ma byas na //
NK027(sha)002:556: sdig pa dag kyang nyer bsags la //
NK027(sha)002:557: bskal pa bye ba brgyar yang ni //
NK027(sha)002:559: de nyid phyir na bcom ldan gyi //
NK027(sha)002:560: rgya mtsho cher g.yeng gnya' shing gi //
NK027(sha)002:561: bu ga rus sbal mgrin chud ltar //
NK027(sha)002:562: mi nyid shin tu thob dka' gsungs //
NK027(sha)002:564: dal 'byor 'di ni shin tu rnyed par dka' //
NK027(sha)002:565: skyes bu don 'grub thob par gyur pa la //
NK027(sha)002:566: gal te 'di la phan par ma gyur na //
NK027(sha)002:567: phyis ni yang dag 'byor pa ga la 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:568: ji ltar mtshan mo'i mun nag spriin rum na //
NK027(sha)002:569: glog 'gyu skad cig bar snang bston mdzad bzhin //
NK027(sha)002:570: de phyir sangs rgyas mthu yi rgya lam na //
NK027(sha)002:571: 'jig rten bsod nams blo gros thang 'ga' 'byung //
NK027(sha)002:572: zhes dal 'byor gyi mi lus shin tu thob par dka' ba gsungs /
NK027(sha)002:573: gal te mi lus thang gcig thob srid kyang //
NK027(sha)002:574: dge ba ma bsags don med stong log yin //
NK027(sha)002:576: mi yi lus kyang thob mi 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:577: mi lus thob par ma gyur na //
NK027(sha)002:578: sdig pa 'ba' zhig dge ba med //
NK027(sha)002:580: nam 'chi tshe la nges pa med de /
NK027(sha)002:582: byas dang ma byas mi sdod par //
NK027(sha)002:583: na dang mi na kun gyis kyang //
NK027(sha)002:584: glo bur tshe la yid mi rten //
NK027(sha)002:585: thams cad bor nas 'gro dgos pas //
NK027(sha)002:586: bdag gis de ltar ma shes so //
NK027(sha)002:588: tshe ma tshor bar zad pa yang //
NK027(sha)002:589: nyin mtshan sdod pa yang med de //
NK027(sha)002:591: snon pa gud nas yang med pas //
NK027(sha)002:593: bdag ni mal na 'dug bzhin du //
NK027(sha)002:594: gnyen bshes kun gyi mtha' bskor yang //
NK027(sha)002:595: srog gcad pa yi tshor ba dag /
NK027(sha)002:596: bdag nyid gcig pur myong bar 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:597: gshin rje'i pho nyas zin pa la //
NK027(sha)002:598: gnyen gyi ci phan bshes ci phan //
NK027(sha)002:599: de tshe bsod nams gcig skyabs na //
NK027(sha)002:600: de yang bdag gi ma bsten no //
NK027(sha)002:601: zhes gsungs pas 'chi ba rjes su dran par bya dgos te /
NK027(sha)002:602: nad med nyi ma 'di lta bu //
NK027(sha)002:603: zag bcas 'tshe ba med kyang ni //
NK027(sha)002:604: tshe 'di skad cig bslu ba ste //
NK027(sha)002:605: lus ni thang gcig gnyen po bzhin //
NK027(sha)002:606: de ring kho nar mi sdod ces //
NK027(sha)002:607: bde bar sdod pa rig ma yin //
NK027(sha)002:608: zhes pas 'chi ba ma dran na //
NK027(sha)002:609: gang byas chos su mi 'gyur te //
NK027(sha)002:611: 'di ni sang bya 'di ni thang gcig 'og tu bya //
NK027(sha)002:612: 'di ni de ring bya zhes skye bo byed sems na //
NK027(sha)002:613: gshin rje'i be con lag thogs zur gyi blta ba yin //
NK027(sha)002:614: mig rtsa dmar khros ma rung gad mo re snyems 'debs //
NK027(sha)002:616: sos ka'i me tog rgyas pa'i dus 'dir 'byung 'gyur zhing /
NK027(sha)002:617: zla ba gsal ba mtshon pa'i ston dus 'di byung zhes /
NK027(sha)002:618: skye bo thams cad dga' 'gyur bdag gi tshe 'di ni //
NK027(sha)002:619: zad pas 'gyur snyam mi dga' mi byed rig ma yin //
NK027(sha)002:620: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir nges 'byung chen po'i dal 'byor
NK027(sha)002:621: gyi snying po blang ba'i phyir tshogs gnyis bsags pa
NK027(sha)002:624: 'jig rten sdug bsngal ci snyed kun //
NK027(sha)002:625: de kun mi dge byas las byung //
NK027(sha)002:626: lha mi'i bde ba ci snyed kun //
NK027(sha)002:627: de kun bsod nams bsags las thob //
NK027(sha)002:628: bsod nams bsags pas bde ba thob //
NK027(sha)002:629: de phyir yang dang yang du bsags //
NK027(sha)002:631: de ltar du 'chi ba mi rtag pa'i gsal 'debs dang /
NK027(sha)002:634: dge ba bcu'i phan yon dang /
NK027(sha)002:635: mi dge ba bcu'i nyes dmigs dang /
NK027(sha)002:636: ngan song gsum gyis sdug bsngal dang /
NK027(sha)002:637: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa'i dad pa skye
NK027(sha)002:638: ba la sogs chos zab cing rgya che ba bshad
NK027(sha)002:639: la / rgyud snod du rung ba'i nges shes bskyed la /
NK027(sha)002:640: khyad par theg pa'i rim pa dgu dang /
NK027(sha)002:642: yang sgos chos 'di'i bka' babs tshul dang /
NK027(sha)002:643: bla ma brgyud pa'i rim pa bshad de spro ba bskyed par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:644: de la sngon 'gro phyag na rdo rje'i dbang bskur ba la /
NK027(sha)002:645: dang po dkyil 'khor ci tsam ran pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ser /
NK027(sha)002:647: mu khyud bar khyams sgo phyogs mdog /
NK027(sha)002:649: cha gsum gyis dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su ling tse dgu'i dbus mthing /
NK027(sha)002:655: mu khyud sogs sgo rta bab thams cad spyi mthun no //
NK027(sha)002:656: dkyil 'khor bri zin nas de'i mtha' mar /
NK027(sha)002:666: man+dala dang phyi'i dkon mchog dang /
NK027(sha)002:667: chos skyong 'gro drug bgegs rnams la dkar gtor cha gsum dang /
NK027(sha)002:668: nang gi sman gtor rak+ta tshogs dang bcas pa rnams bsham ste /
NK027(sha)002:670: nang rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK027(sha)002:672: chos skyong mgon po lcam dral lo //
NK027(sha)002:673: de nas gu gul gyi bum pa bsang /
NK027(sha)002:674: dri chu bum rdzas mgul ching kha rgyan dang bcas pa gtso bo dang /
NK027(sha)002:678: gzhan ci ltar 'os pa bshams shing sku tsaka li yang dgod do //
NK027(sha)002:679: skyabs 'gro'i rten thub pa'i sku dang /
NK027(sha)002:682: snga dro gtor ma brgya tsa dang /
NK027(sha)002:683: chab gtor klu gtor yang bata nga ngo //
NK027(sha)002:684: de nas rang nyid stan bde ba la 'dug ste /
NK027(sha)002:686: sems bskyed pa sngon du song bas /
NK027(sha)002:687: cha gsum dkyil 'khor dbus su rin po che'i khri pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan la /
NK027(sha)002:689: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das
NK027(sha)002:690: rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog sngon po'am dkar po
NK027(sha)002:691: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyi brgyan pa /
NK027(sha)002:692: g.yas thugs kar rdo rje gtod de 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:693: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK027(sha)002:694: zhabs rdo rje'i dkyil krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:695: gtso bo zhal nub tu gzigs pa'i mdun du sgeg mo /
NK027(sha)002:699: nub byang sogs grwa bzhir bdug spos ma /
NK027(sha)002:703: nub sgo phyogs su lcags sgrog ma /
NK027(sha)002:706: zhags pa ma la sogs sku mdog phyag mtshan gzhan dang mthun no //
NK027(sha)002:707: dpal chen po sku mdog sngo skya khyung gshogs can /
NK027(sha)002:709: sbrul stag glang zhing chen thod phreng gi brgyan pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:710: gnyis ka bsnyen dus su rdo rje dril bu 'dzin
NK027(sha)002:711: pa'am rdor sems ltar bsgrub dus su rdo rje dung
NK027(sha)002:712: khrag 'dzin pa'o // de nas gtso bo'i thugs ka'i
NK027(sha)002:713: h'u las 'od 'phros rang bzhin gyi gnas nas ye
NK027(sha)002:715: ar+g+ham la sogs pas mchod pa rnams lngas mchod nas /
NK027(sha)002:716: dzahmh'u bam hohs dam tshig pa la bstim /
NK027(sha)002:718: de nas gtso bo'i thugs ka'i pad+ma kha bye ba'i
NK027(sha)002:719: steng du zla ba nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la h'u
NK027(sha)002:720: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin las /
NK027(sha)002:721: badz+ra sat+wasa bskor ba las 'od byung /
NK027(sha)002:722: sgo gsum gyis sdig sgrib thams cad dag par bsam zhing /
NK027(sha)002:723: snying po de nyid kun gyi 'dzab tu bzlas te
NK027(sha)002:724: bargya'am stong la sogs pa song nas lus ngag yid
NK027(sha)002:726: sku gsung thugs kyi nyams chag bkang /
NK027(sha)002:727: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad mthol lo bshags so //
NK027(sha)002:728: nyes ltung dri ma'i tshogs thams cad byang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:729: zhes brjod la de'i ngang la blo ma bcos par bzhag go //
NK027(sha)002:730: de nas gsang bdag gi dkyil 'khor dbus su /
NK027(sha)002:731: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka'i rigs
NK027(sha)002:732: lnga'i rnam snang gi thugs ka nas gser gyis rdo
NK027(sha)002:733: rje rtse lnga h'u gis mtshan pa gcig byung ba
NK027(sha)002:734: las nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la dpal phyag na rdo
NK027(sha)002:735: rje sku mdog sngon po g.yas rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:736: g.yon bsdigs mdzub zhabs nang ltar g.yas bskum /
NK027(sha)002:738: zhi ba sems dkyil drag po rus rgyan /
NK027(sha)002:741: zhi ba pa ti khro bo dar sngon po'i chas gos dang /
NK027(sha)002:742: seng ge dkar mo'i stod g.yog gsol nas /
NK027(sha)002:743: mi bskyod pa'i dbu rgyan can /
NK027(sha)002:744: ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus nas bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:756: khug phyogs la 'gro ba rigs drug /
NK027(sha)002:757: phyi rol du lan chag gi mgron bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:759: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes pas rang bzhin gyi gnas nas ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK027(sha)002:760: dzahmh'u bam hos dam tshig pa la bstim /
NK027(sha)002:761: tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aas brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:763: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs te /
NK027(sha)002:764: thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' rang 'dra ba gcig bsam /
NK027(sha)002:765: de nas mchod pa lngas mchod nas dbang ma bskur ba'i gong du /
NK027(sha)002:768: n+ai lam b+ha ra d+ha ra badz+ra p+aa ni r+aa dz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:770: de nas las bum du gtso bo'i thugs ka nas bdud rtsi 'khyil pa g.yas rdo rje rgya gram /
NK027(sha)002:772: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa gcig byung bar sgom la /
NK027(sha)002:773: de'i thugs kar rdo rje rgya gram h'u gi mtshan pa las 'od 'phro bar bsgoms te /
NK027(sha)002:774: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas bdud rtsi 'khyil pas las byed bgegs mthar byed la /
NK027(sha)002:775: a big nan ta krid h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:777: a mri ta kun d+ha li h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:780: dri chab dang las bum gnyis kas gtso bo'i dbang gi lha bum bsang la lha gang ltar bskyed /
NK027(sha)002:782: dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK027(sha)002:783: rtsa ba'i snying po bzlas te /
NK027(sha)002:784: chu thig gcig bum par blugs pas /
NK027(sha)002:785: bum pa'i lha gzhal yas khang bum chu gzugs mtsho'i
NK027(sha)002:786: chu zil pa re'ang tshe dpal bde ba bskyed byed
NK027(sha)002:787: kyi lha / rin po che'i ri bo /
NK027(sha)002:788: sman gyi nags tshal spos ngad ldan pa /
NK027(sha)002:794: de ltar bzlas pas brgya rtsa re la mchod pa tshar re de lan bcu stong rtsa'o //
NK027(sha)002:796: bum pa'i kha rgyan spyi bor bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:797: chu khar btung bas bdag kyang lhar nges pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:798: de nas mdun gyi byin gyis brlabs /
NK027(sha)002:799: rang la bsdus pas h'u bzhi dpral ba mgrin pa /
NK027(sha)002:800: thugs ka lte bar thig le byas pas sku gsung
NK027(sha)002:801: thugs ye shes thugs rje'i rang bzhin du bsam la
NK027(sha)002:802: mi rtog pa'i ngang la dar gcig bzhag go //
NK027(sha)002:803: de nas cha gsum btang ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:804: skyabs 'gro yan lag bdun pas phyag 'tshal pas /
NK027(sha)002:805: rang gtso bo'i thugs ka'i 'od zer lha dang mchod rdzas dri ma thams cad dag par bsam zhing /
NK027(sha)002:806: ye d+har+m+aa bzlas te phyogs thams cad du me tog 'thor zhing /
NK027(sha)002:807: lha rdzas las grub pa'i mchod rdzas dwangs shing thogs
NK027(sha)002:808: pa med par bsam gyis mi khyab par bsam la
NK027(sha)002:809: / spos dang rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas /
NK027(sha)002:811: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gi //
NK027(sha)002:812: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)002:813: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK027(sha)002:814: mchod nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:815: ye shes phung po mkha' 'dra ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:816: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK027(sha)002:817: sprul pa kun gyi 'byung gnas gtso //
NK027(sha)002:818: rdo rje sems dpa' gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:819: dmigs pa kun la rab gnas shing //
NK027(sha)002:820: byin rlabs kun gyi gzhir gyur pa //
NK027(sha)002:821: rnal 'byor kun gyi dbang phyug che //
NK027(sha)002:822: sa gzhi lta bur gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:823: thugs rje chen po thabs mkhas pas //
NK027(sha)002:824: gdug pa 'dul phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:825: ye shes rtog pa'i khyad par la //
NK027(sha)002:826: sprul pa mang po'i tshogs dang gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:827: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru
NK027(sha)002:828: ni ka tri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK027(sha)002:829: ma ya s+t+wam / thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs kyi rgyud bskul zhing //
NK027(sha)002:830: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan 'dren nas //
NK027(sha)002:831: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod la //
NK027(sha)002:832: 'dir gshegs bzhugs shing rnal 'byor dgyes par bskyed //
NK027(sha)002:833: badz+ra am gu sha dzah badz+ra s+pho ta bam /
NK027(sha)002:835: badz+ra g+hen+de hoh ka ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK027(sha)002:836: a nu ta ra p+auts+tsha ud ga te s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa //
NK027(sha)002:837: rin chen 'tsher bas brgyan pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:839: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK027(sha)002:841: rim bzhin yangs par bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:842: pad+ma k+aa ma la ye s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:843: ma h+aa su ka badz+ra sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:844: dzahmh'u bam hoh ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti dza ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:845: nags tshal bcud ni yid dgar 'ong //
NK027(sha)002:846: dri zhim rgyas pa lha yi rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:847: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:848: lha rdzas bzang po'i bdug spos 'di //
NK027(sha)002:849: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK027(sha)002:850: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:851: badz+ra d+hu pe p+auts+tsha me g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h'u /
NK027(sha)002:852: gtsang zhing gtsang mar las skyes pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:853: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog 'di //
NK027(sha)002:854: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)002:855: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:856: badz+ra push+pe p+auts+tsha me g+ha sdug bsngal 'joms shing bkra shis pa //
NK027(sha)002:857: dgyes shing mun sel mar me 'di //
NK027(sha)002:858: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK027(sha)002:859: bzhes nas bdag la badz+ra a lo ke p+auts+tsha me
NK027(sha)002:860: g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye
NK027(sha)002:861: h'u / gtsang zhing gtsang mar lha rdzas bzang po'i dri chab 'di //
NK027(sha)002:862: bdag gi dad pas 'bul bzhes nas bdag /
NK027(sha)002:863: badz+ra g+han+d+he p+auts+tsha me g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h'u /
NK027(sha)002:864: sman rnams bcud ni yid dgar 'ong //
NK027(sha)002:865: sngags kyi zhal zas bshos 'di dag /
NK027(sha)002:866: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK027(sha)002:867: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:868: badz+ra nee wi te p+auts+tsha me ga sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h'u /
NK027(sha)002:869: sgra dbyangs snyan cing yid 'ong ldan //
NK027(sha)002:870: lha rdzas dam pa'i rol mo 'di //
NK027(sha)002:871: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK027(sha)002:872: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:873: badz+ra g+han+d+he rat+na sang pra ra ni ta p+auts+tsha me
NK027(sha)002:874: g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye
NK027(sha)002:875: h'u / mchod sprin gyi sngags ring dang /
NK027(sha)002:876: yid du 'ong ba'i mchod sprin dang //
NK027(sha)002:877: rol mo sil snyan sprin gyi tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:878: mchod 'os tshul dang mthun pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:879: nam mkha'i khams kun khyab gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:880: bzang spyod yan lag bdun pa byas la /
NK027(sha)002:882: mi mnyam mnyam pa'i lha khyod rtag tu bdag la ni //
NK027(sha)002:883: thugs rjes spyan gyis gzigs shing rgyun du 'gro ba'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:884: byang chub mchog gi spyod pa bsgrub par dam bcas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:885: bdag gi re ba'i 'bras bu 'di la mchis par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:886: gti mug mun pas bdag cag gnong gyur te //
NK027(sha)002:887: byams mgon ci slad bdag la thugs rjes mi bartse'am //
NK027(sha)002:888: khyod kyi mkhyen rab bskal pa'i me 'dra bas //
NK027(sha)002:889: sems kyi mun sel sgron ma bdag la stsol //
NK027(sha)002:890: mgon po mchog dang shin tu ldan gyur na //
NK027(sha)002:891: sems can don la bskul ba mi 'tshal yang //
NK027(sha)002:892: sdug bsngal rang bzhin dbang du bdag gyur pas //
NK027(sha)002:893: skyobs pa spyan sngar gdung bas gsol ba 'debs //
NK027(sha)002:894: gang zhig pha dang ma la slong na yang //
NK027(sha)002:895: shin tu skyo ngal med pa de bzhin du //
NK027(sha)002:896: 'gro ba'i don brtson mdzad pa khyed lags kyi //
NK027(sha)002:897: tshe rabs kun tu bdag gi skyabs mdzod cig /
NK027(sha)002:899: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams mtha' yas mu med pa na /
NK027(sha)002:900: dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom
NK027(sha)002:901: ldan 'das rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK027(sha)002:902: bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod kyis mi langs ba
NK027(sha)002:903: thams cad la phyag 'tshal zhing gus par skyabs su
NK027(sha)002:904: mchi'o // bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi zhal nas gsungs pa'i chos dkon mchog /
NK027(sha)002:905: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rgyu dang
NK027(sha)002:906: 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK027(sha)002:907: la phyag 'tshal zhing gus par skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:908: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs kyis sras su
NK027(sha)002:909: gyur pa'i dge 'dun rnams la phyag 'tshal zhing gus
NK027(sha)002:911: dkon mchog gsum la mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:918: sil snyan dang rol mo dngos su 'byor ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:919: yid kyi sprul pa'i mchod pa'i sprin dpung bsam gyis
NK027(sha)002:920: mi khyab pa phul bas bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:922: sems can thams cad 'khor ba thog ma med pa
NK027(sha)002:923: nas gzung 'dzin rang kha mar zhen pa'i dbang gi
NK027(sha)002:924: nyon mongs pa 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i dbang gi 'khor
NK027(sha)002:925: ba ngan song gi rgyur gyur zhing mtho ris dang
NK027(sha)002:926: thar pa'i sgrib par gyur ba ci mchis pa thams
NK027(sha)002:927: cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:928: 'di ltar bgyis pa'i dge bas sems can thams cad kyi thun mong du yongs su bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK027(sha)002:929: de ltar bsngosa pa'i sems can thams cad bla na
NK027(sha)002:930: med pa'i byang chub rin po che myur du thob
NK027(sha)002:931: par gyur cig / gnas skabs su tshe ring nad med pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:932: dpal dang 'byor pa rgyas pa dge ba bsgrub pa la bar chad med pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:933: phrin las phun sum tshogs pa bsgrub nus par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:934: sangs rgyas sku gsung brnyes sogs brjod /
NK027(sha)002:936: h+r+aihpad+ma ta krid badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+h+ri wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:939: swa b+ha wa b+hi shud+d+he d+har+m+aa sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:940: a mri ta kun d+ha li ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:941: las mchod pa byin rlabs gong ltar bya /
NK027(sha)002:943: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang /
NK027(sha)002:945: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa lo ki te sam b+ha ra sam b+ha ra h'u /
NK027(sha)002:946: bdag gi bsod nams stobs dang ni /
NK027(sha)002:949: sarba ka ri sarba sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:950: tshangs pa brgya byin rgyal chen lha dang klu //
NK027(sha)002:951: gnod sbyin lto 'phye dri za lha ma yin //
NK027(sha)002:952: mkha' lding grul bum srin po mi'am ci //
NK027(sha)002:953: sems can gang dag bde gshegs sras rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:954: nor med phung po dpal bzhes kun gshegs bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:956: a kar sha ya sarba d+hi ta rash+ta ya gan+d+har+b+ha
NK027(sha)002:957: a ti pa ta ye h'u dzah bi ru d+ha
NK027(sha)002:958: k+aa ye kur ban d+he a ti pa ta ye
NK027(sha)002:959: h'u dzah bi ru pak+sha ye n+aa ga a ti
NK027(sha)002:960: pa ta ye h'u dzah bee sh+r+aa ba na ye
NK027(sha)002:961: a ti pa ta ye h'u dzah bra h+ma ne
NK027(sha)002:962: h'u dzah in+d+ra ya h'u dzah ag+ne ye h'u dzah
NK027(sha)002:963: ya ma ye h'u dzah n+airti t+ya ye h'u dzah
NK027(sha)002:964: wa ru na ye h'u dzah ba ya b+he h'u
NK027(sha)002:965: dzah ku bee r+aa ye h'u dzah i sh+aa na
NK027(sha)002:966: ye h'u dzah ud+d+ha b+h+ra h+ma h'u dzah sur+ya b+h+ra
NK027(sha)002:967: h+ma a ti pa ta ye h'u dzah tsan+d+ra na
NK027(sha)002:968: k+sha tra a ti pa ta ye h+aum dzah a
NK027(sha)002:969: ho pra ti wi b+h+ya h'u dzah a su ra
NK027(sha)002:970: b+h+ya h'u dzah n+aa ga b+h+ya sa pa ri ba
NK027(sha)002:971: sa ma ya s+t+wam h'u dzah h'u /
NK027(sha)002:972: dad pa dad ni dam tshig gi //
NK027(sha)002:973: tshur gshegs phyogs skyongs mgon po rnams //
NK027(sha)002:974: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK027(sha)002:975: mchod pas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:976: a ha ra a ha ra sarba b+h+yi d+ha ra p+auts+tsha te na mahs man+ta pu ta nam /
NK027(sha)002:977: ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:978: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:979: lha rdzas dam pa'i mchod yon dang //
NK027(sha)002:980: me tog bdug spos mar me dri //
NK027(sha)002:981: zhal zas rol mo'i tshogs rnams kun //
NK027(sha)002:982: chos skyong mgon po rnams la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:983: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:985: ri rgyal lhun po'i phyogs bzhi nas //
NK027(sha)002:987: spyan mig bzang dang rnam thos sras //
NK027(sha)002:989: bdag gi re ba bskang du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:990: dbang po rdo rje 'chang ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:991: lha yi rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)002:992: shar phyogs gdon gyi tshogs bcas la //
NK027(sha)002:993: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK027(sha)002:994: me ste bsregs bya za ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:995: drang srong rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)002:996: shar lho gdon gyi tshogs mchod cing gshin rje be con 'chang ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:997: ma mo'i rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)002:998: lho phyogs gdon gyi tshogs mchod cing bden dang bral ba legs ldan lha //
NK027(sha)002:999: srin po'i rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)002:1000: lho nub gdon gyi tshogs mchod cing zhags pa thogs pa chu yi lha //
NK027(sha)002:1001: klu yi rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)002:1002: nub phyogs gdon gyi mchod cing bstod de phyag rlung ste srog kyang 'dzin pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:1003: rig 'dzin rgyal po gdon nub phyogs gdon gyi tshogs
NK027(sha)002:1004: mchod cing bstod gnod sbyin lag na dbyug to thogs
NK027(sha)002:1005: // nor skyong rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)002:1006: byang phyogs gnod sbyin mchod cing dbang dang ldan pa 'dren pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:1007: 'byung po'i rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK027(sha)002:1008: byang shar dbang ldan tshogs bcas la //
NK027(sha)002:1009: mchod cing steng gi tshangs pa chen po dang //
NK027(sha)002:1010: nyi ma zla ba gza' chen po //
NK027(sha)002:1011: gza' dang rgyu skar tshogs bcas la //
NK027(sha)002:1012: mchod cing bstod de tish+thi ra ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1013: b+he ru ka ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1014: be ru bag sha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1015: b+he sha ra ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1020: ba ru na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1022: ku be ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1023: i sha na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1024: ur d+ham pra h+aa ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1026: a ti pa ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1028: a ti pa ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1029: a ho pra ti thi wi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1030: tshad ma mchis pa'i mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya
NK027(sha)002:1031: chen po 'di 'bul zhing bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur
NK027(sha)002:1032: pa ni / yon tan gyi mgron tshangs pa dang brgya byin rgyal po chen po sde bzhi /
NK027(sha)002:1037: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK027(sha)002:1038: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon pi tsi ka dang /
NK027(sha)002:1039: btsun mo dpal ldan ha ri dang /
NK027(sha)002:1040: sras phrog ma'i bu lnga brgya dang /
NK027(sha)002:1041: rdo rje rigs kyi srung ma thugs dam can gtsang
NK027(sha)002:1042: mar gnas pa rnams la mchod pa 'bul ba ni
NK027(sha)002:1048: cang shes kyi rta la sogs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:1049: 'dod pa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa /
NK027(sha)002:1050: ma tshang ba med pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa med pa 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1051: de ltar byung bas thugs brtse bar dgongs te /
NK027(sha)002:1052: byin gyis brlab nas bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:1056: bdag cag rnams kyis mchod pa'i yo byad dman pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1057: rgyu rkyen ma tshogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1058: brjod pa ma dag pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1060: spyod lam bag med pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1061: le lo dang snyoms las su gyur pa /
NK027(sha)002:1062: ci mchis pa thams cad bsrung ma dam tshig can khyed rnams kyis spyan sngar mthol lo bshags so //
NK027(sha)002:1063: de ltar mthol zhing bshags nas bdag cag dpon slob
NK027(sha)002:1064: yon mchod bdag 'khor bcas rnams kyi sngon gyi las
NK027(sha)002:1066: 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur kyang rung /
NK027(sha)002:1067: 'jig rten 'dir yang nad mang ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:1068: tshe thung ba dang sems kyi sdug bsngal thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1070: gnod pa'i bgegs la sogs pa bsam pa ngan pa /
NK027(sha)002:1071: sbyor ba rtsub par byed pa thams cad dang /
NK027(sha)002:1074: ltas ngan pa thams cad bzlog cing zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:1075: gzhan yang 'byung po mi dang mi ma yin pa sdang ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK027(sha)002:1076: gdug pa'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK027(sha)002:1077: drag shul gyi sems dang ldan pa /
NK027(sha)002:1078: de dag thams cad bzlog cing gdug pa zhi zhing bsgyur bar mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:1079: gal te zhi bas 'dul du ma 'tshal na gang la gang 'tsham pa'i chad pa bcad pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1081: bsdig cing dpa' bskum par mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:1083: mthu stobs can khyed rnams kyi mnga' 'og tu ma 'dus pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1084: sde ris su ma gtogs pa gang yang ma mchis
NK027(sha)002:1085: pa de dag thams cad zhi ba dang 'dul bar
NK027(sha)002:1086: mdzad du gsol / mdor na nyes pa'i skyon thams cad byang zhing dag pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1087: legs pa'i yon tan thams cad 'phel zhing rgyas par mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:1088: gtor ma bar pa bsang dang bden sbyangs gong bzhin bya /
NK027(sha)002:1091: pad+ma ta krid badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+r+ai wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:1092: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin lto 'phye grul //
NK027(sha)002:1093: nam mkha'i lding dang 'dab bzang lus srul po //
NK027(sha)002:1094: dri za srin po gdon gyi rigs rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1095: gang dag sa la gnas pa'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK027(sha)002:1096: bu smad bcas shing g.yog 'khor bcas pa la //
NK027(sha)002:1097: bdag gi pus mo sa la btsug nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:1098: thal mo sbyar nas khyed la gsol 'debs kyis //
NK027(sha)002:1099: gsan nas phan gdag slad du 'dir gshegs shig /
NK027(sha)002:1100: sarba lo ka e h+ya hi lo ka ra ya /
NK027(sha)002:1110: sa pa ri wa ra sa ma ya /
NK027(sha)002:1111: an+ri su tri pre du dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh de wa na ga gan d+ha b+h+ya /
NK027(sha)002:1118: sa p+aa ri wa ra na mah sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo /
NK027(sha)002:1120: sarba tar+kham urga te s+pha ra ni i mam ga
NK027(sha)002:1121: ga na kham g+h+ri ha na e dam b+ha lid+ta
NK027(sha)002:1122: ye s+w+aa h+aa / gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:1123: lha rdzas dam pa'i mchod yon dang //
NK027(sha)002:1124: me tog bdug spos mar me dri //
NK027(sha)002:1125: zhal zas dri mchog rol mo'i tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:1126: rigs drug mgron rnams 'bul lo bzhes //
NK027(sha)002:1127: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham sngags kyis 'bul lo //
NK027(sha)002:1129: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma bar pa 'di 'bul zhing bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1130: mtho srid pa'i rtse mo man chad nas /
NK027(sha)002:1131: na rag dmyal khams yan chad du 'gro ba rigs
NK027(sha)002:1132: drug lam rgyud lnga skye ba gnas bzhis bsdus pa'i
NK027(sha)002:1133: sems can snying rje'i mgron du gyur pa thams cad
NK027(sha)002:1137: de ltar bsngosa pas lha ltung ba'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK027(sha)002:1138: lha ma yin 'thab rtsod kyi sdug bsngal /
NK027(sha)002:1140: byol song gcig la gcig za ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK027(sha)002:1141: yi dwags bkres skom gyi sdug bsngal /
NK027(sha)002:1142: dmyal ba tsha grang gi sdug bsngal las thar nas
NK027(sha)002:1143: bde 'gro mtho ris kyi gnas su skye bar gyur
NK027(sha)002:1144: cig / gzhan yang long ba thams cad kyang gzugs mthong bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1145: 'on pa rnams sgra thos par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1146: dig pa rnams kyang smra shes par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1147: zhwa bo rnams kyang 'gro shes par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1148: gcer bu rnams gos rnyed par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1149: dbul po rnams nor rnyed par ltog pa rnams zas rnyed par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1150: 'jigs pa rnams skyabs rnyed par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1151: nad pa rnams nad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1152: sbyin pa dam pa sems kyi rgyan du gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1153: sems kyi yo byad du gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1154: don gyi mchog tu gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1155: 'di ltar mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma 'di la brten
NK027(sha)002:1156: nas bdag cag rnams gnas skabs su nad dang gnod
NK027(sha)002:1157: pa zhi zhing tshe dang bsod nams 'phel ba dang
NK027(sha)002:1158: / sems can gyi sgrib pa gnyis byang /
NK027(sha)002:1159: tshogs rnam pa gnyis rdzogs nas bla na med pa'i
NK027(sha)002:1160: byang chub rin po che myur du thob par gyur
NK027(sha)002:1161: cig / 'byung po gang dag ri rab steng gnas dang //
NK027(sha)002:1162: dga' ba'i tshal dang lha'i gnas rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1163: shar nub ri dang nyi zla'i khyim rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1164: ri bo kun la gang dag gnas pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:1165: rin chen gling nas lhag par gang gnas dang //
NK027(sha)002:1166: chu bo kun dang chu'i mdo rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1167: mtsho dang rdzing bu lding ka chu ngogs dang //
NK027(sha)002:1168: g.ya' chu sil ma can la gang gnas dang //
NK027(sha)002:1169: grong dang phyug klas grong khyer stong pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:1170: khang stong dang ni lha'i gnas rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1171: gtsug lag khang dang mchod rten gnas rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1172: dka' thub gnas dang glang chen bres rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1173: rgyal po'i dkor khang dag na gang gnas dang //
NK027(sha)002:1174: lam srang sum mdo dang ni bzhi mdo dang //
NK027(sha)002:1175: gang dag lam po che dang shing gcig drung //
NK027(sha)002:1176: dur khrod chen po nags tshal chen po dang //
NK027(sha)002:1177: seng ge dred dang gcan gzan gnas rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:1178: 'brog chen 'jigs su rung bar gang gnas dang //
NK027(sha)002:1179: gang dag gling mchog dag na gnas pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:1180: lhun po dur khrod dag la gnas pa rnams //
NK027(sha)002:1181: rab tu dgyes shing mgu bar gyur nas su //
NK027(sha)002:1182: phreng ba me tog dri dang bdug par bcas //
NK027(sha)002:1183: bstod dang gtor ma mar me gus 'bul na //
NK027(sha)002:1184: 'di dag gsol zhing legs par bzhes nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:1185: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:1186: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1187: kun kyang gnod pa rnams dang bral //
NK027(sha)002:1188: yang na dam pas gsungs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1189: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1190: lha klu gnod sbyin dri za dang //
NK027(sha)002:1192: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)002:1194: khro bo chen po'i bka' yis ni //
NK027(sha)002:1195: rang rang gnas su bde bar dengs //
NK027(sha)002:1198: gtor ma gsum pa bsang sbyangs byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK027(sha)002:1200: sarba ka ri sarba sid+d+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:1201: pad+ma ta krid badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+h+ri wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:1202: h+r+aih rgyal ba kun gyi bdag po chos kyi sku //
NK027(sha)002:1203: chos rje 'od dpag med pa rdo rje chos //
NK027(sha)002:1204: spyan ras gzigs sprul h+r+aihls rngams chen sku //
NK027(sha)002:1205: rta mgrin rta skad bzhad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:1206: dbang chen dbang 'dus dbang gi rgyal po ste //
NK027(sha)002:1207: dbang gi mdog dmar skal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NK027(sha)002:1208: dbang chen rngams brjid nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi //
NK027(sha)002:1209: dbang mdzad dbang gi lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:1210: chos nyid bdud rtsi mchog gi dbang bskur zhing //
NK027(sha)002:1211: dus gsum bstan pa bsrung mdzad dpal 'bar ba //
NK027(sha)002:1212: gdug pa'i klu rnams brjid pa'i zhabs kyis gnon //
NK027(sha)002:1213: dug chen bdud rtsi bsgyur la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:1214: rig pa'i rgyal po khro bo kun gyi rje //
NK027(sha)002:1215: byams chen rab khros khro rgyal kun gyi bskor //
NK027(sha)002:1216: stong nyid dbyings las ma g.yos mkha' dkyil nas //
NK027(sha)002:1217: 'jigs gzugs nyi zla 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:1218: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag cing cir yang ma yin pa la /
NK027(sha)002:1219: ci ltar bsam pa bzhin 'byung ba'i bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1220: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes
NK027(sha)002:1221: thugs su chud cing sems can don la dgongs pa
NK027(sha)002:1222: skad cig kyang mi g.yel ba'i bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1223: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis dgongs pa skong
NK027(sha)002:1224: zhing sems can gyi mgon skyabs mdzad par zhal gyi
NK027(sha)002:1225: bzhes pa'i bden pa'i byin rlabs dang /
NK027(sha)002:1226: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i bden pa'i byin rlabs dang /
NK027(sha)002:1227: dkon mchog gsum dang bla ma dam pa'i bka' bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:1228: gdug cing sdang ba'i sems dang ldan pa'i bgegs kyi rigs thams cad skad cig la 'dir 'dus shig /
NK027(sha)002:1229: h'u h'u b+hi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+dala phata phata /
NK027(sha)002:1230: ha la ha la h'u h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:1231: tri yam dza dzah badz+ra am gu sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h'u /
NK027(sha)002:1235: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma tha ma 'di sbyin cing
NK027(sha)002:1236: bsngo ba'i gnas ni bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod
NK027(sha)002:1237: 'khor bcas kyi tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas
NK027(sha)002:1238: da lta yan chad kyi len chags bu lon gyi
NK027(sha)002:1239: mgron du gyur pa bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu'i
NK027(sha)002:1240: tshogs la lus dang srog gi glud dang longs spyod
NK027(sha)002:1247: 'phrog pas nor dbul ba'i lan chags thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1248: bu lon thams cad khyer bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1249: 'khor rtsod thams cad byang bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1250: bgegs kyi bar chad thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1251: sngar gyi gnod pa 'phro bsdus la phyin chad mi byed par dam bca' ba bzhin khas longs shig /
NK027(sha)002:1252: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK027(sha)002:1253: dam tshig 'das nas bsregs par byed //
NK027(sha)002:1254: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK027(sha)002:1256: ci ste dam tshig 'das nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:1257: de ma thag tu dral te gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:1258: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:1259: bdun rgyud rigs ni brlag par byed //
NK027(sha)002:1260: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:1261: rdo rje chen po mchog 'dzin po //
NK027(sha)002:1262: mgon po chen po'i byin rlabs pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1263: blo ldan gang zhig 'da' ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:1264: rdo rje 'dzin pas mod la spangs //
NK027(sha)002:1265: spangs ba'i sems can chen po de //
NK027(sha)002:1266: snying rje 'khor ba'i spyod rgyun du //
NK027(sha)002:1267: ngan song gsum du yang nas yang //
NK027(sha)002:1268: shin tu mi bzad cho nges 'debs //
NK027(sha)002:1269: bdag nyid chen po sangs rgyas bka' //
NK027(sha)002:1270: tshig las 'das nas rdul phran bzhin //
NK027(sha)002:1271: nga ni dbang phyug chen po ste //
NK027(sha)002:1272: rgyal chen rigs bzhi nga yi g.yog /
NK027(sha)002:1273: lha srin sde brgyad nga yi bran //
NK027(sha)002:1274: dam tshig dag la 'da' mi bya //
NK027(sha)002:1275: de ltar khyod kyi shes gyis la //
NK027(sha)002:1276: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' ma gcog /
NK027(sha)002:1277: dam pa chos kyis gzhung ma ral //
NK027(sha)002:1278: sems can dmyal ba'i rgyu ma bsags //
NK027(sha)002:1280: sngags kyi dam tshig tshul ma gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:1281: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK027(sha)002:1283: sems can don la mnyam med byos //
NK027(sha)002:1286: zhes pas so so'i gnas su song bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:1287: de nas sngar bzhin gzhal yas khang lha dang bcas pa gsal gdab la sngar bzhin mchod la /
NK027(sha)002:1288: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab /
NK027(sha)002:1290: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK027(sha)002:1291: khyod kyi sems can don kun mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:1292: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)002:1293: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:1294: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:1295: a ham yu ti dza badz+ra muh zhes pas 'jig rten pa'i mgron rnams gshegs la /
NK027(sha)002:1296: de nas rang bzhin 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin gsol ba btab nas bzung ste /
NK027(sha)002:1297: dbang rnams rdzogs par blang ste slob ma rnams la dbang gi gleng gzhi bshad par bya ste /
NK027(sha)002:1298: de'ang rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi rgyud las /
NK027(sha)002:1299: 'dod pa'i khams kyi gnas ris 'di na /
NK027(sha)002:1300: bram ze'i slob dpon dung gi phreng ba can zhes bya ba la /
NK027(sha)002:1301: gos su dung gi phreng ba gon pa /
NK027(sha)002:1302: rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig la /
NK027(sha)002:1303: slob ma rgyal bu zhig yod de /
NK027(sha)002:1304: de la bram zes slob sbyong du byas pas /
NK027(sha)002:1305: rigs pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas par gyur la /
NK027(sha)002:1307: da ni bdag kyang shes pa mang po dang ldan /
NK027(sha)002:1308: bram zes 'di min pa gong na med pas 'di gong du mi btang snyams nas /
NK027(sha)002:1309: bram ze la rgun chang blud de brgyal ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:1311: lce lcags kyus drangs te bcad /
NK027(sha)002:1312: lus rus sbal gyi khrag gi byug ste /
NK027(sha)002:1314: sgyid pa bcad de bzhag pas /
NK027(sha)002:1315: re zhig na bram ze brgyal ba sang nas /
NK027(sha)002:1316: rtsa na su yod snyams te /
NK027(sha)002:1319: lang bar 'dod pas sgyid pa med /
NK027(sha)002:1320: bud med mang pos mnan pas dran pa nyams /
NK027(sha)002:1321: lus chu bur dang skam pos gang bar gyur pas /
NK027(sha)002:1323: 'di ci ltar yin sdug bsngal zhing nyams thag pa 'di sngon las yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:1324: gzhan gyis phrag dog gi byas pa yin brtag pas /
NK027(sha)002:1325: rgyal bus byas pa rig nas /
NK027(sha)002:1327: rgyal bu khyod la nga de tsam du drin che yang /
NK027(sha)002:1328: nga 'di lta bu byed pa khyod kyang skye ba gcig gi tshe /
NK027(sha)002:1336: nad rnam pa drug gi theb cing lus la sha za mo stong gi tshang bca' ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:1338: yan lag zha ste sdug bsngal bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1339: de nas tshe 'phos nas ngan song gsum rims par
NK027(sha)002:1340: brgyud de dmyal khams bcu drug gi kha brgyud par
NK027(sha)002:1341: skyes nas / bskal pa grangs med par 'phags pa'i 'bras bu zhal ma mthong ste /
NK027(sha)002:1342: byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skam du gyur thugs pa la /
NK027(sha)002:1343: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi thugs ka nas dpal phyag na rdo rje phyungs nas bka' mnong pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1344: khyod song la 'dod khams 'di nas sems can lus
NK027(sha)002:1345: srul po can zhes bya bar tshe snga mar slob
NK027(sha)002:1346: dpon la ngan sems byas pa'i rnam smin du myong
NK027(sha)002:1347: ba ste / de lta bu'i byang chub kyi myu
NK027(sha)002:1348: gu sngo skam la thug cing sdug bsngal la tshe
NK027(sha)002:1350: las gzhan gyi rnam smin la thar srid slob dpon
NK027(sha)002:1351: la ngan sems byas pa'i rnam smin shin tu sbyangs
NK027(sha)002:1352: dka' bas / lag na rdo rje khyod song la
NK027(sha)002:1353: cho ga zab mo'i byin rlabs mchog dbang 'di rnams
NK027(sha)002:1354: bskur la mtho ris kyi gnas su skye bar gyis
NK027(sha)002:1355: dka' bas / shig / ces bka' stsal to //
NK027(sha)002:1356: lag na rdo rje'i yi rang ste /
NK027(sha)002:1357: bcom ldan 'das la slar gsol pa /
NK027(sha)002:1358: bcom ldan 'das dbang rnams kyis rang bzhin bshad du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:1360: bcom ldan 'das kyi bka' rtsal pa /
NK027(sha)002:1361: rgyal rigs btsun par skyes pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)002:1362: rgyal srid 'bangs kyi phul bas na //
NK027(sha)002:1363: tshig btsan yul la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:1364: sa bdag rgyal po gnas pa bzhin //
NK027(sha)002:1365: bcom ldan byang chub spyod pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)002:1366: lha dang lha min 'khor bcas la //
NK027(sha)002:1367: dbang bskur rdzas kyi mnga' gsol ba //
NK027(sha)002:1368: de nas byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK027(sha)002:1369: phyag rgya gsang ba'i gnas bsrungs te //
NK027(sha)002:1370: bdud rtsi bum pas sdig rnams bkru //
NK027(sha)002:1371: phreng ba cod pan tshul khrims dang //
NK027(sha)002:1372: rnam lnga'i thur mas bag chags bsal //
NK027(sha)002:1373: me long 'khor lo dung rgya gram //
NK027(sha)002:1374: sna bdun 'khor lo'i steg btsug ste //
NK027(sha)002:1375: ral gri shes rab mda' gzhu dang //
NK027(sha)002:1376: seng ge nyi zla lta bu dang //
NK027(sha)002:1377: 'bras bu bkra shis rdzas brgyad sbyin //
NK027(sha)002:1378: bden pa'i bka' brjod bden brdar dang //
NK027(sha)002:1379: ting 'dzin tshangs pa'i glu dbyangs dang //
NK027(sha)002:1380: rten 'brel rdzas rnams bsham nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:1381: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:1383: de nas lag na rdo rjes rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par bzhugs nas /
NK027(sha)002:1384: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung
NK027(sha)002:1385: dang thugs rdo rje rnam par dag pa'i phyag rgya
NK027(sha)002:1386: bcing ste sems can lus srul po can gyi gnas
NK027(sha)002:1387: lngar bkod pas / sha za ma stong gi gnas kyang byer ro //
NK027(sha)002:1388: de nas 'du 'bral med par gsang ba'i dbang gi
NK027(sha)002:1389: byang chub myu gu sngo skam du gyur pa la
NK027(sha)002:1391: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can du byin gyis brlabs so //
NK027(sha)002:1392: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis thugs rje'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1393: bdud rtsi bum pas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1394: lus mi bde ba rnams bkrus nas dag par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:1395: me tog phreng bas dbang bskur bas tshul khrims kyi
NK027(sha)002:1396: phreng ba zhig ral yongs su rdzogs nas ngan song
NK027(sha)002:1397: nas yongs su bzlog pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK027(sha)002:1398: to // cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas khams gsum
NK027(sha)002:1399: na gnas pa'i sbyor ba ngan pa'i bag chags rnams
NK027(sha)002:1401: de nas gser gyi thur mas dbang bskur bas ma
NK027(sha)002:1402: rig pa'i ling thog gi 'thib po phyung nas gsal
NK027(sha)002:1403: bar gyur to // me long gi chos rnams gzugs brnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma lta bur mthong /
NK027(sha)002:1404: gser gyi 'khor los rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi
NK027(sha)002:1405: dang ldan nas khams gsum du 'gro nus par gyur
NK027(sha)002:1406: to // dung gi tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:1407: rgya gram gyi phyogs bcu na sngags 'chang rnams rtag tu bsrung bar gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:1408: de nas rin chen sna tshogs mkha' la rgyud mar phyung ste /
NK027(sha)002:1415: glang po rnams kyi dbang bskur bas phyir mi ldog
NK027(sha)002:1416: pa'i 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po sprin dpung zhes
NK027(sha)002:1418: de la ye shes kyi ral gri dang /
NK027(sha)002:1419: thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i mda' gzhu dang /
NK027(sha)002:1420: brjid pa seng ge myur ba gzugs brnyan rnams kyi
NK027(sha)002:1421: dbang bskur bas skad cig ma la sangs rgyas te
NK027(sha)002:1422: bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang mo zhes bya bar
NK027(sha)002:1423: gyur to // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi legs shes bstod nas /
NK027(sha)002:1424: nyi ma dang zla ba phyag tu phul ma thag
NK027(sha)002:1425: tu nyi mas skye 'gro ma lus pa'i sems can
NK027(sha)002:1426: gyi rgyud la ye shes kyi 'od zer chen po
NK027(sha)002:1427: dus mtha' med par shar nas dro zhing 'jom par
NK027(sha)002:1428: gyur to // zla bas ni stong gsum gyis mun
NK027(sha)002:1429: pa thams cad dus gcig tu bsal nas rnam pa
NK027(sha)002:1430: thams cad du bsil zhing snang bar gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:1431: de nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi go 'phang chen po rdzogs par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:1432: thams cad nas thams cad du bkra shis shing 'grub pa'i rdzas su gsungs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1437: gang zag dad pa bsal zhing rig pa'i glang po dang /
NK027(sha)002:1438: mkhyen pa'i dpal la sogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1439: sbyin pa'i gnas su skyed pa'i phyir bkra shis kyi mnga' gsol nas /
NK027(sha)002:1440: gzhan la phan pa'i don du tshigs su bcad de bstod pa /
NK027(sha)002:1441: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa che //
NK027(sha)002:1442: bdag ni gtan du ma btang zhig /
NK027(sha)002:1443: yungs kar dngos grub rdzas kyi ni //
NK027(sha)002:1444: bgegs kyi sbyor ba rnam 'joms zhing //
NK027(sha)002:1445: zho'i rnam par rgyas byed ting 'dzin bcud kyi 'tsho ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:1446: dur bas dge ba'i rtsa ba dpag med tshogs ldan zhing /
NK027(sha)002:1447: li khris lha mo mang po dbang du bsdus par byed par shog /
NK027(sha)002:1448: me long gi chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bur rtogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1449: dung gi 'jig rten gsum du chos kyi grags pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1450: g+hi wang gi nad dug gsum zhi byed tshe srog mang po 'tsho ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:1451: bil bas mtshungs med bla med byang chub snying po thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:1452: ces brjod de bkra shis rdzas brgyad mnga' gsol nas /
NK027(sha)002:1453: so so'i yon tan ci skad gsung pa bzhin bkra shis par gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:1454: de lta bas na gzhan gyi sdig pa mtshams med pa lnga dang /
NK027(sha)002:1456: logs pa brgyad la sogs pa rnams dag pa lta ci smos /
NK027(sha)002:1457: bla ma la brnyas pa byas pa'i rnam smin yang
NK027(sha)002:1458: dbang bskur bas phrin las khyad par can gyi dag
NK027(sha)002:1459: par gyur pa ni khyad par rmad du byung ba'i
NK027(sha)002:1460: phrin las te don chen po dang ldan par thugs
NK027(sha)002:1461: la dgongs te spro ba chen po mdzod cig /
NK027(sha)002:1462: de dag ni dbang gi gling bzhi bshad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:1463: de nas dbang de dag bskur yang mi chags pa'i gag brgyad bshad par byas te /
NK027(sha)002:1465: dper na chu rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa la /
NK027(sha)002:1466: glo bur du snyog ma byung na mi gsal bas /
NK027(sha)002:1467: 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' rang bzhin gyi rnam
NK027(sha)002:1468: par dag kyang glo bur sprin dang khu rlangs rnams
NK027(sha)002:1469: kyis sgrib nas mi gsal ba bzhin /
NK027(sha)002:1470: chos nyid kyi rang bzhin rnam par dag kyi gsal yang /
NK027(sha)002:1471: glo bur gyi rnam rtog gam bag chags kyi sgrib pa ni 'di ltar te /
NK027(sha)002:1472: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub dang //
NK027(sha)002:1473: byin rlabs dbang chog 'byung ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:1474: dper na rgyal mtsho dwangs pa la //
NK027(sha)002:1475: nyi zla gza' skar 'byung ba yang //
NK027(sha)002:1476: snyog ma chu yi gar 'gyur bzhin //
NK027(sha)002:1477: byin rlabs dbang mchog 'byung ba'i gag /
NK027(sha)002:1478: rnam pa brgyad du 'byung bar bshad //
NK027(sha)002:1480: sngon 'byung ston pa slob dpon la /
NK027(sha)002:1481: bka' gcog brnyas pa byed pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:1482: dbang dang dngos grub dam pa'i gag /
NK027(sha)002:1484: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku /
NK027(sha)002:1485: dngos grub 'byung ba'i rtsa ba lags pas /
NK027(sha)002:1486: bka' la brnyas pa spang bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1487: bla med rdo rje 'gro ba'i spun 'khu ldog gdung ba'i sems med na /
NK027(sha)002:1488: dbang dang dngos grub gag gnyis pa /
NK027(sha)002:1489: zhes pas mched grogs la gdung sems cher bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1490: byang chub lam la 'dud med cing //
NK027(sha)002:1491: thar par 'dren pa'i lha spangs pa //
NK027(sha)002:1492: dngos grub 'byung pa'i gag gsum pa //
NK027(sha)002:1493: zhes pas don dam byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK027(sha)002:1494: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems ma spangs shig /
NK027(sha)002:1495: snying rje'i yul gyur sems can la //
NK027(sha)002:1496: thag pa bcad pa gag bzhi pa /
NK027(sha)002:1497: zhes sems can blos mi gtong bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1498: gsang sngags pa'i longs spyod rnams /
NK027(sha)002:1499: yangs la byin pa lnga pa'i gag /
NK027(sha)002:1500: ces pas snod ma smin pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1501: chos kyi ma smin pa'i gag ni snod du mi
NK027(sha)002:1502: rung bas zab mo gsang sngags kyi don ma ston
NK027(sha)002:1503: cig pa'o // thar lam ston pa 'dud med cing //
NK027(sha)002:1504: ser snas bcing ba drug pa'i gag /
NK027(sha)002:1505: ces pas dbang bskur ba'i bla ma la mos gus med pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1506: phyag rten la ser sna ma byed cig /
NK027(sha)002:1507: gzu lum dbang med las la spyod //
NK027(sha)002:1508: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gag bdun pa /
NK027(sha)002:1509: zhes pas bla ma la bka' lung ma thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:1510: gzhan la bstan pa la sogs gzu lum ras chod ma byed cig /
NK027(sha)002:1511: 'dod pa khe drag lhur len zhing //
NK027(sha)002:1512: gsal ba'i dam tshig spangs pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:1513: 'di ni brgyad pa'i gags su bstan /
NK027(sha)002:1514: ces pas 'dod pas khe drag lhur mi len pa
NK027(sha)002:1515: sngags kyi dam tshig gi rin po che dang 'dra
NK027(sha)002:1517: nyams pa 'di dag sus spangs pa //
NK027(sha)002:1518: dngos grub dbang gi snod du bshad //
NK027(sha)002:1519: 'di ltar khyod kyi rab brtan na //
NK027(sha)002:1520: bu khyod nang par 'dri byed na //
NK027(sha)002:1521: dkyil 'khor drung du legs par nyol //
NK027(sha)002:1522: ces pas gag brgyad po de shes par byas la /
NK027(sha)002:1523: nyes pa de dag las bzlog par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1524: de nas rang nyid gsang bdag gi nga rgyal dang
NK027(sha)002:1525: ldan pas bgegs gtor slob ma rnams la bskor te
NK027(sha)002:1526: btang / las bum chus khrus bya /
NK027(sha)002:1529: dad po gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1531: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK027(sha)002:1532: brtse bar dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK027(sha)002:1533: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK027(sha)002:1534: de ring rab tu stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:1535: zhes pas gsol ba lan gsum gdab /
NK027(sha)002:1536: de nas bla ma'i rjes su thams cad kyi mgrin gcig tu /
NK027(sha)002:1538: khams gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK027(sha)002:1539: bu bzhin skyob pa'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)002:1540: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin sku //
NK027(sha)002:1541: bla med mgon la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:1542: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
NK027(sha)002:1545: rdo rje bsnam la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:1546: las kyis gnod sbyin chen po ni //
NK027(sha)002:1547: 'jigs su rung ba'i cha byad can //
NK027(sha)002:1548: thams cad ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:1550: ston pa bla med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:1551: skyobs pa bla med 'dren pa bla med bla med dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:1552: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK027(sha)002:1553: dus gsum kun tu bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:1554: mchog gsum bstan pa'i zhing gyur pa //
NK027(sha)002:1555: gnyis med yid kyi skyabs su mchi //
NK027(sha)002:1556: dngos 'byor yid kyi rnam sprul ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:1557: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:1558: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK027(sha)002:1559: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK027(sha)002:1560: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK027(sha)002:1561: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK027(sha)002:1562: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK027(sha)002:1563: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sems bskyed do //
NK027(sha)002:1564: bde gshegs byang chub sems bskyed la //
NK027(sha)002:1565: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK027(sha)002:1566: tshe rabs bgrang ba'i las rnams kun //
NK027(sha)002:1567: bsdus te byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
NK027(sha)002:1568: zhes pas yan lag brgyad pa byas la /
NK027(sha)002:1569: smon pa sems bskyed pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1570: phyogs dus kun nas brtse bar bzhugs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1571: bla ma dkon mchog ma lus dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:1572: sangs rgyas chos dang byang chub bdag gi /
NK027(sha)002:1573: 'gro la phan phyir zhes brjod la 'jug pa sems bskyed pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1574: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK027(sha)002:1575: yang dag byang chub bskyed mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:1576: de bzhin bla ma byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)002:1577: dam pa bdag gi bskyed par bgyi //
NK027(sha)002:1579: de nas skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:1580: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum la skyabs su mchi //
NK027(sha)002:1581: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum la chos sku
NK027(sha)002:1582: longs sku sprul sku rang sems stong gsal chos kyi
NK027(sha)002:1583: sku la bla ma sangs rgyas rin po che la
NK027(sha)002:1584: zhes phyi nang gsang ba'i de kho na nyid bzhi'i
NK027(sha)002:1585: skyabs 'gro bya'o // da ni kun dril nas /
NK027(sha)002:1586: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK027(sha)002:1587: byang chub snying po mchis kyi bar //
NK027(sha)002:1588: dkon mchog gsum dang yi dam lha //
NK027(sha)002:1589: bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK027(sha)002:1590: dbang bskur dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:1594: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na'i skyabs su 'gro bas rgyud dag par byas nas /
NK027(sha)002:1595: mchod dbang bcu drug bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:1596: thog mar ngan song gnas 'dren gyi phyag na rdo
NK027(sha)002:1597: rje g.yon sdig mdzub bsgreng ba'i sku de bla mas
NK027(sha)002:1598: sgom zhing slob ma'i mgor bzhag la /
NK027(sha)002:1599: de yang dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK027(sha)002:1600: ngan song gsum dang rigs drug bag chags dag par byas te /
NK027(sha)002:1601: bu dmyal ba'i yi ge du bsgoms /
NK027(sha)002:1603: na ra ka b+hu d+ha tsak+shu pra we sha a +aah thal mo bsdams pa dral /
NK027(sha)002:1606: phyag rdor la dad pas gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1607: kyee ma kye hud gang nas byon //
NK027(sha)002:1608: mgon po thugs rjes bdag skyongs shig /
NK027(sha)002:1609: dbang mchog rgyal po'i bsgral du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:1610: slad nas mi 'chab mi bgyid do //
