NK027(sha)002:1612: bla mas lag tu rdo rje gtad /
NK027(sha)002:1613: rigs kyi bu khyod 'dir shog cig /
NK027(sha)002:1614: rang gi nyams dang zlas nyams pas //
NK027(sha)002:1615: na rag dmyal ba'i ltung ba la //
NK027(sha)002:1616: skyabs phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)002:1617: zhes rdo rjes gral drang ste /
NK027(sha)002:1619: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka ga te he dun h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:1621: ram yam kham +aah zhes pas me rlung chus sbyangs nas stong pa nyid du dag /
NK027(sha)002:1623: rigs kyi bu 'di'i rgyu nyon mongs pa zhe sdang
NK027(sha)002:1624: dang rkyen srog gcod pa la sogs kyi dmyal bar
NK027(sha)002:1625: skye ba'i sa bon bag chags thams cad skad cig
NK027(sha)002:1627: slar gang nas kyang mi ldang bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1628: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre da ka ga te he dun h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:1631: rigs kyi bu 'di'i rgyu 'dod chags dang rkyen ma
NK027(sha)002:1632: byin par len pa sogs kyi yi dwags su skyes
NK027(sha)002:1633: pa'i sa bon bag chags thams cad byang gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:1634: / ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ka ga te hi dun h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:1636: rigs kyi bu 'di'i rgyu gti mug dang /
NK027(sha)002:1637: rkyen log lta la sogs kyi dud 'gror skye ba'i
NK027(sha)002:1638: sa bon bag chags la sogs skad cig la byang
NK027(sha)002:1640: de dag gi zhar la nga rgyal phrag dog ser sna rdzun tshig sogs kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1641: sgrib pa sbyang ba'i spyi gcod du /
NK027(sha)002:1642: na mo b+ha ga wa ti sarba dur ka ti tshang par brjod /
NK027(sha)002:1643: nang sems mi 'khrugs shing spyir zhing khams rnam par dag par skye ba'i phyir /
NK027(sha)002:1644: na mo rat+na tra ya ya kam ka ni tshang bar brjod /
NK027(sha)002:1645: ces pas ngan song gnas 'dren no //
NK027(sha)002:1646: de nas dbu rgyan thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1647: de nas lag pa rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge
NK027(sha)002:1648: 'dzin la bzhugs nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK027(sha)002:1649: kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcing ste
NK027(sha)002:1650: gnas lngar gtug pas sha za ma stong gi tshogs
NK027(sha)002:1651: bskrad cing byer ba de bzhin du dbang bskur te
NK027(sha)002:1658: a mi d+he wa h+r+aih r+aa ga ra ti h+r+aih
NK027(sha)002:1659: a mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aah ta ra ta ri +aah
NK027(sha)002:1660: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan 'di //
NK027(sha)002:1661: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun 'dus pa //
NK027(sha)002:1662: gzi brjid rigs sngags rgyal ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:1663: bu khyod gtsug na nor bu 'bar //
NK027(sha)002:1664: rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1665: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlab ste /
NK027(sha)002:1666: rigs kyi bu la dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas
NK027(sha)002:1667: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang dam pa thob
NK027(sha)002:1668: par gyur cig / de nas gsal ba'i rten /
NK027(sha)002:1670: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK027(sha)002:1671: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:1672: gsang ba gsang chen yang gsang ni //
NK027(sha)002:1673: bdag por khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:1674: b+hud+d+ha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1675: phyogs bcu'i dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs te /
NK027(sha)002:1676: rigs kyi bu la gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1677: byang chub kyi myu gu skam pa sos nas /
NK027(sha)002:1678: byang chub kyi snying po can du gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:1679: gsang ba'i bdag pos dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1682: de nas bum pa thogs la /
NK027(sha)002:1683: rin chen sna tshogs rgyu las byung //
NK027(sha)002:1684: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1685: shes rab yum gyi bum pa 'dis //
NK027(sha)002:1686: 'gro don mchog gi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:1687: b+hud+d+ha ka la a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK027(sha)002:1689: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1690: rigs kyi bu la bum pas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1691: nad rnams byang zhing dag nas /
NK027(sha)002:1692: rang sems spros pa dang bral te ye shes rnam
NK027(sha)002:1693: pa lnga dang ldan nas 'gro ba'i don chu bo'i
NK027(sha)002:1694: rgyun bzhin du byed pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:1695: / me tog phreng ba thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1696: byang chub yan lag me tog 'thor //
NK027(sha)002:1697: khams gsum btsun pa'i bdag po ste //
NK027(sha)002:1698: bder gshegs mchod pa thob pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:1699: 'gro don byed par dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:1700: rat+na ma le tram tra a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1701: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin bshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:1702: cad kyi rigs kyi bu la me tog thod kyi
NK027(sha)002:1703: dbang bskur bas / tshul khrims yongs su rdzogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1704: sgrib gnyis byang ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1706: ye shes bdag nyid cod pan 'di //
NK027(sha)002:1707: klu gdug gnod pas mi rdzi zhing //
NK027(sha)002:1708: 'khor ba'i nyes pas mi gos pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1709: rgyan mchog dam pas dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:1710: badz+ra sa t+wa a b+hi h'u +aah mam sa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1711: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK027(sha)002:1712: rigs kyi bu la cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1713: mya ngan las 'das kyang khams gsum du gnas nas srid pa gsum gyi sdug bsngal thams cad kyis /
NK027(sha)002:1714: rigs kyi bu la cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1715: mya ngan las 'das kyang khams gsum du gnas nas
NK027(sha)002:1716: srid pa gsum gyi sdug bsngal thams cad bral bar
NK027(sha)002:1717: gyur cig / thur ma thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1718: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yi //
NK027(sha)002:1719: mig gi ling thog bsal ba ltar //
NK027(sha)002:1720: bu khyod kyi ni mi shes pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1721: ling thog rgyal ba rnams kyi bsal //
NK027(sha)002:1722: tsak+shu tsak+shu dz+ny+aa na tsak+shu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1724: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1725: rigs kyi bu la thur ma rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1726: ma rig pa'i ling thog bsal te spyan lnga dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1728: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK027(sha)002:1729: rten 'brel mthu la snang ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:1730: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:1731: don dam chos nyid brjod par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:1732: badz+ra +aa dar+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:1734: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK027(sha)002:1735: rigs kyi bu la me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1736: chos rnams gzugs brnyan ltar du rten 'brel sgyu mar mthong ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1739: brjod pa'i don du 'bru bkod nas //
NK027(sha)002:1740: gzhan don 'di la phan bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:1741: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:1742: tsakra rat+na b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1743: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1744: rigs kyi bu la 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1745: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan pas khams gsum
NK027(sha)002:1746: kun tu bsgrod cing 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po
NK027(sha)002:1749: chos dung rgyas pa bos nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:1750: 'jigs rten sems can skal can la //
NK027(sha)002:1751: gnyid bsal sdig sbyangs chos thob pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1752: skyobs pa mgon po'i tshangs skad sgrogs //
NK027(sha)002:1753: b+h+ra ma w+aak+ka a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1754: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:1755: cad kyi rigs kyi bu la dung gi dbang bskur
NK027(sha)002:1756: bas / chos ston pa la tshangs pa'i sgra skad
NK027(sha)002:1757: phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK027(sha)002:1758: bas / cig / rdo rje rgya gram thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1759: rdo rje 'di ni sna tshogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1760: las rnams rgya mtsho dbang bskur gyi //
NK027(sha)002:1761: de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyi //
NK027(sha)002:1763: bi shwa badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1764: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1765: rigs kyi bu la rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1766: phyogs bcu dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i rigs sngags 'chang
NK027(sha)002:1767: grub pa rnams kyi rtag tu bsrung ba'i dbang dam
NK027(sha)002:1769: rgyal srid sna bdun thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1770: bsod nams dpal la legs grub pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1771: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun 'di //
NK027(sha)002:1773: phyogs bcur dge bcu bskor bar gyis //
NK027(sha)002:1774: 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas sangs rgyas kyis sa la nges par lung bstan pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1775: btsun mos dbang bskur bas gzung dang ting nge 'dzin gyi nges pa'i don dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1776: dmag dpon gyi dbang bskur bas phas kyi rgol ba zil gyis gnon par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1777: blon po'i dbang bskur bas blo dang brtson 'grus su ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1778: rta mchog gi dbang bskur bas mi gnas pa'i dbyings su thogs med du bgrod nus par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1779: glang po'i dbang bskur bas rigs drug thar pa'i gnas su 'dren nus par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1780: nor bu'i dbang bskur bas bsam pa yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i yon tan thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1789: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:1790: cad kyi rigs kyi bu la rin chen sna bdun
NK027(sha)002:1792: phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dbang phyug dam pa thob pa gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1794: lag tu byin pas dug gsum gyi 'khrul pa rgyun bcad de /
NK027(sha)002:1795: bag chags thams cad rtsa ba nas dag par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1797: mda' gzhu lag tu byin pas /
NK027(sha)002:1798: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel bas ye shes dag pa'i rtse mor gnas par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1800: brjid pa'i seng ge shin tu myur ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:1801: gzugs can mchog de lag tu byin pa yis //
NK027(sha)002:1802: gsung rab rgya mtsho kun gyi sgra sgrogs te //
NK027(sha)002:1803: log pa'i phyogs kun zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)002:1804: badz+ra sing ha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK027(sha)002:1805: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1806: rigs kyi bu la brjid pa seng ge'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1807: gsung rab rgya mtsho'i sgra sgrogs pas logs pa'i phyogs zil gyi gnon pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1809: steng phyogs mnga' mdzad thugs rje nyi ma brdal //
NK027(sha)002:1810: brtse ba'i mun sel thugs rje zla ba'i 'od //
NK027(sha)002:1811: stong gsum mun pa dus gcig bsal nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:1812: 'jig rten kun tu snang ba bskyed par shog /
NK027(sha)002:1813: sur+ya tsan dra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:1815: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:1816: rigs kyi bu la nyi zlas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:1817: skye 'gro ma lus pa'i sems can gyi rgyud la ye shes kyi 'od shar nas /
NK027(sha)002:1818: khams gsum gyi mun pa thams cad skad cig la
NK027(sha)002:1819: sel nus pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:1820: / bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:1821: gsang bdag bstan pa rgyas pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:1822: yun ring gnas par gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1823: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK027(sha)002:1824: gsang ba rab tu sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)002:1825: yungs dkar rdo rjes bgegs tshogs 'dul //
NK027(sha)002:1826: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu bo che //
NK027(sha)002:1827: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:1828: byin rlabs mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:1829: zho ni kun gyi snying po gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1830: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs te //
NK027(sha)002:1831: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1832: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:1833: dur was tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:1834: 'chi med rdo rje tshe ni rab grub pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1835: sdug bsngal skye 'chi'i rtsa ba rgyun bcad de //
NK027(sha)002:1836: bkra shis des kyang tshe ni brtan gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1837: li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK027(sha)002:1838: chos rnams ma lus dbang du gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1839: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur te //
NK027(sha)002:1840: bkra shis des kyang rgyal srid brtan gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1841: dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:1842: yon tan rgya mtsho'i mchog tu bdag gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:1843: rnam dag chos la thog med longs spyod pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1844: bkra shis des kyang tshig gi dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:1845: g+hi wang dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman //
NK027(sha)002:1846: sman mchog des kyang chos nyid rab rtogs te //
NK027(sha)002:1847: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1848: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK027(sha)002:1849: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK027(sha)002:1850: ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du bdag gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:1851: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:1852: bkra shis des kyang don gyi dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:1853: bil wa rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK027(sha)002:1854: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK027(sha)002:1855: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:1856: bkra shis des ni 'gro bas thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:1857: ces pas mchog dbang bcu drug rdzogs par bskur ba'i rjes su bum chus kyang bkru 'thung ngo //
NK027(sha)002:1858: de nas lam khyer bzhi las /
NK027(sha)002:1859: theg pa chen po'i skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya /
NK027(sha)002:1860: dbang gi dam tshig gag brgyad bsrung ba /
NK027(sha)002:1861: mchog dbang bcu drug lha gsang ba'i bdag po /
NK027(sha)002:1862: snying po n+ai lam b+ha ra bazla'o //
NK027(sha)002:1863: de nas mchod pa gso ste /
NK027(sha)002:1865: d+hu pe d+ai pam g+han+d+he nee we te /
NK027(sha)002:1867: puts+tsha me ga sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:1870: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)002:1871: byin gyis brlabs shing dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:1872: gsang bdag 'phags pa gos sngon can //
NK027(sha)002:1877: lhag mas 'byung po tshim par byed //
NK027(sha)002:1878: yo byad lhag ma bsags na'ang de'i nyin mo 'dzom par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1879: de yan chad kyi sngon 'gro'i cho ga'o //
NK027(sha)002:1880: de nas dngos gzhi'i cho ga mdo yongs rdzogs dang /
NK027(sha)002:1882: dang po yan lag gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK027(sha)002:1884: de yang dbang gi chu bo bzhi las /
NK027(sha)002:1885: yo ga la sogs theg drug las //
NK027(sha)002:1886: phyi rgyud dbang gi chu bo bya //
NK027(sha)002:1888: thog mar yan lag gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1895: de la dang po lha mi'i theg pa'i sgrub khrigs las /
NK027(sha)002:1896: dal bshams khung dang mchod pa bshams //
NK027(sha)002:1897: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK027(sha)002:1898: dpang skong khrus byas sdom rten khri //
NK027(sha)002:1899: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzegs thub pa bsgom //
NK027(sha)002:1900: gsol btab sdom pa dus khrims dpog /
NK027(sha)002:1901: rin chen ldan pa'i bum pa la //
NK027(sha)002:1902: bdag 'jug rin chen chos bshad dang //
NK027(sha)002:1903: ka smad lha dbang lam khyer bzhi //
NK027(sha)002:1904: theg pa lha snying bslab bya la'ang //
NK027(sha)002:1905: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //
NK027(sha)002:1907: gdams ngag ngang bsgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK027(sha)002:1909: dang po dal bshams pa la dgongs pa gsum /
NK027(sha)002:1912: dang po cho ga 'jug pa nas bla ma yi dam chos skyongs gzhi bdag la mchod gtor bsham /
NK027(sha)002:1914: khyad par e yam ram kham zhes nam mkha' rlung
NK027(sha)002:1915: me chu rnams mas brtsegs su chags pa'i chu'i dal
NK027(sha)002:1917: gnyis pa ni tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa la /
NK027(sha)002:1918: rta babs la lha mi'i theg pa bsgom pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:1919: gsung pa lha mi'i dkyil 'khor sgos su bri ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:1920: ri rgyal phyogs mdog ri bdun ser /
NK027(sha)002:1923: phyi'i rgya mtsho gling bcu gnyis la shar zlum po dkar /
NK027(sha)002:1927: phyi lcags ril gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgya'i thig dgod do //
NK027(sha)002:1928: gnyis pa ni rkang stong las /
NK027(sha)002:1929: theg pa'i dang po bcu drug mgon /
NK027(sha)002:1932: 'khor ba dang ngan song las skyob pa'i sta gon du bstan no //
NK027(sha)002:1933: gsum pa mchod pa bsham pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1934: tsha tsh+wa dkar zhal ston pa'i ming grangs sam /
NK027(sha)002:1935: so so'i lo grangs dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor du bzhugs /
NK027(sha)002:1936: bsnyen sngags kyi rab gnas bya /
NK027(sha)002:1938: bum pa rin po che sman 'bru sna dri bzang
NK027(sha)002:1939: dang lha khrus me long la gnas pa'i chu blugs
NK027(sha)002:1940: / kha rgyan mgul ching gzung thag dang bcas pa'i mchu bla ma la bstan pa bzhag la /
NK027(sha)002:1941: gtso bo lha lnga'i snying po brgya rtsa bzlas la pho brang du dgod /
NK027(sha)002:1942: mi 'khrugs dal pad+ma 'dab brgyad dbus sngo /
NK027(sha)002:1945: dus bzang gi dal gsum 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog /
NK027(sha)002:1946: dbus ser po dmar po sngon po bya /
NK027(sha)002:1948: dus gsum sangs rgyas dkon mchog gsum gyi dal pad+ma brgya ldan dbus ser /
NK027(sha)002:1949: 'dab ma sna tshogs pa gcig ste lnga /
NK027(sha)002:1950: de rnams sgo rta babs yod med gang mos bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1957: gtor ma gsum dang man+dala yang bsham mo //
NK027(sha)002:1958: bzhi pa rab gnas ni rten 'brel rab gnas bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1959: lnga pa ni thar pa chen po phyogs su rgyas pa pa'am /
NK027(sha)002:1960: rtog pa chen po dpang kong phyag rgya pa'i cho gas gzhung bsrang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:1961: drug pa khrus ni bum pa'i chus thams cad khrus byas la gos gsar pa gon par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1962: bdun pa brgyad pa bsdam rten la gsum ste /
NK027(sha)002:1963: mdo dbang thos pa'i shes rab la dbang bskur byed /
NK027(sha)002:1964: dus gzhug bsam pa'i shes rab la bshad par byed pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:1965: bsgom pa'i shes rab la khrid du byed pa dang gsum las /
NK027(sha)002:1966: dbang bskur mjug chog dang bcas pa tsakli yin /
NK027(sha)002:1968: skabs 'dir phyag rten gang yod ngan song las nges par 'byung ba'i blos 'bul lo //
NK027(sha)002:1969: dgu pa khri ni bla ma 'jig rten skyongs ba de /
NK027(sha)002:1970: sems can la brtse bas zhing khams la dbang bskur ba'i phyir slob mas rtsig go //
NK027(sha)002:1971: bcu pa rgyan ni zhing khams la dbang mdzad pa
NK027(sha)002:1972: de mnga' gsol ba'i phyir rgyan mdzes shing brjid par
NK027(sha)002:1973: bya'o // bcu gcig pa khrir 'dzeg pa ni lhas gnang bar bsam la /
NK027(sha)002:1974: lus dkyil krung tshugs thub par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:1975: bcu gnyis pa thub pa bsgom pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1976: dge bcu 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po'i khrims yin /
NK027(sha)002:1977: de'ang bstan pa dang lha'i gtso bo ston pa sangs rgyas yin /
NK027(sha)002:1978: de la lha mi'i 'khor bzhi yod pas de bsgom na bsnyen gnas 'bog pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:1979: bcu gsum pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1980: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK027(sha)002:1981: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnam sbyangs pa //
NK027(sha)002:1982: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen mchog /
NK027(sha)002:1983: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin stsol //
NK027(sha)002:1984: zhes me tog dang bcas pas thal mo sbyar te
NK027(sha)002:1985: mtho ris kyi legs smon dang ngan 'gro'i nges 'byung
NK027(sha)002:1986: gi blos bya'o // bcu bzhi pa sdom pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:1988: sdom pa'i tshul khrims ci srid 'tsho'i bar du bsrung ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:1989: bac+wo lnga pa dus khrims ni /
NK027(sha)002:1991: de yang sku gsung thugs kyi rten bshams /
NK027(sha)002:1992: mchod pa bshams la phyag 'tshal la tsog pur 'dug
NK027(sha)002:1993: la ngan song las thar pa'i phyir ci srid 'tsho'i
NK027(sha)002:1994: bar du lha mi'i theg par 'jug snyam du song
NK027(sha)002:1995: la / bla mas sdom pa kun la yod mod kyi //
NK027(sha)002:1996: skyabs su ma song ba med /
NK027(sha)002:1997: ces pa dang sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun ni //
NK027(sha)002:1998: thar pa 'dod pa rnams kyis skyabs //
NK027(sha)002:2001: mi'i chos lugs legs spyod na //
NK027(sha)002:2002: lha yul bsgrod pa thag mi ring //
NK027(sha)002:2003: lha dang mi'i them skas la //
NK027(sha)002:2006: sdom pa thob 'dod kyi blo dang ldan par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2007: bcu drug pa sdom pa 'bog pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:2008: sngar chos 'brel med na btsun pa zhes brjod /
NK027(sha)002:2010: slob dpon gyi bzung du gsol bya /
NK027(sha)002:2016: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:2017: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:2020: dge 'dun la bdag ci srid 'tsho'i bar du lha
NK027(sha)002:2021: mi'i theg pa la gnas par slob dpon gyis bzung
NK027(sha)002:2022: du gsol / zhes lan gsum bya /
NK027(sha)002:2023: slob dpon gyi thabs yin no //
NK027(sha)002:2027: de nas bslab pa brjod pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:2029: ci ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyi /
NK027(sha)002:2030: lha mi'i theg pa la zhugs te /
NK027(sha)002:2031: ci srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2032: ma byin pa len pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2033: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2040: log par lta ba la sogs pa mi dge ba bcu spangs /
NK027(sha)002:2041: mi dge ba bcu las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK027(sha)002:2042: sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyis rjes
NK027(sha)002:2043: su slob pa'i lha mi'i theg pa bzang po la
NK027(sha)002:2049: yang na dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spang byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:2050: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK027(sha)002:2051: tshad med bzhi spyod lha mi bsgom byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:2052: tshangs pa'i gnas sogs rim par skye ba'i rgyu //
NK027(sha)002:2056: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa drang srong chen po de dag gi lha mi'i theg par zhugs te /
NK027(sha)002:2057: bsam gtan dang snyoms 'jug gi sems bsgrubs te /
NK027(sha)002:2058: bsam gtan dang mngon par shes pa brnyes pa de bzhin du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK027(sha)002:2060: snying rje dang dga' ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2061: btang snyoms tshad med pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2062: bsam gtan gyi sems rtog dpyod bral ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2063: snyoms 'jug mi g.yon ba la gnas te /
NK027(sha)002:2064: bsam gtan dang mngon par shes pa thob par bagyi'o //
NK027(sha)002:2065: ci ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa drang srong chen po rnams kyi rjes su slob bo //
NK027(sha)002:2071: gcig dang brgyad dang bac+wo lnga la /
NK027(sha)002:2072: bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad bsrung na //
NK027(sha)002:2075: gnam stong gi gso sbyong mi thub pa na /
NK027(sha)002:2076: tshes gcig la yang rung ste /
NK027(sha)002:2078: nya nas gnam stong gi bar la /
NK027(sha)002:2079: tshes gang yang rung ba gcig chad na'ang gnam stong gi ngo bo de nyid yin no //
NK027(sha)002:2083: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas zla ba zung ngo
NK027(sha)002:2084: cog gi nya dang gnam stong tshes brgyad la ci
NK027(sha)002:2085: srid 'tsho'i bar du bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad par
NK027(sha)002:2086: slob dpon gyi bsrung du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:2087: ci ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa chen
NK027(sha)002:2088: po rnams kyis zla zung gi nya dang tshes brgyad
NK027(sha)002:2089: gnam stong la srog gcod pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2090: ma byin pa len pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2091: mi tshangs bar spyod pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2094: bcos pa'i chang myos par gyur pa'i gnas dang /
NK027(sha)002:2098: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2100: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas spang ste /
NK027(sha)002:2101: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas las slar log pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:2102: yan lag brgyad pa 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi bslab pa la /
NK027(sha)002:2106: yang na yan lag bcu pa la khri sta mthon po dang /
NK027(sha)002:2108: rtsa ba yan lag kyang gang thub pa srung zhing blang du rung ba la /
NK027(sha)002:2109: dus kyang nya stong brgyad gsum ka re re'ang rung ngo //
NK027(sha)002:2110: de la nyams pa na gzhi nas bskyar /
NK027(sha)002:2111: yan lag nyams na bshags pas dag go //
NK027(sha)002:2112: sbyor dngos rjes dang rnam pa bzhi las /
NK027(sha)002:2113: rjes ma tshangs na nyes pa smad pa ces bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2114: bcu bdun pa rin chen ldan pa'i bum pa ni
NK027(sha)002:2115: rgyal rigs ma nyams pa la gser dngul gyi bum
NK027(sha)002:2116: pa / nyams nas ma 'byed na rdza bum du rin po che bcug la bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2118: slar dbang thob pa'i bla ma la yid kyi blang /
NK027(sha)002:2119: bsnyen gnas sngar blangs dus la blangs kyang bskyar ma bskyar yang skye /
NK027(sha)002:2122: ngang sgom dang lam khyer yang bskyar bas bzang du 'agro'o //
NK027(sha)002:2123: btsun pa rin chen bdag sh+aakya thub pa'i nga rgyal dang ldan pa byas te /
NK027(sha)002:2124: snang srid kyi bcud bsdus la bu'i spyi bor bstim pas /
NK027(sha)002:2125: rin po che 'bar bar gyur de las 'od 'phros /
NK027(sha)002:2126: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang dkon mchog mchod nas byin rlabs kyi 'od zer rang la bstim /
NK027(sha)002:2127: lha la rjes su gnang bar zhu /
NK027(sha)002:2129: sems can gyi dgos 'dod bskang bas yi ge'i rnam
NK027(sha)002:2130: par rang la thim pas chos thams cad lhun grub
NK027(sha)002:2131: tu 'byung bar de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis byin
NK027(sha)002:2133: nyi shu pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:2134: lha 'di rnams ni lha kun gyi phyi mo yin pas dge ba la mtho ris dang /
NK027(sha)002:2135: mi dge ba la ngan 'gro dang /
NK027(sha)002:2136: mi g.yo ba'i las kyi khams gong ma dang /
NK027(sha)002:2137: dkon mchog gsum la dad pas chos kyi rgyal po thob pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2138: nyer gcig pa ka kha bum pa'i dbang ni /
NK027(sha)002:2139: rgya yig dang bod yig cha gnyis su byung ba'i rgya yig kun bzang /
NK027(sha)002:2141: rang bum pa tsaka li la thim /
NK027(sha)002:2142: bla ma dang tsakli la mar me gcig las gnyis chad pa lta bu byung /
NK027(sha)002:2143: slob ma la thim pas dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung bar bsam zhing rim par thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:2144: rgya yig ka smad thog &&& ahni ma skyes ye shes yin //
NK027(sha)002:2145: rang bzhin thams cad stong par ston //
NK027(sha)002:2146: &&&ka ni bya ba'i ye shes te //
NK027(sha)002:2147: las kyis thams cad grol bar bshad //
NK027(sha)002:2148: &&&kha ni khyad par byed pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2149: mi dmigs thams cad grol bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:2150: &&& ga ni don du gyur pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2151: yul med thams cad grol bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:2152: &&& g+ha ni gnas pa'i sgo yin no //
NK027(sha)002:2153: gcig tu ma nges grol bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:2154: &&& nga ni 'dzin pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2155: 'dzin yul thams cad grol bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:2156: &&& tsa ni 'gags pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2157: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2158: &&& tsha ni 'da' ba med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2159: bral ba med par thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2160: dza ni ma byung ba yi sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2161: mi gnas pas ni thams cad grol /
NK027(sha)002:2162: dz+ny+aa ni rtog pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2163: dri ma dag pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2164: nya ni spyod pa bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2165: bya ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2166: ta ni nga rgyal med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2167: ngo bo med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2168: tha ni sgyu stsal med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2169: byed pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2170: da ni 'dren pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2171: rtsol ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2172: d+ha ni bslu ba med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2173: sgyu ma thams cad grol bar byed //
NK027(sha)002:2174: na ni kun tu 'gyur ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2175: g.yo ba skyobs pas las rnams grol //
NK027(sha)002:2176: ta ni tha snyad med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2177: brjod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2178: tha ni rten dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2179: gnas pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2180: da ni rang bzhin med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2181: mtshan nyid med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2182: d+ha ni gtang dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2183: len pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2184: na ni yul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2185: 'dzin pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2186: pa ni nges par 'byung ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2187: 'gag pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2188: pha ni dngos po med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2189: cir yang med la thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2190: ba ni brjod pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2191: smra ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2192: b+ha ni rdul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2193: rtog pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2194: ma ni chags pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2195: zhen pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2196: ya ni dri ma med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2197: gos pa med par thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2198: wa ni rgyu rkyen med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2199: 'bras bu med par thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2200: ra ni rkyen dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2201: dor ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2202: la ni blang ba med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2203: yon tan med par thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2204: sha ni spros pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2205: zhi bas thams cad grol bar byed //
NK027(sha)002:2206: sha ni khur dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2207: lci ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2208: sa ni yang dag gsang ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2209: nges pas thams cad grol bar byed //
NK027(sha)002:2210: ha ni rgyu dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2211: rkyen dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2212: k+sha ni khams dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2213: mtshan nyid med par grol bar byed //
NK027(sha)002:2214: a +aa ni ma skyes ye shes yin //
NK027(sha)002:2215: rang bzhin thams cad stong bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:2216: i +ai ni mthong ba med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2217: gzugs dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2218: u +au ni thos pa med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2219: sgra ni bral bas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2220: e +aee ni tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2221: dri dang bral bas thams cad grol bar byed //
NK027(sha)002:2222: o +aoo ni tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK027(sha)002:2223: reg dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2225: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK027(sha)002:2229: ka ni dbang byed sgrol ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:2230: zhes khams gsum gyi sems can la dbang byed cing nyon mongs pa sgrol bar byed pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2231: de'i byin rlabs kyi chos sku don gyi gsungs /
NK027(sha)002:2232: gzugs brnyan du byung ba'i sgra 'dis kyang /
NK027(sha)002:2233: sems can thams cad dbang du byed cing nyon mongs
NK027(sha)002:2234: pa las sgrol ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:2235: / rgya yig longs sku lha yi yi ge mtshon /
NK027(sha)002:2236: bod yig thub pa sprul sku'i yi ge bstan pa /
NK027(sha)002:2237: phyogs kun tu rgyas nas thams cad skad du chos ston par mtshon /
NK027(sha)002:2238: kha ni khams gsum kun gyi rgyan //
NK027(sha)002:2239: zhes pas khams gsum sems can kun gyi rgyan du 'byung ba yin no //
NK027(sha)002:2240: de'i byin rlabs don gyi gsung sgra snyan tshig 'di sems can gyi rgyan du gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:2241: 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2242: ga ni ma chags dag par mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:2243: ces pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK027(sha)002:2244: po ci la yang ma chags shing rnam par dag
NK027(sha)002:2245: pa yin pas / de'i byin rlabs kyi chos sku'i
NK027(sha)002:2246: gsungs 'dis kyang 'gro ba rnams ci la yang ma
NK027(sha)002:2247: chags shing rnam par dag pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK027(sha)002:2248: pa yin pas / gyur cig / nga ni nga med dang las rgyal //
NK027(sha)002:2249: zhes pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK027(sha)002:2250: po mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing
NK027(sha)002:2251: / mtshan ma las rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2252: sems can thams cad chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa nyid
NK027(sha)002:2253: kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing mtshan ma las rgyas
NK027(sha)002:2254: ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2255: ca ni gnyis med don rtogs te //
NK027(sha)002:2256: zhes pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen po'i de mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med /
NK027(sha)002:2257: gnyis su med pa'i byin rlabs kyis sems can thams
NK027(sha)002:2258: cad mtshan 'dzin gnyis su med pa'i dbang dang ldan
NK027(sha)002:2259: par gyur cig / cha ni thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK027(sha)002:2260: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po la thabs
NK027(sha)002:2261: shes gnyis su med pa'i sprul pa ci snyed cig
NK027(sha)002:2263: de'i byin rlabs kyis thabs shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2264: ja ni chos sku dag par mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:2265: ces pas chos sku bag chags kyi ma gos shing /
NK027(sha)002:2266: rnam par dag pa'i byin rlabs bu rnams kyi rgyud
NK027(sha)002:2267: dang bag chags kyi ma gos shing dag pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:2268: dang nya ni chos nyid gdar sha gcod //
NK027(sha)002:2269: ces pas chos nyid rgyal ba rgyal mtsho dang 'dra ba la /
NK027(sha)002:2270: rigs pa'i ye shes rlabs dang 'dra bas gdar sha
NK027(sha)002:2271: gcod pa'i byin rlabs kyi bu rnams chos nyid rgya
NK027(sha)002:2272: mtsho las rig pa'i ye shes kyi byin gyis brlabs
NK027(sha)002:2273: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2274: ta ni mkhas pa'i 'od zer can //
NK027(sha)002:2275: zhes pas chos sku las thugs rje'i sku las thugs
NK027(sha)002:2276: rje'i 'od zer byung ba'i byin rlabs kyi bu rnams
NK027(sha)002:2277: kyi sems la snying po'i 'od zer byung ba'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:2278: tha ni dkon mchog 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK027(sha)002:2279: zhes pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK027(sha)002:2280: po la dgongs pa zab mo 'byung ba de'i byin
NK027(sha)002:2281: rlabs kyi chos sku'i dgongs pa zab mo'i ye shes
NK027(sha)002:2282: rtog pa'i dbang da ni rgyu 'bras gnyis med la
NK027(sha)002:2283: / zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po rgyu
NK027(sha)002:2284: 'bras kyi chos gnyis su med pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK027(sha)002:2285: chos kyi 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol te /
NK027(sha)002:2286: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang bde ba'i dbang na ni sdug bsngal med pas bde //
NK027(sha)002:2287: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po la las
NK027(sha)002:2288: bde ba'i ngang rgyun du 'byung ba'i byin rlabs kyis
NK027(sha)002:2289: / 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gtan nas spang ba'i dbang pa ni thams cad bskyed par byed //
NK027(sha)002:2290: ces pas chos sku bde ba chen po ye shes bskyed pa'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)002:2291: gsung 'di mthong ba tsam gyi gzhan gyi rigs bskyed pa'i dbang pha ni pha rol phyin la gnas //
NK027(sha)002:2292: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po 'khor ba'i
NK027(sha)002:2293: pha rol du phyin pa la gnas pa'i byin rlabs
NK027(sha)002:2294: kyis / 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mthar phyin nas mya
NK027(sha)002:2295: ngan las 'das pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:2296: kyis / / ba ni bde ba chen po ste //
NK027(sha)002:2297: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po mnyam pa
NK027(sha)002:2298: nyid kyi byin rlabs kyi dngos po dang mtshan ma
NK027(sha)002:2299: thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi dbang ma ni srid
NK027(sha)002:2301: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po kun gyi gzhi mar gyur pa'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)002:2302: srid pa gsum las rgyal zhing kun gyi gzhi rten du gyur pa'i dbang /
NK027(sha)002:2303: tsa ni 'du 'bral med pa ste zhes pas chos
NK027(sha)002:2304: sku bde ba chen po sku dang ye shes stobs
NK027(sha)002:2305: dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK027(sha)002:2306: byin rlabs kyi chos sku dang 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK027(sha)002:2307: dbang tsha ni don dam lus la rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:2308: zhes pas don dam chos kyi sku ni rgyu dang
NK027(sha)002:2309: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yin
NK027(sha)002:2310: no // de'i byin rlabs kyi chos sku'i rgyu 'bras
NK027(sha)002:2311: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dza ni bar
NK027(sha)002:2313: zhes pas chos sku las thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2314: thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i dbang wa ni mya ngan thams cad 'dul //
NK027(sha)002:2315: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po'i ngang la
NK027(sha)002:2316: 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba'i byin rlabs
NK027(sha)002:2317: kyis / 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang zha ni gzhal yas chen po ste //
NK027(sha)002:2318: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po thams cad kyi gnas yin pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2319: gzhal yas chen po'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2320: za ni skye mched ches las 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:2321: zhes pas chos thams cad rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2322: chos nyid gsal ba'i ye shes kyi ma rig pa'i
NK027(sha)002:2323: mun pa sel ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:2324: / 'a ni goms pa'i tshogs la btsan //
NK027(sha)002:2325: zhes pas gsung gis tshogs rang bzhin med par sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang dang /
NK027(sha)002:2326: ya ni mthar byed pho nya'i bdag /
NK027(sha)002:2327: ces pas gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2328: gro' ba'i don byed pa'i dbang ra ni gcod byed yul la dbang //
NK027(sha)002:2329: zhes pas ye shes kyi bcad par bya ba'i yul
NK027(sha)002:2330: nyon mongs pa gcod pa'i dbang la ni mnyam nyid
NK027(sha)002:2331: sprul pa'i sku // zhes pas mnyam pa nyid las
NK027(sha)002:2332: sprul pa'i sku byung nas sems can gyi don byed
NK027(sha)002:2333: sprul pa'i sku // pa'i dbang / sha ni snang byed mkha' la shar //
NK027(sha)002:2334: zhes pas chos sku las ye shes kyi rol pa
NK027(sha)002:2335: shar nas 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang sa ni
NK027(sha)002:2337: zhes pa'i thugs phyag mtshan las sna tshogs byung nas
NK027(sha)002:2338: 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang ha ni thabs mkhas
NK027(sha)002:2339: dbyings nas byon // zhes pas bde ba chen po'i
NK027(sha)002:2340: dbyings nas thabs mkhas pa'i mdzad spyod bsam gyis mi
NK027(sha)002:2341: dbyings nas byon // khyab pas / 'gro ba'i don
NK027(sha)002:2342: mthar phyin pa'i dbang a ni skye med chos kyi
NK027(sha)002:2343: dbyings nas byon // khyab pas / dbyings // zhes
NK027(sha)002:2344: pas rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i dbyings nas 'gro ba'i
NK027(sha)002:2345: don la ma 'gags par 'gro don mthar phyin pa'i
NK027(sha)002:2346: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2347: glegs shing ka ba li zung gcig gtad de /
NK027(sha)002:2349: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2350: yig shing gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2351: chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2353: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:2355: shes bya'i ye shes la thog pa med pa'i gzhan
NK027(sha)002:2356: don 'grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:2357: / rnam snang 'od du zhu ba'i bum pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK027(sha)002:2359: dbang bskur bas lus ngag gi dri ma dag /
NK027(sha)002:2360: chu'i lhag ma yar lud pa la rnam snang gi dbang brgyan /
NK027(sha)002:2362: bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2363: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2364: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2365: rigs kyi bu la rin po che'i dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2366: rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyi mnan pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2368: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2369: yum gyis phyag gis reg cing dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2370: nyon mongs pa'i sdug bsngal zhi ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2371: seng ge'i phru gu zung gcig gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2372: rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang dam par thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2373: glang po che'i phru gu zung gcig gis dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2374: 'jig rten thams cad 'dren pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2375: na bza' ka shi ka'i ras kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2376: mkhyen pa'i ye shes gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang dam na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2377: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2378: rigs kyi bu la rgyan gyi bye brag gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2379: 'gro ba thams cad kyi sems shes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2380: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2381: rigs kyi bu la gnam ru zung gcig gis dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:2382: snyan pa'i sgra sgrogs cing bdud dpung 'dul ba'i 'phang rtsal dang ldan par na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2383: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2384: rigs kyi bu la btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:2385: bstan pa'i rigs mi nub cing /
NK027(sha)002:2386: ci ltar 'dul ba de bzhin du 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2387: de ltar dbang bcu gcig po des lha mi mtho ris kyi chas su bcug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2388: nyer gnyis pa lha dbang ni /
NK027(sha)002:2389: de nas rnam snang dang tshes brgyad kyi lha rnams rim par thog ste /
NK027(sha)002:2391: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i gtso bo longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK027(sha)002:2392: bcom ldan 'das kun rig rnam par snang mdzad ngan
NK027(sha)002:2393: song thams cad yongs su sbyangs shing mngon shes dang
NK027(sha)002:2394: rdzu 'phrul ster ba'i dbang thob par sarba b+hud+d+ha a
NK027(sha)002:2396: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:2397: cad kyi rigs kyi bu la mngon par dga' ba'i
NK027(sha)002:2398: zhing khams nas / bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa
NK027(sha)002:2399: sku mdog sngon po g.yas sa gnon g.yon mnyam bzhag
NK027(sha)002:2402: dran pa tsam gyi mi dmigs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2403: sdig sgrib ngan 'gro thams cad sel zhing mtho ris
NK027(sha)002:2404: dang thar pa thob par mdzad pa de'i dbang mchog
NK027(sha)002:2407: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2408: stong gi lha rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog
NK027(sha)002:2409: gser btso ma lta bu g.yas sa gnon g.yon mnyam
NK027(sha)002:2410: bzhag / lhung bzed can de nyid kyi sngon sbyin pa'i bsod nams thob pa las bsngosa te /
NK027(sha)002:2411: bdag mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa na /
NK027(sha)002:2412: bdag gi 'khor rnam bzhi 'tsho bas mi brel bar
NK027(sha)002:2413: smon lam grub pa'i byin rlabs kyis stong la bsnyen
NK027(sha)002:2414: gnas bsrung bas phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du
NK027(sha)002:2415: mu ge'i bskal pa nas thar pa'i dbang mchog dam
NK027(sha)002:2418: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2419: nya yi lha snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog dmar po mnyam bzhag tshe bum can /
NK027(sha)002:2420: de nyid kyis thos bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab kyi bsod nams thob pa las bsngosa te /
NK027(sha)002:2421: bdag mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pas na bdag gi 'khor rnams kyis /
NK027(sha)002:2422: bde ba can gyi zhing khams su phyir mi ldog
NK027(sha)002:2423: pa'i 'phags pa thob par smon lam grub pa'i byin
NK027(sha)002:2424: rlabs kyis nya la bsnyen gnas bsrung bas phyogs dus
NK027(sha)002:2425: thams cad kyi mtshon gyi bskal pa las thar pa'i
NK027(sha)002:2426: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2428: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:2429: cad kyi rigs kyi bu la tshes brgyad kyi lha
NK027(sha)002:2430: sman gyi lha beed+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po sku mdog
NK027(sha)002:2431: mthing ka g.yas mchod sbyin a ru ra /
NK027(sha)002:2432: g.yon mnyam bzhag lhung bzed can /
NK027(sha)002:2433: smon lam gyi mthu las gang gis bdag gi mtshan lan bdun brjod cing phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2434: bskor ba dang tshes brgyad la bsnyen gnas bsrung bas /
NK027(sha)002:2435: phyogs dus thams cad du rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2439: nad kyi bskal pa las thar pa'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2441: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyi rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2442: nyi ma shar ba'i shar phyogs la /
NK027(sha)002:2443: shar phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos thams cad dang gang zag chos ldan skyong ba /
NK027(sha)002:2444: 'dzam bu gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK027(sha)002:2445: dri za'i rgyal po yul 'khor bsrung gi dbang dam pa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2446: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyi rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2448: lho phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang gang zag chos ldan skyong ba /
NK027(sha)002:2449: 'dzam bu'i gling grul bum gyi rgyal po 'phags skyes po'i dbang dam na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2450: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK027(sha)002:2451: cad kyi rigs kyi bu la nyi ma dbus nas
NK027(sha)002:2452: lhun po'i nub / nub phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang gang zag chos ldan skyong ba /
NK027(sha)002:2453: 'dzam bu gling gi klu yi rgyal po spyan mi bzang gi dbang dam na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2455: rigs kyi bu la nyi ma dbus nas lhun po'i
NK027(sha)002:2456: byang phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang gang
NK027(sha)002:2458: 'dzam bu'i gling gnod sbyin gyi rgyal po rnam thos sras kyi dbang dam na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2461: shar phyogs dbang po dang btsun mo 'gro ba thams
NK027(sha)002:2462: cad la bde ba ster ba de'i dbang na mo
NK027(sha)002:2465: shar gling g.yas na mngag gzhug pa /
NK027(sha)002:2466: 'gro ba kun gyi yid du 'ong ba skye 'gro'i
NK027(sha)002:2467: nyon mongs pa gcod pa de'i dbang mchog dam pa
NK027(sha)002:2469: shar gling g.yon na pho nya rab tu myur ba'i shugs can /
NK027(sha)002:2470: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal las rab tu sgrol ba de'i na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2471: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2472: 'dzam bu gling na lha tshangs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2473: btsun mo tshangs ma 'dod khams kyi sdug bsngal dang bral zhing /
NK027(sha)002:2474: 'khor gyod khrims dang 'dra ba'i skyon gyi ma gos
NK027(sha)002:2475: pa de'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:2477: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2478: lho gling g.yas na mngag gzhug pa //
NK027(sha)002:2479: 'gro ba yid du 'ong ba nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa de'i dbang dam na mo /
NK027(sha)002:2482: lho gling g.yas na pho nya rab tu myur ba'i
NK027(sha)002:2483: shugs can ngan song gsum gyis sdug bsngal las grol
NK027(sha)002:2485: phyogs bcu nub na lha khyab 'jug btsun mo dpal
NK027(sha)002:2486: lha mo phrin las kyis kun tu khyab par de'i
NK027(sha)002:2488: nub gling g.yas na mngag gzhug pa rdo rje bde
NK027(sha)002:2489: bas nyon mongs pa gcod pa de'i dbang na mo
NK027(sha)002:2491: nub gling g.yon na pho nya rdo rje ded dpon
NK027(sha)002:2492: 'gro ba la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba de'i
NK027(sha)002:2495: byang na lha dbang phyug chen po dang /
NK027(sha)002:2496: btsun mo dka' thub zlog ma dug gsum 'joms par byed pa de'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2498: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2499: byang gi gling g.yas phyogs na dbang phyug chen po'i mngag gzhug pa /
NK027(sha)002:2500: ded dpon nag po mdung thogs pa /
NK027(sha)002:2501: 'gro ba sems can sdug bsngal sgrol bar bskul ba de'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2503: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin rlabs kyis rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:2504: byang gling g.yon na pho nya mngag gzhug drang srong khros pa'i cha byad can /
NK027(sha)002:2505: 'gro ba kun la rnam par snang ba de'i dbang dam par thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:2506: ces sum cu rtsa drug po dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2507: nyer gsum pa lam khyer la bzhi /
NK027(sha)002:2508: theg pa lam khyer lha mi'i theg pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2509: de yang dang po 'jug sgo chos spyod bcu ste /
NK027(sha)002:2511: yi ge bri mchod sbyin pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:2512: nyan dang bsgom dang kha ton klog /
NK027(sha)002:2513: 'chad dang rtsom dang de sems pa //
NK027(sha)002:2514: 'di bcu chos kyi sgo mo yin //
NK027(sha)002:2517: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:2519: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
NK027(sha)002:2520: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
NK027(sha)002:2521: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
NK027(sha)002:2525: sgo gsum mi dge ba rnams te /
NK027(sha)002:2527: lus kyi me dge rnam gsum ste //
NK027(sha)002:2528: ngag gi las ni bzhi yin te //
NK027(sha)002:2529: yid kyi las ni rnam gsum ste //
NK027(sha)002:2530: mi dge bcu ni spang bya ste //
NK027(sha)002:2532: bzhi pa bsgom bya'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK027(sha)002:2534: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo bsgom byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:2535: tshangs gnas la sogs rim par skyes pa'i rgyu //
NK027(sha)002:2538: dge ba bcu ni ci nus kyi bsgrub ste /
NK027(sha)002:2539: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spang byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:2540: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK027(sha)002:2544: nyer bzhi pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK027(sha)002:2545: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su ri rab kyi lte bar seng ge'i khri /
NK027(sha)002:2547: rnam par snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:2548: rdo rje'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK027(sha)002:2549: shar gyi dbus su brgya byin dkar po rdo rje gdengs ba /
NK027(sha)002:2550: g.yon nor bu las mchod sbyin ster ba /
NK027(sha)002:2551: dbang mo go rgyud mang bsnams pa /
NK027(sha)002:2553: g.yas kyi gling du mngag gzhug la 'gro ba'i yid 'ong ljang ku g.yas ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2554: g.yon du pho nya myur ba'i shugs can sngon po g.yas mdung rtse gsum pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2555: lho'i dbus su tshangs pa ser po g.yas spyi blug 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2558: blta na sdug ljang ku ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2559: g.yon du pho nya mgyogs byed dmar pos pad dkar 'dzin pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2560: dbus kyi nub phyogs su lha khyab 'jug sngo nag 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2561: dpal ldan lha mo gsal shing 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2562: g.yas su mngag gzhug rdo rje bde ba dkar mo mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2563: g.yon du pho nya rdo rje sde dpon ljang ser 'khor lo 'dzin pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2564: byang gi dbus su dbang phyug chen po dmar po rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2566: g.yas su mngag gzhug ded dpon nag po mdung thung 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2567: g.yon na pho nya drang srong khros pa dmar po mda' gzhu 'geng pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2568: sgo bzhir yul 'khor srung dkar po pi wam 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2569: 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2570: g.yon mig mi bzang dmar po sprul zhags bsnams pa /
NK027(sha)002:2571: rnam thos sras ser po ne'u le 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:2572: gzhan yang zhing sbyong ba'i lha mi 'khrugs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2573: stong gi lha ston pa sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2574: nya'i lha sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK027(sha)002:2575: tshes brgyad kyi lha sangs rgyas sman gyi bla dang /
NK027(sha)002:2576: ston pa sh+aakya'i gtso bo la phyogs bcu dus gsum
NK027(sha)002:2577: gyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i bskor ba
NK027(sha)002:2578: rnams dran zhing / de dag gi bka' las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:2579: nyer lnga pa snying po lam khyer ni /
NK027(sha)002:2581: na mo b+ha ga wa ti /
NK027(sha)002:2583: mi bskyod pa'i kam ka ni tshang bar bzlas so //
NK027(sha)002:2584: thub pa'i mu ne snang ba mtha' yas kyi /
NK027(sha)002:2587: b+hi sha dz+yee tshangs bar bzlas so //
NK027(sha)002:2589: sngags mi shes na skyabs 'gro bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2590: nyer drug pa bslab bya ni /
NK027(sha)002:2593: dkon mchog la dad pa skyo ngal med par byed pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2594: don dam par dam pa'i chos btsal ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2595: gtsug lag bzang po mkhas par bslab pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2596: ci yang dran cing tshod zin par bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2597: ma bcol ba'i las gtogs 'dod mi byed pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2598: mig gi mthong sar blta zhing gong ma rnams kyi rjes snyag pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2599: dus gsum gyi pha ma la drin lan du blan pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2600: phu nu dang pha tshan nang du shong yangs che ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2601: rim pas rgan la bkur sti bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2602: khyim mtshes la byams par bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2603: gnyen grogs kyi dge bshes la dka' las kyi phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2604: srid kyi 'brel ba'i nye ring la chab gang mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2605: rig byed bzo la mkhas pas gzhan la phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2606: ltos pa'i mi dran gyi skyabs 'og tu gzhug pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2607: ngan byed kyi gros bkag la rgyal khams bde yangs kyi gros gzhi bting pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2608: las mtha' chos la gtad de phyi ma bu smad kyi byang chub kyi gzhi thob par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2609: de ltar gang nus khas len du bzhag go //
NK027(sha)002:2611: gnas chu bo ne ra dza na'i 'gram /
NK027(sha)002:2616: dgos pa 'jig rten pa'i bya ba las 'das pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2617: de yang mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang mtshams sbyar ro //
NK027(sha)002:2619: gang gi gang la ci phyir gang dgod pa //
NK027(sha)002:2620: 'di ni lha mi'i theg pa'i 'gag drug yin //
NK027(sha)002:2622: nyer brgyad pa ngang bsgom ni /
NK027(sha)002:2623: khrid du byed na mi rtog ngang bsgom chung du /
NK027(sha)002:2625: des gar spyin la sbrang ma zin pa lta bu /
NK027(sha)002:2626: shes pa snga phyi'i 'khrul thag bcad pa gnad /
NK027(sha)002:2627: sems nang du zin pa srog phyi nang snang ba mthong ste gol sa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2628: de'ang dang po rten can la bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:2629: de nas ci la yang rten mi bca' /
NK027(sha)002:2630: yul gang la yang mi dmigs /
NK027(sha)002:2632: sems rang sar ma bskrog pa'i ri dwags ltar /
NK027(sha)002:2635: zhib tu dgrol na bag mar lta bu'i lus klod /
NK027(sha)002:2636: gar spyin sbrang ma lta bu dbugs klod pa snga
NK027(sha)002:2637: phyi'i mi 'khrul bar sems 'gyu ba nang du zin
NK027(sha)002:2639: stong nyid dngos zin pa srog sems yul du snang ba khams gsum sa dgu ste /
NK027(sha)002:2640: 'phrang rang snang stong pa'i rtsal du shar ba de
NK027(sha)002:2641: stong pa'i rang gzugs su ma shes pas chags sdang
NK027(sha)002:2642: gi blang dor byas pas ngan song gsum du skye
NK027(sha)002:2645: 'jig rten dang po bsam gtan bzhi /
NK027(sha)002:2646: snyoms 'jug bzhi gol sa dgu ste /
NK027(sha)002:2647: zhes pas sa gcig pa 'dod khams dang /
NK027(sha)002:2648: gzugs khams bsam gtan dang po gnyis pa /
NK027(sha)002:2651: snyoms 'jug bzhi gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi ste dagu'o //
NK027(sha)002:2652: sems rang gso 'dzin pa dgu bskyed cing mi 'ching ste /
NK027(sha)002:2655: zhen med chos sku spyod par bshad //
NK027(sha)002:2657: de nas lha mi ngang bsgom bstan pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2658: de nas gang du bstan pa'i cho gas cha gsum btang /
NK027(sha)002:2659: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod bstod bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:2660: ston mchog dam pa lha mi'i mchod 'os pa //
NK027(sha)002:2661: sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:2662: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba //
NK027(sha)002:2663: de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:2664: zhi ba chags bral lha mi'i mchod 'os pa //
NK027(sha)002:2665: chos la phyag 'tshal deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:2666: sems can gang dag de dag thams cad tshogs kyi dam pa lha mi'i mchod 'os pa //
NK027(sha)002:2667: dge 'dun phyag 'tshal deng sems can gang dag de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:2669: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo /
NK027(sha)002:2670: lha mi'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'o //
NK027(sha)002:2671: nyan thos kyi dal sgrub khrigs la dkyil 'khor bya zhing mchod pa bshams /
NK027(sha)002:2672: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang /
NK027(sha)002:2673: dbang dang khrus bya sdom rten 'dri /
NK027(sha)002:2674: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzegs ston pa sgom /
NK027(sha)002:2675: tshul khrims ldan pa'i bum dbang la /
NK027(sha)002:2676: gso sbyong tshul khrims btsun chas lha gsol btab sdoms pa bslab bya 'bog /
NK027(sha)002:2677: chos bshad dbang lung ngang bsgom khyer //
NK027(sha)002:2678: theg pa lha snying bslab bya la'ang /
NK027(sha)002:2679: theg sgo lha khrims ting spyod 'bras //
NK027(sha)002:2681: gdams ngag ngang bsgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK027(sha)002:2683: dang po dkyil 'khor la gsum las /
NK027(sha)002:2686: zhes pas mkha' rlung me chu sa'i dkyil 'khor rim brtsegs kyi dkyil 'khor la nyan thos 'god pa /
NK027(sha)002:2687: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi them brgyad kyi gnyis pa yan chad la /
NK027(sha)002:2688: nyan thos rgyu la gnas pa /
NK027(sha)002:2689: rgyan gyi rta babs gnyis man chad la nyan thos 'bras bu la gnas pa 'god pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2690: gsum pa bri ba dal lnga ste /
NK027(sha)002:2691: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa gnyis dang /
NK027(sha)002:2693: de'i phyi rim brgyad de'i phyi rim yang brgyad pa gcig /
NK027(sha)002:2694: 'dab ma bcu drug byas pa gnyis so //
NK027(sha)002:2695: de rnams kyi lte ba ser /
NK027(sha)002:2700: 'du shes bcu ldan nyan thos rnams //
NK027(sha)002:2702: gsum pa mchod pa bsham pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:2703: sku gsung thugs kyi rten dang /
NK027(sha)002:2714: chu tshags la sogs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2716: man+dala la sogs pa bsham mo //
NK027(sha)002:2719: bum pa'i steng du a las zla ba'i steng du sngags kyi phreng ba dkar po bsam ste /
NK027(sha)002:2720: ye d+har+m+aa lan bdun bzlas pas sngags phreng las 'od zer 'phros /
NK027(sha)002:2721: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad lha'i bdud rtsir zhu /
NK027(sha)002:2723: de nas gzung thag la bzung ste /
NK027(sha)002:2724: sngags brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas te /
NK027(sha)002:2725: phyogs thams cad du ku shas gtor bas /
NK027(sha)002:2726: rten dang mchod pa ma dag pa bsang /
NK027(sha)002:2727: so so'i ye shes pa thim pas dag cing /
NK027(sha)002:2728: bzang ba phun sum tshogs par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:2729: lnga pa chog gzhung sman lha'i mdo chog dang /
NK027(sha)002:2730: gnas brtan bcu drug gi cho ga'o //
NK027(sha)002:2731: drug pa cha gsum la rdo rje sems dpa'i tshab tu sh+aakya thub pa bsgom gzhan 'dra'o //
NK027(sha)002:2732: bdun pa ni dpang skong gi yan lag bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2733: brgyad pa ni bum pa'i chus thams cad khrus bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2735: sdom pa zhu ba'i yon dngos po dag pa gcig 'bul lo //
NK027(sha)002:2736: bcu pa ni khru gang yang lhag pa'i steng du mi rung yang /
NK027(sha)002:2737: 'dir chos pas khri'i steng du 'dug par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2738: bcu gcig pa rgyan gyi mchog tshul khrims yin pas hrul yang btsun chas bgo //
NK027(sha)002:2739: 'dzom na bzang po kho na mchog tu mdzes pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2740: bcu gnyis pa khri ni rgyan gyi tshogs rdzogs shing
NK027(sha)002:2741: chos kyi che ba 'byin pa de la 'dzegs pa'o
NK027(sha)002:2742: // bcu gsum pa ni ston pa bsgoms pas rang bzhin gyi blo 'gyur /
NK027(sha)002:2744: ser mo tsam zhig gon pa'ang //
NK027(sha)002:2745: ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya //
NK027(sha)002:2747: bcu bzhi pa bum pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:2751: chu bo chen po nas blang ba'i chus /
NK027(sha)002:2752: rten gsum me long gi ngos la khrus gsol /
NK027(sha)002:2754: lha rnams kyi thugs rje'i bdud rtsir bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:2755: bac+wo lnga pa gso sbyong ni /
NK027(sha)002:2756: dkon mchog rten drung du mchod pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2757: yan lag bdun pa bya ste /
NK027(sha)002:2759: ci ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK027(sha)002:2765: rang gi don rjes su thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:2766: srid pa yang dag par sbyor ba /
NK027(sha)002:2767: nyon mongs pa yongs su zad pa /
NK027(sha)002:2769: legs par rnam par grol ba'i thugs /
NK027(sha)002:2770: legs par rnam par grol ba'i shes rab can /
NK027(sha)002:2771: sems can thams cad gyi don gyi phyir dang /
NK027(sha)002:2772: phan par bya ba'i sems dang /
NK027(sha)002:2773: grol bar bya ba'i sems dang /
NK027(sha)002:2774: mu ge med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK027(sha)002:2775: byang chub kyi chos rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK027(sha)002:2776: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK027(sha)002:2777: gso sbyong len par mdzad pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:2778: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK027(sha)002:2779: ci srid sang nyi ma ma shar gyi bar du /
NK027(sha)002:2780: gso sbyong legs par yang dag pa blang bar bagyi'o //
NK027(sha)002:2781: deng nas srog gcod mi bya zhing //
NK027(sha)002:2782: gzhan gyi nor yang blang mi bya //
NK027(sha)002:2783: 'khrigs pa'i chos kyang mi bya zhing //
NK027(sha)002:2784: rdzun gyi tshig kyang mi smra'o //
NK027(sha)002:2785: skyon ni mang po nyer bsten pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:2786: chang ni yongs su spang bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:2787: khri gdan mthon po mi bya zhing //
NK027(sha)002:2788: de bzhin dus ma yin pa'i zas //
NK027(sha)002:2789: dri dang phreng ba rgyan dang ni //
NK027(sha)002:2790: gar dang glu sogs spang bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:2791: ci ltar dgra bcom rtag tu ni //
NK027(sha)002:2792: srog gcod la sogs mi byed ltar //
NK027(sha)002:2793: de bzhin srog gcod la sogs spang //
NK027(sha)002:2794: bla med byang chub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:2796: srid pa'i mtsho las sgrol bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:2797: ces lan gsum dag par blang ba'i rjes su /
NK027(sha)002:2798: tshul khrims rnam dag gi gzungs 'di nyer gcig gam /
NK027(sha)002:2799: brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2800: yang gang phyir dge ba ma lus gso ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2801: rnyed pa srid pa 'di ni yang dag byed /
NK027(sha)002:2802: de bzhin gshegs pas gso sbyong len gsungs so //
NK027(sha)002:2804: sam b+ha ra sam b+ha ra /
NK027(sha)002:2807: pad+ma bi b+hu shi ta b+hu dza /
NK027(sha)002:2810: a wa lo ki te h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:2811: zhes tshig gzhan gyi bar ma chod par bazla'o //
NK027(sha)002:2812: yang na so sor thar pa'i sdom pa la rtsa ba'i ltung ba byung na /
NK027(sha)002:2813: lhag ma gang yod phul la /
NK027(sha)002:2814: rtsa ba nas bskyar bar bya /
NK027(sha)002:2815: yan lag gi nyes pa phra rag gang yang ngo shes par byas te /
NK027(sha)002:2816: 'chab sems rtsod sems med par ltung bar ngo shes shing /
NK027(sha)002:2817: dran pas nya stong la sogs pa la spyi bshags byas pas /
NK027(sha)002:2818: nyams chag thams cad sor chud cing gso /
NK027(sha)002:2819: sgrib pa dag pa rang bzhin gyi dge ba gso zhing sdig pa sbyong ste /
NK027(sha)002:2820: thams cad kyi thal mo sbyar te /
NK027(sha)002:2821: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs te //
NK027(sha)002:2822: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:2823: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:2824: bdag sh+aakya'i dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK027(sha)002:2825: tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas tha ma da lta la thug gi bar du /
NK027(sha)002:2830: ma mthol ma bshags na ni de ltar mi 'gyur ba lags so //
NK027(sha)002:2831: zhes pa'i bar lan gsum brjod /
NK027(sha)002:2834: bcu drug pa tshul khrims ni /
NK027(sha)002:2835: lha mi'i yul gyi chos lugs dang /
NK027(sha)002:2836: rgyal ba'i lung gi chos lugs 'dul ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2837: mdo sde mngon pa nas 'byung ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:2838: bcu bdun pa btsun chas ni /
NK027(sha)002:2839: rab tu byung ba la 'os pa rnams dge bsnyen gyis kyang mos rten du bcang bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2840: bac+wo brgyad pa lha ni gtso bo ston pa sh+aakya thub pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2843: khyad par dus chen po'i lha 'das pa'i sangs rgyas
NK027(sha)002:2844: thams cad sku tshab sangs rgya mar me mdzad don
NK027(sha)002:2845: dam pa'i chos ston pas rten 'brel gyi phyag rgya
NK027(sha)002:2846: / da ltar sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku tshab
NK027(sha)002:2847: sh+aakya thub pa skye 'gro thugs rjes skyong bas sa
NK027(sha)002:2848: / gnon mnyam bzhag / ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK027(sha)002:2849: thams cad kyi sku tshab mgon po byams pa gdul
NK027(sha)002:2850: bya rjes su 'dzin pas mchod sbyin spyi blug skyabs
NK027(sha)002:2852: 'dir dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi gtso bo thub pa /
NK027(sha)002:2853: 'khor ni g.yas su sh+aa ri'i bu /
NK027(sha)002:2864: de'i phyi rol du de dag las gyes pa'i sprul pa brgyad /
NK027(sha)002:2865: de'i phyi rol du rang rgyud pa brgyad /
NK027(sha)002:2866: yang mdun nas rim par mchog bcu drug ni /
NK027(sha)002:2867: kun dga' bo bsil g.yab sh+aa ri'i bu rin po che /
NK027(sha)002:2883: kun kyang dbu reg zhabs rjen rab tu byung ba'i cha lugs can no //
NK027(sha)002:2884: yang gnas brtan bcu drug ni /
NK027(sha)002:2885: phyogs re rer bzhi bzhi ste /
NK027(sha)002:2886: shar nas rim pa b+ha ra ng+h+wa dza bsod snyoms pa /
NK027(sha)002:2903: kun kyang dgra bcom pa mkhar gsil lhung bzed 'dzin pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:2905: d+harma t+aa la dge bsnyen no //
NK027(sha)002:2906: bcu dgu pa gsol ba gdab pa la gnyis /
NK027(sha)002:2912: dge 'dun gsum la phyag gsum byas la /
NK027(sha)002:2913: dkon mchog gsum du mos gus bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:2915: bla ma thub par bsgom pa'i dbu gtsug tu nor bu 'phros pa las /
NK027(sha)002:2916: rang gi dgos 'dod 'byung bar bsam la /
NK027(sha)002:2919: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK027(sha)002:2920: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnams sbyangs pa //
NK027(sha)002:2921: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen mchog /
NK027(sha)002:2922: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin stsol //
NK027(sha)002:2923: zhes lan gsum gsol ba gdab bo //
NK027(sha)002:2924: nyi shu pa sdom pa zhu ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:2930: khyad par dge bsnyen la bar chad dris pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2932: mkhan por 'du shes bskyed mi dgos /
NK027(sha)002:2933: dge tshul dge slong ma la sun phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2935: skabs 'dir dge tshul gyi bar chad dri ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:2936: bar chad yod med dris pas /
NK027(sha)002:2937: yin pa la yin pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:2938: ma yin pa la ma yin zhes /
NK027(sha)002:2939: nged kyi dri ba rnams la sems ma yengs bar /
NK027(sha)002:2940: ci ltar yin pa bzhin du lan thongs shig bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:2942: khyod mu stegs can ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2943: lo bco lnga ma lon pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2944: lo bac+wo lnga lon pa yang bya rog skrod mi nus pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2945: bya rog skrod mi nus pa la lo bdun ma lon pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2946: bran la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2947: bu lon chags pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2948: phas ma gnang ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2949: mas ma gnang ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2950: pha mas gnang yang yul thag mi ring ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2952: dge slong ma sun phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2953: rku thabs su gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2954: tha dad du gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2955: gnas par mi bya ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2960: mu stegs can du zhugs pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2961: ma bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2962: pha bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2963: dgra bcom pa bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2964: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byas pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2965: de bzhin gshegs pa la ngan sems kyi khrag phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2966: pham par gyur pa'i ltung ba bzhi po dag las
NK027(sha)002:2967: ltung ba gang yang rung ba byung ba ma yin
NK027(sha)002:2968: nam / rgyu las bzlog pa'i chad pa khas mi len pa gnas nas phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2969: lag rdum la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2971: sor mo gcig pa la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2972: rgyal pos bkrabs pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2973: rgyal pos ma gnang ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2974: rgyal pos ma gnang ba'i yul thag mi ring ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2975: chom rkun par grags pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2976: phung khrol ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2978: ko lpags mkhan ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2981: mi ma yin pa'i 'gro ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2982: byang sgra mi snyan pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2983: mtshan lan gsum du gyur pa ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2984: skyes pa 'dra ba'i bud med ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2985: sdig sdig lta bu'i mtshan nyid can ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2986: gling gzhan nas skyes pa'i tshul byed mi 'dra ba ma yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:2988: khyod bar chad bzhi dang mi ldan pas bstan pa'i
NK027(sha)002:2989: snod du rung bar 'dug pas khyod kho bos rab
NK027(sha)002:2994: slob dpon gyi bar chad dag gam dris /
NK027(sha)002:2995: dag zhe na las byed pa'i dge slong la gtad de /
NK027(sha)002:2997: dge 'dun gyi gnang nas gal te yongs su da ga na'o //
NK027(sha)002:2998: zhes gsungs nas gtsug phud breg par spro 'am dri /
NK027(sha)002:2999: slob dpon gyi bslab pa 'bogs par gsol te /
NK027(sha)002:3002: rgan pas dus go bar byed pa yin pas 'di slob mkhan gnyis dang dge tshul gsum dril nas /
NK027(sha)002:3003: mkhan pos dge tshul du slob ma tshar bar byed pa'i lugs so //
NK027(sha)002:3004: sdom pa dngos la gsum ka tshang dgos pa las /
NK027(sha)002:3005: 'dir mkhan po la sangs rgyas su mos /
NK027(sha)002:3006: de'i bka' lung gi tshig dang mthun pa'i don yid la rjes su bzung ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:3007: rang rjes zlos lan gsum gyis tha ma la /
NK027(sha)002:3008: bslab sdom tshul khrims thabs shes kyi sems la gdengs brtan po dang /
NK027(sha)002:3010: tsaka li'i gzugs rnams kyis kyang bar chad yongs su dag par nges shing /
NK027(sha)002:3011: sdom pa mthar phyin pa las 'phro ba'i 'dun ldan du nges pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3018: rkang gnyis dam pa rnams kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:3019: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:3020: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:3025: sh+aakya seng ge sh+aakya'i rgyal po gtso bo de rab
NK027(sha)002:3026: tu byung ba'i rjes su bdag rab tu byung ba'i
NK027(sha)002:3027: rjes su bdag rab tu dbyung bar 'tshal te /
NK027(sha)002:3028: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas khyim pa'i rtags spang zhing /
NK027(sha)002:3029: rab tu byung ba'i rtags yang dag par len to /
NK027(sha)002:3030: slob dpon mkhan pos bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:3031: brjod pa gsum gyi sa tha ma ra mkhan bos /
NK027(sha)002:3035: de nas gnang ba sbyin pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:3036: dngos dang yid kyi dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i gnas
NK027(sha)002:3037: brtan dge slong thams cad kyi gal te yongs su
NK027(sha)002:3038: dag na'o // zhes gsung bar bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:3039: de nas smad kyi mthang gos /
NK027(sha)002:3044: lhung bzed la sogs bla mas phyag nas gnang zhing mkho ba'i yo byad rnams gtad de /
NK027(sha)002:3046: tshul khrims kyi phung po dang /
NK027(sha)002:3047: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK027(sha)002:3048: shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK027(sha)002:3049: rnam par grol ba'i phung po dang /
NK027(sha)002:3050: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes gzigs pa'i phung po yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3051: ces thams cad kyis mthun 'gyur brjod /
NK027(sha)002:3053: mkhan pos gtad pa'i slob dpon gyi chos bshad nas /
NK027(sha)002:3055: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bsam pa brtan pos /
NK027(sha)002:3056: 'khor ba'ang sdug bsngal las grol nas /
NK027(sha)002:3057: sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK027(sha)002:3058: de'i ched du dge tshul gyi sdom pa bla na med pa bsrung la /
NK027(sha)002:3059: sangs rgyas kyi gdong sob tu bya snyam pa'i rjes zlos mdzod byas la /
NK027(sha)002:3062: dus 'di nas bzung ste ci srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK027(sha)002:3063: rkang gnyis dam pa rnams kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:3064: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:3065: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:3066: chos la tshogs rnams kyi mkhan pos /
NK027(sha)002:3067: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK027(sha)002:3069: dge tshul du mkhan pos bzung du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:3070: ci ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi srog gcod pa spang ste /
NK027(sha)002:3071: srog gcod pa las slar du log pa de bzhin du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK027(sha)002:3075: srog gcod pa las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK027(sha)002:3076: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de'i rjes su slob bo //
NK027(sha)002:3079: gzhan yang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi
NK027(sha)002:3080: ci srid 'tsho'i bar du ma byin par len pa
NK027(sha)002:3081: dang / mi tshangs rdzun dang 'bru'i chang dang /
NK027(sha)002:3092: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
NK027(sha)002:3093: gser dngul len pa las spangs te /
NK027(sha)002:3094: gser dngul len pa las slar ldog pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:3095: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK027(sha)002:3097: ma sbyin bar len pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:3099: gser dngul len pa las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK027(sha)002:3100: yan lag phyi ma 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK027(sha)002:3101: pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su bslab
NK027(sha)002:3108: dge slong ltar bar chad bri ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:3109: 'phags pa gcig dge slong bcu dang mnyam par gsung pas /
NK027(sha)002:3110: 'phags pa sde snod 'dzin pa gcig la'ang rten du
NK027(sha)002:3111: rung mod kyi dge slong phal pas yul dbus dang
NK027(sha)002:3112: / mtha' 'khob tu lnga la gnang ba thob dgos pas /
NK027(sha)002:3113: 'dir mkhan slob dge 'dun gyi gtso sangs rgyas /
NK027(sha)002:3115: chos cho ga'i tshig rnams bka' yin pas gus par mdzod /
NK027(sha)002:3116: khyod ma 'dzem par byos la yin pa la yin par smos /
NK027(sha)002:3117: ma yin pa la ma yin par smros shig /
NK027(sha)002:3119: skyes pa'i dbang po ldan nam /
NK027(sha)002:3121: khyod bab pa nas bslab pa legs par phul lam /
NK027(sha)002:3128: ci ltar khyod rab tu byung ba yin nam /
NK027(sha)002:3132: bdag dge tshul bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong thob par smon pas /
NK027(sha)002:3135: me tog bkram la gtor zhing /
NK027(sha)002:3136: chas su bcug ste rtsa dang gding ba bzhag la mkhan pos /
NK027(sha)002:3139: dge slong mkhan slob la sogs pa dge 'dun grangs dang mtshan nyid tshang ba thams cad /
NK027(sha)002:3140: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes gsal ba la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:3141: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba /
NK027(sha)002:3142: dge slong du bzung du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:3147: de ni dkon mchog gi byin rlabs dang /
NK027(sha)002:3148: sdom pa rgyud la skye bas thams cad kyi dge
NK027(sha)002:3149: slong du gyur pa'i mos pa byas pas bskyed rim
NK027(sha)002:3150: brtan pas lhar mthong ba bzhin te /
NK027(sha)002:3151: nyer gcig pa dge slong gi bslab bya zhib tu bstan mi dgos so //
NK027(sha)002:3157: mtshang bru yang slar mi bru bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:3158: nyer gnyis pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:3159: bden bzhi dang sbyar shes dgos pas sdig pa 'khor ba'i chos rgyu kun 'byung /
NK027(sha)002:3160: de'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi skyon spang bar bya /
NK027(sha)002:3161: dge ba thar pa thob pa'i rgyu lam bsgom par bya /
NK027(sha)002:3162: 'bras bu 'gog pa'i yon tan mngon du bya zhes bstan to //
NK027(sha)002:3163: nyer gsum pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:3165: ci ltar bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa yang
NK027(sha)002:3166: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa mngon
NK027(sha)002:3170: sh+aakya'i gtso bo de rab tu byung ba'i na bza'
NK027(sha)002:3171: ngur smrig gi chos gos 'di mkhan po ngas khyod
NK027(sha)002:3172: la bskon gyi / khyod kyi 'chang shing gces pa'i tshad ni /
NK027(sha)002:3174: mi 'bral ba'i tshad ni sha dang rus pa ltar gyis la gon shog /
NK027(sha)002:3175: khyod kyi gos kyi bya ba gyis la /
NK027(sha)002:3178: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)002:3179: bcom ldan 'das kyi na bza' ngur smrig gi rgyal mtshan 'dis /
NK027(sha)002:3180: skal ldan rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3181: dbang bskur bas tshe rabs thams cad du ngo tsha khrel yod kyi gos gon te /
NK027(sha)002:3182: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3183: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3189: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i /
NK027(sha)002:3198: mdzes ma chag ma gas mi skya la /
NK027(sha)002:3200: ci ltar bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa mngon par
NK027(sha)002:3201: rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de'i zhal zas kyi bya
NK027(sha)002:3203: dge slong khyod la zas kyis snod du gtad pas /
NK027(sha)002:3204: khyod kyi zas kyis bya ba gyis shig /
NK027(sha)002:3206: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3207: bcom ldan 'das kyi mkhar sil lhung bzed kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3209: de ni ma dpe gsar rnying gnyis kar med /
NK027(sha)002:3210: ma dpe gzhan dag nang gzigs rogs zhu /
NK027(sha)002:3211: &&& gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3212: 'phags pa ma 'gags pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3213: lha'i mig mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3214: mu ne a b+hi na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3215: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3217: khyim bdag dad pa skye ba'i dbang dam pa mu ne a b+hi na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3218: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3219: 'phags pa koon+di nya'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3220: thos grol snga ba mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3221: mu ne a b+hi na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3222: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3223: 'phags pa rta thul gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3224: spyod lam mdzes pa mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par mu ne a b+hi na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3225: dkon mchog 'phags pa nye bar 'khor gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3226: 'dul ba 'dzin pa mchog gi dbang dam pa thob
NK027(sha)002:3227: par gyur cig mu a b+hi na mo dkon mchog
NK027(sha)002:3228: gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3229: 'phags pa ba glang bdag gis dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3230: 'gog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mchog gi mu ne a b+hi na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3231: dkon mchog 'phags pa 'od srung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3232: sbyangs pa'i yon tan che ba'i mchog gi dbang dam mu ne mu ne a b+hi shiny+tsa mum /
NK027(sha)002:3234: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i 'phags pa sgra gcan 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3235: bslab pa la gus pa rnams kyi mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3236: mu ne mu ne a b+hi shiny+tsa mum /
NK027(sha)002:3238: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden 'phags pa gcung dga' bos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3239: mtshan dang dpe byad mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3240: mu ne mu ne a b+hi shiny+tsa mum /
NK027(sha)002:3242: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden 'phags pa ming can gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3243: rgyal ba'i bka' la gus pa mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3244: mu ne mu ne a b+hi shiny+tsa mum /
NK027(sha)002:3245: 'phags pa nor sbyin 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3246: dbul ba sel ba mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3247: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3250: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3251: 'phags pa gang pos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3252: yon tan sbyangs pa mchog gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3253: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3255: ye d+harma de nas gnas brten chen po bcu drug gi sku thogs la /
NK027(sha)002:3257: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3259: 'phags pa gnas brtan chen po b+ha ra d+h+wa dza bsod snyoms len pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3260: rgyal ba'i bstan pa ci srid gnas kyi bar du skyongs ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:3261: dam pa'i chos kyi chab srid 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3263: mu ne mu ne a b+hi na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3264: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3265: 'phags pa gnas brtan chen po gser can gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3266: rgyal ba'i bstan pa gnas kyi bar du skyongs ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:3267: dam pa'i chos kyi chab srid 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3269: mu ne mu ne na mo /
