NK027(sha)002:3270: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3271: 'phags pa gnas brtan chen po mi phyed pas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3272: rgyal ba'i bstan pa gnas kyi bar du dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3274: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3276: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3277: 'phags pa gnas brten chen po shing kun pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3278: rgyal ba'i bstan pa gnas bar du dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3279: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3280: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3281: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po shing shun pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3282: rgyal ba'i bstan pa ci srid gnas kyi bar du skyong ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:3283: dam pa'i chos kyi chab srid 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3285: mu ne mu ne na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3286: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3287: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po bzang po pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3288: rgyal ba'i bstan pa tad+ya th+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3289: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3291: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3292: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po 'das pa dus ldan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3294: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3296: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3297: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po b+ha ra d+h+wa dza gser can gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3298: rgyal ba'i bstan pa tad+ya th+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3300: dkon mchog gsum gyi 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po ba glang skyong gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3302: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3303: dkon mchog gsum gyi 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po lam phran bstan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3306: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3308: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po sgra gcan 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3309: rgyal ba'i tad+ya th+aa mu ne mu ne ma na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3310: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3312: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po klu'i sde'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3313: rgyal ba'i bstan pa ci srid gnas kyis bar du skyong ba dang tad+ya th+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3315: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3317: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po nags su gnas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3318: rgyal ba'i bstan pa tad+ya th+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3319: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3320: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3322: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po ma pham pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3324: mu ne mu ne na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3325: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3327: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po tsun d+ha'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3329: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3330: dkon mchog gsum gyi skal ldan 'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po d+harma t+aa la'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3331: rgyal ba'i bstan pa gnas bar du mu ne mu ne ma h+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa mum /
NK027(sha)002:3333: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3335: bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3336: nyon mongs pa bag chags kyi dri ma dag pa'i
NK027(sha)002:3337: dbang dam pa mu ne mu ne ma h+aa ma
NK027(sha)002:3338: h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3340: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3343: shes bya thams cad la rtogs pa med pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3344: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3346: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3347: shing rta 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3348: 'khor lo bsgyur rgyal bdag pos dbang bskur thob nas /
NK027(sha)002:3349: gling bzhi la dbang bsgyur cing /
NK027(sha)002:3350: skye rgas na 'chi'i sdug bsngal rnams sun dbyung ba'i
NK027(sha)002:3351: dbang dam pa thob par mu ne mu ne na
NK027(sha)002:3352: mo / dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3355: rtag tu rab tu byung zhing nyon mongs pa'i 'ching
NK027(sha)002:3356: ba las grol ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK027(sha)002:3357: cig / mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3359: dkon mchog gsum gyi shan ral gri'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3360: 'khrul ba'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang mu ne mu ne na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3361: dkon mchog gsum gyi skal ldan gseg par gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3362: bdag dang 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin pa rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3363: mu ne mu ne na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3364: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3366: na bza' ngur smrig gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3367: 'khor ba'i gdung ba las skyobs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3368: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3369: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden bkra shis sbrang rtsi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3370: 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3371: mu ne mu ne na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3372: 'o thug 'bras chan gyi dbang mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3373: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3375: rtsa gding ba'i rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3376: bkra shis thob cing bar chad kyi mi tshugs pa'i
NK027(sha)002:3377: dbang dam mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne
NK027(sha)002:3378: na mo / dkon mchog gsum gyi skal ldan rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3379: de las snying po'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:3380: bdag lhar bsgom pa'i mdun gyi dkyil 'khor sangs rgyas su dmigs te /
NK027(sha)002:3381: 'od zer spro bsdu bya zhing nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad zhi bar bsam zhing /
NK027(sha)002:3382: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3385: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3387: chos sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong tshang ba'i snying po'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3388: chos thams cad kyi mdzod 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3389: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3391: bum pa'i chus kyang dbang bskur 'thung /
NK027(sha)002:3393: ye d+harma me tog gtor ro //
NK027(sha)002:3394: nyer bzhi pa ngang bsgom la gsum gyis /
NK027(sha)002:3400: 'phags lam yan lag brgyad mya ngan 'das kyi rgyur shes /
NK027(sha)002:3402: chags sdang rmongs gsum zad nas sku gsung thugs su shes /
NK027(sha)002:3403: mi dge ba shes pa ga pur ltar phan gnod med par nges pa med par shes /
NK027(sha)002:3404: chos shes pa ni sgyu ma lta bur shes /
NK027(sha)002:3406: phung khams skye mched rten 'brel sgyu ma shes /
NK027(sha)002:3408: 'khor 'das lam gyis chos thams cad kun rdzob ste thabs su shes pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3411: smon lam gyi mthu sems sogs bcu shes pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3413: lta ba rtogs pa las mtha' mtshams rtsol dran ting ste /
NK027(sha)002:3414: yang dag pa'i lta ba la gsum /
NK027(sha)002:3415: mi rtog pa'i ye shes gzhi mi 'gyur ba'i dngos grub dang /
NK027(sha)002:3416: rjes la skye ba'i ye shes /
NK027(sha)002:3418: phyi ci ma log pa'i ye shes yongs grub dang /
NK027(sha)002:3419: sprul sku ye shes 'bras bu ma dag pa'i ye shes dang /
NK027(sha)002:3420: 'bras bu dag pa'i 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes dang gsum mo //
NK027(sha)002:3421: yang dag pa'i rtogs pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:3422: ye shes gsum las yang du rtogs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3423: yang dag pa'i ngag ni sems can thams cad kyi chos dge ba bcu rtag tu smra'o //
NK027(sha)002:3424: yang dag pa'i las mtha' ni thams cad du chos dge ba bcu spyod /
NK027(sha)002:3426: 'tsho ba ni dam pa'i chos 'tsho ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:3429: ting nge 'dzin la nang du yang dag par 'jog pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3430: gnyis pa dngos gzhi ye shes ngang bsgom ni /
NK027(sha)002:3431: de nas dbang brtan pa'i phyir gsal gdab ni /
NK027(sha)002:3432: rang gi dpral bar rus pa'i thig le yungs kar tsam gcig bsgom /
NK027(sha)002:3433: de las shes pa gtad pas theg le je cher 'phel /
NK027(sha)002:3434: snang srid thams cad keng rus pa'i dal du bsam /
NK027(sha)002:3435: de yang yul rang rgyud pa la brten nas chags
NK027(sha)002:3436: sdang rmongs gsum skye bas nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i
NK027(sha)002:3437: rgyu yin / des 'bras bu sdug bsngal myong ba yin /
NK027(sha)002:3438: de'i gnyen por yul mi sdug pa bsgom pas chags sdang mi dge ba kun 'byung /
NK027(sha)002:3439: nyon mongs pa rtsa ba bcad pas 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin 'gag /
NK027(sha)002:3440: de 'gog pa dang lam bden pa yin no //
NK027(sha)002:3441: de las lam khyer bzhi las /
NK027(sha)002:3442: theg pa lam khyer ni nyan thos kyi theg pa /
NK027(sha)002:3443: de la dang po 'jug sgo ni /
NK027(sha)002:3448: de dag dbye na bden chung bcu drug de ni /
NK027(sha)002:3449: spang byed ye shes bcu drug /
NK027(sha)002:3452: sdug bsngal gyi bden pa bzhi 'khor ba'i 'bras bu shes nas spong /
NK027(sha)002:3453: 'gog pa ni bden pa 'das pa'i rgyu /
NK027(sha)002:3454: lam gyi bden pa 'das pa'i 'bras bur shes nas bsgrub /
NK027(sha)002:3455: de la phye na bden chung bcu drug ste /
NK027(sha)002:3469: de dag spong byed ye shes bcu drug ste /
NK027(sha)002:3470: dang po kun 'byung la shes pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:3471: kun 'byung shes pa'i chos shes pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:3473: bzod pa la shes pa'i chos shes pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3475: gnyis pa ni de'i don la mi skrag pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3477: bzhi pa nges pa'i don la mi skrag pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3479: de'ang rigs brgyad dbye ba las /
NK027(sha)002:3480: bden bzhi'i don rtogs rab tu spangs byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:3481: ye shes bcu drug rab tu sbyangs byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:3482: rgyun zhugs la sogs rim pas sbyangs nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:3483: nyon mongs dgra bcom zhi ba'i sa ru 'gro //
NK027(sha)002:3485: lta ba gang zag gi bdag med rtogs /
NK027(sha)002:3486: chos kyi bdag dang bcas pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3487: gang zag gi bdag la gnyis las /
NK027(sha)002:3488: rang bzhin lhan skyes gang zag gi bdag dang /
NK027(sha)002:3489: ched du byas pa'i gang zag gi bdag go //
NK027(sha)002:3491: phung po lnga'i rgyu la bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin /
NK027(sha)002:3492: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i bdag ces bya /
NK027(sha)002:3494: de las brten nas mu stegs lha rnams 'jug pa
NK027(sha)002:3495: so so skye bo phung po lnga'i rgyu rkyen las
NK027(sha)002:3496: rnam par ma phyes te bdag tu 'dzin pa dang
NK027(sha)002:3497: / de la brten nas mu stegs kyi phyin ci
NK027(sha)002:3498: log tu brtags pa'i bdag rang bzhin med par rtogs
NK027(sha)002:3499: / pa'o // gnyis pa chos kyi bdag la gnyis /
NK027(sha)002:3501: gzung yul la bdag ma grub ste /
NK027(sha)002:3502: rang bzhin med pa yin kyang nyan thos blo chung
NK027(sha)002:3503: bas mu stegs chad pa gol gyi dogs nas rdul
NK027(sha)002:3505: de las mdo sde ba dang bye brag pa gnyis
NK027(sha)002:3506: rdul gyis 'dus lugs tsam tshul ma ni mthun te
NK027(sha)002:3507: / mdo sde pas po ti'i shog bu'am 'bru'i phung po ltar reg la ma 'byar bar 'dod /
NK027(sha)002:3508: bye brag pas g.yag rnga'am ne'u seng ltar bskor ba bar bcas su 'dod /
NK027(sha)002:3510: 'di ltar snang ba 'di ni sgyu ma tsam //
NK027(sha)002:3511: yang dag nyid na yod pa ma yin te //
NK027(sha)002:3512: shin tu chad ltar gyur na mi rung bas //
NK027(sha)002:3513: nyan thos byis pa rnams la ngas ma bstan //
NK027(sha)002:3515: nang 'dzin pa'i sems la bdag ma grub ste /
NK027(sha)002:3516: kun gzhi mtha' bral du gnas pa yin kyang /
NK027(sha)002:3517: nyan thos pa blo chung bas kun gzhi gsang ste /
NK027(sha)002:3518: skad cig ma skye 'gag dang bcas par 'dod ces bcom ldan 'das kyi gsung ste /
NK027(sha)002:3519: de'ang len pa'i rnam par shes pa zab cing phra /
NK027(sha)002:3520: sa bon thams cad chu bo'i rgyun bzhin 'bab /
NK027(sha)002:3521: bdag tu rtogs par gyur na mi rung ngo zhes /
NK027(sha)002:3522: nyan thos byis pa rnams la ngas ma bstan /
NK027(sha)002:3524: gzung yul phyi rol rdul du grub //
NK027(sha)002:3525: 'dzin pa'i shes pa skad cig ma //
NK027(sha)002:3526: bden pa bzhi la nges pa'i rten can ces //
NK027(sha)002:3529: phyi rol rdul la rtsod byed cing /
NK027(sha)002:3531: bsrung ba'i tshul khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu bsrung ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:3533: blo rab kun 'byung spyi 'khor ba'i rgyur shes na 'dod chags kyi gnyen por mi sdug pa sogs /
NK027(sha)002:3534: gnyen po sgo drug gi sgo nas tshogs drug bkag nas 'gog pa snyoms par 'jug go //
NK027(sha)002:3535: spyod pa ni sems bskyed rgya chung bas spyod pa
NK027(sha)002:3536: gzhan don spyad kyang rang don la dmigs pas gzhan
NK027(sha)002:3537: phan snying rje ma 'byung bar 'dod do //
NK027(sha)002:3539: spyod pa rkyal mkhan rang thar 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3541: 'bras bu ni skyes bu zung bzhi gang zag ya brgyad do //
NK027(sha)002:3542: lha lam khyer ni dus gsum sangs rgyas sam bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa bsgom pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3543: snying po mu ne bzlas pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3544: 'dug tshul ni blo pheb pa dang sdug gtam btang ba lta bu'o //
NK027(sha)002:3545: bslab bya lam khyer mi dge bcu spong /
NK027(sha)002:3546: dgra dang nyon mongs pa tsher ma ltar spong /
NK027(sha)002:3547: dge bcu sman dang kha zas ltar len /
NK027(sha)002:3548: de'ang thun mong du 'du shes bcu ste /
NK027(sha)002:3549: srog gcod pa la btsan dug lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3550: gos la rma dkris lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3551: nyon mongs pa la dug sbrul lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3552: kha zas la rgan rgon bu sha za ba lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3553: bsnyen bkur la rgya dang rnyi lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3554: bla ma dkon mchog la nor bu rin po che lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3555: chos la lam bzang po lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3556: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gser lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3557: tshul khrims la rgyan lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK027(sha)002:3558: chos nyid mngon du gyur pa la mun khang du
NK027(sha)002:3559: sgron me bteg pa lta bu'i 'du shes dang bcu'o
NK027(sha)002:3560: // de dag dbang rdo rje zam pa las gsungs /
NK027(sha)002:3562: gnas wa ra na si'i bsil khang /
NK027(sha)002:3564: 'khor mchog brgyad dam bcu drug sogs /
NK027(sha)002:3565: chos bden bzhi nyan thos kyi theg pa /
NK027(sha)002:3566: dgos mu stegs rtags chad rang rgyud par 'dod pa las grol ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:3567: gang du gang gi gang la bstan /
NK027(sha)002:3568: ci'i phyir dgos pa bcas pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:3571: de nas slar yang mchod gshegs /
NK027(sha)002:3573: bla ma la yon phul la /
NK027(sha)002:3574: de nas me tog bkram la /
NK027(sha)002:3576: bcom ldan rnam par gzigs ni rgyal rigs gzi brjid can //
NK027(sha)002:3577: tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus na grong khyer gnyen drung du /
NK027(sha)002:3578: po ta la yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i /
NK027(sha)002:3579: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:3580: bde gshegs gtsug tor can ni rgyal rigs rdzu 'phrul can //
NK027(sha)002:3581: tshe lo bdun khri'i dus na ka ni'i grong khyer du //
NK027(sha)002:3582: pun+da ri ka'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:3583: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:3584: rgyal ba thams cad skyobs ni rgyal rigs blo gros can //
NK027(sha)002:3585: tshe lo drug khri'i dus na grong khyer mnyan yod du //
NK027(sha)002:3586: shing mchog s+aa la'i drung du mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:3587: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:3588: thub pa 'khor ba 'jigs ni stobs ldan bram ze'i rigs //
NK027(sha)002:3589: tshe lo bzhi khri'i dus na grong khyer bde ldan du //
NK027(sha)002:3590: shi ri sha'i drung du mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:3591: bkra shis phun sum 'dren pa gser thub bslab pa mchog ldan bram ze'i rigs /
NK027(sha)002:3592: tshe lo sum khri'i dus na grong khyer mdzes ldan du /
NK027(sha)002:3593: u dum wa ri'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i /
NK027(sha)002:3594: bkra shis phun sum skyobs pa 'od srung bram ze bla med yon tan can /
NK027(sha)002:3595: tshe lo nyis khri'i dus na wa ra na si ru /
NK027(sha)002:3596: nya gro d+ha'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i /
NK027(sha)002:3597: bkra shis 'gro mgon sh+aakya thub pa rgyal rigs brtson 'grus can //
NK027(sha)002:3598: tshe lo brgya pa'i dus na ser skya'i grong khyer du //
NK027(sha)002:3599: a sho ta'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:3600: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:3601: ces brjod pas me tog gtor /
NK027(sha)002:3603: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo'o //
NK027(sha)002:3604: nyan thos kyi theg pa 'grig rim mo //
NK027(sha)002:3605: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'i bsgrub khrig las /
NK027(sha)002:3606: dkyil 'khor bshams khung mchod pa bshams //
NK027(sha)002:3607: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK027(sha)002:3608: dpang kong khrus bya sdom brtan khri //
NK027(sha)002:3609: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzeg ston pa bsgom //
NK027(sha)002:3610: gsol gdab sdom pa bslab bya 'bog /
NK027(sha)002:3611: dka' thub ldan pa'i bum dbang lha //
NK027(sha)002:3612: bkra shis khrim chas drang srong lha //
NK027(sha)002:3613: chos bshad dbang bskur lam khyer bzhi //
NK027(sha)002:3614: theg pa lha snying bslab bya dang //
NK027(sha)002:3615: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //
NK027(sha)002:3617: gdams ngag ngang bsgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK027(sha)002:3619: dang po dkyil 'khor la yongs rdzogs las 'byung ba
NK027(sha)002:3620: lnga ri rab gcig tu 'dres pa'i gzhal yas khang
NK027(sha)002:3622: rdo rjes rwa ba gzugs khams /
NK027(sha)002:3626: rang rgyal rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni /
NK027(sha)002:3627: bswe ru la dbus gru bzhi rked nyag /
NK027(sha)002:3628: de'i phyir 'dab ma bcu gnyis ni /
NK027(sha)002:3629: gtso bo'i chung ba las pad+ma 'dab bzhi //
NK027(sha)002:3631: tshogs spyod che 'bring la rang brgyud pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:3632: sprul pa'i 'dab ma bcu pa gnyis so //
NK027(sha)002:3633: thams cad kyi lte ba ser /
NK027(sha)002:3636: sgo rta bab sogs spyi dang 'dra /
NK027(sha)002:3637: phyi'i khyams su dpag bsam shing /
NK027(sha)002:3638: rtsa ba myu gu sdong bu /
NK027(sha)002:3642: nam mkha' rlung me chu sa /
NK027(sha)002:3645: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi mtshan ma dgod do //
NK027(sha)002:3648: rten 'brel don la brten gnas pa'i /
NK027(sha)002:3649: 'phags pa rang rgyal bcu gnyis ni //
NK027(sha)002:3650: 'byung dang ldog la rab zhugs pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:3654: bum pa la keng rus kyi mtshan ma bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:3656: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi dri bzang gi byug par bum
NK027(sha)002:3657: pa mgul ching kha rgyan gzung thag bum rdzas 'bru
NK027(sha)002:3658: chus bkang ba'i gzungs thag drang zhing mchod pa bsang
NK027(sha)002:3659: sbyang / byin rlabs skyabs 'gro bdag nyid tshad med pa bzhi bsgom /
NK027(sha)002:3660: tsan dan dkar po brdar ba'i snag tshas me long la rten 'brel snying po tshar bdun bri /
NK027(sha)002:3661: tshar re zhing lan bdun bdun bzlas te /
NK027(sha)002:3663: der zla ba la sngags phreng dkar po las 'od 'phros pas /
NK027(sha)002:3664: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du zhu /
NK027(sha)002:3665: tshur 'dus bum par thim par bsgom zhing /
NK027(sha)002:3666: lag pa g.yas pas bum pa la bkab ste sngags brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas so //
NK027(sha)002:3667: de nas me long chus bkru nas bum par blug /
NK027(sha)002:3668: yang sngags phreng gi 'od kyi phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' nyan thos spyan drangs te /
NK027(sha)002:3669: rten dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha la thim par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:3670: de nas lugs sku la sogs la dngos su khrus gsol /
NK027(sha)002:3671: ras bris po ti sogs la me long gi ngos
NK027(sha)002:3672: la khrus gsol la de'i chus mchod rdzas thams cad
NK027(sha)002:3673: la gtor te / ma dag pa sbyangs /
NK027(sha)002:3674: kha dog dri ro nus pa phun sum tshogs par bsam zhing sngags bzlas pas byin gyis brlabs so //
NK027(sha)002:3678: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK027(sha)002:3679: dkon mchog bla med rin chen gsum //
NK027(sha)002:3681: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK027(sha)002:3682: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:3683: ye d+har+m+aa he tu pra b+ha w+aa he tun te
NK027(sha)002:3684: shan ta th+aa ga to h+ya wa dad te sh+aan
NK027(sha)002:3685: tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma
NK027(sha)002:3686: h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3688: gnas mchog pho brang gzhal yas 'dir //
NK027(sha)002:3689: rin chen pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK027(sha)002:3690: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:3691: ye d+har+m+aa rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:3692: dkon mchog bla med rin chen gsum //
NK027(sha)002:3693: sku ni rten cing 'brel ba'i sku //
NK027(sha)002:3695: thugs ni rten 'brel thams cad mkhyen //
NK027(sha)002:3696: sku gsung thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:3697: ye rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:3698: lha rdzas dam pa'i mchod yon 'di //
NK027(sha)002:3699: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:3701: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK027(sha)002:3702: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:3703: ye d+har+m+aa he du pra b+ha rten cing 'brel bar lha rdzas dam pa'i bdug spos 'di //
NK027(sha)002:3704: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:3706: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK027(sha)002:3707: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:3708: ye d+har+m+aa rten cing 'brel bar lha rdzas dam pa'i me tog 'di //
NK027(sha)002:3709: bla med dkon mchog rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:3710: 'gro ba sems can don thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes
NK027(sha)002:3711: ye d+har+m+aa rten cing 'brel bar lha rdzas dam pa'i
NK027(sha)002:3712: mar me 'di // bla med dkon mchog rten cing
NK027(sha)002:3713: 'brel 'gro ba sems can thugs rjes dgongs te ye
NK027(sha)002:3714: rten cing 'brel lha rdzas dam pa'i dri mchog 'di
NK027(sha)002:3715: mar me 'di // // bla med dkon mchog rten
NK027(sha)002:3716: cing 'brel bar 'gro ba sems can don thugs rjes
NK027(sha)002:3717: ye d+har+m+aa he du pra rten cing 'brel bar lha
NK027(sha)002:3719: bla med dkon mchog rten cing 'brel bar 'gro ba
NK027(sha)002:3720: sems can thugs rjes dgongs ye d+har+m+aa rten cing 'brel
NK027(sha)002:3721: lha rdzas dam pa'i rol mo 'di //
NK027(sha)002:3722: bla med dkon mchog rten cing 'brel bar 'gro ba
NK027(sha)002:3723: sems can thugs rjes dgongs ye rten cing 'brel bar
NK027(sha)002:3724: rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK027(sha)002:3725: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK027(sha)002:3726: ci srid cho ga ma grub bar //
NK027(sha)002:3727: thugs rjes dgongs te mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK027(sha)002:3728: ye d+har+m+aa rgyal ba dgra rgyal bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)002:3729: bden pa gsung pa de la sdig med cing //
NK027(sha)002:3730: lhar bcas lha min gyis ni rtag mchod cing //
NK027(sha)002:3731: bden pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:3732: ye d+har+m+aa dam chos bdud rtsi thams cad mkhyen pa yis //
NK027(sha)002:3733: zhal nas gsung pa bsil ba'i ro 'di yi //
NK027(sha)002:3734: nyon mongs 'bar ba me yi gdung ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:3735: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal rtag tu zhi byed shog /
NK027(sha)002:3736: ye d+har+m+aa 'byung po gang dag 'di ni lhag gyur te //
NK027(sha)002:3740: ye d+har+m+aa he du pra b+ha w+aa he dun te
NK027(sha)002:3741: sh+aan ta th+aa ga to h+ya ba dad te sh+aan
NK027(sha)002:3742: tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam wa d+ai ma
NK027(sha)002:3743: h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3744: zhes pas me tog thams cad du gtor ro //
NK027(sha)002:3754: bcu bzhi pa sdom pa yan chad nyan thos dang mthun no //
NK027(sha)002:3755: bac+wo lnga pa bslab bya ni /
NK027(sha)002:3756: bzod 'bring yan chad nyan thos ltar //
NK027(sha)002:3757: 'bring na nyan rang so sor dbye ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:3758: bcu drug pa bum dbang ni /
NK027(sha)002:3759: dka' thub shor nas rdzu 'phrul nyams 'gro ba ltar /
NK027(sha)002:3760: dka' thub dang ldan pas dbang bskur dgos pa'i phyir /
NK027(sha)002:3766: drang srong gi brtul zhugs smra bcad dang rdzu 'phrul lo //
NK027(sha)002:3767: bac+wo brgyad pa khrims chas ni rab byung yin yang snam sbyar dang 'khar gsil med do //
NK027(sha)002:3768: bcu dgu pa lha ni kun gyi gtso bo thub pa yin la /
NK027(sha)002:3769: rang rgyal rnams kyang bslab sbyangs mthar phyin pas /
NK027(sha)002:3770: smon pa yid bzhin 'grub cing blo che chung gi bse ru ne tso gnyis su 'byung la /
NK027(sha)002:3771: ye shes gcig pas gtso bo gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3772: rten 'brel la rigs mang yang gtso bo bcu gnyis su 'dus pas /
NK027(sha)002:3773: grangs bcu gnyis su nges pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3774: nyi shu pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:3775: brjod pa sgrar bcas rnam g.yeng gi skyon rig pas smra ba bcad de brda'i chos ston pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3776: nyer gcig pa dbang bskur ba ni rdzas dang /
NK027(sha)002:3777: lha dbang rim par thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:3778: gyur shog dang ye d+har+m+aa thams cad kyi brjod par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:3780: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3781: rigs kyi bu la bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3782: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags thams cad byang zhing dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3783: ye d+har+m+aa he du pra b+ha w+aa he dun te
NK027(sha)002:3784: shan ta th+aa ga to h+yo wa dad te sh+aan
NK027(sha)002:3785: tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+ha ti ma
NK027(sha)002:3786: h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:3788: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3789: rigs kyi bu la ming gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3790: shes bya la ma rmongs pa rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3792: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:3793: shan ral gri'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3794: 'khrul ba'i d+r+wa ba thams cad gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3796: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:3797: na bza' ngur smrig gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3798: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba las skyob pa'i dbang dam pa ye na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3799: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam gsum rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:3800: bkra shis pa'i sbrang rtsis dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3801: mthu phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3803: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:3804: rtsa gding ba'i rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3805: bkra shis shing bar chad gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3806: ye d+har+m+aa rten 'brel skye mched bcu gnyis ni /
NK027(sha)002:3807: ma rig rgan mo long ma 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3808: lugs 'byung lugs ldog mngon gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:3809: yid bzhin bde mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:3810: ye 'du byed rdza ma mkhan po 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3811: lugs 'byung lugs ldog yid bzhin bde mchog ye rnam par shes pa sprel dang 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3812: lugs 'byung yid bzhin ye d+har+m+aa ming dang gzugs ni gru dang 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3813: lugs 'byung lugs ldog yid bzhin bde mchog ye skye mched cig char grong lta bu //
NK027(sha)002:3814: lugs 'byung lugs yid bzhin bde ye d+har+m+aa reg pa 'o byed nang gi nang //
NK027(sha)002:3815: lug 'byung lugs bzlog yid bzhin bde mchog ye d+har+m+aa tshor ba pus mo mda' zug 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3816: lug 'byung yid bzhin bde mchog ye sreg pa 'o thug 'thung ba 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3817: lugs 'byung yid bzhin bde ye d+har+m+aa len pa me tog thu ba 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3818: lugs 'byung yid bzhin bde ye d+har+m+aa srid pa sbrum ma bu skye 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3819: lugs 'byung lugs ldog mngon gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:3820: yid bzhin bde mchog ye d+har+m+aa skye ba na chung gzhon nu 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3821: lugs 'byung yid bzhin ye d+har+m+aa he rga shi rgud dang shi ba 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3822: lugs 'byung yid bzhin ye d+har+m+aa mkha' rlung me chus sa khams lnga //
NK027(sha)002:3823: dus kyi 'gyur dang drug phyi nang //
NK027(sha)002:3824: rgyu dang 'brel ba drug ces bya //
NK027(sha)002:3825: lugs 'byung yid bzhin ye d+har+m+aa sa bon myu gu sdong po 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:3826: lo ma me tog 'bras bu drug /
NK027(sha)002:3827: dpag bsam shing dang rten 'brel te //
NK027(sha)002:3828: lugs 'byung yid bzhin ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3829: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam pa gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3832: bswe ru dang ni ne tso lta bu yi //
NK027(sha)002:3833: 'bras bu la sogs phyi'i rten 'brel dang //
NK027(sha)002:3834: ma rig la sogs nang gi rten 'brel dang //
NK027(sha)002:3835: lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spang bya shing //
NK027(sha)002:3836: lugs ldog 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras rab bsgrub nas //
NK027(sha)002:3837: 'jig rten pa dang nyan thos rang sa drug /
NK027(sha)002:3838: 'das nas rang sangs rgyas sar phyin par shog /
NK027(sha)002:3839: ye d+har+m+aa he du a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:3840: rigs kyi bu khyod la rten 'brel gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3841: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3843: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam pa gsum gyis bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3845: bcom ldan 'das gtso bo'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3846: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:3848: phyogs bcu dus gsum rigs kyi bu la /
NK027(sha)002:3849: rang rgyal bse ru dang ne tso lta bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3850: gcig pur bsam gtan la gnas pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:3851: tshogs spyod kyi grogs la bsten nas /
NK027(sha)002:3853: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3855: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam pa gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3857: rang sangs rgyas rdo rje 'jigs byed /
NK027(sha)002:3858: rdo rje rtse dgu pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3859: 'khor ba bsreg par byed pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa he du na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3860: phyogs bcu dus gsum rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3861: rang sangs rgyas snang ba brtsegs pa rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3862: ting nge 'dzin rab tu snang ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3864: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam pa gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3866: rang sangs rgyas dpa' bo 'dul ba'i rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3867: srid pa bsnyil ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3869: phyogs bcu dus gsum rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3870: rang sangs rgyas gdung ba sel bas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3871: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3873: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin chen rnam par gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:3875: rang sangs rgyas shes rab mgyogs chen gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3876: shes rab rtsal dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3877: phyogs bcu dus gsum rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3878: rang sangs rgyas rdzu 'phrul cher ston gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3879: sprul pa'i cho 'phrul dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3880: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3881: rang sangs rgyas smra ba'i sgra chen gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3882: gsung gi dbang phyug gi dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3883: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3884: rang sangs rgyas bswe ru lta bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3885: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig tu gyur pa'i dbang dam ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3886: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3887: rang sangs rgyas ri'i rgyal po'i dbang pos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3888: 'khor ba'i rlung gi mi bskyod pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3889: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:3890: rang sangs rgyas seng ge lta bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3891: 'jigs pa thams cad bral ba'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK027(sha)002:3892: phyogs bcu dus gsum rigs sangs rgyas yid myur ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:3893: ting nge 'dzin rdzu 'phrul myur ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:3894: ye d+harma he du pra b+ha wa ces pas dbang bskur te /
NK027(sha)002:3895: slar yang bum pas dbang bskur khrus bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:3896: nyer gnyis pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK027(sha)002:3897: gtso bo sh+aakya thub pa ser po sa gnon mnyam bzhag dang /
NK027(sha)002:3898: g.yas g.yon bswe ru ne tso rab byung gi tshul thal mo sbyar ba /
NK027(sha)002:3902: dpa' bo 'dul ba rdo rje rtse lnga /
NK027(sha)002:3903: nyon mongs gdung sel bsil yab /
NK027(sha)002:3904: shes rab mgyogs can zla tshes /
NK027(sha)002:3908: bswe ru lta bu mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:3909: ri rgyal rin chen snye ma /
NK027(sha)002:3910: seng ge lta bu rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:3911: yid myur rnga yab bsnams pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:3912: nyer gsum pa snying po ni /
NK027(sha)002:3914: nyer bzhi pa dbang lam khyer ni /
NK027(sha)002:3915: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:3916: nyer lnga pa theg pa rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:3917: de la 'jug sgo phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis /
NK027(sha)002:3918: de'ang rdzas g.yung drung shug pa'i 'bras bu las shes te /
NK027(sha)002:3919: 'bras bu de ci las byung brtags pas /
NK027(sha)002:3923: de sa bon la thugs te rgyu dang 'brel ba drug go //
NK027(sha)002:3930: dus kyis mi rtag par gyur nas 'byung bar shes te phyi'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis so //
NK027(sha)002:3931: phra ba bag chags kyi tshul du 'khor bar 'dod /
NK027(sha)002:3932: de'ang nyan thos bye brag pa'i tshogs lam pa dang
NK027(sha)002:3933: mnyam par sbyangs nas sbyor lam bzod 'bring nas rig
NK027(sha)002:3934: byed / shes rab che bas dur khrod du phyin te keng rus kyi phung po la brtags pas /
NK027(sha)002:3935: shi ba las byung ba shes /
NK027(sha)002:3946: de ma rigs pa las gang byung brtags pas ma
NK027(sha)002:3947: rnyed de stong par rtogs pas thams cad stong nyid
NK027(sha)002:3948: du shes te / rga shi nas lugs ldog tu
NK027(sha)002:3949: rten 'brel bcu gnyis bkag shul du stong nyid re
NK027(sha)002:3952: rgyu snga ma la brten nas 'bras bu phyi ma
NK027(sha)002:3953: 'byung ba la ma rig pa nas rga shi'i bar
NK027(sha)002:3954: brtags pas 'a gro ba'i rgyur shes so //
NK027(sha)002:3956: dang po brgyad dang dgu nyon mongs //
NK027(sha)002:3957: gnyis pa bcu pa las yin te //
NK027(sha)002:3958: lhag ma bdun gyi sdug bsngal lo //
NK027(sha)002:3961: dang po brgyad dang dgu pa rgyu //
NK027(sha)002:3962: gnyis pa bcu pa rkyen yin no //
NK027(sha)002:3965: de'ang tshe dum bu gsum dang /
NK027(sha)002:3966: rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum dang 'phel 'grib yan lag lngar 'dod de /
NK027(sha)002:3967: nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis po dngos su 'khor ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:3969: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig yor tshul shes nas //
NK027(sha)002:3970: dngos po gzugs la thogs pa med par 'jug /
NK027(sha)002:3971: dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtogs //
NK027(sha)002:3973: nyer drug pa lta ba gang zag gi bdag med
NK027(sha)002:3974: rtogs pa'i steng du chos kyis bdag phyogs gcig pa
NK027(sha)002:3975: la bdag med par rtogs pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:3976: de gzung yul dang 'dzin sems gnyis las /
NK027(sha)002:3977: gzung yul rdul phran rang bzhin med par stong pa nyid du rtogs /
NK027(sha)002:3978: 'dzin pa'i shes pa skad cig ma skye 'gag dang bcas pa nyan thos ltar 'dod /
NK027(sha)002:3979: dri med lung bstan pa las /
NK027(sha)002:3980: 'dzin pa'i sems ni ma spang ste //
NK027(sha)002:3981: gzung bya'i yul ni rnam rtog bcom //
NK027(sha)002:3982: rang sangs rgyas kyi lta ba ste //
NK027(sha)002:3983: nyan thos pa las khyad phar 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:3985: nyer bdun pa bsrung bya tshul khrims ni /
NK027(sha)002:3987: nyer brgyad pa ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK027(sha)002:3988: rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs ldog tu bsgom ste /
NK027(sha)002:3990: ma rig pa dang sred len gsum //
NK027(sha)002:3991: snga ma'i dus te rgyu ru 'dod //
NK027(sha)002:3992: 'du byed dang ni srid pa gnyis //
NK027(sha)002:3993: da lta'i dus kyi rkyen du 'dod //
NK027(sha)002:3994: rnam shes ming dang skye mched drug /
NK027(sha)002:3995: reg pa dang ni tshor ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:3996: skye ba rga shi bdun po ni //
NK027(sha)002:3998: nyer dgu pa spyod pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:3999: stod nas me 'bar smad nas chu 'brub /
NK027(sha)002:4000: bar na rlung g.yo ba sogs rdzu 'phrul ya ma zung bstan nas /
NK027(sha)002:4001: rigs mthun du don mdzad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:4003: ngag gi rdo rje yi ge med //
NK027(sha)002:4004: lus kyi rdo rje snang byas nas //
NK027(sha)002:4005: brjod med spul pa'i chos ston pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:4008: rang sangs rgyas kyi dgra bcom pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:4010: gnas ri bo bya rkang can /
NK027(sha)002:4014: dgos pa lugs 'byung lugs ldog gi 'khor 'das dbyer med du rtogs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:4016: dbang de chags shing brtan pa'i phyir ngang bsgom gdams ngag gsal gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:4017: rang gi spyo bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam gcig bsam /
NK027(sha)002:4018: de las khru gang gis mtho bar dkar po sran ma tsam zhig bsam /
NK027(sha)002:4019: thig le dmar po de la shes pa gtad pas je cher 'phel /
NK027(sha)002:4020: snang srid thams cad dmar lam gyi song bar bsam /
NK027(sha)002:4021: dmar po de chags pa'i rang bzhin lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos so //
NK027(sha)002:4022: yang dkar po la shes pa gtad pas je cher snang srid dkar lam gyi song bar bsam /
NK027(sha)002:4023: de lugs ldog mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos yin /
NK027(sha)002:4024: dkar dmar gnyis po de 'dres nas spyi bo nas mar bab /
NK027(sha)002:4025: snying gi dkyil du thim nas rang gi sems dang
NK027(sha)002:4026: dbyer med du 'dres nas 'khor 'das gnyis med ngang
NK027(sha)002:4027: du bzhag go // so gsum pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:4030: dkyil 'khor bsdu ste mi rtog pa bsgom mo //
NK027(sha)002:4032: de nas me tog so sor bkram ste /
NK027(sha)002:4033: rol mo sgra dang bcas pas /
NK027(sha)002:4034: shin tu brgal dka' 'khor ba'i mtsho las brgal //
NK027(sha)002:4035: bsod nams ye shes dpag med tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:4036: 'gro ba kun gya gnyen gcig de bzhin gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:4037: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:4038: skye rgas na 'chi rtag tu mtha' dag spangs //
NK027(sha)002:4039: ma rigs mun pa 'joms pa'i sgron me mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4040: dmigs pa'i mtha' spangs lam gyi bde 'gror bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:4041: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:4042: rang don spang zhing gzhan don lhur len pa //
NK027(sha)002:4043: 'dod pa'i yon tan lta bas rgyang bsring ste //
NK027(sha)002:4044: dad dang brtson 'grus grogs mchog byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)002:4045: bkra shis des kyang snyigs dus smon lam dbang gi sku sprul nas //
NK027(sha)002:4046: shin tu nyon mongs gdul dka' 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:4047: thabs mkhas thugs rje che mnga' rkang gnyis gtso //
NK027(sha)002:4048: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:4051: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:4052: de ni rang rgyal gyi cho ga'o //
NK027(sha)002:4053: byang chub sems dpa'i las khrig las /
NK027(sha)002:4054: dal mchod bshams dang lha tshogs bskyed //
NK027(sha)002:4055: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum btang //
NK027(sha)002:4056: spang skong khrus bya sdom rten khri //
NK027(sha)002:4057: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzegs ston pa bsgom //
NK027(sha)002:4058: gsol btab sdom pa bslab bya 'bog /
NK027(sha)002:4059: chos bshad dbang bskur lam khyer bzhi //
NK027(sha)002:4060: theg pa lha snying bslab bya la'ang //
NK027(sha)002:4061: theg dag lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //
NK027(sha)002:4063: gdams ngag ngang bsgom bkra shis brjod //
NK027(sha)002:4065: dang po dal gyis mtshams ri rab kyi kha khyer mu tig dang nor bu bkram pa'i brag /
NK027(sha)002:4066: gnyis pa bsgom pa'i rta babs bang rim bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:4067: gsum pa bri ba ni dkyil 'khor bcu ste /
NK027(sha)002:4068: pad+ma 'dam ma bzhi pa gnyis dang /
NK027(sha)002:4070: nang 'dab bzhi pa lha snam can gnyis dang /
NK027(sha)002:4072: phyir 'khor lo rtsib bcur pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi bzhi gru chad lha snam can gnyis dang /
NK027(sha)002:4073: nang 'dab brgyad phyi lho byang drang po'i rtsib drug la 'dab brgyad pa re re ste /
NK027(sha)002:4074: gru chad lha snam can dang /
NK027(sha)002:4075: nang 'dab brgyad kyi phyir yang 'dab brgyad che ba'i nang du 'dab brgyad re re ste /
NK027(sha)002:4076: shar nub tu gnyis gnyis so //
NK027(sha)002:4082: gru chad lha rnams phyogs mdog /
NK027(sha)002:4083: sgo rta babs 'khor yug la sogs phyogs spyi dang mthun no //
NK027(sha)002:4084: gnyis pa mchod pa bshams pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:4086: me tog la sogs rol mo sta gon bya /
NK027(sha)002:4087: bum pa mgul ching sogs dang mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang rdzas cha gsum la sogs pa bsham mo //
NK027(sha)002:4088: gsum pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:4089: rang nyid skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4090: sems bskyed pa byas nas phyag 'tshal mchod pa 'bul /
NK027(sha)002:4092: dge ba rjes su yi rangs ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4093: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:4094: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4095: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngosa te /
NK027(sha)002:4096: bsod nams kyi tshogs bsag go //
NK027(sha)002:4098: swa b+ha wa shud+d+ho sarba d+harma swa b+ha wa shud+d+ho&a ha /
NK027(sha)002:4100: bdag dang snang ba thams cad stong par bsam //
NK027(sha)002:4101: de'i ngang las rdor sems su mos pa'i snying khar h'u /
NK027(sha)002:4102: de las e yam ram lam sum chad pa las
NK027(sha)002:4103: nam mkha' rlung me chu sa ri rab kyi steng
NK027(sha)002:4104: du / b+h+r+au rat+na bi shwa b+hi shud+d+he man+dala /
NK027(sha)002:4106: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas
NK027(sha)002:4107: gsal dwangs sgrib g.yogs med pa'i dbus su rin po
NK027(sha)002:4108: che'i khri / nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la mum las thub pa ser po sa gnon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4109: shar du pam las yum chen mo ser mo mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4112: lhor h'u las phyag na rdo rje sngon po g.yas rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:4114: nub tu mam las sha ri'i bu ser po mkhar bsil lhung bzed can /
NK027(sha)002:4115: byang du h+r+aihls spyan ras gzigs dkar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK027(sha)002:4117: de dag gi snying po rim pa bzhin mu ne dang /
NK027(sha)002:4118: di pra b+ha wa ye ya ti dud pra ti
NK027(sha)002:4119: dud pra ni b+hi shud+d+he b+h+ya d+har+m+aa d+h+aar tu b+ha
NK027(sha)002:4120: ga wan dzahmh'u bam hoh a la la ho /
NK027(sha)002:4121: a mri a ra hi dza h'u /
NK027(sha)002:4122: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:4123: na mahs man+ta b+hud+d+h+aa n+aam b+ha ga wan pra sa
NK027(sha)002:4124: ta th+aa ga ta b+hi sha ya swa b+h+aa wa
NK027(sha)002:4125: s+w+aa h+aa / sarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa
NK027(sha)002:4126: lo ki te ka ru nam ma ra ya badz+ra
NK027(sha)002:4127: s+w+aa h+aa / s+w+aa h+aa / zhes pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:4128: yang yum dang thub pa gnas barjesa pas dkyil 'khor gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK027(sha)002:4130: dbus dang phyogs bcur a sing a hri las /
NK027(sha)002:4131: rin po che'i khri nyi zla'i gdan re las /
NK027(sha)002:4132: dbus su yum chen dkar mo g.yas mchod sbyin /
NK027(sha)002:4133: g.yon pad+ma po ti'i mtshan pa /
NK027(sha)002:4134: shar du sangs rgyas dkon mchog 'byung gnas dkar po /
NK027(sha)002:4137: lhor mya ngan med pa sngon po g.yas 'khor lo /
NK027(sha)002:4138: nub tu rin chen 'od 'phro dkar po g.yas mche ba /
NK027(sha)002:4139: byang du rgyal ba'i dbang po g.yas pad+ma /
NK027(sha)002:4140: byang shar du rin chen glang po dam pa'i dpal ser po g.yas chos 'chad /
NK027(sha)002:4141: shar lhor sangs rgyas pad+mo dam pa'i dpal dkar po pad+ma /
NK027(sha)002:4142: lho nub tu nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal dmar po nyi ma /
NK027(sha)002:4143: nub byang du gdugs chen dam pa'i dpal ljang ku sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:4144: steng du dga' ba'i dpal sngo skya bum pa /
NK027(sha)002:4145: 'og tu pad+mo dam pa'i dpal ser po pad+ma /
NK027(sha)002:4146: de dag gi snying po rim pa bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:4147: di pra dz+ny+aa ma h+aa pra dz+ny+aa h'u d+harma d+h+aa tu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4148: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a yu pu ra ga ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4149: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na a tsi ya ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4150: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na tri thi sha ga pa ri bi sa ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4151: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+hi sha rat+na si ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4152: sarba ta th+aa ga ta bad te b+hi sha ya sam b+ha we s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4153: sarba ta th+aa ga ta du du ma le ke ta to ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4154: mug ti b+hi mug ti mrgam sha du ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4155: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sud+ya b+hi la ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4156: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ra ti ra ma ti badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4157: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma pa la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4159: yang thub pa dang yum gnas barjesa pas dal gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK027(sha)002:4161: dbus su mam las thub pa /
NK027(sha)002:4162: shar du tri las yum chen mo //
NK027(sha)002:4163: lhor h'u las phyag na rdo rje //
NK027(sha)002:4164: nub tu mam las sh+aa ri'i bu //
NK027(sha)002:4165: byang du tram las spyan ras gzigs //
NK027(sha)002:4166: lha rnams shar du hrihls sangs rgyas glang po'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4168: nub tu h+r+aihls pad+ma dam pa'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4169: byang du h+r+aihls ting 'dzin rgyal po /
NK027(sha)002:4170: shar lhor nya las rdo rje'i sems ma /
NK027(sha)002:4171: lho nub tu sa las rin chen sems ma /
NK027(sha)002:4172: nub byang du ra las chos kyi sems ma /
NK027(sha)002:4173: byang shar du mi las las kyi sems ma'o //
NK027(sha)002:4174: de dag gi sngags kyang rim pa bzhin du gtso bo lha gang dang 'dra /
NK027(sha)002:4175: k+shu ban a tse nan sarba b+hu ta nam mrga b+hi sha ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4176: rat+na bi lo ka ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4177: pad+ma b+hi sho d+ha ni shud+d+he si ti nam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4178: pa ti pa ma ti pra sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4179: badz+ra sa t+wa dzi ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4180: rat+na dzi rat+na ba ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4181: pad+ma dzi pad+ma h+r+ai sho d+ha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4182: karma dzi karma hri sho di s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4184: 'dir yang yum dang thub pa gnas barjesa pas dkyil 'khor gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK027(sha)002:4185: yang ling rtse dgu'i dbus su yum chen mo /
NK027(sha)002:4186: phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas /
NK027(sha)002:4187: 'khor lo rtsibs bcur phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas re la byang chub sems dpa' bzhi bzhi'i bskor ba /
NK027(sha)002:4188: gru chad bzhi la sgegs sogs bzhi /
NK027(sha)002:4189: khyams la sems dpa' bcu drug /
NK027(sha)002:4190: 'dod snam la bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad /
NK027(sha)002:4191: sgo ma bzhi ste dgu bcu rtsa gcig go //
NK027(sha)002:4192: 'dir thub pas gtso byas yang dkyil 'khor gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK027(sha)002:4193: 'di dag gi sku mdog phyag mtshan sngags rnams 'og tu zhib tu bstan nam /
NK027(sha)002:4194: yang na 'dab ma brgyad kyi lte bar /
NK027(sha)002:4195: thub pa'i ngo bo dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sngon po sa non mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4196: shar du dga' ba'i spyan dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4197: lhor yongs su dgongs pa'i rgyal po sngo ser mchod sbyin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4198: nub tu gser gyi 'od zer dmar po ting nge 'dzin rgyal po'i phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4199: shar lho zhi ba'i dbang po sngon po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4200: lho nub tu me long 'od dkar ljang skya skyabs sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4201: nub byang du yid 'ong dbyangs dmar ljang ting nge 'dzin /
NK027(sha)002:4202: byang shar du me long 'od dkar ljang skyabs sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4203: de'i phyi la byang shar gyi rtsibs kyi dbus su thub pa chen po /
NK027(sha)002:4204: shar du yum chen mo ser mo phyag bzhi ma gong bzhin /
NK027(sha)002:4205: shar lhor lha'i thub pa srid thub 'dzin sngon po go mtshon can /
NK027(sha)002:4206: lhor rnam par snang mdzad ser po mnyam bzhag can /
NK027(sha)002:4207: lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa snang byed dmar nag sgrom bu can /
NK027(sha)002:4208: nub tu sh+aa ri'i bu ser po gseg par can /
NK027(sha)002:4209: nub byang du byol song thub pa rnam gnon ser nag po ti can /
NK027(sha)002:4210: byang du lha min thub pa rnam rgyal mthing ka pad+ma can /
NK027(sha)002:4211: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa rab rgyal dud ka me chu can /
NK027(sha)002:4212: shar lho rtsibs kyi dbus su rnam snang dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4213: shar du zla 'od dpal dkar po sa gnon can /
NK027(sha)002:4214: lhor nyi ma'i snying po ser po mchog sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4215: nub tu spos kyi dpal dmar po ting 'dzin can /
NK027(sha)002:4216: byang du sngon 'phro'i rgyal po ljang skya skyabs sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4217: shar lho rin chen rgyal po dkar ser sa gnon can /
NK027(sha)002:4218: lho nub tu 'od zer dpal ser skya mchod sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4219: nub byang du dka' thub rgyal dmar skya ting nge 'dzin can /
NK027(sha)002:4220: byang shar du gtsug tor snying po dkar ljang skyabs sbyin can no //
NK027(sha)002:4221: lho'i rtsibs kyi dbus su rin 'byung ser po mchod sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4222: shar du gser 'od 'phro dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4223: lhor bkod pa'i rgyal po ser po sa gnon can /
NK027(sha)002:4224: nub tu gser gyi gzugs dmar po ting nge 'dzin can /
NK027(sha)002:4225: byang dpal gyi rgyal po sngon po skyabs sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4226: shar lho snang ba brtsegs pa dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:4227: lho nub tu mya ngan med pa dmar ser sa gnon can /
NK027(sha)002:4228: nub byang du dga' ba'i dpal dmar ljang mnyam bzhag can /
NK027(sha)002:4229: byang shar du gzi brjid dpal dkar ljang skyabs sbyin can no //
NK027(sha)002:4230: lho nub kyi rtsibs kyi dbus su sh+aakya seng ge ljang gu po ti thugs kar bsnams pa /
NK027(sha)002:4231: shar du dri med sgra dkar po byang chub mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4232: lhor dkon mchog sprin sngon po mchog sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4233: nub tu yon tan 'byung dmar po mnyam bzhag can /
NK027(sha)002:4234: byang du seng ge sgra ljang gu skyabs sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4235: shar lho mdzes pa'i tog dkar ser byang chub mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4236: lho nub tu gzi brjid rgyal dmar ser mchod sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4237: nub byang du tsan+dana dpal dmar ljang mnyam bzhag can /
NK027(sha)002:4238: byang shar snying po'i rgyal dkar lhang skyabs sbyin no //
NK027(sha)002:4239: nub byang gi rtsibs kyi dbus su snang ba mtha'
NK027(sha)002:4240: yas dmar po ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya can
NK027(sha)002:4241: / shar du nges par gshegs dkar po byang chub mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4242: lhor nges pa'i gsung sngon po mchod sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4243: nub tu bdal ba che dmar po sa gnon /
NK027(sha)002:4244: byang du me tog dbyangs ldan ljang gu skyabs sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4245: shar lho grags pa'i dpal dmar skya byang chub mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4246: lho nub tu sprul pa'i rgyal dmar po chos 'chad /
NK027(sha)002:4247: nub byang du sgra dbyangs mi zad pa dmar po sa gnon can /
NK027(sha)002:4248: byang shar du sman gyi rgyal po dmar ljang skyabs sbyin mdzad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:4249: byang gi rtsibs kyis dbus su bcom ldan don yod grub pa ljang ku skyabs sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:4250: shar du dge ba'i bshes gnyen dkar po byang chub mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4251: lhor ngan song sbyongs ba sngon po chos 'chad /
NK027(sha)002:4252: nub tu kun gyi slob dpon dmar po mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4253: byang du rnam par rgyal ba ljang gu sa gnon /
NK027(sha)002:4254: shar lho me tog bkod pa'i rgyal po ljang sngon byang chub mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4255: lho nub tu thams cad snang ljang ser chos 'chad /
NK027(sha)002:4256: nub byang du tsan+dana dri dmar ljang mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4257: byang shar du seng ge 'bum ljang skya sa gnon /
NK027(sha)002:4258: grwa bzhi'i nang du sgeg mo dkar mo rab tu bsnyen ma /
NK027(sha)002:4259: phreng ba ser mos phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:4260: glu ma dmar mos pi wang 'dren pa /
NK027(sha)002:4261: gar ma ljang gus gar byed pa'o /
NK027(sha)002:4262: phyir bdug pa ma sngon mos spos khang 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:4263: me tog ma ser mos me tog gi za ma tog 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:4264: mar me ma dmar mos mar me'i sdong bu 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:4265: dri chab ma ljang gus dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa /
NK027(sha)002:4266: lha rnams la shar du byams pa /
NK027(sha)002:4278: byang du rdo rje'i snying po /
NK027(sha)002:4282: shar sgor lcags kyu ma dkar mo lcags kyu /
NK027(sha)002:4283: lho sgor zhag pa ma ser mo /
NK027(sha)002:4284: nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo /
NK027(sha)002:4285: byang sgor dril bu ma ljang ku'o //
NK027(sha)002:4286: 'dod snams la shar du dpal be'u 'khor lo 'dzin pa'i lha mo gnyis dkar /
NK027(sha)002:4287: lhor pad+ma rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa'i lha mo gnyis ser /
NK027(sha)002:4288: nub tu gdugs dang bum pa 'dzin pa'i lha mo gnyis dmar /
NK027(sha)002:4289: byang du dung dang nya 'dzin pa'i lha mo gnyis ljang ste lha dgu bcu rtsa dagu'o //
NK027(sha)002:4296: dbus su rin chen seng ge brgyad kyi btegs pa'i
NK027(sha)002:4297: steng du nyi zla'i pad+ma'i gdan cha gnyis d+hi prahls
NK027(sha)002:4300: de'i mdun zhal sprod du mum las thub pa chen
NK027(sha)002:4301: po phyogs bzhir hri las glang po dam pa'i dpal
NK027(sha)002:4305: shar lhor nya las rdo rje sems ma /
NK027(sha)002:4306: lho nub tu pa las rin chen sems ma /
NK027(sha)002:4307: nub byang du ra las chos kyi sems ma /
NK027(sha)002:4308: byang shar du mi las las kyis sems ma'o //
NK027(sha)002:4309: de'i phyir shar gyi pad+ma'i dbus su d+h+rihls mya ngan med pa'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4310: de'i shar du a las byang chub sems dpa' chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK027(sha)002:4311: lhor tram las dbang phyug rgyal po /
NK027(sha)002:4312: nub tu h+r+aihls bkod pa'i rgyal po /
NK027(sha)002:4313: byang du tram las rin chen 'od 'phro /
NK027(sha)002:4316: lho'i pad+ma'i dbus su di las rin chen dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4317: shar du a las snang ba'i mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4318: lhor h'u las phyag rgya'i rgyal po /
NK027(sha)002:4319: nub tu t+r+aam las spos kyi glang po /
NK027(sha)002:4320: byang du d+hu las spobs pa brtsegs pa /
NK027(sha)002:4322: nub kyi pad+ma'i dbus su di las gdugs pa'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4323: shar du h+r+aih las pad+ma'i rgyal po /
NK027(sha)002:4324: lhor pa las pad+ma sems dpa' /
NK027(sha)002:4325: nub tu h'u las mi g.yo ba /
NK027(sha)002:4326: byang du e las thogs med rgyal po /
NK027(sha)002:4328: byang gi pad+ma'i dbus su di las dbang du gyur pa /
NK027(sha)002:4329: shar du tram las rin chen dbang phyug /
NK027(sha)002:4330: lhor tram las grub pa'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4331: nub tu las dga' ba ston pa /
NK027(sha)002:4332: byang du las mi bskyod pa /
NK027(sha)002:4334: byang shar pad+ma'i dbus su di las sh+aakya seng ge /
NK027(sha)002:4335: shar du du las phyag na rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:4336: lhor h'u las spyan ras gzigs /
NK027(sha)002:4337: nub tu tram las nam mkha'i snying po /
NK027(sha)002:4338: byang du d+hihls sa'i snying po /
NK027(sha)002:4340: shar lhor pad+ma'i dbus su di las chags pa'i 'od /
NK027(sha)002:4341: shar du tram las kun tu bzang mo /
NK027(sha)002:4343: nub tu a las sgrib pa rnam sel /
NK027(sha)002:4344: byang du mee las byams pa /
NK027(sha)002:4346: lho nub tu pad+ma'i dbus su di las rnam par grol ba'i pad+ma /
NK027(sha)002:4347: shar du pa las mthu chen thob /
NK027(sha)002:4349: nub tu tram las yon tan snying po /
NK027(sha)002:4350: byang du a las mthong na dga' /
NK027(sha)002:4352: nub byang du pad+ma'i dbus su di las bdud rtsi rgyal ba /
NK027(sha)002:4353: shar du a las gzhon nu rgyan /
NK027(sha)002:4354: lhor h'u las skyes bu dam pa /
NK027(sha)002:4355: nub tu h+r+aihls seng ge sgra /
NK027(sha)002:4356: byang du h'u las spyan gsal /
NK027(sha)002:4358: steng gi pad+ma'i dbus su di las dga' ba'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4359: shar du h'u las bzang skyongs /
NK027(sha)002:4360: lhor tram las dkon mchog 'byung gnas /
NK027(sha)002:4361: nub tu h+r+aihls dpa' bar 'gro ba /
NK027(sha)002:4362: byang du a las zla 'od gzhon nu /
NK027(sha)002:4364: 'og gi pad+ma'i dbus su d+hihls pad+mo dam pa'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4365: shar du tram las ye shes me tog /
NK027(sha)002:4366: lhor a las mya ngan kun sel /
NK027(sha)002:4367: nub tu ha las blo gros mi bzad pa /
NK027(sha)002:4368: byang du a las ye shes 'od zer /
NK027(sha)002:4378: lha snams la shar du brgya byin /
NK027(sha)002:4392: de dag gi sngags gtso bo yab yum gnyis /
NK027(sha)002:4395: 'khor sems dpa' bzhi bcu'i sngags rim pa bzhin /
NK027(sha)002:4396: na mahs man ta bud+d+ha n+aam d+har+m+aa ke tu s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4397: ke tu shwa r+aa tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4398: pad+ma pa la pad+ma d+ha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4399: rat+na b+ha tra ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4400: rat+na a tsi ya rat+na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4401: a kra a lo ke s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4402: tsa ra mu tsa pra b+ha ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4403: pra ti r+aa dza no s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4404: pra ti ban kun ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4405: d+har+m+aa hri to ya ba ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4406: ka m+aa la tsa pad+ma d+ha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4408: a mo ga r+aa dza d+ha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4409: rat+na sha ra da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4410: karma sid+d+hi da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4411: ru ti a dar sha da ra a sho sa ma ya da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4412: badz+ra tsan+da ro sha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4413: a wa lo ki te shwa ra ya a kar+sha gar+b+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4414: k+shi ti garba rat+na da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4415: sa man+ta rat+na da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4416: man+dzu sh+r+ai ku ma ra mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4417: sa na sarba bi shwa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4418: mee tri ma h+aa ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4419: bi mu ge mrga la da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4420: ka ru na b+ha dra da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4421: gu na hri to ya ba s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4422: rat+na a ma ki ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4423: sa na da ku ma ra da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4424: bu ling a tse na sing h+aa h+r+aihshanga ka ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4425: badz+ra tsak+shu da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4426: sa la pra wa le s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4427: rat+na swa b+h+aa wa da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4428: shum ram ga me sa ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4429: tsan tra pra b+ha ku m+aa ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4430: sarba sho ga nag ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4431: ma ti phu ba ri dz+ny+aa na pra ba b+ha ta da ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4433: 'dir gtso bo yab yum gnyis bsdom pas lha brgyad cu rtsa gcig go //
NK027(sha)002:4434: bzhi pa rab gnas gong bzhin no //
NK027(sha)002:4435: lnga pa cho ga gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:4437: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK027(sha)002:4438: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK027(sha)002:4439: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po nas //
NK027(sha)002:4441: thugs rje'i dbang gi gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4443: de nas spos dang rol mo dang /
NK027(sha)002:4444: sa ma ya dza dzah h'u /
NK027(sha)002:4445: chos kyi dbyings nas ye shes dbyer med kyang //
NK027(sha)002:4446: gzhi dang lam dang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen //
NK027(sha)002:4447: bdag nyid stong pa don dam yan lag mtha' //
NK027(sha)002:4448: yum chen pha rol phyin ma gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4449: bcom ldan bskal pa grangs med du ma ru //
NK027(sha)002:4450: 'gro ba brtse phyir thugs rjes rnam sbyangs nas //
NK027(sha)002:4451: khyed bzhed 'gro don mdzad dus 'di lags na //
NK027(sha)002:4452: de phyir chos dbyings pho brang lhun grub nas //
NK027(sha)002:4453: ston pa 'khor dang bcas te gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4454: shar phyogs rin chen spyod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4455: bder gshegs rin chen 'byung gnas 'khor bcas gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:4456: lho phyogs mya ngan med pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4457: bder gshegs mya ngan med pa 'khor bcas gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:4458: nub phyogs bde dang ldan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4459: bder gshegs rin chen 'od 'phro 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4460: byang phyogs rgyal ba can gyi zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4461: bder gshegs rgyal ba'i dbang po 'khor bcas gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:4462: byang shar ting 'dzin brgyan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4463: ting 'dzin glang po dpal la 'khor bcas gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:4464: shar lhor snying po byang chub zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4465: bder gshegs pad+mo'i dpal la lho nub rdul tshogs bral ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4466: bder gshegs nyi ma nyid snang dpal la nub byang
NK027(sha)002:4467: dbang du gyur pa'i zhing bder gshegs gdugs mchog dam
NK027(sha)002:4469: 'og phyogs pad+ma can gyi zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4470: bder gshegs pad+mo dpal ba 'khor bcas steng phyogs 'jig rten mdangs dag'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4471: bder gshegs dga' ba dpal ba 'khor bcas gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:4472: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sh+ya ho sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:4475: mya ngan mi 'da' thugs rje'i dang //
NK027(sha)002:4476: nyon mongs ma spangs gos pa med //
NK027(sha)002:4477: ma chags rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK027(sha)002:4478: mnyam nyid ngang du bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4479: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK027(sha)002:4480: thugs rjes dgongs pa'i phrin las rnams //
NK027(sha)002:4481: 'gro don rdzogs mdzad de bzhin du //
NK027(sha)002:4482: yun ring brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4483: pad+ma a si ti tish+tha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:4488: rnam dag sku lnga mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK027(sha)002:4489: ye shes rgya mtsho gser ri lhun po 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:4490: grags pa 'jig rten bkra nas lham me ba //
NK027(sha)002:4491: mgon po mchog nyid la ni phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:4492: zhing bcur skus khyab zab yangs gsung sgra can //
NK027(sha)002:4493: ji snyed thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs //
NK027(sha)002:4494: dus rnams kun tu lhun grub pas //
NK027(sha)002:4495: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:4496: gdul bya'i zhing du 'gro don rdzogs mdzad phyir //
NK027(sha)002:4497: mi snyel thugs rjes 'khor ba'i mtha' la gzigs //
NK027(sha)002:4498: thabs mkhas thugs rjes 'gro don lhur mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:4499: bla med byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:4500: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK027(sha)002:4501: bder gshegs mchod sprin skur sprul ba //
NK027(sha)002:4502: lha mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:4503: sangs rgyas bstan pa srungs mdzad cing //
NK027(sha)002:4504: so so'i bgegs rnams 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:4505: phyogs skyongs rgyal chen phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:4506: bla med dkon mchog gsum po dang //
NK027(sha)002:4507: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK027(sha)002:4508: yid 'ong mchod sprin thams cad dang //
NK027(sha)002:4509: rol mo sil snyan 'phan gdugs dang //
NK027(sha)002:4510: bla re rgyal mtshan lhab lhub dang //
NK027(sha)002:4511: me tog phreng ba bdug spos dang //
NK027(sha)002:4512: mar me dri byug zhal zas sogs //
NK027(sha)002:4513: mchod sprin sna tshogs phyogs bcur 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:4514: sna tshogs rigs pa'i bden pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:4515: dngos 'byor yid kyis sprul pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:4516: sangs rgyas zhing khams rab 'byams su //
NK027(sha)002:4517: bla med mchog pa'i sprin byung zhing //
NK027(sha)002:4518: yon tan dpag med thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)002:4519: zhabs la spyi bos gtug gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:4521: 'jig rten khams dang 'jig rten gzhan dag na //
NK027(sha)002:4522: mchod par 'os pa'i gzugs sgra dri //
NK027(sha)002:4523: ro dang reg bya thugs dang mi 'gal ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:4524: gtsang dang ma nyams sman gyi mchog gyur pa //
NK027(sha)002:4525: chu gtsang bsil dang me tog khyad par can //
NK027(sha)002:4526: dbyibs legs dri zhim kha dog sna tshogs 'di //
NK027(sha)002:4527: tsan+dana gurgum ga pur sbyar ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:4528: so sor bsags pa'i gtor ma ci snyed pa //
NK027(sha)002:4529: nyi zla ltar gsal rin chen 'bar ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:4530: rin chen sgron me mar me mdzes pa'i 'od //
NK027(sha)002:4531: gla rtsi hu lu ka sogs legs sbyar dri //
NK027(sha)002:4532: sku mdzes don du byi dor byug pa'i rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:4533: sman dang shing 'bras sna tshogs dam pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:4534: yul rigs 'tsho ba rnams kyang legs par 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:4535: sgra snyan dbyangs dang sil snyan rol mo bcas //
NK027(sha)002:4536: rin chen rgyan dang rin chen gzhan rnams dang //
NK027(sha)002:4537: bkra shis rtags brgyad gzhan yang bkra shis rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:4538: bdag gi lus ngag yid bcas khyed la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:4539: rgyal ba sras bcas thugs rjes brtser dgongs la //
NK027(sha)002:4540: 'gro rnams bde bar bya phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4542: gzhan yang mchod pa rgyas par byas la /
NK027(sha)002:4543: gong bzhin cha gsum btang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:4545: thar pa chen po phyogs bcur rgyas pa'i mdo dang /
NK027(sha)002:4547: spang skong phyag rgya pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:4549: gnas brtan bcu drug gi gsol 'debs la sogs pa /
NK027(sha)002:4550: pad+ma stong ldan gyi lha tshogs la tshogs dang /
NK027(sha)002:4551: sgrib gnyis sbyangs pa'i cho ga thams cad kyi rgyas par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:4552: brgyad pa bum pa lhar bskyed bzlas pa byas te /
NK027(sha)002:4555: gzhan don du tshogs gsogs sgrib pa sbyangs ba'i phyir phyag rten bzang po phul lo //
NK027(sha)002:4557: dgu pa bla ma byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pas khri la 'dug ste ston pa bsgom mo //
NK027(sha)002:4558: bcu gcig pa dkon mchog gi rten dang mchod pa bsham la /
NK027(sha)002:4559: dge ba'i bshes gnye na la ston pa dngos kyi 'du shes bskyed /
NK027(sha)002:4560: sems can thams cad 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las bsgral te sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'god par bya /
NK027(sha)002:4561: de'i phyir byang chub sems mchog blang snyam pas bla ma la phyag 'tshal /
NK027(sha)002:4563: thal mo sbyar la 'di skad du /
NK027(sha)002:4565: rigs kyi bu la la dag la dus gsum gyi
NK027(sha)002:4566: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bsgrod pa gcig tu
NK027(sha)002:4567: gyur pa'i lam skyabs su sngon du 'gro ba can
NK027(sha)002:4568: gyi byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa stsal
NK027(sha)002:4569: du gsol // slob dpon gyi nus pa ci lta ba bzhin du sbyin no //
NK027(sha)002:4571: de nas yan lag bdun pa rgyas bsdus gang rung byas la thal mo sbyar la /
NK027(sha)002:4572: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:4573: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:4574: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK027(sha)002:4575: byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du /
NK027(sha)002:4577: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:4578: zhi ba 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4579: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i dam pa'i chos rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:4581: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i dge
NK027(sha)002:4582: 'dun phyir mi ldog pa rnams la skyabs su mchi'o
NK027(sha)002:4586: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:4587: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4588: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK027(sha)002:4589: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK027(sha)002:4590: 'das rnams dang / byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de /
NK027(sha)002:4591: sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med
NK027(sha)002:4592: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon
NK027(sha)002:4593: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas /
NK027(sha)002:4594: sems can ma bsgral ba rnams sgrol ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4595: ma grol ba rnams grol ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4596: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4597: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams mya
NK027(sha)002:4598: ngan las 'das pa'i sa la 'god pa de bzhin
NK027(sha)002:4599: du / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK027(sha)002:4600: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK027(sha)002:4601: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de /
NK027(sha)002:4602: sems can ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4603: ma grol ba rnams grol ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4604: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4605: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar bagyi'o //
NK027(sha)002:4607: slob dpon gyi thabs yin no //
NK027(sha)002:4610: bcu gsum pa chos spyod bcu'i bshad pa 'chad pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:4611: de'ang khyod rnams de ring nas byang chub sems dpar gyur pas /
NK027(sha)002:4612: mi lus thob pa don chen yin no //
NK027(sha)002:4613: deng dus bdag tshe 'bras bu yod //
NK027(sha)002:4614: mi'i srid pa legs par thob //
NK027(sha)002:4615: bdag gi gson pa'ang 'bras bur bcas //
NK027(sha)002:4616: de ring sangs rgyas rigs su skye //
NK027(sha)002:4617: sangs rgyas sras su da gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:4619: dga' bas spro ba chen po mdzad do //
NK027(sha)002:4620: de'ang bdag gi ci nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:4621: rigs dang mthun pa'i las brtson zhing //
NK027(sha)002:4622: skyon med btsun pa'i rigs 'di la //
NK027(sha)002:4623: rnyog par mi 'gyur de ltar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:4624: zhes pas bla ma la gus pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:4625: nag po'i chos bzhi spangs ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:4626: sems can blos mi btang ba la bslab pa bsod nams dpag tu med de /
NK027(sha)002:4627: dpal byin gyi zhus pa las /
NK027(sha)002:4628: byang chub sems kyi bsod nams gang //
NK027(sha)002:4629: gal te de la gzugs mchis na //
NK027(sha)002:4630: nam mkha' 'di ni kun bkang ste //
NK027(sha)002:4631: de las kyang ni lhag gyur pa //
NK027(sha)002:4633: bcu bzhi pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:4637: yum de bzhin gshegs pa bcu'i nga rgyal gyi /
NK027(sha)002:4638: slob ma rnams man+da la phul /
NK027(sha)002:4640: slob dpon sangs rgyas dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4641: bden gnyis don rtogs theg chen gyi //
NK027(sha)002:4642: rgyal ba'i mdzad pa mthar phyin pa //
NK027(sha)002:4643: zab cing rgya che'i dbang rnams stsol //
NK027(sha)002:4644: zhes lan gsum gsol ba gdab bo //
NK027(sha)002:4645: pad+ma 'dab bzhi sgo khyud can gnyis lha'o //
NK027(sha)002:4646: de nas bla mas dbang rdzas rnams rim par thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:4648: gser gyi mdog can rkang gnyis gtso //
NK027(sha)002:4649: spyan yangs mdzod spu mthing kar ldan //
NK027(sha)002:4652: sh+aakya'i rgyal pos byin gyis rlobs //
NK027(sha)002:4653: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4657: shar phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK027(sha)002:4658: yum chen rgyan ldan rdo rje skyil //
NK027(sha)002:4659: gser mdog sku ni shin tu rgyas //
NK027(sha)002:4660: phyag bzhi dang po mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:4662: 'gro ba sems can don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:4663: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4664: d+hi pra dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa pra dz+ny+aa h'u d+har+m+aa d+hardu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4665: a b+hi lho phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK027(sha)002:4666: phyag na rdo rje zhi ba'i zhal //
NK027(sha)002:4668: rin chen rgyan ldan sems dkyil bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:4669: de'i byin rlabs dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:4670: badz+ra tsan+da ro sha na h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:4671: a b+hi nub phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK027(sha)002:4672: sh+aa ri'i bu ni gser mdog can //
NK027(sha)002:4673: rab byung 'khar gsil lhung bzed bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:4674: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4675: b+ha ga wan pra wa ta th+aa ga ta b+hi sha ya swa b+h+aa wa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4677: byang phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK027(sha)002:4678: spyan gzigs dkar po zhi ba'i zhal //
NK027(sha)002:4680: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4681: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa lo ki te ka ru na ma badz+ra /
NK027(sha)002:4682: a b+hi gzhal yas lha rnams shar phyogs su //
NK027(sha)002:4683: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas ni //
NK027(sha)002:4684: sku mdog shel ltar dkar ba la //
NK027(sha)002:4685: mchod sbyin rin chen g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4686: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4687: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a yu ra ga ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4688: a b+hi gzhal yas lho phyogs pad zla'i steng //
NK027(sha)002:4689: bder gshegs mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4690: sngon po 'khor lo g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4691: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4692: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na a tsi ya ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4693: a b+hi gzhal yas nub phyogs pad zla'i steng //
NK027(sha)002:4694: bde gshegs rin chen 'od 'phro rab tu dkar //
NK027(sha)002:4695: g.yas pas mche ba g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4696: de'i dbang mchog sarba ta th+aa ga ta tri thi sha ga pa ri b+he sha ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4698: byang phyogs pad steng bder gshegs rigs //
NK027(sha)002:4699: rgyal ba'i dbang po sku mdog ljang //
NK027(sha)002:4700: g.yas pas pad dkar g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4701: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4702: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+hi sha ra na san ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4704: shar lho bder gshegs pad ma'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4705: dung ltar pad+ma gzhan mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4707: de'i dbang sarba ta th+aa ga ta du ma lo ka de ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4709: lho nub pad steng bder gshegs rigs //
NK027(sha)002:4710: nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal /
NK027(sha)002:4711: dmar smug nyi ma g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:4712: de'i dbang mchog sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi mu ti mrgad du sha ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4713: a b+hi nub byang pad zla bder gshegs rigs //
NK027(sha)002:4714: gdugs chen dam pa in dra'i mdog /
NK027(sha)002:4715: sna tshogs rdo rje g.yon mthil ston //
NK027(sha)002:4716: de'i sarba ta th+aa ga ta sur+ya b+hi ta la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4718: byang shar pad zla bder gshegs rigs //
NK027(sha)002:4719: glang po dam pa gser ltar 'tsher //
NK027(sha)002:4721: de'i dbang mchog sarba ta th+aa ga ta d+ha thir+ya b+hi sha ya b+ha wa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4722: a b+hi steng gi bder gshegs dga' ba'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4723: sngon po rin chen bum pa g.yas //
NK027(sha)002:4724: g.yon pas dkur bsten dkyil krung bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:4725: de'i dbang sarba ta th+aa ga ta ra ti ra ma ti badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4727: 'og gi sangs rgyas pad+ma'i dpal gser mdog g.yas pas pad+ma bsnams /
NK027(sha)002:4728: g.yon pas lte bar mthil phyir bstan /
NK027(sha)002:4729: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4730: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma b+ha la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4732: zhes pas thub pa la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi bskor ba'i dbang dang /
NK027(sha)002:4734: yum chen mo la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi bskor ba'i dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:4735: 'dab brgyad pa gnyis kyi lha rnams so //
NK027(sha)002:4737: phyogs bcu'i dbus su seng ge khri //
NK027(sha)002:4738: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK027(sha)002:4739: dbus phyogs bde bar gshegs pa yum //
NK027(sha)002:4740: sku mdog dkar gsal g.yas mchod sbyin //
NK027(sha)002:4741: g.yon na pad+ma po ti'i mtshan //
NK027(sha)002:4742: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4743: d+hi prad dz+ny+aa h'u d+harma d+hartu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:4745: shar phyogs sangs rgyas dkon mchog 'byung //
NK027(sha)002:4746: dkar gsal mchod sbyin rin chen g.yas //
NK027(sha)002:4747: g.yon pas lte bar dku bsten tshul //
NK027(sha)002:4748: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:4749: lho phyogs sangs rgyas mya ngan med //
NK027(sha)002:4750: mkha' ltar phyag g.yas 'khor lo bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:4751: g.yon pas dkur brten snyems pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:4752: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4756: g.yas pas mche ba g.yon dkur bsten //
NK027(sha)002:4757: sangs rgyas pad zla nyi mar bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:4759: byang phyogs rgyal ba'i dbang po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4760: nyi zla pad steng sku mdog ljang //
NK027(sha)002:4761: pad dkar g.yas la g.yon dkur brten //
NK027(sha)002:4762: de'i a b+hi byang shar pad steng gser gyis mchog /
NK027(sha)002:4763: ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4764: chos 'chad g.yas te g.yon dkur brten //
NK027(sha)002:4765: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi shar lho pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4766: dung ltar pad dkar g.yas na ste //
NK027(sha)002:4767: g.yon pas dkur brten snyems pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:4768: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi lho nub nyi snang dam pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4769: mar gad lta bu g.yas nyi ma //
NK027(sha)002:4770: g.yon pas snyems tshul dku la brten //
NK027(sha)002:4771: de'i a b+hi nub byang sangs rgyas gdugs dam pa //
NK027(sha)002:4772: ljang gu sna tshogs rdo rje g.yas //
NK027(sha)002:4773: g.yon pas dkur brten 'gying tshul can //
NK027(sha)002:4775: steng phyogs dga' bar byed pa po //
NK027(sha)002:4776: sangs rgyas ut+pala lta bu'i mdog /
NK027(sha)002:4777: bum pa g.yas la dku brten g.yon //
NK027(sha)002:4778: de'i dbang a b+hi 'og gi sangs rgyas pad+ma'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4779: gser mdog pad+ma dmar po g.yas //
NK027(sha)002:4780: g.yon pas dku brten thugs rje'i bdag /
NK027(sha)002:4781: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4783: de yang lha lnga ma dang /
NK027(sha)002:4785: brgya nyer gcig ma'i gtso bo yab yum 'dra /
NK027(sha)002:4787: rtsa ba'i lha bcu drug cu rtsa gsum pa 'di /
NK027(sha)002:4788: pad 'dab brgyad 'khor lo rtsib drug go //
NK027(sha)002:4790: dbus su pad zla'i gdan steng nas //
NK027(sha)002:4791: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:4792: sngon po sa gnon phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4793: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4795: rin chen bkod pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4796: sangs rgyas dag pa'i spyan dkar po //
NK027(sha)002:4797: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4798: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi rnam par bkram pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4799: yongs su dgongs pa'i rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4800: sngo ser mchod sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4801: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi bee d+aur+ya yi snying po nas //
NK027(sha)002:4802: sangs rgyas gser gyi 'od zer ni //
NK027(sha)002:4803: dmar po ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4804: de'i a b+hi gser 'od dam pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4805: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od kyi dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4806: ljang gu skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4807: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:4808: rnam par zhi ba'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4809: sangs rgyas zhi ba'i dbang po ste //
NK027(sha)002:4810: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4811: de'i a b+hi sprin rnams bkod pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4812: de bzhin gshegs pa sprin gyi dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4813: ser ljang mchod sbyin de'i dbang mchog a b+hi me long dkyil 'khor shin tu sbyangs pa nas //
NK027(sha)002:4814: sangs rgyas me long 'od snang ni //
NK027(sha)002:4815: ljang dkar skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4816: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi yid mngon dga' ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4817: sangs rgyas yid du 'ong ba'i dbyangs //
