NK027(sha)002:4818: dmar ljang ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4819: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi dkyil 'khor byang shar 'khor lo'i dbus //
NK027(sha)002:4820: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:4821: gser mdog phyag rgya chos 'chad can //
NK027(sha)002:4822: de'i a b+hi shar du yum chen pha rol phyin //
NK027(sha)002:4823: sku mdog ser po mnyam bzhag dang //
NK027(sha)002:4824: rdo rje po ti 'dzin mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:4825: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi shar lho lha yi thub pa che //
NK027(sha)002:4826: srid thub 'dzin zhes bya ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:4827: sku mdog dkar po pi wang can //
NK027(sha)002:4828: de'i dbang mchog thob par a b+hi lho phyogs mi yi thub pa che //
NK027(sha)002:4829: sh+aakya seng ge sku mdog ser //
NK027(sha)002:4830: gseg shing par bu mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:4831: de'i a lho nub yi dwags thub pa che //
NK027(sha)002:4832: rnam par snang mdzad ces bya ni //
NK027(sha)002:4833: sku mdog dmar nag sgrom bu can //
NK027(sha)002:4834: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi nub phyogs pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK027(sha)002:4835: sh+aa ri'i bu ni sku mdog ser //
NK027(sha)002:4836: gseg shang dang ni par bu can //
NK027(sha)002:4837: de'i a b+hi nub phyogs byol song thub pa che //
NK027(sha)002:4838: rnam par gnon pa'i zhes bya ni //
NK027(sha)002:4839: sku mdog ser nag po ti can //
NK027(sha)002:4840: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi byang du lha min thub pa che //
NK027(sha)002:4841: rnam par rgyal ba zhes bya ni //
NK027(sha)002:4842: sku mdog mthing ka go mtshon can //
NK027(sha)002:4843: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi byang shar dmyal ba'i thub pa che //
NK027(sha)002:4844: chos kyi rgyal po zhes bya ni //
NK027(sha)002:4845: sku mdog dung ka me chu can //
NK027(sha)002:4848: rnam par snang mdzad dkar po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4849: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4850: de'i dbang a b+hi zla bas brgyan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4851: de bzhin gshegs pa zla 'od dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4852: dkar po sa gnon mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:4854: nyi ma'i 'od zer brgyan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4855: sangs rgyas nyi ma'i snying po dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4856: ser po mchod sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4857: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi spos ngad ldan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4858: sangs rgyas spos kyi rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4859: dmar po ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4860: de'i dbang a b+hi rnam par spros pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4861: mngon par spro ba'i rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4862: ljang gu skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4863: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi rin chen spros pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4864: sangs rgyas rin chen rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4865: dkar ser sa gnon phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4866: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:4868: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4869: ser skya mchod sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4870: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:4871: dag pa rnam par spyod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4872: sangs rgyas dka' thub rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4873: dmar skya ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4874: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi gtsug tor bkod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4875: sangs rgyas gtsug tor snying po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4876: dkar ljang skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4877: de'i a b+hi dkyil 'khor lho phyogs 'khor lo dbus //
NK027(sha)002:4878: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan ni //
NK027(sha)002:4879: ser po mchod sbyin phyag rgya mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:4880: de'i a b+hi gser 'od snang ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4882: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4883: de'i dbang a b+hi 'od zer bkod pa'i zhing khams su //
NK027(sha)002:4884: sangs rgyas bkod pa'i rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4885: sku mdog ser po sa gnon can //
NK027(sha)002:4886: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi zhing khams gser gyi 'byung gnas su //
NK027(sha)002:4887: sangs rgyas gser gyi gzung ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:4888: dmar po ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4889: de'i a b+hi zhing khams dpal gyi 'byung gnas nas //
NK027(sha)002:4890: sangs rgyas dpal gyi rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4891: sngo skya skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4892: de'i a b+hi snang ba dam pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4893: sangs rgyas snang ba brtsegs pa dkar //
NK027(sha)002:4894: byang chub mchog gi de'i a b+hi mya ngan med pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4895: sangs rgyas mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4896: dmar ser sa non phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4897: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi dga' ba'i mdangs kyi zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4898: de bzhin gshegs pa dga' mchog dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4899: dmar ljang mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4900: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi gzi brjid dam pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4901: de bzhin gshegs pa gzi brjid dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4902: dkar ljang mnyam bzhag de'i dbang mchog a b+hi dkyil 'khor lho nub 'khor lo'i dbus //
NK027(sha)002:4903: bcom ldan sh+aakya seng ge ni //
NK027(sha)002:4904: ser po chos 'chad phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4905: de'i dbang a b+hi shar phyogs 'jig rten dri ma med pa nas //
NK027(sha)002:4906: de bzhin gshegs pa dri med sgra dkar po //
NK027(sha)002:4907: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4908: de'i dbang a b+hi lho phyogs yon tan 'byung ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4909: de bzhin gshegs pa dkon mchog sprin //
NK027(sha)002:4910: sngon po mchod sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4911: de'i a b+hi nub phyogs rgyan rnams shin tu bkram pa'i zhing //
NK027(sha)002:4912: de bzhin gshegs pa yon tan 'byung gnas ni //
NK027(sha)002:4913: dmar po mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4914: de'i dbang a b+hi byang phyogs bag tsha med pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4915: de bzhin gshegs pa seng ge'i sgra //
NK027(sha)002:4916: sku mdog ljang skya skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4917: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi shar lho rnam par mdzes pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4918: de bzhin gshegs pa thub pa mdzes pa'i tog /
NK027(sha)002:4919: dkar ser byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4920: de'i a b+hi lho nub rab tu snang ba'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4921: de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen rgyan //
NK027(sha)002:4922: dmar ser mchod sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4923: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi nub byang 'jig rten rab tu dang ba nas //
NK027(sha)002:4924: de bzhin gshegs pa tsan+dana dri mchog dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4925: dmar ljang mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4926: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi byang shar gdung ba sel ba'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4927: de bzhin gshegs pa snying rje'i rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4928: dkar ljang skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4929: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi dkyil 'khor nub byang 'khor lo'i dbus //
NK027(sha)002:4930: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas ni //
NK027(sha)002:4931: dmar po ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4932: de'i a b+hi nges pa can gyi zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4933: sangs rgyas nges par gshegs pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:4934: dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4935: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi nges par 'phags pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4936: sangs rgyas nges par gsung ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:4937: sngon po mchod sbyin de'i dbang mchog a b+hi bde spyod ces bya'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4938: sangs rgyas bde ba chen po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4939: dmar po sa gnon phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4940: de'i dbang a b+hi me tog bkram pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4941: sangs rgyas me tog dbang po'i dbyangs //
NK027(sha)002:4942: ljang gu skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4943: de'i a b+hi yongs su grags pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK027(sha)002:4944: de bzhin gshegs pa grags pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:4945: dmar skya byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4946: de'i a b+hi rnam par sprul pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4947: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4948: dmar po chos 'chad phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4949: de'i a b+hi rnam par sbyangs ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4950: sangs rgyas sgra dbyangs mi bzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:4951: dmar po sa gnon phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4952: de'i a b+hi sman gyi brgyan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4953: sangs rgyas sman gyi rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4954: dkar ljang skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4955: de'i a b+hi dkyil 'khor byang phyogs 'khor lo'i dbus //
NK027(sha)002:4956: bcom ldan don yod grub pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:4957: ljang gu skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4958: de'i dbang a b+hi sangs rgyas mang 'dus zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4959: sangs rgyas kun gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni //
NK027(sha)002:4960: dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4961: de'i a b+hi yongs su sbyangs ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4962: ngan song thams cad sbyangs byed ni //
NK027(sha)002:4963: sngon po chos 'chad phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4964: de'i dbang a b+hi tha dad spyod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4965: sangs rgyas 'jig rten kun gyi slob dpon ni //
NK027(sha)002:4966: dmar po mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4967: de'i dbang mchog zhing khams rgyal mtshan rtse mo'i dpung rgyan nas //
NK027(sha)002:4968: sangs rgyas rnam par rgyal ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:4969: ljang gu sa non phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4970: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi me tog mdzes pas brgyan pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4971: sangs rgyas me tog bkod pa'i rgyal po ni //
NK027(sha)002:4972: ljang sngon byang chub mchog gi de'i dbang a b+hi mdzes par snang ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4973: sangs rgyas thams cad snang ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:4974: ljang ser chos 'chad phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4975: de'i dbang mchog a b+hi tsan+dana bkod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4976: sangs rgyas tsan+dana dri mchog ni //
NK027(sha)002:4977: dmar ljang mnyam bzhag de'i dbang a b+hi seng ge 'byung gnas zhing khams nas //
NK027(sha)002:4978: sangs rgyas seng ge 'bum gzigs ni //
NK027(sha)002:4979: ljang skya sa non phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:4980: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:4982: zhes lha dgu bcu rtsa dgu ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK027(sha)002:4983: rtsa ba'i lha drug cu rtsa gsum gyi lha dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:4984: phyi nang gi lha mo brgyad /
NK027(sha)002:4985: byang chub sems dpa' bcu drug /
NK027(sha)002:4991: de'i phyir 'dab brgyad re re'i nang du yang 'dab brgyad re re /
NK027(sha)002:4992: shar nub gnyis ldan re re'i lha'o //
NK027(sha)002:4994: rnam dag dbus kyi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK027(sha)002:4995: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub //
NK027(sha)002:4996: sa gnon mnyam bzhag gseg shang par bu can //
NK027(sha)002:4997: byin rlabs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:4998: mu ne a b+hi yum chen gser mdog ral gri mchod sbyin g.yas //
NK027(sha)002:4999: g.yon pas ut+pala po ti phreng ba can //
NK027(sha)002:5000: rgyal ba'i yum gyi 'gro la thugs rjes bzung //
NK027(sha)002:5001: byin rlabs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5002: g+ha te a b+hi mdun du glang po dam pa dkar po ni //
NK027(sha)002:5003: g.yas pas rdo rje g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5004: 'gro la thugs rjes byin gyis brlab pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:5005: sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5006: mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su rin chen 'byung gnas ni //
NK027(sha)002:5007: ser po rin chen mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5008: 'gro la thugs rjes byin gyis rlobs pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:5009: sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5010: mu ne g+ha te a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:5011: rgyab tu pad+mo dam pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:5012: dmar po pad+mo mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5013: 'gro la thugs rje byin gyis rlob pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:5014: sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5015: mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yon du ting 'dzin rgyal po ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5016: rgya gram dang ni mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5017: 'gro la thugs rjes byin gyis rlob pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:5018: sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur dam pa mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5019: a b+hi rdo rje sems ma sku mdog dkar mo
NK027(sha)002:5020: ste // g.yas g.yon phyag ni chos 'chad phyag rgya mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5021: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur mu ne
NK027(sha)002:5022: g+ha te a b+hi rin chen sems ma sku mdog
NK027(sha)002:5023: ser mo ste // phyag gnyis rin po che dang mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5024: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi chos kyi sems ma sku mdog dmar mo ste //
NK027(sha)002:5025: g.yas g.yon phyag gnyis chos 'chad phyag rgya ste //
NK027(sha)002:5026: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi las kyi sems ma sku mdog ljang gu ste //
NK027(sha)002:5027: g.yas pas rgya gram g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5028: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi shar gyi dbus su mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:5029: sku mdog dkar po 'khor lo mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5030: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi mdun du sems dpa' chos kyi rgyal mtshan ni //
NK027(sha)002:5031: ser po chu srin rgyal mtshan mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5032: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su sems dpa' dbang phyug rgyal po ser //
NK027(sha)002:5033: g.yas pas lcags kyu g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5034: 'gro la thugs rje byin sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5035: mu ne g+ha te a b+hi rgyab tu sems dpa' bkod pa'i rgyal po dmar //
NK027(sha)002:5036: g.yas pas me tog g.yon pa mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5037: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a g.yon du sems dpa' rin chen 'od 'phro ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5038: g.yas pas rin chen g.yon pa mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5039: 'gro la thugs sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur dam mu ne
NK027(sha)002:5040: g+ha te a b+hi lho yi pad+ma'i dbus su rin
NK027(sha)002:5041: chen dpal // sku mdog sngo skya rin chen mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5042: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi mdun du sems dpa' snang ba mchog dkar po //
NK027(sha)002:5043: phyag g.yas rdo rje g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5044: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su sems dpa' phyag rgya'i rgyal po ser //
NK027(sha)002:5045: g.yas pas rgya gram g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5046: 'gro la sgrib mu ne g+ha te a b+hi rgyab tu sems dpa' spos kyi glang po dkar //
NK027(sha)002:5047: g.yas pas 'bud dung g.yon pa po ti can //
NK027(sha)002:5048: 'gro la thugs sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a
NK027(sha)002:5049: b+hi g.yon du sems dpa' spob pa brtsegs pa ljang
NK027(sha)002:5050: // za ma tog dang mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:5051: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi nub kyi dbus su gdugs mchog dam pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:5052: dmar po pad+ma g.yon pas mchod sbyin can //
NK027(sha)002:5053: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5054: a b+hi mdun du pad+ma'i rgyal po sku mdog dkar
NK027(sha)002:5055: // pad+ma sgrom bu g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5056: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5057: mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su pad+ma'i sems dpa' sku mdog sngo /
NK027(sha)002:5058: g.yon pas pad+ma g.yas pas kha 'byed mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5059: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5060: a b+hi rgyab tu rdo rje mi g.yo dmar po
NK027(sha)002:5061: yi / g.yas pas lcags kyu g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5062: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yon du thogs med rgyal po sku mdog ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5063: g.yas pa ral gri g.yon pa mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5064: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:5065: byang gi dbus su rgyal ba'i dbang po ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5066: g.yas pas skyabs sbyin mdzad cing nyi ma 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5067: g.yon pas mchod sbyin thugs rje chen po yin //
NK027(sha)002:5068: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib mu ne g+ha te a
NK027(sha)002:5069: b+hi mdun du rin 'byung rin chen zur brgyad 'dzin
NK027(sha)002:5070: // sku mdog dkar po g.yon pa mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5071: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su grub pa'i dpal ni sku mdog sngo //
NK027(sha)002:5072: g.yas pas rgya gram g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5073: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi rgyab tu dga' ba ston pa sku mdog dmar //
NK027(sha)002:5074: g.yas pas me long g.yon pa mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5075: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yon du sems dpa' mi bskyod sku mdog ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5076: g.yas g.yon phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag phyag rgya mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5077: 'gro la thugs sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi byang shar dbus su sh+aakya seng ge ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5078: g.yas pas po ti g.yon pas chos gos 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5079: 'gro la sgrib mu ne g+ha te a b+hi mdun du phyag na rdo rje sku mdog sngo //
NK027(sha)002:5080: g.yas pas rdo rje g.yon pas dril bu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5081: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su spyan ras gzigs dbang sku mdog dkar //
NK027(sha)002:5082: g.yas pas pad+ma g.yon pas skyabs sbyin mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5083: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs dbang bskur mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5084: a b+hi rgyab tu nam mkha'i snying po sku mdog
NK027(sha)002:5085: dmar // za ma tog dang g.yon pas mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5086: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yon du sa yi snying po sku mdog ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5087: rin chen myu gu g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5088: 'gro sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi shar lhor pad+ma'i dbus su chags pa'i 'od //
NK027(sha)002:5089: dkar ser nyi ma g.yon pa mnyam bzhag can //
NK027(sha)002:5090: 'gro la thugs sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a
NK027(sha)002:5091: b+hi mdun du kun tu bzang po sku mdog dkar
NK027(sha)002:5092: // rin chen sdong bu g.yas la g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:5093: 'gro la thugs sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a
NK027(sha)002:5094: b+hi g.yas su 'jam dpal gzhon nu sku mdog ser
NK027(sha)002:5095: // g.yas pas ral gri g.yon pas ut+pala 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5096: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi rgyab tu sgrib pa rnam sel sku mdog dmar //
NK027(sha)002:5097: g.yas pas po ti g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5098: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yon du byams pa mgon po sku mdog ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5099: g.yas pas klu shing g.yon pas g+hen+de 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5100: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5101: a b+hi lho nub dbus su rnam grol pad+mo ni
NK027(sha)002:5102: // dmar ser nyi ma g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5103: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi mdun du mthu chen thob ni sku mdog dkar //
NK027(sha)002:5104: g.yas pas rdo rje g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5105: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su sman gyi rgyal po sku mdog sngo //
NK027(sha)002:5106: g.yas pas bum pa g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5107: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5108: a b+hi rgyab tu yon tan snying po sku mdog
NK027(sha)002:5109: dmar // g.yas pas rin chen snye ma g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:5110: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yon du mthong na dga' ba sku mdog ljang //
NK027(sha)002:5111: klu shing lo ma g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5112: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi nub byang dbus su bdud rtsi rgyal ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:5113: dmar ljang gdugs 'dzin g.yon pa mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5114: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi
NK027(sha)002:5115: shiny+tsa mdun du gzhon nu rgyan ni sku mdog dkar
NK027(sha)002:5116: // g.yas pas ut+pala g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5117: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su skyes bu dam pa sku mdog sngo //
NK027(sha)002:5118: g.yas pas dung dang g.yon pas rnga yab 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5119: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi rgyab tu seng ge sgra ni sku mdog dmar //
NK027(sha)002:5120: ku mu ta dang g.yon pa mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5121: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:5122: g.yon du spyan gsal sku mdog ljang gu ni //
NK027(sha)002:5123: g.yas pas mar me g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:5124: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te h'u /
NK027(sha)002:5125: steng gi dbus su dga' ba'i dpal dkar po //
NK027(sha)002:5126: g.yas pas rgyal mtshan g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:5127: 'gro la thugs sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha a b+hi mdun du bzang skyong sku mdog dkar //
NK027(sha)002:5128: g.yas pas gser bum g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5129: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su dkon mchog 'byung gnas ser po ni //
NK027(sha)002:5130: rin chen sgrom bu g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:5131: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi rgyab tu dpa' bar 'gro ba dmar po ni //
NK027(sha)002:5132: g.yas pas ral gri g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5133: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs dbang mu ne g+ha te a
NK027(sha)002:5134: b+hi g.yon du zla 'od gzhon nu sku mdog ljang
NK027(sha)002:5135: // g.yas pas zla tshes g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzes //
NK027(sha)002:5136: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5137: a b+hi 'og gi sangs rgyas pad+mo dam pa'i dpal
NK027(sha)002:5138: // sku mdog sngon po pad+ma chos 'chad mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5139: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te
NK027(sha)002:5140: a b+hi mdun du sems dpa' ye shes me tog
NK027(sha)002:5141: ni // g.yas pas tog dkar g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5142: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yas su mya ngan med 'joms sngon po ste //
NK027(sha)002:5143: g.yas pas ral gri g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5144: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi rgyab tu blo gros mi zad sku mdog dmar //
NK027(sha)002:5145: g.yas pas po ti g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5146: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi g.yon du ye shes 'od zer sku mdog ser //
NK027(sha)002:5147: g.yas pas rdo rje g.yon pas mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5148: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs dbang mu ne g+ha te a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:5149: shar du glang po'i gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5150: brgya byin ser po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5151: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi shar lho ra skyes gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5152: me lha dmar po bgrang phreng 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5153: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:5154: lho phyogs ma he'i gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5155: gshin rje sngon po be con bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:5156: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi lho nub ro lang gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5157: srin po smug nag ral gri 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5158: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi nub tu chu srin gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5159: chu lha sngon po sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5160: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs dbang mu ne g+ha te a b+hi nub byang shwa ba'i gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5161: rlung lha ljang gu ba dan 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5162: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a byang du rta'i gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5163: gnod sbyin ljang sngon dbyug pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5164: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi byang shar khyu mchog gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5165: dbang ldan nag po rtse gsum 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5166: 'gro la thugs rjes sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi steng du ngang pa'i gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5168: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi 'og tu phag gi gdan khri la //
NK027(sha)002:5169: brtan ma ser mo gter bum 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5170: 'gro la sgrib sbyangs mu ne g+ha te a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:5171: sgegs phreng glu gar me tog spos //
NK027(sha)002:5172: mar me dri chab sgo skyongs bzhi //
NK027(sha)002:5173: rgyal ba mchod cing bstan pa bsrungs //
NK027(sha)002:5174: tshad med phrin las gdul bya skyongs //
NK027(sha)002:5175: 'gro la thugs rjes byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5176: sgrib sbyang dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5177: mu ne g+ha te a b+hi de rnams ni lha'i dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:5178: de nas rdzas dbang bskur ba rim pa bzhin thogs te 'di skad du /
NK027(sha)002:5179: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po de dga' ldan gyi gnas nas /
NK027(sha)002:5180: yum sgyu ma lha mdzes kyi lhums su zhugs pa'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:5181: dbu las rin po che'i prog zhu phud nas /
NK027(sha)002:5182: mi pham mgon po la chos kyi rgyal tshab tu lha rnams kyis dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:5183: de bzhin du rin po che'i cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5184: chos kyi rgyal tshab byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5186: tog gi dbu las rin chen cod pan phud //
NK027(sha)002:5187: de nyid phyag gi bu yi dbu la bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:5188: mi pham mgon po chos kyi rgyal tshab rje //
NK027(sha)002:5189: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po byed par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5190: chos kyi dbyings nas byung nas da la bar //
NK027(sha)002:5191: sprul sku kun khyab yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK027(sha)002:5192: dang po tshogs rdzogs smon lam mthar phyin pa //
NK027(sha)002:5193: 'di ni bsod nams rdzogs pa'i bkra shis dang po'o //
NK027(sha)002:5194: sngon byang byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po de yum gyi lhums na zhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5195: yum gyi phyag gi sems can rnams la reg cing dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5196: sems can rnams kyi na tsha dang sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:5197: de bzhin du 'dir yang yum gyi phyag gi reg cing dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5198: nyon mongs pa dang na tsha sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5199: sgyu ma lha mdzes lha yi lcam //
NK027(sha)002:5200: lha yi lus la rin chen mdzes //
NK027(sha)002:5201: nyon mongs sdug bsngal kun zhi nas //
NK027(sha)002:5202: na tsha'i sdug bsngal thar bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:5203: byin rlabs yum chen shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK027(sha)002:5204: kun la byams snyoms thugs rje che ba'i ma //
NK027(sha)002:5205: gzhan la phan mdzad don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK027(sha)002:5206: 'di ni lhun gyis grub pa'i bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5207: sngon byang chub sems dpa' lum bi'i tshal du sku bltams pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5208: seng ge'i phru gu zung gcig gi bskor ba byas shing dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5209: rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyi gnon pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK027(sha)002:5210: de bzhin du 'dir yang seng ge'i phru gu zung gcig gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5211: phyir rgol ba thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5212: seng ge'i nga ro skad chen thogs med pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5213: 'jigs skrag med pa'i sgra rnams bsgrag nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:5214: bar du gcod pa'i bdud kyi sde btul te //
NK027(sha)002:5215: rgol ba'i phyogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5216: thams cad zil gnon cho 'phrul che ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:5217: yon tan kun tshangs gdug pa zil gyis gnon //
NK027(sha)002:5218: che ba'i mthu stobs gzhan las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:5219: 'di ni mthu stobs ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5220: sngon byang chub sems dpa' grong khyer ser skya na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5221: glang po che'i phru gu gnyis kyi snas byug cing dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5223: de bzhin du 'dir yang glang po che'i phru gu gnyis kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5224: 'jig rten 'degs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5226: theg pa bzhi'i don rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)002:5227: bye brag 'byed pa'i stobs rdzogs te //
NK027(sha)002:5228: stobs kyis pha rol phyin rdzogs shog /
NK027(sha)002:5229: mthu stobs phun sum tshogs ldan pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5230: rin chen gser rgyan kun gyis spras //
NK027(sha)002:5231: dpe byad mtshan rdzogs glang po'i stobs //
NK027(sha)002:5232: 'di ni stobs bcu ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5233: sngon byang chub sems dpa' lum bi'i tshal du sku bltams pa'i tshe //
NK027(sha)002:5234: tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyi blangs te /
NK027(sha)002:5235: na bza' ka shi ka'i ras gsol nas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5236: mkhyen pa'i ye shes gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:5237: de bzhin na bza' ka shi ka'i ras kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5238: mkhyen pa'i ye shes gsal shing ma 'dres pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5239: nyon mongs skyon spangs ka shi ka'i ras //
NK027(sha)002:5240: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus kun rdzogs te //
NK027(sha)002:5241: nyes pa'i skyon las grol ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:5242: mkhyen pa'i bye brag so sor gsal bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:5243: brgya byin bsod nams dag pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:5244: tshangs pa mngon shes lnga dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:5245: bdud rtsi chos 'khor zhu ba'i bdag /
NK027(sha)002:5246: 'di ni yon tan rin chen dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5247: sngon byang chub sems dpa' yum gyi lhum nas bltams pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5248: klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang /
NK027(sha)002:5249: nye dga' bo gnyis kyi lho phyogs chu mig rta
NK027(sha)002:5250: rnga 'dzin nas bdud rtsi'i chu blangs nas sku khrus
NK027(sha)002:5251: gsol bas / nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5252: de bzhin du 'di yang bum chu'i dbang bskur bas
NK027(sha)002:5253: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma dag pa'i
NK027(sha)002:5254: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5255: klu rgyal bdud rtsi'i chu blang ste //
NK027(sha)002:5256: bcom ldan drin lan bsab pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:5257: sku'i dri ma yongs su bkrus //
NK027(sha)002:5258: skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5259: yon tan kun ldan byang chub sems dpa'i rigs //
NK027(sha)002:5260: bcom ldan rjes dran smon lam grub pa'i mchog /
NK027(sha)002:5261: dri ma kun bkru legs pa'i mthar phyin pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5262: 'di ni sku tshe ring ba'i dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5263: sngon byang chub sems dpa' bltams nas dgung bdun lon pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5264: sh+aakya'i rigs rnams tshogs nas gzhon nu don grub par ming btags te dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5265: shes bya ma rmongs pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5266: de bzhin du 'dir yang ming gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5267: shes bya la ma rmongs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5268: rigs kyi bu khyod deng phyin chad //
NK027(sha)002:5269: ming mchog grags pas dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:5270: gzhon nu don grub yin pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:5271: rgyal ba'i don kun grub par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5272: rgyal khrims gtsang ma rgyal bu kun 'dus pas //
NK027(sha)002:5273: lha mi kun la dbang bsgyur rgyal por bskos //
NK027(sha)002:5274: kun las 'phags pa'i rgyal dbang dam pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:5275: 'di ni kun gyi dbang gi bkra shis 'dun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5276: sngon byang chub sems dpa' sru skye dgu'i bdag mos
NK027(sha)002:5277: rin po che'i bye brag gi brgyan cing dbang bskur
NK027(sha)002:5278: bas / sa rdo las byas pa'i bsam mno med par phyag gi tshur 'tshal ba'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5279: de bzhin du rgyan gyi bye brag gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5280: 'gro ba thams cad shes pa dang ldan par byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5281: mdzes pa'i rgyan rnams myur du btag nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:5282: legs pa'i yon tan kun tshang ye shes sku //
NK027(sha)002:5283: ma rigs thar lam ma lus 'dren pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:5284: rtogs pa ye shes mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5285: yon tan kun ldan sru mos mdzes par brgyan //
NK027(sha)002:5286: legs pa kun rdzogs yon tan mthar phyin pa //
NK027(sha)002:5287: che ba'i yon tan mthar phyin mi lang ste //
NK027(sha)002:5288: 'di ni legs brgyan dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5289: sngon byang chub sems dpa' kun gyi bshes gnyen la yi ge slob pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5290: tsan+dana sbrul gyi snying po can gyi byang shing la gser gyi gtsang mig btag /
NK027(sha)002:5291: rin po che sna tshogs kyi brgyan te yi ge slob pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5292: yig dpon yang sngangs te lha mi'i yi ge thams cad la mkhas pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5293: de bzhin du yi ge shing gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5294: chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5295: tsan+dana sbrul gyi yig shing la //
NK027(sha)002:5296: rin chen gser gyi gtsang mig btags //
NK027(sha)002:5297: 'gro ba'i don byed yi ge'i mthu //
NK027(sha)002:5298: pha rol zil gnon kun las rgyal //
NK027(sha)002:5299: yon tan bla med yi ge mchog /
NK027(sha)002:5300: dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5301: sngon byang chub sems dpa' sgyu rtsal gyi stobs 'dren pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5302: myes seng ge 'gram gyi gnam ru brdung bas sgra'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa byung ste /
NK027(sha)002:5303: rgyu rtsal gyi 'dul ba'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5304: de bzhin du gnam ru'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5305: snyan pa'i sgra sgrogs shing bdud dpung bzhi 'dul ba'i
NK027(sha)002:5306: mthu rtsal dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK027(sha)002:5307: gyur cig / snyan pa'i sgra sgrogs gnam ru'i mchog /
NK027(sha)002:5308: 'gro ba kun gyi yid tshim shing //
NK027(sha)002:5309: gnod pa'i bdud rnams bcoms nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:5310: ma rung 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:5311: thams cad kun 'dul mthu stobs phun sum tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:5312: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyis pha rol zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)002:5313: don dang mi ldan gdug pa zhi mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:5314: 'di ni gnam ru dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5315: sngon byang chub sems dpa'i rgyal srid khab tu bzhes pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5316: sh+aakya lag na be con gyi bu mo //
NK027(sha)002:5317: sa 'tsho ma phul te rigs mi nub cing 'gro
NK027(sha)002:5318: ba khyim dang 'du 'dzi 'dul ba'i dbang thob pa
NK027(sha)002:5319: / de bzhin du btsun mos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5320: rigs mi nub cing ci ltar 'dul ba bzhin du
NK027(sha)002:5321: 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK027(sha)002:5322: gyur cig / nor bu rin chen byi dor byas shing gsal /
NK027(sha)002:5323: sh+aakya sa 'tsho ma bkab phyar na yang /
NK027(sha)002:5324: blos mos yid gcug dang po'i sems bskyed de //
NK027(sha)002:5325: dgos pa'i don rnams yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5326: khyim dang 'du 'dzi 'dul bar gzigs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:5327: khab dang rgyal srid 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:5328: khams gsum khyim pa rnams kyis don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:5329: btsun mo'i dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5330: sngon byang chub sems dpa' grong khyer gyi phyogs bzhir
NK027(sha)002:5331: shing rta kha lo bsgyur bas 'khor ba'i chos thams
NK027(sha)002:5332: cad mi rtag par mkhyen pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5333: de bzhin du shing rta kha lo bsgyur ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5334: skye rgas na 'chi'i sdug bsngal sun phyung ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5335: rgyal srid longs spyod dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog /
NK027(sha)002:5336: 'gro ba'i don mdzad 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:5337: lha mi yongs kyi spyod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)002:5338: skye shi mi rtog pa las bzlog par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5339: rgya chen dpal 'byor longs spyod phun sum tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:5340: gling bzhi'i mtha' bskor skye rga na 'chi spongs //
NK027(sha)002:5341: 'khor ba'i skyon sel bde sbyin yon tan mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:5342: shing rta dbang gi bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5343: sngon byang chub sems dpa' khab nas byung ba'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5344: 'bangs mos pas chibs ngang pa basngagasa ldan brgyan te phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:5345: mtshan phyed la dpag tshad brgya 'das te rab tu
NK027(sha)002:5346: byung nas nyon mongs pa las thar pa'i dbang thob
NK027(sha)002:5347: pa / de bzhin chibs rta'i dbang bskur bas rab tu byung zhing /
NK027(sha)002:5348: nyon mongs pa las grol ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5349: gar yang thogs med brtson 'grus myur ba'i shugs //
NK027(sha)002:5350: tshangs pa brgya byin mthun rkyen che ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:5351: rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:5352: thogs med tshangs par spyod pa'i mthu ldan shog /
NK027(sha)002:5353: 'khor ba'i chos rnams mchil ma bzhin du dor //
NK027(sha)002:5354: nyes pa ma lus dgra rnams gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:5355: 'dod pa'i rgyu spangs rnam rtog 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:5356: chibs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5357: sngon byang chub sems dpa' mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du rab tu byung ba'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5358: sum cu rtsa gsum gyis lhas mdzes pa'i tog gi phyag shan phul te dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5359: nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5360: de bzhin du ral gris dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5361: nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5362: nyon mongs d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i ral gri ste //
NK027(sha)002:5363: mi shes nyon mongs rgyu rnams bcad nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:5364: bla med byang chub gnas su dgod bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:5365: nyon mongs sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5366: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus bcom nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:5367: bde ba'i don rtogs nags khrod dben par gnas //
NK027(sha)002:5368: bdag don lhun grub gzhan don mthar phyin pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5369: tshul khrims dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5370: sngon byang chub sems dpa' chu bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du dka' thub rdzogs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5371: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha'i bu yid bzhin 'byung bas gseg shang dang par bu phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:5372: 'gro don mthar phyin pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5373: de bzhin du gseg shang dang par bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5374: 'gro don mthar phyin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5375: ser sna'i mdud pa grol phyir gseg shang dang //
NK027(sha)002:5376: chog shes dgos pa blang phyir par bu bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:5377: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs byang chub nyid kyi sku //
NK027(sha)002:5378: bdag gzhan don gnyis mthar phyin rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5379: ma rigs gnyid slong bsal byed sgra //
NK027(sha)002:5380: lhung bzed zag med yon tan sgo //
NK027(sha)002:5381: zhi zhing dbang po rab dul ba //
NK027(sha)002:5382: zhi dul dbang gi bkra shis bac+wo lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5383: sngon byang chub sems dpa' bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5384: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha'i bu yid bzhin 'byung bas /
NK027(sha)002:5385: na bza' ngur smrig phul bas srid pa'i gdung ba las skyob pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5386: de bzhin du na bza' ngur smrig gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5387: srid pa'i gdung ba las skyobs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5388: ngan 'gro skyobs phyir na bza' chos gos gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5389: mi shes rmongs pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:5390: bag chags skyon gyi dri mas ma gos pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5391: 'bras bu byang chub gnas su grub par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5392: bslab gsum tshul khrims sgo gsum rnam par dag /
NK027(sha)002:5393: bde ba mchog brnyes srid pa'i dgra las rgyal //
NK027(sha)002:5394: rab byung dge slong rkang gnyis lha mi'i gtso //
NK027(sha)002:5395: na bza' dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5396: sngon byang chub sems dpa' chu bo nee rany+dza na'i
NK027(sha)002:5397: 'gram du dka' thub lo gnyis la 'bras nyag ma
NK027(sha)002:5398: re / lo gnyis la chu thig pa re /
NK027(sha)002:5399: lo gnyis la ci yang ma gsol bas /
NK027(sha)002:5400: nyid la 'tsho ba mi mnga' bas sku rid cing skem pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5401: grong pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas /
NK027(sha)002:5402: 'o thug 'bras chan gzhong gang phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:5403: sku gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa ltar gyur te mtshan dang dpe byad kyi dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5404: de bzhin du 'o thug 'bras chan gyi dbang bskur
NK027(sha)002:5405: bas sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyi brgyan pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:5406: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5407: nyon mongs med pa'i 'bras bu mchog /
NK027(sha)002:5408: zhi ba'i ngang la rab tu gnas //
NK027(sha)002:5409: bsod nams thob phyir bsngosa pa 'dis //
NK027(sha)002:5410: mtshan dang dpe byed rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5411: zag med bdud rtsi chos kyis ro //
NK027(sha)002:5412: bsod nams lus rdzogs ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)002:5413: mtshan dpes rab brjid rgyal ba'i sku //
NK027(sha)002:5414: dbang mchog 'bras chan bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5415: sngon byang chub sems dpa' bkra shis kyi shing drung du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5416: r+ts+wa tshong bkra shis kyi r+ts+wa rma bya'i mgrin pa
NK027(sha)002:5417: ltar sngo ba phyag tu phul ba gdan du bting
NK027(sha)002:5418: ste bzhugs pas / bar chad kyi mi tshugs pa'i dbang thob pa /
NK027(sha)002:5419: de bzhin du r+ts+wa dur ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5420: bar chad kyi mi tshugs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5421: sngon gyi drang srong rnams kyi grub pa'i rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:5422: ngo mtshar r+ts+wa mchog rma bya'i mgrin pa 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:5423: nyes med legs pa tha dag rdzogs byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5424: 'gro ba'i don du bkra shis rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5425: mnyam nyid mi g.yo rdo rje lta bu'i sku //
NK027(sha)002:5426: ting 'dzin 'jigs tshogs lta ba nyi shu 'joms //
NK027(sha)002:5427: bdud kyi tshogs btul mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5428: r+ts+wa mchog dbang gi bkra shis bac+wo brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5429: sngon bcom ldan 'das ma ga d+ha ra bsod snyoms la gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5430: spre 'us sbrang rtsi lhung bzed gang phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:5431: bkra shis pa'i rdzas la mnga' brnyes par gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:5432: de bzhin bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:5433: 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5434: rgyal srid spre'u gtso bo yi //
NK027(sha)002:5435: sbrang rtsi phul ba'i bsod nams mchog /
NK027(sha)002:5436: thugs mthun pa yi byin brlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)002:5437: bkra shis stobs mchog ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5438: stong nyid rang byung zag med snying po'i bcud //
NK027(sha)002:5439: dus gsum rgyal bas zhen med rol par mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5440: gang gi 'di 'thung mnyam nyid sku gsung rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:5441: rtsi mchog dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5442: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyes bu brgyad kyi nye 'khor na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:5443: byang phyogs kyi tshong dpon ga gon dang /
NK027(sha)002:5444: bzang pos bu ram sbrang rtsi phul ba bzhes pas
NK027(sha)002:5445: bkra shis pa'i rdzas la mnga' brnyes par gyur te
NK027(sha)002:5446: / de bzhin du bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyi dbang
NK027(sha)002:5447: bskur bas skye shi med pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK027(sha)002:5448: / cig / kun gyi snying po yon mchog dad pas phul //
NK027(sha)002:5449: mchod nas mchog gi rab bzhes 'bras bu ni //
NK027(sha)002:5450: rgyal bas lung bstan smon lam myur thob phyir //
NK027(sha)002:5451: 'di dag bkra shis thogs med rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:5452: yon tan rab rdzogs sangs rgyas mkha' na gnas //
NK027(sha)002:5453: go 'phang bla med rgyal thabs spyod pa gcig /
NK027(sha)002:5454: 'gro don mthar phyin 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK027(sha)002:5455: mdzad pa mthar phyin dbang mchog nyi shu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5456: 'di yan chad rgya che rol pa 'gro ba 'dul ba'i rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:5457: bco lnga pa lam khyer ni /
NK027(sha)002:5458: theg pa rgyu mtshan nyid byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5460: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi bskor ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:5461: snying po tad+ya g+ha te bzlas pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5462: dbang mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:5463: 'jug sgo bden pa gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK027(sha)002:5464: de'ang sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos bstan pa //
NK027(sha)002:5465: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //
NK027(sha)002:5466: 'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:5467: dam pa chos kyi bden pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5468: zhes pas kun rdzob kyi bden pa la bzhi /
NK027(sha)002:5470: ngo bo ni yul sna tshogs su snang ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:5471: de kun rdzob kyi mtshon pa'i mtshan nyid ni rigs pas dpyad na mi 'thad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5474: nges tshig ni tha snyad pa'i shes pa la snang zhing yang dag pa'i don la sgrib pa med /
NK027(sha)002:5476: gang zhig gi sems gang zhig la //
NK027(sha)002:5477: yang dag sgrib byed kun rdzob 'dod //
NK027(sha)002:5480: snang ba don byed nus pas yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK027(sha)002:5481: snang ba don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun rdzob bo //
NK027(sha)002:5482: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK027(sha)002:5483: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK027(sha)002:5484: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa //
NK027(sha)002:5485: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba byas //
NK027(sha)002:5487: don dam pa'i bden pa la bzhi ste /
NK027(sha)002:5488: mtshan nyid ngo bo ni spros pa dang bral bar snang ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:5489: don dam mtshon par byed pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK027(sha)002:5490: rigs pas dpyad na 'thad pa ste shes bya yin lugs ltar gnas pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5491: go don nam nges tshig ni /
NK027(sha)002:5492: rigs shes kyi yul yin pas don mi bslu bas dam pa /
NK027(sha)002:5493: yun gyi de'i ngo bor bden pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5495: rnam grangs kyi don dam bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5496: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam bden pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5498: spros pa phyogs gcig pa dang bral ba ste /
NK027(sha)002:5499: skye ba la sogs bkag pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:5500: yang dag pa dang mthun phyir 'dod //
NK027(sha)002:5502: gnyis pa spros pa thams cad dang bral ba ste /
NK027(sha)002:5504: yod med ces bya 'di yang mtha' /
NK027(sha)002:5505: de phyir mtha' gnyis rnam spangs nas //
NK027(sha)002:5506: mkhas pas dbus la gnas mi bya //
NK027(sha)002:5507: zhes pas dbu ma rang rgyud pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5508: thal 'gyur ba'i 'dod lugs mang du yod do //
NK027(sha)002:5509: kun rdzob rnam dpyod dgag byar byas nas bkag /
NK027(sha)002:5510: don dam yongs spyod bsgrub par byas nas bsgrub pa de 'jug go //
NK027(sha)002:5512: gang zag gi bdag gcig dang du bral gyi rtag 'dzin gyi rang bzhin med par rtogs la /
NK027(sha)002:5513: chos kyi bdag dang gzung yul thams cad sgyu ma
NK027(sha)002:5514: ltar rtogs pas phyi rol yul la bdag ma grub
NK027(sha)002:5515: la / 'dzin pa'i shes pa kun gzhi mtha' bral
NK027(sha)002:5516: du gnas pa de la skad cig tu grub pa
NK027(sha)002:5517: la / med do // de'ang chos dang gang zag bdag med na //
NK027(sha)002:5518: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' yin //
NK027(sha)002:5520: gsum pa bsrung ba'i tshul khrims ni /
NK027(sha)002:5521: byang chub sems dpa' rtsa ba'i sdom pa bzhi ni sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK027(sha)002:5522: gzhan gyi bshags kyang mi nyan par //
NK027(sha)002:5523: spros pa gzhan la 'tshogs pa sogs //
NK027(sha)002:5524: sdug bsngal mgon med gyur pa la //
NK027(sha)002:5525: ser snas chos nor ma byin len //
NK027(sha)002:5526: rnyed dang bkur stir chags pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:5527: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa sogs //
NK027(sha)002:5528: theg pa chen po spangs byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:5529: dam chos 'drar snang ston pa rdzun //
NK027(sha)002:5532: nying lag du ma ma nyams bsrungs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5536: sgom gyi ngo bo byang chub phyogs so bdun te /
NK027(sha)002:5537: chos nyid du dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi yang dag par spong ba bzhi /
NK027(sha)002:5539: sbyor lam du dbang po lnga /
NK027(sha)002:5541: mthong lam du byang chub yan lag bdun /
NK027(sha)002:5542: bsgom lam du 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad /
NK027(sha)002:5543: mthong lam du gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya /
NK027(sha)002:5544: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag go //
NK027(sha)002:5546: bdag bas gzhan gces kyi sgo nas /
NK027(sha)002:5547: sems can gyi don byed pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:5548: de'ang spyod pa'i rang bzhin phar phyin bzhi la spyod pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:5554: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa 'dzin chags med pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:5556: gling bzhi legs par brgyan pa mchil ma'i thal ba 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:5557: byin na dga' bar gyur gyi gling thob de ltar min //
NK027(sha)002:5559: nang yongs su btang ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:5560: rang gi lus srog dang bu dang chung ma la sogs pa gtong ba ste /
NK027(sha)002:5561: mgo dang yan lag gtong zhing zhum pa'i sems med kyang //
NK027(sha)002:5562: bdog pa thams cad btang zhing zhen med pa /
NK027(sha)002:5567: sems can don byed gsum mo //
NK027(sha)002:5571: phyir mi ldog pa'i brtson 'grus so //
NK027(sha)002:5573: gnod pa la ci mi snyam pa /
NK027(sha)002:5574: chos la nges par sems pa /
NK027(sha)002:5577: lam lnga sa bcu rim par bsgrod nas /
NK027(sha)002:5578: sku gsum ye shes lnga ldan kun tu 'od kyi sa thob pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5580: bdag nyid gnyis don pha rol phyin rtogs pa //
NK027(sha)002:5581: sa bcu rim gyi sgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK027(sha)002:5582: bden gnyis sangs rgyas go 'phang thob par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:5585: gnas ni bya rgod phung po'i ri'am /
NK027(sha)002:5587: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa sangs rgyas /
NK027(sha)002:5588: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' don grub /
NK027(sha)002:5590: ci'i phyir na mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i ched du'o //
NK027(sha)002:5591: dgos pa bdud dpung bcom nas chos kyi rgyal srid 'dzin pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5592: de'ang gang gi gang du ci lta bar /
NK027(sha)002:5593: tshul dgos pa rnams bcas pa rnam drug gis /
NK027(sha)002:5596: gdams ngag la bsgom tshul ni /
NK027(sha)002:5597: yul dpon yul rtsis byed pa lta bu ste /
NK027(sha)002:5598: gzhan don kho na la yongs su dmigs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5599: de dang bsgom gyi dbang du byas na bden gnyis kyi don bsgom pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:5600: de'ang kun rdzob kyi dbang du byas na dbang rdzas gtad cho ga dang /
NK027(sha)002:5601: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bya bskur byed dang
NK027(sha)002:5602: bcas pa ye shes chen po mdzad pa nyi shu'i
NK027(sha)002:5604: don dam par snying gi dkyil du thig le lcog
NK027(sha)002:5605: sgong tsam 'od kha dog gang du yang ma nges
NK027(sha)002:5606: pa gcig bsgom / de'ang thig le stong pa skye med pa /
NK027(sha)002:5608: de la brtags pas kho'i rnam pa ma 'gag pa cir yang snang ba la /
NK027(sha)002:5609: kha dog de dag la brtags pas /
NK027(sha)002:5610: phyogs gcig pa gang yang ma grub /
NK027(sha)002:5611: de bzhin du dbang bskur ba dang bcas pa ma 'gag par shar yang /
NK027(sha)002:5612: don dam par gang du yang ma dmigs /
NK027(sha)002:5613: chos nyid spros pa thams cad dang bral ba ci'i
NK027(sha)002:5614: ngo bor yang ma grub bar gnas pa yin no
NK027(sha)002:5615: // de ltar spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK027(sha)002:5616: ngang las ma g.yos par gnas pa med pa'i tshul
NK027(sha)002:5618: de'i rjes su kun rdzob ma 'gag pa'i snang cha'i
NK027(sha)002:5619: nyid yum sher phyin du lam gyi bsgom zhing spyod
NK027(sha)002:5620: lam rnam bzhi lha dang mi 'bral bar bden gnyis
NK027(sha)002:5621: zung 'jug gi lam ste ye shes ngang bsgom chen
NK027(sha)002:5622: po'o // de nas bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:5623: me tog bkram ste rol mo dang bcas pas /
NK027(sha)002:5625: dam pa tog dkar dga' ldan pho brang dam pa ru //
NK027(sha)002:5626: mi pham mgon la rgyal tshab dam par dbang bskur zhing //
NK027(sha)002:5627: 'dzam bu'i gling nyid du ni glang chen thal dkar lhums su gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:5628: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:5629: rgyal po'i khab kyi ser skya'i grong khyer zas gtsang sras //
NK027(sha)002:5630: bud med mchog gyur g.yo sgyu spang ba lha mdzes yum //
NK027(sha)002:5631: lhums su zla bcur bzhugs nas 'byor ldan sh+aakya'i rigs //
NK027(sha)002:5632: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:5633: lum bi'i tshal ni nyams dga' p+aaka sha ljon pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:5634: yal ga nas bzung bltams tshe tshangs pa brgya byin 'dus //
NK027(sha)002:5635: mkha' la gshegs te phyogs bcur pad+ma byung gyur gang //
NK027(sha)002:5636: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:5637: pho brang gzhal yas khang mdzes drang srong mdun bzhag nas //
NK027(sha)002:5638: mtshan ltas shis pa brjod med ston par 'gyur ro zhes //
NK027(sha)002:5639: sh+aag rigs bud med 'khor gyi bskor zhing rab tu brgyan //
NK027(sha)002:5640: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng pho brang nas byung phyogs bzhir skye rga na 'chi gzigs //
NK027(sha)002:5641: mi rnams smin mdzad lha yis btegs te mkha' la gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:5642: srid gsum rgyal phyir rab byung dbu skra mthon mthing breg /
NK027(sha)002:5643: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng lha'i rdzu 'phrul blang nas na bza' ngur smrig phul //
NK027(sha)002:5644: nee ra dza na thub pa'i dka' thub lo drug rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:5645: bsam gtan nas bzhengs legs skyes mas phul 'o thug bzhes //
NK027(sha)002:5646: bkra shis dam pa pad+ma la sogs khyu mchog byang chub shing drung du //
NK027(sha)002:5647: dkyil mo krung bcas mi g.yo mchog brnyes bdud btul nas //
NK027(sha)002:5648: tho rangs bdud rtsi 'chi med phun sum tshogs pa brnyes //
NK027(sha)002:5649: bkra shis dam pa wa ra na sir thog mar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK027(sha)002:5650: kun mkhyen ston pas lnga sde bzang la bden bzhi bstan //
NK027(sha)002:5651: lha dang mi dang lha min rnams kyang 'dus gyur pa //
NK027(sha)002:5652: bkra shis dam pa des kyang nga rgyal dregs pa'i mu stegs ston pa drug btul nas //
NK027(sha)002:5653: glang chen rab myos rbad pas ma rung lha sbyin btul //
NK027(sha)002:5654: drang srong mchog dang spre'usa cang shes sbrang rtsi phul //
NK027(sha)002:5655: bkra shis dam pa byams pa stobs kyi 'gro ba ma lus rab tu sgrol //
NK027(sha)002:5656: sems can thams cad smin grol zhi ba'i lam la bkod //
NK027(sha)002:5657: rtsa mchog drung du mdzad pa mthar phyin dgongs pa rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:5658: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:5659: pad+ma lta bur skyon gyi ma gos sh+aakya'i rigs //
NK027(sha)002:5660: zas gtsang sras po rgyal rigs mchog gyur 'khor los bsgyur //
NK027(sha)002:5661: sku bltams gyur pa de'i mdzad pa ma lus rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:5662: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:5663: ces brjod cing me tog gtor /
NK027(sha)002:5665: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo'o //
NK027(sha)002:5666: de ni byang chub sems dpa'i chog 'grig go //
NK027(sha)002:5667: kri ya'i theg pa'i cho ga ni /
NK027(sha)002:5668: da la mchod bshams lha tshogs bskyed //
NK027(sha)002:5669: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK027(sha)002:5670: khrus bya nang zhug gsol ba gdab //
NK027(sha)002:5671: sdom bzung chos bshad bslab bya 'bog /
NK027(sha)002:5672: dbang bskur lam khyer bzhi yang bstan //
NK027(sha)002:5673: theg sgo lta khrim ting spyod 'bras //
NK027(sha)002:5674: 'gag gnas ston 'khor the ga phyir dgod //
NK027(sha)002:5675: gdams ngag gsang sgo bkra shis sogs //
NK027(sha)002:5677: dang po dal gyi sa mtshams ni //
NK027(sha)002:5678: rab kyi rdo rje'i brag ri la'o //
NK027(sha)002:5680: pad+ma 'dab bzhi'i lte ba ser dkar sngo ba gsum dang /
NK027(sha)002:5681: 'dab drug nang du 'khor lo ser po rtsib bzhi pa /
NK027(sha)002:5682: de'i phyi la pad+ma dmar po 'dab bzhi pa /
NK027(sha)002:5683: de'i phyi sngon po rgya gram can gsum mo //
NK027(sha)002:5684: sgo rta babs sogs spyi dang mthun /
NK027(sha)002:5685: rgyas par lha nyer bdun la bskyed pa ltar lha rnams yang bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:5686: de nas bum pa'i nang du rigs gsum bskyed la dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs so //
NK027(sha)002:5696: de nas rang nyid khrus bya /
NK027(sha)002:5697: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sngon du song bas bdun rnam dag yang bya /
NK027(sha)002:5698: swa b+h+aa was bdag snang thams cad stong par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:5699: de'i ngang las mdun bskyed dal rnams rim pa bzhin /
NK027(sha)002:5700: mum las 'jam dpal ser po g.yas ral gri /
NK027(sha)002:5701: g.yon ud pa la 'dzin pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5702: h+r+aihls spyan gzigs dkar po thal mo sbyar zhing 'og
NK027(sha)002:5703: ma gnyis kyi shel phreng dang me tog dkar po
NK027(sha)002:5704: 'dzin pa / h'u las phyag na rdo rje g.yas
NK027(sha)002:5705: rdo rje g.yon sdig mdzub can te lha gsum pa'o
NK027(sha)002:5706: 'dzin pa / // dbus su sku gsung thugs kyi rigs gang mos /
NK027(sha)002:5707: shar nas rim pa bzhin sbyang ba'i lha sh+aakya thub
NK027(sha)002:5708: pa thugs ka thal mo khong stong du sbyar ba'i
NK027(sha)002:5709: nang du a dkar po can /
NK027(sha)002:5712: spel ba'i lha rnam par snang mdzad mdzod spur rin
NK027(sha)002:5713: po che'i sgrom bu sngon po phyag rgya kha bsdam
NK027(sha)002:5715: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo b+hi shwa mu khe /
NK027(sha)002:5717: bsgyur ba'i lha bdud rtsi 'khyil pa mgrin par thal mo kha gyed la dza dmar po can /
NK027(sha)002:5720: thob pa'i lha rin chen 'byung ldan g.yon mdzub mo thugs kar bsgrengs ba /
NK027(sha)002:5721: g.yas mchod sbyin la tram ser po can /
NK027(sha)002:5723: a wa lo ki te tshang ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:5724: tshim pa'i lha don yod grub pa ljang ku g.yas khu tshur /
NK027(sha)002:5725: g.yon mchod sbyin 'degs pa ha ljang gu can /
NK027(sha)002:5727: dz+ny+aa na a wa lo ki te dang dbang du
NK027(sha)002:5728: byed pa'i lha phyag na rdo rje spyi bor sor
NK027(sha)002:5729: mo nang du bsnol bar dza dmar po can /
NK027(sha)002:5731: na mahs man+ta b+hu ta nam /
NK027(sha)002:5734: lha bac+wo lnga la steng gi dbus su rnam snang /
NK027(sha)002:5735: mdun du sangs rgyas spyan ma /
NK027(sha)002:5737: g.yon du khro bo gshin rje gshed /
NK027(sha)002:5738: rgyab tu pho nya sngon po /
NK027(sha)002:5739: bar gyi dbus su 'od dpag med /
NK027(sha)002:5742: g.yon du khro bo rta mgrin /
NK027(sha)002:5743: rgyab tu pho nya rdo rje phur bu'o //
NK027(sha)002:5744: 'og gi dbus su rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK027(sha)002:5745: mdun du kun tu bzang mo /
NK027(sha)002:5746: g.yas su phyag na rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:5747: g.yon du khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba /
NK027(sha)002:5748: rgyab tu pho nya rdo rje khro bo'o //
NK027(sha)002:5750: lha rnams la khro bo bcu'o //
NK027(sha)002:5752: yang na lha rnams la bskal bzang gi sems dpa' bcu drug dgod pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:5754: rab gnas yang gong bzhin bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:5755: lha'i bum pa'i bzlas pa tshar ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:5757: khams gsum rnam rgyal dkar ljang phyag gnyis phur bu can bskyed de /
NK027(sha)002:5759: tree lokya bi dza ya h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:5763: bus ting ka ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5766: de nas bum chu phyogs bcur gtor te /
NK027(sha)002:5767: stong gsum kun du dri mchog 'byung gyur pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5768: spos dang sman sbyar chu gtsang rgyal ba'i khrus //
NK027(sha)002:5769: ye shes sprin dpung mkha' la char 'bebs pa //
NK027(sha)002:5770: mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:5771: shud+d+he shud+d+he shwo d+ha na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5772: zhes bzlas la thal mo sbyar te /
NK027(sha)002:5774: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol lo //
NK027(sha)002:5775: dus 'di nas bzung ste thog ma ma mchis pa'i bar du mi dge ba'i las bgyis pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5777: bgyid pa la rjes su yi rang ba thams cad mthol lo bshags so //
NK027(sha)002:5778: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:5779: bdag gi lus 'bul gyi bzhes su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5783: bsod nams dam pa'i dpal gyi zhing /
NK027(sha)002:5784: yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK027(sha)002:5787: mchod gnas bla na med pa'i mgon po la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK027(sha)002:5788: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5789: bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5790: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs dang /
NK027(sha)002:5795: lha dang drang srong rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5796: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK027(sha)002:5801: phyag na rdo rje la sogs pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:5802: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:5803: mchod pa cho ga la bar du gcod pa'i bgegs
NK027(sha)002:5804: dang log 'dren me ltar g.yo zhing rlung ltar 'tshub
NK027(sha)002:5805: pa / sbal pa rma can dang /
NK027(sha)002:5810: log 'dren sna yo la sogs pa thams cad 'dir ma gnas pa deng shig /
NK027(sha)002:5812: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)002:5813: mngag gzhug pho nya las byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:5814: khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yis //
NK027(sha)002:5815: bgegs kyi sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK027(sha)002:5817: na mo rat+na tra ya y+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5818: na mahs man+ta badz+ra kro ta ya /
NK027(sha)002:5819: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK027(sha)002:5820: na mahs man ta b+hu ta nan /
NK027(sha)002:5821: ka ya wa ka tsit+ta badz+ra nan /
NK027(sha)002:5823: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK027(sha)002:5824: na mahs man+ta b+hu ta nan /
NK027(sha)002:5825: ka ye waka tsit+ta badz+ra nan /
NK027(sha)002:5826: ma h+aa di sha do be re ya a mi
NK027(sha)002:5827: mu sa la ta ra ya pa ri shu pa
NK027(sha)002:5828: sha ha s+t+wa ya tad ya th+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5829: a mri ta kun+d+ha li kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK027(sha)002:5839: b+hi s+pho ta b+hi s+pho ta ya /
NK027(sha)002:5842: ma h+aa n+aa ga g+ha n+aa ti pa ye /
NK027(sha)002:5843: dz+hi tra bi tshin+d+ha an d+ha ka ra ya /
NK027(sha)002:5851: ta th+aa ga to ba b+ha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5852: badz+roda b+ha wa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5853: zhes brjod pas rigs gsum 'khor dang bcas pa dmigs la /
NK027(sha)002:5854: 'jig rten dag ni phyogs bcu na //
NK027(sha)002:5855: de bzhin gshegs pa gang bzhugs dang //
NK027(sha)002:5856: dgra bcom byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK027(sha)002:5857: bdag gi ma 'tshams sdig bgyis dang /
NK027(sha)002:5858: gang yang bgyid du stsal ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:5859: rjes su yi rang bgyis la sogs //
NK027(sha)002:5860: bag med pa ni phra mo yang //
NK027(sha)002:5861: lus ngag yid kyi bgyis pa rnams //
NK027(sha)002:5862: yang dang yang du mthol zhing bshags //
NK027(sha)002:5863: slan chad de ltar yang mi bgyid //
NK027(sha)002:5864: bdag gi mi dge bgyis pa rnams //
NK027(sha)002:5865: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi mkhyen pa ltar //
NK027(sha)002:5866: bdag kyang de ltar dam bca' 'o //
NK027(sha)002:5867: srog chags sdug bsngal zhi bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:5868: ci srid byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK027(sha)002:5869: de nas mchog gi sa bon gang //
NK027(sha)002:5870: thar pa'i bdud rtsi 'bras bu smin //
NK027(sha)002:5871: shin tu sgom pas mchog gyur te //
NK027(sha)002:5872: dngos grub phyir ni de bskyed do //
NK027(sha)002:5873: dge ba'i las rnams gang dag kun //
NK027(sha)002:5874: 'di dang gzhan du bsags rnams kyi //
NK027(sha)002:5875: chos kyi longs spyod sna tshogs la //
NK027(sha)002:5876: mnyam par bzhag pas yid rang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:5877: sngon gyi rgyal ba sras bcas kyi //
NK027(sha)002:5878: smon lam ci ltar btab pa ltar //
NK027(sha)002:5879: bdag kyang dge ba kun rtogs nas //
NK027(sha)002:5880: de bzhin du ni smon lam 'debs //
NK027(sha)002:5881: 'phags pa rnams kyi rjes dgongs te //
NK027(sha)002:5882: mgon ma mchis pa bdag myur du //
NK027(sha)002:5883: sangs rgyas grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5885: 'phags pa'i tshogs rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5886: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi gzigs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:5887: de'ang dus drug lha'i nyi ma thams cad dge /
NK027(sha)002:5888: gza' skar thams cad bkra shis /
NK027(sha)002:5889: dgra bcom thams cad zag pa zad /
NK027(sha)002:5890: sangs rgyas thams cad rdzu 'phrul che ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK027(sha)002:5891: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas
NK027(sha)002:5892: pa thams cad spyan 'dren phyag 'tshal gshegs su gsol
NK027(sha)002:5893: / stobs bcu'i rtsal mnga' mi'i seng ge gshegs /
NK027(sha)002:5894: gti mug mun sel 'jig rten sgron ma gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:5895: nyon mongs nad sel sman pa'i rgyal po gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:5896: bdud bzhi pham mdzad thar pa'i lam ston dbang mchog rgyal po 'dir byon phrin las mdzod /
NK027(sha)002:5897: na mahs man+ta b+hu ta nam /
NK027(sha)002:5899: sa mi tri sa me ma h+aa sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5900: phyogs bcur rgya yang ma chad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5901: rin chen lhun grub gzhal yas khang //
NK027(sha)002:5902: dbye sdom rtogs pa mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)002:5903: srid zhu'i tshul du sgo dabye'o //
NK027(sha)002:5904: badz+ra s+pho ta ga ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5906: tshur gshegs 'dir ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5907: bdag gi mchod pa bzhes nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:5908: thugs la dgongs shing gnang bar mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:5909: a ha ra a ha ra sarba b+hi d+ha ra p+au dza ga na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5910: rin chen ye shes gzhal yas nas //
NK027(sha)002:5911: pad+ma nyi ma'i gdan steng du //
NK027(sha)002:5912: bde gshegs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK027(sha)002:5913: 'gro ba'i don du bzhugs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:5914: pad+ma a wa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5915: de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:5916: rab 'byams rgya tsho dpag med du //
NK027(sha)002:5917: mchod yon ci snyed yod pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:5918: bdag gi gus pas bshams pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:5919: rgyal ba sras dang bcas la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:5920: lha rdzas bzang dang me tog bdug spos mar me
NK027(sha)002:5921: dri mchog zhal zas rol mo rgyal ba sras dang
NK027(sha)002:5922: 'gro ba'i don du bzhes su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:5923: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa p+aa ri wa ra ar+g+ham pra ti dza ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5928: shab+da pra ti dza ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:5930: yon tan rin chen mang po'i tshogs mnga' zhing //
NK027(sha)002:5931: mtshan rab ye shes yongs su dag pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)002:5932: gser gyi mdog can lha dang mis mchod pa //
NK027(sha)002:5933: bcom ldan lha yi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5934: dam chos nyi ma'i 'od zer stong 'phro bas //
NK027(sha)002:5935: skye bo srid pa'i chu bo sgrol bar mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5936: thar pa'i lam ston 'dren pa'i them skas mchog /
NK027(sha)002:5937: ma lus skem pa'i gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5938: bder gshegs sras po dge 'dun me tog grol //
NK027(sha)002:5939: thugs rje chen pos yid ni rang byung ste //
NK027(sha)002:5940: blo spyan bye bar gyur pa de dag la //
NK027(sha)002:5941: rgyun mi chad par spyi bos phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5942: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)002:5943: mi gdung mi g.yo mnyam bzhag kyang //
NK027(sha)002:5944: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen gter //
NK027(sha)002:5945: bsam pa tsam gyi gnas su phyin //
NK027(sha)002:5946: bltas pa tsam gyi grub par mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:5947: snang mdzad khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5948: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas ni //
NK027(sha)002:5949: sngon dus bskal pa grangs med nas //
NK027(sha)002:5950: 'khor ba'i skyon rnams sel mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:5951: las dang nyon mongs sa bon las //
NK027(sha)002:5952: dgongs nas srid pa stong mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:5953: snang mtha' khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5954: bcom ldan mi bskyod rdo rje ni //
NK027(sha)002:5956: lta ba rtogs pa rnam bsil te //
NK027(sha)002:5958: spyan 'dren dus ldan byin rlabs so //
NK027(sha)002:5959: mi bskyod pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5960: dpal gyi dam pa 'jam dbyangs dpal //
NK027(sha)002:5961: ye shes gsung mdzes gsung snyan ni //
NK027(sha)002:5962: mthong thos kun dang yid mthun pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5963: gzhon nur gyur la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5964: shes rab thugs rje che ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:5965: mtshan brgya phrag bcu'i spyan gyis gzigs //
NK027(sha)002:5966: sems can kun gyi dpung dang skyabs //
NK027(sha)002:5967: rtag par brtse la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5968: rigs pa'i rgyal po grub pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:5969: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam yas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:5972: rigs kyi yum mchog sangs rgyas spyan //
NK027(sha)002:5974: phyag na thor gtsug rgyan gyis spras //
NK027(sha)002:5976: rigs kyis yum chen gos dkar mo //
NK027(sha)002:5980: rigs kyi yum mchog ma ma ki //
NK027(sha)002:5982: phyag na rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:5983: rdo rje mkha' 'gro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:5984: dpal gyi lha mo sku mdog dkar //
NK027(sha)002:5985: chu skyes dkar po phyag na bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:5986: grags ldan ma ni shel ltar dkar //
NK027(sha)002:5988: stobs chen ma ni mig sman mdog /
NK027(sha)002:5989: phyag na rdo rje rtse gcig go //
NK027(sha)002:5990: mdzod sprul ma ni zla ba'i 'od //
NK027(sha)002:5991: phyag gi yid bzhin nor bu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:5992: lu gu rgyud la gser gyis mdog /
NK027(sha)002:5994: rnam par rgyal ma kun d+ha'i mdog /
NK027(sha)002:5996: gshin rje gshed po smug nag 'bar //
NK027(sha)002:5997: bee con dbyug to klad la phyar //
NK027(sha)002:5998: khro bo'i rgyal po rta mgrin dmar //
NK027(sha)002:6000: khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang //
NK027(sha)002:6001: pho nya skra chen ma mo'i mdog /
NK027(sha)002:6002: pho nya phur bu le brgan mdog /
NK027(sha)002:6003: rdo rje phur bu drag tu bsgril //
NK027(sha)002:6004: pho nya lcags kyu sngo zhing nag /
NK027(sha)002:6005: lcags kyus dbang du sdud pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:6006: sems dpa'i mdog can seng ge bcibs //
NK027(sha)002:6007: dmar po pad+ma rgyas pa can //
NK027(sha)002:6008: lha chen dmar po rtse gsum ste //
NK027(sha)002:6009: khyab mjug mthing ga 'khor lo can //
NK027(sha)002:6010: mthu stobs dbang phyug phun tshogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:6013: de dag kyang rim pa bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:6015: bee ro tsa na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6016: a mi d+he wa h+r+aihs+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6017: badz+ra a k+sho b+h+ya h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6018: many+dzu sh+r+ai ku ma ra mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6019: a wa lo ki t+ya ka ru na ma ram h'u dza s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6020: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6021: ru ru phu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi lo tsa ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6022: ban+da lo ki ta ram pa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6023: sug sme dz+ny+aa na dza h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6024: ma h+aa sh+r+ai ya tsi ri mi ri ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6025: tra ka pa ri te te shan te shan s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6027: sarba d+harma ni pe ta ni badz+ra si pa ri ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6028: badz+ra ta badz+re pra b+ha te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6029: b+had+ha b+han me h+aa ya badz+roda b+ha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6030: b+han d+ha b+han mo ha ya mo h+aa ya badz+roda b+ha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6031: dz+wa la dz+wa la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6032: badz+ra yak+sha kro ta h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:6033: kha rga b+ha na s+pho ta ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6034: a mri ta ha na bi du na bi du
NK027(sha)002:6035: na go pa kha a mri te ma kha s+w+aa
NK027(sha)002:6036: h+aa / b+h+ra ma ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6037: ga na pa ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK027(sha)002:6040: de nas cha gsum rgyas pa gong bzhin btang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:6041: de nas slob bu rnams khrus bya phyag dang man+dala phul /
NK027(sha)002:6042: thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:6043: bla ma dkon mchog gsum po dang //
NK027(sha)002:6044: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK027(sha)002:6045: bdag la dgongs shing gzigs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:6046: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:6047: yi dam gtso 'khor dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:6048: lha dang byin rlabs dam tshig dang //
NK027(sha)002:6049: dbang rnams rim par bskur du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:6050: zhes gsol ba lan gsum gdab /
NK027(sha)002:6052: yi dam dbang bskur dam tshig sbyin //
NK027(sha)002:6053: gus pa'i sems kyi bsgrub par bgyis //
NK027(sha)002:6054: nyes pa dag ni ma gos na //
NK027(sha)002:6057: de nas rigs gsum spyi'i dam tshig bzung ba'i bsam pas /
NK027(sha)002:6058: bla med dkon mchog gsum po la //
NK027(sha)002:6059: bdag ni rtag tu skyabs su mchi //
NK027(sha)002:6060: bdag gi sangs rgyas bstan pa la //
NK027(sha)002:6061: spyi dang mi 'gal legs gnas te //
NK027(sha)002:6062: theg chen gsang sngags bya ba'i gzhung //
NK027(sha)002:6063: khyad par dam tshig bdag gi bzung //
NK027(sha)002:6064: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK027(sha)002:6065: theg pa chen po sngags kyi lha //
NK027(sha)002:6066: don gcig gnyis med ye shes don //
NK027(sha)002:6067: yang dag nyid du bdag gi bzung //
NK027(sha)002:6068: sku'i rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK027(sha)002:6069: dam tshig sdom pa la gnas te //
NK027(sha)002:6070: bsgrub pa dag kyang ci nus brtsam //
NK027(sha)002:6071: pad+ma'i rigs mchog dag pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:6072: phyi nang gsang ba'i gsung sgrogs te //
NK027(sha)002:6073: dam pa'i chos kyi ma lus bzung //
NK027(sha)002:6074: rdo rje rigs mchog dam tshig ni //
NK027(sha)002:6075: rdo rje dril bu'i phyag rgya yang //
NK027(sha)002:6076: bla ma rdo rje rigs brten bya //
NK027(sha)002:6077: mtha' yas sems can don gyi phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6078: gsang sngags dam tshig bdag gi blang //
NK027(sha)002:6079: yang dag par ni bzung bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:6080: byang chub sems dpa' mchog bsgrub bgyi //
NK027(sha)002:6083: phyi pa mu stegs pa las nang pa khyad par 'phags shing /
NK027(sha)002:6084: nang pa la yang lha mi /
NK027(sha)002:6087: byang sems de dag rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:6088: de dag las 'dir gsang sngags kyi theg pa khyad par du 'phags te /
NK027(sha)002:6090: don gcig la yang ma rmongs dang //
NK027(sha)002:6091: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:6092: dbang po rnon po dbang byas pas //
NK027(sha)002:6093: gsang sngags theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:6096: kri ya'i dam tshig bcu gsum ste //
NK027(sha)002:6097: de ring phan chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK027(sha)002:6098: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK027(sha)002:6099: gsang sngags gzugs sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK027(sha)002:6100: dad pas rab tu brtan par bya //
NK027(sha)002:6101: rtag tu phyag rgya chen po la //
NK027(sha)002:6102: khyad par du yang mos par bya //
NK027(sha)002:6103: dam tshig can dang 'dza' bo bya //
NK027(sha)002:6104: bla ma la ni gus par bya //
NK027(sha)002:6105: lha rnams kun la sdang mi bya //
NK027(sha)002:6106: dus mtshams dag tu mchod pa bya //
NK027(sha)002:6107: ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi chod //
NK027(sha)002:6108: rtag tu bla ma mchod mgron bya //
NK027(sha)002:6109: srog chags rnams la byams pa'i sems //
NK027(sha)002:6110: rab tu brtan por nye bar bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:6111: theg pa mchog la dga' rnams kyi //
NK027(sha)002:6112: bsod nams tshogs la nan tan bskyed //
NK027(sha)002:6113: bzlas brjod byed la 'bad par bya //
NK027(sha)002:6114: gsang sngags rgyud la bstan pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:6115: dam tshig rnams kyang bsrung bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:6116: dam tshig med pa rnams la ni //
NK027(sha)002:6117: sngags dang phyag rgya sbyin mi bya //
NK027(sha)002:6118: gsang sngags rgyud nas legs gsung zhing //
NK027(sha)002:6119: de yang bdag gi rtogs par gyis //
NK027(sha)002:6121: de nas bum pa'i chu sbyin zhing /
NK027(sha)002:6122: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK027(sha)002:6123: dam tshig 'das na bsregs par byed //
NK027(sha)002:6124: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK027(sha)002:6125: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'dis grub //
NK027(sha)002:6127: de nas man+dala du me tog gtor te /
NK027(sha)002:6128: rig brtags te ming btag go //
NK027(sha)002:6129: de nas lha dbang rim bzhin thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:6130: bum pa spyi bor gtug la /
NK027(sha)002:6132: don dam bden pa'i chos nyid la //
NK027(sha)002:6133: mi dmigs sems dpa'i mngon sum du //
NK027(sha)002:6134: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:6135: rigs gsum kri ya'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:6137: pad+ma a mi d+he wa h+r+aih badz+ra ak+sho b+h+ya h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6138: w+aa gi shwa ri a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6139: dkon mchog gsum dang kri ya rigs gsum lha tshogs kyi byin rlabs kyi /
NK027(sha)002:6140: rigs gsum bu la bum pas dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:6141: kri ya don gyi lha drug gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6144: d+h+ai dpal gyi 'byung gnas 'jam dpal kun gyi dpal /
NK027(sha)002:6145: tha dag yongs la khyab pa 'jam dpal ngang //
NK027(sha)002:6146: 'jam dang dpal du grags pa'i don dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:6147: 'jam dpal yang dag dpal gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:6148: w+aa gi shwa ri a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u //
NK027(sha)002:6149: yon tan rgyas pa'i sku mdog gser dang mtshungs //
NK027(sha)002:6150: shes rab rtags su po ti ral gri bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6151: 'phags pa 'jam dpal shes bya gang yin pa //
NK027(sha)002:6152: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:6153: h+r+aih dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa chos kyi sku //
NK027(sha)002:6154: nam mkha' lta bur khyab pa'i bcu gcig zhal //
NK027(sha)002:6155: gzi brjid 'od dpag med kyi dbang bskur ro /
NK027(sha)002:6158: thugs rjes rtag tu sku mdog zla ba'i 'od //
NK027(sha)002:6159: ma chags skyon gyi ma gos pad+ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6160: spyan ras gzigs kyi bkra shis deng 'dir shog /
NK027(sha)002:6162: lcang lo can gyi gnas mchog dam pa ni //
NK027(sha)002:6163: gsang sngags rigs sngags kun gyi bdag po ste //
NK027(sha)002:6164: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:6165: bcom ldan rdo rje can gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:6167: a b+hi chos nyid mi 'gyur rtag tu sku mdog sngo //
NK027(sha)002:6168: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med rdo rje 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:6169: mthu stobs can gyi deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:6171: sh+aakya thub pa nyes skyon sbyongs ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:6172: sku mdog ser po thal mo khong stong can //
NK027(sha)002:6173: de'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6174: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho sarba a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6175: rnam par snang mdzad yon tan spel ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:6176: dkar po mdzod spur rin chen sgrom bu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:6177: de'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6178: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo b+hi shwa mu khe b+h+ya /
NK027(sha)002:6182: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba mos par bsgyur ba'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:6183: ljang gu mgrin par thal mo kha bskyed mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:6184: de'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6185: a mri ta kun+d+ha li h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6188: rgyal chen shugs ldan ser po thob pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:6189: g.yas pas mchod sbyin g.yon pas mdzub mo bsgreng //
NK027(sha)002:6190: de'i dbang mchog a wa lo ki te a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6191: don yod grub pa thams cad tshim pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:6192: ljang gu g.yas g.yon khu tshur mchod sbyin can //
NK027(sha)002:6193: de'i sa mat+na ra smi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6194: phyag na rdo rje dbang du byed pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:6195: sngon po spyi bor sor bskum the'u bsgreng //
NK027(sha)002:6196: de yi a sa man+ta b+hu ta nan /
NK027(sha)002:6198: rigs bdag sku mchog rnam snang mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:6199: nyes pa'i skyon bral sku mdog dkar //
NK027(sha)002:6200: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:6201: de'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6203: 'jam pa'i dbyangs ni sku yi rigs //
NK027(sha)002:6205: phyag na ral gri ut+pala bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6207: rigs kyi yum mchog sangs rgyas spyan //
NK027(sha)002:6208: dkar mo'i phyag na spyan 'bras bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6210: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NK027(sha)002:6211: smug nag be con klad la phyar //
NK027(sha)002:6213: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6214: ba mo'i len sku chan pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:6216: mdzod sprul ma ni zla ba'i 'od //
NK027(sha)002:6217: phyag gi yid bzhin nor bu 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:6218: sku yi rigs kyis dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:6220: lha chen tshangs pa seng ge bcibs //
NK027(sha)002:6221: dmar po pad+ma rgyas pa can //
