NK027(sha)002:6222: de yi bee ro tsa na /
NK027(sha)002:6223: a b+hi +aah rigs bdag gsung mchog snang mtha' yas //
NK027(sha)002:6224: thugs rjes chags pas sku mdog dmar //
NK027(sha)002:6225: ting 'dzin mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:6227: spyan ras gzigs dbang gsung gi rigs //
NK027(sha)002:6228: dmar po phyag na pad+ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6230: rigs kyi yum mchog gos dkar mo //
NK027(sha)002:6231: dmar po phyag na pad+ma bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6233: khro bo'i rgyal po rta mgrin dmar //
NK027(sha)002:6236: pho nya phur bu le brgan mdog /
NK027(sha)002:6237: rdo rje phur bu drag tu bsgril //
NK027(sha)002:6239: lu gu rgyud ma gser gyi mdog /
NK027(sha)002:6242: lha chen ma h+aa d+he wa ni //
NK027(sha)002:6243: dmar po phyag na rtse gsum thogs //
NK027(sha)002:6245: rigs bdag thugs mchog rdo rje sems //
NK027(sha)002:6246: chos nyid mi 'gyur sku mdog sngo //
NK027(sha)002:6247: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK027(sha)002:6249: phyag na rdo rje thugs kyi rigs //
NK027(sha)002:6250: sngon po phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6252: yum chen bzang mo sku mdog sngo //
NK027(sha)002:6253: phyag na rdo rje rtse gsum can //
NK027(sha)002:6255: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang //
NK027(sha)002:6256: rdo rje rgya gram klad la bskor //
NK027(sha)002:6258: pho nya lcags kyu sngo zhing nag /
NK027(sha)002:6259: lcags kyus dbang du sdud pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:6261: rnam par rgyal ba kun d+ha'i mdog /
NK027(sha)002:6264: lha chen khyab 'jug chen po ni //
NK027(sha)002:6265: sku mdog mthing ga 'khor lo bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6267: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6268: dpa' bar 'gro dkar ral gri ste //
NK027(sha)002:6269: de'i dbang b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6271: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6272: kun nas gang ltar rang bzhin ni //
NK027(sha)002:6273: de'i dbang mchog b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6275: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6277: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6279: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6280: bzang skyongs dung mdog bum pa can //
NK027(sha)002:6281: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6283: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6285: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6287: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6288: nam mkha' mdzod ni rin chen sgrom //
NK027(sha)002:6289: dbang mchog dam pa b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6291: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6292: nam snying rdo rje rtse gsum can //
NK027(sha)002:6293: dbang mchog b+ho a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6294: bskal pa bzang po'i 'od dpag med ni rin chen sgrom //
NK027(sha)002:6296: bskal pa bzang mya ngan kun 'joms ral gri phyar //
NK027(sha)002:6297: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6299: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6300: ye shes tog ni rin chen tog /
NK027(sha)002:6301: dbang mchog b+ho a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6302: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6303: spob pa brtsegs ni rin chen gnyer //
NK027(sha)002:6304: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi sa t+wa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6306: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6307: blo gros mi bzad glegs bam can //
NK027(sha)002:6308: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6309: bskal pa bzang byams pa klu shing spyi blug can //
NK027(sha)002:6310: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6311: bskal pa bzang po'i spos kyi glang pos dung dkar 'bud //
NK027(sha)002:6312: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6313: bskal pa bzang po'i sems dpa' ni //
NK027(sha)002:6315: dbang mchog b+ho d+hi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6316: bskal pa don kun 'grub byed rgya gram 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:6317: dbang mchog dam b+ho a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6318: shar du dus ldan pad+ma can //
NK027(sha)002:6319: dkar mo dpal ber 'khor lo bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:6320: lha mo de'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:6321: tram mam ga la de wi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6324: lha mo de'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:6325: tram mam ga la de wi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6326: nub tu mdangs can dri ma med //
NK027(sha)002:6327: dmar mo gdugs dang bum pa 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:6328: lha mo de'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:6329: tram mam ga la de wi a b+hi h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6330: byang du skyal gsung yid bzang ma //
NK027(sha)002:6331: ljang gu dung dang gser nya 'dzin //
NK027(sha)002:6332: lha mo de'i dbang tram mam ga la de wi a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:6333: zhes pa yan chad lha dbang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:6335: rdzas dbang 'di 'og u pa ya la'ang sbyor byas kyi /
NK027(sha)002:6336: de nas rdzas dbang rnams kyi dang po rgya mtsho gtad la /
NK027(sha)002:6338: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgya mtsho chen po'i gling du gshegs pa'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:6339: dpal phyag na rdo rje la rgya mtsho chen pos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6340: skye ba med pa'i chos zab cing rgya che ba rgyud la rtogs par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6341: de bzhin du rgya mtsho chen pos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6342: skye ba med pa gting zab cing rgya mtsho yangs
NK027(sha)002:6343: pa kun tu snyams pa'i yon tan chen po ste
NK027(sha)002:6344: / skye 'gags med pa rgya mtsho chen po las
NK027(sha)002:6345: zab cing rgya mtsho chen po las zab cing rgya
NK027(sha)002:6346: che ba'i chos don rtogs par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6347: chos nyid rgya mtsho lta bu thugs chud nas //
NK027(sha)002:6348: zab cing gting dpag dka' ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK027(sha)002:6349: yid bzhin nor bu kha dog mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:6350: 'di ni rgya mtsho dbang gi bkra shis gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6352: sngon bcom ldan 'das mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyin pa'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:6353: u dum wa ra'i me tog dang sbyar nas /
NK027(sha)002:6354: dpal phyag na rdo rje la rang byung gi mchod
NK027(sha)002:6355: rten dang sprul pa'i mchod rten la sogs pas dbang
NK027(sha)002:6356: bskur bas rnam par mi rtog pa'i chos kyi sku
NK027(sha)002:6358: de bzhin du 'dir yang mchod rten chen po'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6359: chos sku thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6360: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa'i bang rim las /
NK027(sha)002:6361: skye 'gag med pa'i bum pa zlum pos brgyan //
NK027(sha)002:6362: chos kyi 'khor lo ma 'dres rtogs la sogs //
NK027(sha)002:6363: rnam par mi rtog chos sku thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6364: lta ba'i sa dang mngon par byang chub mtshungs pa mi mnga' yang //
NK027(sha)002:6365: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor dang cho 'phrul ston la sogs //
NK027(sha)002:6366: lha yul nas gshegs ston pa dbyings su bzhugs //
NK027(sha)002:6367: stobs bcu mthar phyin mnga' ba'i mchod rten dbang gi bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6369: sngon bcom ldan 'das gyad yul gyi nye 'khor na bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:6370: dpal phyag na rdo rje la dpag bsam shing gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6371: dgos 'dod thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6372: de bzhin du dpag bsam shing gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6373: dgos 'dod thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6374: gang la ci 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //
NK027(sha)002:6375: yon tan zad med yid bzhin gter dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:6376: rten pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul yin te //
NK027(sha)002:6377: dgos pa'i don rnams yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6378: lha'i re bskang dpag bsam ljon shing ltar //
NK027(sha)002:6379: 'phags pa'i yon tan brjod kyis mi langs te //
NK027(sha)002:6380: re ba yid bzhin phun sum tshogs pa'i rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:6381: 'dod dgu'i 'byung gnas rin chen dpag bsam shing //
NK027(sha)002:6382: 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6383: de nas rdzas dbang rim par thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:6384: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyis zom la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:6385: dpal phyag na rdo rje la rin chen sna lnga'i ri rab kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6386: mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan te /
NK027(sha)002:6387: mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:6388: rin chen sna lnga'i ri rab kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6389: mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa de mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6390: gzi brjid lhun sdug ri rab mchog gi sku //
NK027(sha)002:6391: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i bang rim mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6392: thams cad gnas pa'i ri bo chen po la //
NK027(sha)002:6393: mthu stobs mi 'gyur sku rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6394: skye ba 'gro drug khams rnams yongs kyis srog /
NK027(sha)002:6395: kha dog mdzes legs rin chen sna tshogs zhing //
NK027(sha)002:6396: phyogs bzhi dbus kyis rigs dang skur bstan pa //
NK027(sha)002:6397: 'di ni rin chen sna lnga'i ri rab kyi //
NK027(sha)002:6398: dbang gi bkra shis le'u bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6399: sngon byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje gdan drung na bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:6400: dpal phyag na rdo rje la sa gzhi chen po gnas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6401: bkra shis byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6402: de bzhin du sa gzhi gnas kyi sa dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6403: bkra shis byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6404: rab tu dben pa'i gnas mchog dam pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:6405: me tog dri bsung mang po skye ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:6406: yon tan tshangs pa ma lus kun rdzogs te //
NK027(sha)002:6407: bden pa'i bkra shis 'byor ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:6408: me tog mdzes ldan yid 'ong brgyan pa'i gnas //
NK027(sha)002:6409: chos kyi sgra snyan sna tshogs sgra skad sgrogs //
NK027(sha)002:6410: yon tan kun ldan ston pa'i byin rlabs nas //
NK027(sha)002:6411: gnas gzhi dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6412: sngon bcom ldan 'das wa ra na sir bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6413: dpal phyag na rdo rje la bdud rtsi chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6414: skye 'chi mi mnga' ba'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6415: de bzhin du bdud rtsi bum pa'i chus dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6416: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6417: bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun 'gro ba'i gsob kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6418: nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad rnams ma lus la //
NK027(sha)002:6419: ma rig dag byed bdud rtsi'i chu mchog ste //
NK027(sha)002:6420: skye shi med pa dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:6421: bum pa'i kha rgyan dpag bsam shing //
NK027(sha)002:6422: dbang bskur bum par spyi blug pa //
NK027(sha)002:6423: bdud rtsi bum pa 'dir stsol cig /
NK027(sha)002:6424: 'di ni bdud rtsi chu bo'i rgyun dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6425: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zom la bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6426: dbang po brgya byin gyi chos zhus pa'i da ru
NK027(sha)002:6427: kad za rang tshag phul bas chos sgra chen po
NK027(sha)002:6428: sgrog pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6429: de bzhin da ru kad kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6430: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6431: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po mnga' brnyes shing //
NK027(sha)002:6432: ma rig mun pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:6433: rmongs pa'i shes pa ma lus sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6434: chos rnams thams cad gang bzhin sgrogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6435: 'jam mnyen reg bde dar gyi za ra tshags //
NK027(sha)002:6436: lhab lhub dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6437: sngon bcom ldan 'das sum cu rtsa gsum gyii gnas
NK027(sha)002:6438: su brgya byin la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK027(sha)002:6439: tshe / rin po che'i khri rkang phul nas bzhugs
NK027(sha)002:6440: pas chos shes pa'i rgyud la go zhing sgrogs par
NK027(sha)002:6441: tshe / gyur to // de bzhin du rat+na'i khri rkang gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6442: chos ma nor bar go zhing sgrogs pa'i dbang thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6443: rin chen gser gyi khri stengs su //
NK027(sha)002:6444: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:6445: 'gro ba rnams kyi mi shes grol //
NK027(sha)002:6446: chos rnams go zhing sgrogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6447: tshad med bzhi ldan legs byed gser gyis khri //
NK027(sha)002:6448: yon tan tshogs rdzogs rin chen sna tshogs 'char //
NK027(sha)002:6449: 'gro ba'i yid bzhin zad med dgos 'dod bskang //
NK027(sha)002:6450: khri mchog dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6451: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6452: brgya byin gyi me tog chun po bres pas sems
NK027(sha)002:6453: can 'khor ba las bslu shing bred pa'i mchog tu
NK027(sha)002:6454: gyur to // de bzhin du me tog chun pos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6455: 'khor ba la yid dbyung ba mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6456: sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:6457: kha dog ma 'dres so sor gsal ba mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6458: sems can kun gyi lta bar 'os pa'i gnas //
NK027(sha)002:6459: mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6460: me tog chu skyes thang skyes dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:6461: rin chen phreng ldan me tog chun por 'beb //
NK027(sha)002:6462: 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6463: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab khang pa brtsegs par /
NK027(sha)002:6464: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6465: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu nyi 'od dam pas /
NK027(sha)002:6466: rnga yab kyi g.yas pas gzi mdangs dang ldan par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6467: de bzhin du rnga yab kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6468: dgyes pa chen po'i gzi brjid dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6469: snyan pa'i sgra rnams ma lus sgrogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:6470: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dri ma ma lus pa //
NK027(sha)002:6471: thams cad myur du go ba'i blo thob nas //
NK027(sha)002:6472: bkra shis gzi mdangs mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6473: rgyal ba'i sku la nyes pa ma gos kyang //
NK027(sha)002:6474: dag cing bsil bar byed pa'i rnga yab 'di //
NK027(sha)002:6475: sku'i dri ma ljan ljin dag par byed //
NK027(sha)002:6476: rnga yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6477: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6478: sum cu rtsa gsum gyis lha'i bu kun nas 'od zer byung bas rdul g.yab kyi rdul g.yab pas /
NK027(sha)002:6479: chos nyid skyon gyi gos par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6480: de bzhin du lha'i rdul g.yab kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6481: chos nyid zab mo'i don la 'jug pa'i dbang thob
NK027(sha)002:6482: par nyon mongs rdul rnams ma lus phyi ba dang
NK027(sha)002:6483: // dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK027(sha)002:6484: ma chags skyon gyi dri ma bsal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6485: bkra shis gtsang ma'i ras kyi sku phyi bas //
NK027(sha)002:6486: rdul g.yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6487: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6488: sum cu rtsa gsum lha'i bu zhig gi sbrang g.yab kyi g.yab pas /
NK027(sha)002:6489: sems can du 'dzin pa'i skyon las grol bar gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6490: de bzhin du lha'i sbrang g.yab kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6491: 'dzin chags kyi skyon las grol ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6492: nyon mongs sems can ma rig bsal ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:6493: 'bras bu thar pa'i go 'phang thob pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:6494: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhabs drung 'khor ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6495: 'jig rten skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6496: drang srong chen po bsam gtan gnas pa la //
NK027(sha)002:6497: srog chags gdug pa'i gzugs brnyan bsam pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6498: rnga yab rgyal ba'i ring bsrel bskor ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6499: sbrang g.yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6500: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6501: 'khor rnam bzhi'i bla re bres pas nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba zhi bar gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6502: de bzhin du bla re'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6503: nyon mongs pa'i rdul gyi dri mas ma gos pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6504: chos 'khor bskor phyir bla re bre //
NK027(sha)002:6505: mi'i rgyal po bder gshegs bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK027(sha)002:6506: dbang phyug chen po'i mnga' bdag chen po ste //
NK027(sha)002:6507: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma med par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6508: dpag bsam ljon shing me tog lo 'dab rgyas //
NK027(sha)002:6509: nyi zla gza' skar mang pos sprin gtib nas //
NK027(sha)002:6510: bkra shis bya skad mang po 'phur zhing lding //
NK027(sha)002:6511: dar zab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6512: sngon bcom ldan 'das bya rgod phung po'i rir chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6515: che ba'i yon tan mi nub nub pa med pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6516: de bzhin du rgyal mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6517: che ba'i yon tan nub pa med pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6518: lhun grub sku brnyes rdzogs pa'i rgyal mtshan te /
NK027(sha)002:6519: nub dang 'dzad med dus med slar zhing rgyas //
NK027(sha)002:6520: yon tan mchog gyur kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:6521: che ba'i yon tan nub pa med par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6522: dpa' brjid mdzes pa'i 'jig rten yongs kyis rgyan //
NK027(sha)002:6523: bdud dang mu stegs tshogs dpung 'joms par byed //
NK027(sha)002:6524: rgyal ba'i sku dang dbyer med tshul gcig gis //
NK027(sha)002:6525: rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6526: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6527: 'khor rnams kyis tsha ba'i gdung ba la gdugs kyi
NK027(sha)002:6528: bkab pas tsha ba'i gdung ba zhi bar gyur to
NK027(sha)002:6529: // de bzhin du gdugs kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6530: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba thams cad zhi ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6531: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i gdung ba kun sel cing //
NK027(sha)002:6532: grang zhing bsil ba'i gdugs mchog dam pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:6533: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs tsha gdung zhi ba'i gsos //
NK027(sha)002:6534: rim bzhin sdug bsngal ma lus sel bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6535: ci ltar nyon mongs tsha bas gdungs pa las //
NK027(sha)002:6536: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i sdug bsngal skyob pa ltar //
NK027(sha)002:6537: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal nyes pa skyobs pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6538: gdugs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bac+wo lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6539: sngon bcom ldan 'das yangs pa can gyi grong khyer
NK027(sha)002:6540: du spre'u rdzing gi 'gram khang bu brtsegs pa na
NK027(sha)002:6541: bzhugs pa'i tshe / bram ze kham pas sngon gyi
NK027(sha)002:6542: nyes pa brdas nas nya pa rnams kyis nya zin
NK027(sha)002:6543: pa la 'gyod pa dran nas nya rgya che chung
NK027(sha)002:6544: bzhugs pa'i tshe / phul bas / nya pa lnga brgya sangs rgyas par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6545: de bzhin du nya rgya'i rtags dar gyi lda ldi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6546: ngan song du song nges kyang de las thar te /
NK027(sha)002:6547: sangs rgyas pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6548: dar gyi lda ldi'i nyon mongs kun spangs te //
NK027(sha)002:6549: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus rab rdzogs nas //
NK027(sha)002:6550: ma rig 'khrul pa'i shes pa blo dag cing //
NK027(sha)002:6551: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i nad las thar bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6552: 'khor ba'i nyes pa dag bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6553: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho bkra shis rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:6554: bag chags kun dag lda ldi'i brgyan //
NK027(sha)002:6555: dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6556: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6557: khyim bdag gi bu mo bzang ldan mas /
NK027(sha)002:6558: a par se'i sku reg phul bas sku brtan pa'i dbang mchog dang ldan par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6559: de bzhin du sku reg gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6560: lus brtan pa'i sku reg gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6561: dri ma dag pa'i sku reg gtsang ma'i mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6562: khyim bdag dad pas 'bul ba'i sku chings 'di //
NK027(sha)002:6563: sku la dkris shing rab tu bsdam pas na //
NK027(sha)002:6564: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i sku mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6565: thar pa mchog gi legs par gang gsungs pa //
NK027(sha)002:6566: mi dmigs dag pa'i ye shes chos sku yi //
NK027(sha)002:6567: nyon mongs dri ma med pa'i sku brtan pa //
NK027(sha)002:6568: sku reg dbang gi bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6569: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri bo gangs chen na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6570: gnod sbyin rnams kyis spos rnam pa lnga phul ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:6575: du ru ka ste de rnams phul zhing dbang po tshim nas bkra shis par gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:6576: de bzhin du spos rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6577: dbang po tshim nas bkra shis pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6578: dbang po tshim byed bdug pa'i spos mchog 'di //
NK027(sha)002:6579: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa mchod pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:6580: 'gro ba ma lus dbang po kun tshim zhing //
NK027(sha)002:6581: dri zhim 'phags pa'i sku dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6582: dri zhim ngad ldan yon tan phun sum tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:6583: mkha' la mchod pa'i sprin dpung gtibs byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:6584: yongs su khyab pa'i bdug mchog dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:6585: tshim byed dbang gi bkra shis bac+wo brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6586: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6587: klu'i rgyal po rnams kyis tsh+wa mar sbrang rtsi ka ra /
NK027(sha)002:6588: til te snying po lnga phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:6589: chos kyi snying po mi zad pa'i mdzod du bkra shis par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6590: de bzhin du snying po lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6591: tshe mi zad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6592: snying po lnga ni gsos kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6594: legs pa'i yon tan mthar phyin nas //
NK027(sha)002:6595: tshe dang longs spyod 'phel bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6596: tsh+wa'i ro bsgyur mar gyi mdangs dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:6597: sbrang rtsis stobs rgyas ka ras nad rnams zhi //
NK027(sha)002:6598: til gyi sdig zhi dge tshogs rnam par 'phel //
NK027(sha)002:6599: snying po dbang gi bkra shis bcu dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6600: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri bo gru 'dzin na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6605: mu man te rin po che rnam pa lnga phul
NK027(sha)002:6606: bas 'dzad mi shes pa'i dkor mdzod dang ldan par
NK027(sha)002:6607: gyur to // de bzhin du rin chen rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6608: longs spyod 'dzad mi shes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6609: rin chen gser dngul zangs lcags sogs //
NK027(sha)002:6611: 'phags pa'i nor bdun dang ldan te //
NK027(sha)002:6612: 'gro ba'i dbul ba sel bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6613: dgos pa'i nor 'byung rin chen sna tshogs mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6614: 'dzad mi shes par re ba bskangs pa'i gter //
NK027(sha)002:6615: bkra shis dbul 'phong sdug bsngal sel byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:6616: dgos 'byung dbang gi bkra shis nyi shu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6617: sngon bcom ldan 'das yul ang ga ma ga d+ha ra bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6623: sran ma ste 'bru lnga phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:6624: mu ge med cing bkra shis par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6625: de bzhin du 'bru lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6626: mu ge'i bskal pa las thar pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6627: rin chen 'bru mchog 'gro ba kun gyi gsos //
NK027(sha)002:6628: mu ge'i bskal pa kun las thar byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:6629: sbyin pa'i longs spyod rtag tu 'phel ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:6630: zas gos mi 'dzad gter dang ldan par shog /
NK027(sha)002:6631: longs spyod tshogs chen 'byor pa kun ldan pa //
NK027(sha)002:6632: gang la ci bzhin 'byung ba'i gter chen po //
NK027(sha)002:6633: phun sum tshogs pa dge ba'i stobs bskyed pa //
NK027(sha)002:6634: longs spyod dbang gi bkra shis nyer gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6635: sngon bcom ldan 'das tsan dan gyi nags su gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6636: gcan gzan gyi rgyal po stag gis sman b+y+aa gri phul bas bkra shis par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6637: de bzhin du sman stag tsher gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6638: bkra shis pa'i dbang dam bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)002:6639: byol song gti mug kun kyang 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:6640: b+y+aa gri sman mchog gcan gzan stag gi phul //
NK027(sha)002:6641: sman gyi nang rnams ma lus zhi bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6642: sems can gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:6643: thabs kyi kun la cho 'phrul cir yang ston //
NK027(sha)002:6644: thugs rje chen pos gnas nas 'dzin mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:6645: cho 'phrul dbang gi bkra shis nyer gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6646: sngon bcom ldan 'das seng lding gi nags tshal na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6647: gcan gzan gyi rgyal po seng ges seng lding phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:6648: sman gyi mchog tu bkra shis par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6649: de bzhin du seng lding tsher mas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6650: sman mchog bkra shis pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6651: seng lding sman mchog gcan gzan rgyal pos phul //
NK027(sha)002:6652: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)002:6653: byol song gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:6654: sman mchog nad rnams kun las thar bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6655: gzi brjid 'gro mkhas 'gying ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK027(sha)002:6656: gling bzhi 'gying ba'i dud 'gro'i rgyal po ste //
NK027(sha)002:6657: sgra skad bsgrags tshe gcan gzan zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)002:6658: gdul byed dbang gi bkra shis nyer gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6659: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri btang bzung chen por bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6660: klu'i rgyal po 'jog pos bri ha ti phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:6661: mchog gi sman bkra shis par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6662: de bzhin du shu dag dkar pos dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6663: sman mchog bkra shis pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:6664: shu dag sman mchog klu yis phul ba ste //
NK027(sha)002:6665: bcom ldan thugs rje chen pos byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)002:6666: klu rigs gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:6667: sman mchog nad rnams rab tu sel bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6668: rigs pa'i cha ldan byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK027(sha)002:6669: 'gro ba'i re bskangs gtsug na rin chen mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6670: thabs kyi don mdzad mthu dpung che ba'i klu //
NK027(sha)002:6671: nad sel dbang gi bkra shis nyer bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6672: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6673: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyi sman ha sa d+he wa phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:6674: sman mchog snying por bkra shis par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6675: de bzhin du dbang po lag pas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6676: sman mchog dam pa'i dbang thob dbang po lag pa lha'i dbang pos phul //
NK027(sha)002:6677: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK027(sha)002:6678: chen po lha yi sems kyang go mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:6679: sman mchog nad kun rab tu zhi bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6680: longs spyod ldan pa lha dbang brgya byin mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6681: sum cu rtsa gsum lha las rnam rgyal ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:6682: longs spyod dbang gi bkra shis nyer lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6683: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po'i tshal du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:6685: kan ta ka ri phul bas sman mchog snying po bkra shis par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:6686: de bzhin du kan ta ka ris kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:6687: sman mchog snying po'i dbang bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK027(sha)002:6688: shing gi lha mo'i sems kyang go mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:6689: kan ta ka ri shing gi lha mos phul //
NK027(sha)002:6690: sman mchog de'i nad kun zhi bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:6691: nags tshal chen po ljon shing la //
NK027(sha)002:6692: bde ba dgos pa'i re bskang ba //
NK027(sha)002:6694: dbang mchog bkra shis nyer drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6695: zhes pa'ang dbang rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:6696: de nas lam khyer gyi theg pa kri ya /
NK027(sha)002:6697: lha rigs gsum mgon po'i snying po /
NK027(sha)002:6701: dbang kri ya'i dbang nyi shu rtsa drug go //
NK027(sha)002:6702: de'ang theg pa 'jug sgo khrus dang gtsang sbra ste /
NK027(sha)002:6703: las la 'jug pa'i skabs dag tu //
NK027(sha)002:6704: lus ni sa yi dril phyis byas //
NK027(sha)002:6705: chu nang snyogs ma med zhugs te //
NK027(sha)002:6706: ci ltar 'dod pa bzhin du bkru //
NK027(sha)002:6708: lta ba don dam pa'i bden pa sems dag pa'i
NK027(sha)002:6709: mtha' dang bral ba 'di stong gsal gyi ye shes
NK027(sha)002:6710: chen por rtogs / de'i yon tan kun rdzob rigs
NK027(sha)002:6711: gsum lha'i dal du ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod
NK027(sha)002:6712: chen por rtogs / de / de'ang yul phar snang phyi rol gyi mtho 'jam rtsub dang /
NK027(sha)002:6714: tshur nang nas 'char ba'i sgo gsum dug gsum /
NK027(sha)002:6715: srid gsum lha'i dal du 'dod de /
NK027(sha)002:6716: kun rdzob snang ba rigs gsum 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:6718: don dam dag pa'i chos nyid do //
NK027(sha)002:6719: drug byed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK027(sha)002:6720: mthong ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK027(sha)002:6723: sdom pa gcig gsum la sogs /
NK027(sha)002:6726: nyi shu rtsa drug tu bsrung ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:6727: rigs gsum dbang byas gsum mam bdun /
NK027(sha)002:6728: yang na nyi shu dag tu bsrung /
NK027(sha)002:6729: ting 'dzin ni lha ye shes sems dpa' rje /
NK027(sha)002:6730: dam tshig pa bran du dmigs te /
NK027(sha)002:6732: ye shes sems dpa' rjer dmigs te //
NK027(sha)002:6733: dam tshig sems dpa' bran du lta //
NK027(sha)002:6734: gtsang ma'i phud kyi mchod byed nas //
NK027(sha)002:6735: dngos grub dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:6737: spyod pa ni bya ba drug ste /
NK027(sha)002:6738: bza' ba zas dkar gsum dang /
NK027(sha)002:6740: bza' ba sha chang sgog tsong bsrung ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:6741: bgo ba gos kyi bya ba ras kha tshar ma nyams pa gyon pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6742: gtsang sbra khrus kyi bya ba bzhi ste /
NK027(sha)002:6743: nyon mongs pa mngon du rgyu ba rags pa'i bag chags lta ba rtogs pas dag /
NK027(sha)002:6744: bag nyal gyi bag chag ting nge 'dzin sgom pas dag /
NK027(sha)002:6745: spyod lam nyams pa'i dri ma lha'i dal bsdu zhing ye shes pa gshegs pas dag /
NK027(sha)002:6746: tha mal pa'i dri ma chus dag pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6747: de'ang tha ma la dri ma chu'i dag /
NK027(sha)002:6748: chu ni sngags kyi dag par bya /
NK027(sha)002:6750: dngos grub rten gyi bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:6751: dmigs pa'i rten yi dam lha'i sku gzugs /
NK027(sha)002:6752: gtsang sbra'i bzhengs nas byed pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6753: 'jug pa dus tshod kyi bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:6755: tshes grangs bzang po la 'jug ste /
NK027(sha)002:6756: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK027(sha)002:6757: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK027(sha)002:6758: gza' skar shis pas blang bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:6761: bzlas brjod sngags kyi bya ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:6762: de nyid gsum dang ldan pa ste /
NK027(sha)002:6763: lha'i bdag gi 'phro 'du'i de nyid dang ldan /
NK027(sha)002:6764: sngags kyi skyon bcu spang bazla'o //
NK027(sha)002:6766: gsang ba gsum ldan skyon bcu spangs te blangs /
NK027(sha)002:6767: mtshams med lnga dang mi dge bcu spyod dang /
NK027(sha)002:6768: sdig pa gang byas bzlas brjod byas pas byang /
NK027(sha)002:6771: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob ste /
NK027(sha)002:6772: dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba chos sku /
NK027(sha)002:6774: rigs kyi khro bo pho nya la sogs sprul sku'o //
NK027(sha)002:6776: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK027(sha)002:6778: sangs rgyas phrin las kun rdzogs nas //
NK027(sha)002:6785: ston pa bcom ldan 'das phyag na rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:6788: dbang ri rab mchod rten la sogs kri ya'i dbang nyer drug /
NK027(sha)002:6789: gang gi phyir na dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rjes su bzung phyir /
NK027(sha)002:6790: dgongs pa dbang bskur ba'i 'bras bu de dag go //
NK027(sha)002:6791: de nas dbang de mthar brtan pa'i phyir /
NK027(sha)002:6792: gdam ngag lam khyer gsal gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:6793: spyi bor thig le dkar dmar mthing gsum brtsegs mar bsal /
NK027(sha)002:6794: dkar po la sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK027(sha)002:6797: 'jam dpal sku mdog ser po ral gri ut+pala 'dzin par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:6799: sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK027(sha)002:6802: spyan gzigs dkar po pad+ma 'dzin par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:6804: sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK027(sha)002:6805: tshur 'dus snying khar thims pas phyag rdor sku mdog sngon po rdo rje 'dzin par bsgom /
NK027(sha)002:6806: de ltar sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor
NK027(sha)002:6807: bsgom nas spyod lam rnam bzhir la gsum gyi ngang
NK027(sha)002:6813: bcom ldan gser mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:6814: 'jig rten gsum mgon 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyis sku //
NK027(sha)002:6815: bder gshegs sku yi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK027(sha)002:6816: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:6817: bcom ldan dung mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:6818: 'jig rten gsum mgon spyan ras gzigs kyi gsungs //
NK027(sha)002:6819: bder gshegs gsung gi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK027(sha)002:6820: bkra shis des bcom ldan mthing mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:6821: 'jig rten gsum mgon phyag na rdo rje'i thugs //
NK027(sha)002:6822: bder gshegs thugs kyi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK027(sha)002:6823: bkra shis shar lho nub byang dpal be'u 'khor lo dang //
NK027(sha)002:6824: pad+ma rgyal mtshan gdugs bum dung dang nya //
NK027(sha)002:6825: lha mo brgyad kyi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK027(sha)002:6826: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:6830: dge rtsa byang chub tu bsngo bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:6831: de nas kri ya'i cho ga'i 'grig rim mo //
NK027(sha)002:6833: u pa ya'i theg pa la /
NK027(sha)002:6834: dus bzang sa btsal blang bsrung sbyangs /
NK027(sha)002:6835: sa bzung byin rlabs bsnyen thig gdab //
NK027(sha)002:6836: gsol btab dal bri mchod bshams khrus //
NK027(sha)002:6837: chos bshad spyan drangs phyag bya ba //
NK027(sha)002:6838: gzhug bsrung spyan drangs mchod pa cha gsum btang /
NK027(sha)002:6839: bum bzlas 'dzab dbyangs sbyin bsregs bya /
NK027(sha)002:6840: chos bshad sems bskyed dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:6841: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //
NK027(sha)002:6843: phyir sgos btang rag rig dbye bya //
NK027(sha)002:6844: gshegs gsol bkra shis bsngo ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:6845: de la dang po dus ni /
NK027(sha)002:6846: sangs rgyas kyi dus mchod la byas nas bsod nams bye ba phrag brgya'i 'gyur yod de /
NK027(sha)002:6848: rgyal gyi nya la bltams zhing chos la gshegs //
NK027(sha)002:6849: dgun gyi nyi ma ldog pa'i dus yin no //
NK027(sha)002:6850: stag gi yar ngo cho 'phrul che bar bstan //
NK027(sha)002:6851: mu stegs ston pa rnam gsum 'khor bcas brtul //
NK027(sha)002:6852: khra zla'i nya nas zhag bcu nyer lnga la //
NK027(sha)002:6853: tshangs pa'i drang srong brtul nas sngags dbang bskur //
NK027(sha)002:6854: nag pa'i brgyad nas bco lnga sangs rgyas kun //
NK027(sha)002:6855: dngos kyi dbang bskur rdo rje theg lam ston //
NK027(sha)002:6856: sa ga'i nya'i dkar nag mtshams sangs rgyas //
NK027(sha)002:6857: dpyid kha nam dang nyi ma mnyam dus yin //
NK027(sha)002:6858: chu zla'i tshes lnga tshes brgyad chos 'khor bskor //
NK027(sha)002:6859: dbyar nyi zlog dus me tog ug chos skye //
NK027(sha)002:6860: dbyug zla cho 'phrul chung ba mu stegs kyi //
NK027(sha)002:6861: ston pa drug btul ston kha nyin mtshan mnyam //
NK027(sha)002:6862: mya ngan 'das te chos brgyad nam phyed yin //
NK027(sha)002:6863: zhes pas dus de dag la 'jug par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:6864: gnyis pa sa btsal ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:6865: zhi rgyas la bkra shis pa'i sa //
NK027(sha)002:6866: drag po la gdug pa can gyi sa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6867: gsum pa sa blang ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:6868: bzhi pa sa bsrung ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:6869: lnga pa sa sbyangs ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:6870: drug pa sa bzung ba rnams gong ltar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:6872: spyir theg pa dgu'i chog khrig gang rung ba'i rgyas bsdus /
NK027(sha)002:6874: srid rtse nas 'og dmyal ba'i bar gyi gnas dang /
NK027(sha)002:6875: 'gro ba thams cad 'od zer gyi khyab pa'i bskyed rdzogs bstan pa gcig bsgom par bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:6876: de'ang byang sems kyi mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang /
NK027(sha)002:6877: kri ya'i bkra shis nyer drug /
NK027(sha)002:6878: yo ga'i dbang drug cu rtsa bzhi la tshang bar byas nas /
NK027(sha)002:6879: bya rgyud gtsor byas pa'i u pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:6880: rnal 'byor rgyud gtsor byed pa'i u pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6881: dang po ni phyag rdor dbang bskur ba'i rgyud dang /
NK027(sha)002:6882: rdo rje ri rab brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK027(sha)002:6883: u pa ya'i dbang sgos su mi byed pa yod kyang /
NK027(sha)002:6884: dka' thub rig byed theg pa yang //
NK027(sha)002:6885: 'di yang yul gyi gsum nyid de /
NK027(sha)002:6886: zhes 'bring gi tha ma kri ya /
NK027(sha)002:6888: 'bring gi rab yo gas 'dul bar gsungs pas /
NK027(sha)002:6889: u pa cis kyang dgos so //
NK027(sha)002:6894: chang la sogs pa yang ma bkag /
NK027(sha)002:6895: bya ba'i rgyud dang 'gal ba ltar snang yang skyon med de /
NK027(sha)002:6897: lha rigs gsum gang byed kyang bum bzlas kyi skabs
NK027(sha)002:6898: su chur zhugs pa las kyi lha gcig dgos pa
NK027(sha)002:6899: gzhan yang de nyid du khams gsum rnam rgyal bskyed
NK027(sha)002:6900: bzlas nas bar chad bsrung bar dgos pa rigs gsum
NK027(sha)002:6902: de yang lus snang ba lha /
NK027(sha)002:6904: h'u yid dran pa thugs te /
NK027(sha)002:6905: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs te /
NK027(sha)002:6907: sku gsung thugs su ldan pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:6908: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gi /
NK027(sha)002:6909: bdag por khyod kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:6916: u pa ya ni rig gsum dang /
NK027(sha)002:6917: rigs lnga la sogs par 'dod ces gsungs la /
NK027(sha)002:6918: ling rtse dgu'i dbus su rnam snang ser po mnyam bzhag can /
NK027(sha)002:6919: shar du rdo rje sogs kyang gsungs /
NK027(sha)002:6921: ye shes rin po che'i dbu rgyan mchog /
NK027(sha)002:6922: sangs rgyas rgyal ba kun 'dus pa /
NK027(sha)002:6925: rnam snang mdzad kyi ye shes ni //
NK027(sha)002:6926: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs la gsal //
NK027(sha)002:6927: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes ni //
NK027(sha)002:6928: rnam snang mdzad kyi thugs la gsal //
NK027(sha)002:6934: bya grub don grub yod kyang /
NK027(sha)002:6935: slob dpon pad+ma'i sku gsum dbye ba las //
NK027(sha)002:6936: rigs pa rnam snang chos kyis sku /
NK027(sha)002:6937: mi bskyod pa snying po byang chub nas bzhugs pa'i sku /
NK027(sha)002:6938: rin 'byung yon tan dang snang mtha' longs sku /
NK027(sha)002:6940: zhes ye shes lnga rigs lnga yang /
NK027(sha)002:6941: ye shes dang rdo rje bzhir dbyer med pas u pa ya'o //
NK027(sha)002:6942: yang sems dpa' bzhi ltar na bdag dam tshig sems dpa' /
NK027(sha)002:6945: phyi lus dam tshig sems dpa' /
NK027(sha)002:6946: nang thugs ye shes sems dpa' /
NK027(sha)002:6947: bar ting nge 'dzin sems dpa' gsum gcig tu gsal bar rdo rje sems dpa' ste /
NK027(sha)002:6948: de'i dbus su gtsang sme med par sha chang la spyod cing rdzas mchod pa'am bran pas chog pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6949: de'ang bdag bskyed mdun bskyed gnyis ka'ang sems dpa' bzhi ste /
NK027(sha)002:6951: da ni bdun pa u pa'i khrid //
NK027(sha)002:6952: lha dang bdag nyid dpon g.yog ltar //
NK027(sha)002:6953: lus ngag yid gsum phyag rgya bsgom //
NK027(sha)002:6956: stegs bu dris byug thig bkod /
NK027(sha)002:6965: dbus su rnam snang chos 'chad kyi steng na 'khor lo can /
NK027(sha)002:6966: shar du mi bskyod pa sa gnon rdo rje can /
NK027(sha)002:6967: lhor rin 'byung mchog sbyin rin chen can /
NK027(sha)002:6968: nub tu snang mtha' mnyam bzhag pad+ma can /
NK027(sha)002:6969: byang du don grub skyabs sbyin rgya gram can no //
NK027(sha)002:6970: kun rdo rje skyil krung chos gos can rgyan gyi spras pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6971: grwa bzhir mchod pa'i lha mo dang /
NK027(sha)002:6972: snam bu la bkra shis kyi lha mo /
NK027(sha)002:6973: khyams la dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa lnga ste /
NK027(sha)002:6978: rgyas bsdus gang mos su bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:6980: mchod pa bshams la thar mo sbyar te /
NK027(sha)002:6981: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:6983: chee ge mo'i slob ma'i don phyir ru //
NK027(sha)002:6984: sta gon la ni dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:6985: zhes zhus la gnang ba thob par bsam mo //
NK027(sha)002:6987: slob dpon pad+ma'i sku gsum dbye ba las /
NK027(sha)002:6988: u pa ya'i sku gsum ni /
NK027(sha)002:6990: rang gi ngo bo bstan du med pas ye shes rang rig pa tsam gyi chos kyi sku'o //
NK027(sha)002:6991: longs sku rdo rje 'dzin pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:6992: lag na pad+ma la sogs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:6993: sprul sku ni kha gcig las nyan thos dang kha gcig las dbang po'i gzugs can no //
NK027(sha)002:6997: 'dab bzhi'am rtsib bzhi gang mos su bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:6998: sgo rta babs la sogs spyi dang mthun no //
NK027(sha)002:6999: bcu pa bla ma la phyag 'tshal man+dala phul /
NK027(sha)002:7001: bla ma slob dpon dgongs su gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7002: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:7003: bla ma dam par gsol 'debs kyi //
NK027(sha)002:7004: bdag gi bla ma mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7005: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab /
NK027(sha)002:7008: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7009: ma grol ba rnams grol bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7010: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams dbyung bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7016: de nas skyabs 'gro sems bskyed gong bzhin phog la /
NK027(sha)002:7017: +aahmh'u zhes dri chu rdo rje dang bcas pa gnas gsum du reg cing bsrung ba bya /
NK027(sha)002:7018: skyor chu blud de dam la bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:7019: so shing dor la dngos grub brtags /
NK027(sha)002:7021: ku sha byin la rmi lam brtags /
NK027(sha)002:7022: bcu gcig pa dkyil 'khor bri ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:7025: rang byung gi tshon rnams med na bsgyur tshon gyi gong du bstan pa ltar bri bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:7026: de nas slar yang mchod pa bsham /
NK027(sha)002:7027: cha gsum dang gtor ma gzhan na bsham mo //
NK027(sha)002:7028: bcu gnyis pa rten 'brel rab gnas byas te /
NK027(sha)002:7029: bum pa'i chus thams cad khrus bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:7030: bcu gsum pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:7032: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gtam gyi 'jigs pa skye //
NK027(sha)002:7033: mya ngan 'das pa gtam gyi brod pa bskyed //
NK027(sha)002:7034: dal 'byor phun sum tshogs pa'i lus 'di la //
NK027(sha)002:7035: nyon mongs dbang gi skyon gyi chud mi gsan //
NK027(sha)002:7036: zhes pas rang yang de'i don dran pas dal du
NK027(sha)002:7037: zhugs la slob ma'i rgyud la'ang de'i don bskyed par
NK027(sha)002:7038: bya'o // de nas bu ci la dga' dri /
NK027(sha)002:7039: skal bzang bdag bde chen la dga' //
NK027(sha)002:7043: tshur shog theg pa chen po'i snod //
NK027(sha)002:7044: bla med spyod pa'i chu dbang sbyin //
NK027(sha)002:7045: zhes rdo rjes drangs la gral du bzhag go //
NK027(sha)002:7046: de nas yan lag bdun rnam brgyad pa 'bul /
NK027(sha)002:7047: rigs gsum spyi'i dam tshig bzungs /
NK027(sha)002:7048: de nas rdo rje dril bu spos thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:7050: ma lus sems can bdud sde dngos rnams bcom ldan
NK027(sha)002:7051: zhes pas mchod bstod la sogs pas spyan drangs la
NK027(sha)002:7052: cha gsum rgyas par btang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:7053: bum par cha gsum gyi rdo rje sems dpa' bskyed pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:7054: dal du rigs lnga bskyed cing /
NK027(sha)002:7060: a mi d+he wa h+r+aih a mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aah zhes bzlas so //
NK027(sha)002:7061: skabs 'dir zhi rgyas dbang drag gi sbyin bsregs bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:7063: dang por byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:7064: bar du dge ba bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:7065: mthar dge ba byang chub tu bsngo dgos pa yang bshad do //
NK027(sha)002:7066: de nas rigs lnga'i sku'am phyag rgya thogs la /
NK027(sha)002:7068: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon dang //
NK027(sha)002:7069: mchod sbyin mnyam bzhag phyag rgya rnams //
NK027(sha)002:7070: skyabs kyi phyag rgya rnam pa lnga //
NK027(sha)002:7071: rigs lnga'i phyag rgya'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:7075: pad+ma a mi d+he wa h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7077: de nas bum pa'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:7080: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK027(sha)002:7081: bum pa zlum po chos dbyings gter //
NK027(sha)002:7082: phan byed sman pa'i thugs yin te //
NK027(sha)002:7083: 'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:7084: h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah a b+hi shiny+tsa mum /
NK027(sha)002:7087: de nas rdo rje 'chang gi sku thogs la /
NK027(sha)002:7089: don dam bde ba'i chos nyid las //
NK027(sha)002:7090: mi g.yo sems dpa' mngon sum du //
NK027(sha)002:7091: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa //
NK027(sha)002:7092: u pa ya yi dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:7094: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rnams kyis bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK027(sha)002:7095: skal ldan rigs kyis bu rnams la u pa ya'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7096: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7099: rgyas par spro na kri ya'i rdzas nyer drug kyang bskur bar bya'o gsungs /
NK027(sha)002:7102: lha rnam snang gtso 'khor snying po rigs lnga'i sngags /
NK027(sha)002:7103: dbang sems dpa' bzhi lam khyer ro //
NK027(sha)002:7104: lta ba yo ga dang mthun /
NK027(sha)002:7105: dam tshig rje 'bangs kyi tshul te /
NK027(sha)002:7108: snang ba rigs bzhi dpon g.yog tshul //
NK027(sha)002:7112: sems rang rig rang gsal du bsgom pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7114: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang thob ste //
NK027(sha)002:7116: mi g.yo sems dpa' mngon du gyur //
NK027(sha)002:7117: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang thob ste //
NK027(sha)002:7125: lte bar tram ser po bsgom pas /
NK027(sha)002:7126: ming bzhi'i phung po sbyangs nas /
NK027(sha)002:7127: rdo rje bzhi mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7130: ston pa dpal 'byung lag na rdo rje /
NK027(sha)002:7136: me tog bkram nas bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:7137: sangs rgyas gtso la yon tan mchog mnga' gang //
NK027(sha)002:7138: che dgus mchod cing smon lam sprin tshogs 'du //
NK027(sha)002:7139: go 'phang mchog brnyes bde ba'i char 'beb pa //
NK027(sha)002:7140: sangs rgyas bden pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:7141: skyobs pa'i chos la legs pa'i mchog mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)002:7142: shin tu phan zhing bde dang brtser ldan zhing //
NK027(sha)002:7143: 'khor ba rtag bde mya ngan 'das thob pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7144: dam chos bden pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:7145: dge 'dun che la mthu rtsal rmad mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)002:7146: bslab bzhi legs bcas brtson pa'i rnal 'byor can //
NK027(sha)002:7147: bdag gzhan don chen bsgrub pa'i lam zhugs pa //
NK027(sha)002:7148: dge 'dun bden pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:7151: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub bsngo bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:7152: u pa ya'i chog 'grig lags so //
NK027(sha)002:7155: dal bsham khung dang mchod pa bshams /
NK027(sha)002:7156: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum /
NK027(sha)002:7157: dbang skong khrus bya bsdom rten khri //
NK027(sha)002:7159: mchod bstod bdag 'jug chos bshad dang //
NK027(sha)002:7161: rdzas dbang lha dang lam khyer bzhi //
NK027(sha)002:7162: theg pa lha snying bslab bya dang //
NK027(sha)002:7163: theg sgo rta khrims ting spyod 'bras //
NK027(sha)002:7165: mdams ngag dang bsgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK027(sha)002:7167: dang po dal gyi bkra shis kyi sa mtshams ni /
NK027(sha)002:7168: ri rab kyi steng nas rdo rje rtse gcig rtse
NK027(sha)002:7169: gsum rtse lnga'i brag ri la bya spyod rnal 'byor
NK027(sha)002:7170: gsum ma h+aa yo ga'i gzhal yas khang /
NK027(sha)002:7171: zhi khro'i dal man chad la /
NK027(sha)002:7172: a nu yo ga ye shes kyi me dpung dang lung gi zhi khro man chad /
NK027(sha)002:7173: a ti yo ga dbu yi gtsug /
NK027(sha)002:7174: sangs rgyas rnams kyi steng gi rgyal mtshan rtse gcig tu 'dus pa la dgod pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7175: bsgom pa ni rta babs them skas man chad la dbu sems dang /
NK027(sha)002:7176: bya spyod rnal 'byor te spyod pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7177: de ni ma h+aa yo ga'i gtsor byas pa'i lugs so //
NK027(sha)002:7178: a nu gtsor byed na dbu sems gcig tu dril nas ma h+aa brgyad pa la'o //
NK027(sha)002:7180: lta spyod gcig tu dril ba nas a nu brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7181: bri ba ni sa chog ltar byas pa'i shul yin na ma byas kyang rung /
NK027(sha)002:7184: de'i dbus su ling rtse dgu'i 'khor lo rtsib brgyad glo 'bur gru chad sgo gnyis rim bya /
NK027(sha)002:7185: sgo rkyang byed na lha rnams bya /
NK027(sha)002:7193: sgo mtshams phyogs mdog gzhan dang spyi mthun no //
NK027(sha)002:7194: khung ni de nyid 'dus pa la'o //
NK027(sha)002:7197: gtor ma cha gsum la sogs gong bzhin du bshams /
NK027(sha)002:7198: rab gnas rgyas bsdus gang 'os bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:7199: cho ga gzhung 'og nas 'byung ba ltar byas la khrus bya /
NK027(sha)002:7200: slob mas yon phul nas khrir 'dzeg la skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bya /
NK027(sha)002:7201: bgegs gtor btang la sum b+ha nis bgegs bskrad do //
NK027(sha)002:7202: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa gzhan phan ltar bya gsungs /
NK027(sha)002:7203: 'di ltar byed na sngags gzhan phan dang 'dra /
NK027(sha)002:7204: de nas tshad med bzhi bsgom /
NK027(sha)002:7205: shu nyee ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ha /
NK027(sha)002:7206: zhes pas bdag dang snang ba thams cad stong par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:7207: stong pa'i ngang las yam las rlung /
NK027(sha)002:7211: sum las ri rab kyi steng du /
NK027(sha)002:7213: snod kyi ma dag pa sbyangs /
NK027(sha)002:7214: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK027(sha)002:7215: lha'i gzhal yas rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa /
NK027(sha)002:7217: rta babs dang bcas pa'i dbus seng ge'i khri la /
NK027(sha)002:7218: rnam snang ser po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:7219: shar glang po che'i khrir mi bskyod pa dkar po sa non gyi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:7220: lhor rta'i khri la rin chen 'byung ldan sngon po mchog sbyin can /
NK027(sha)002:7221: nub tu rma bya'i khri la snang ba mtha' yas dmar po mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:7222: byang du shang shang gi khri la don yod grub pa ljang gu skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK027(sha)002:7223: shar lhor spyan ma dkar mo rdo rje can /
NK027(sha)002:7224: lho nub tu ma ma ki sngon mo rin chen spyan /
NK027(sha)002:7225: nub byang du gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma can /
NK027(sha)002:7226: byang shar du sgrol ma ljang gu rgya gram can no //
NK027(sha)002:7227: gtso bo rigs bzhi'i mdun rgyab g.yas g.yon du sems dpa' bzhi bzhi ste /
NK027(sha)002:7228: mi bskyod pa nas rim pa bzhin /
NK027(sha)002:7229: rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po rdo rje can /
NK027(sha)002:7230: rdo rje rgyal po ser po lcags kyu can /
NK027(sha)002:7231: rdo rje chags pa dmar po mda' gzhu can /
NK027(sha)002:7232: rdo rje legs pa ljang gu se gol can /
NK027(sha)002:7233: rdo rje rin chen sngon po rin chen can /
NK027(sha)002:7234: rdo rje gzi brjid dmar po nyi ma can /
NK027(sha)002:7235: rdo rje rgyal mtshan sngon po rgyal mtshan can /
NK027(sha)002:7236: rdo rje bzhad pa dkar po phreng ba can /
NK027(sha)002:7237: rdo rje chos kyi dmar po pad+ma can /
NK027(sha)002:7238: rdo rje rnon po sngon po ral gri can /
NK027(sha)002:7239: rdo rje rgyu ser po 'khor lo can /
NK027(sha)002:7240: rdo rje smra ba dmar po ljags can /
NK027(sha)002:7241: rdo rje las ljang gu rgya gram can /
NK027(sha)002:7242: rdo rje bsrung ba ser po go khrab can /
NK027(sha)002:7243: rdo rje gnod sbyin sngon po mche ba can /
NK027(sha)002:7244: rdo rje khu tshur ser po khu tshur can no //
NK027(sha)002:7245: shar du sgeg mo dkar mo me long can /
NK027(sha)002:7246: lhor phreng ba ma ser mo phreng ba /
NK027(sha)002:7247: nub tu glu ma dmar mo pi wang /
NK027(sha)002:7248: byang du gar ma ljang gus gar byed pa /
NK027(sha)002:7249: shar du bdug spos ma dkar mo spos khang /
NK027(sha)002:7250: lho nub tu me tog ma ser mo me tog /
NK027(sha)002:7251: nub byang du mar me ma dmar mo mar me /
NK027(sha)002:7252: byang shar du dri chab ma ljang gu dung chos /
NK027(sha)002:7253: shar lhor lcags kyu ma dkar mo /
NK027(sha)002:7254: lho sgor zhags pa ser mo /
NK027(sha)002:7255: nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo /
NK027(sha)002:7256: byang sgor dril bu ma ljang gu'o //
NK027(sha)002:7257: sgo phyi nang gi khyam rtsig bar la /
NK027(sha)002:7258: shar du byang chub sems dpa' byams pa /
NK027(sha)002:7261: mya ngan dang mun pa thams cad nges par 'joms pa /
NK027(sha)002:7270: byang du rdo rje snying po /
NK027(sha)002:7273: kun tu bzang po rnams phyogs kyi mdog can rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7274: de nas rang stong pa nyid kyi lkog mar h+r+aihls
NK027(sha)002:7275: pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad par lce las h'u las rdo
NK027(sha)002:7277: badz+ra 'dzi ha zhes pas lce byin brlab kyi /
NK027(sha)002:7278: lag pa gnyis su a las zla ba'i dal du
NK027(sha)002:7279: h'u las rdo rje'i ser mo rnams kyang rdo rje
NK027(sha)002:7280: rtse gcig par gyur par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:7282: e ma sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)002:7283: thugs rje can gyi thams cad kyi //
NK027(sha)002:7284: zhi yang sems can 'dul don du //
NK027(sha)002:7285: dri ma med pa'i khro bor gyur //
NK027(sha)002:7287: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK027(sha)002:7288: dpa' bo chen po stang stabs brkyang bskum tshul //
NK027(sha)002:7289: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyi sdang mig gi //
NK027(sha)002:7290: bgegs dpung bsregs par mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK027(sha)002:7291: ces bskrad cing mtshams bcad de /
NK027(sha)002:7292: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad rdo rje'i gur dang sa gzhir bsam /
NK027(sha)002:7293: de nas bum pa'i chu phyogs kun du gtor zhing /
NK027(sha)002:7295: tsan+dana chu la bden pa brdar ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:7296: phyogs bcur gtor bas yongs su dag gyur te //
NK027(sha)002:7297: mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:7298: dri med yon tan dag dang ldan gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7299: sarba b+hi shwo d+ha ni h'u h+r+aihth+aah zhes brjod /
NK027(sha)002:7300: rdo rje me'i phyag rgya dang /
NK027(sha)002:7301: badz+ra dz+wa la a na la zhes pas mchod la /
NK027(sha)002:7303: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya waka ka tsit+ta /
NK027(sha)002:7304: pra na me na badz+ra b+han+d+ha ka ro mi /
NK027(sha)002:7306: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
NK027(sha)002:7307: de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje dang /
NK027(sha)002:7310: las kyi rigs su gyur pa thams cad dang /
NK027(sha)002:7314: rigs sngags kyi lha thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:7315: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas phyogs bcu'i rigs sngags
NK027(sha)002:7316: kyi lha thams cad spyan sngar sdig pa thams cad
NK027(sha)002:7322: 'phags pa nyan thos yang dag par song ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:7323: yang dag par bzhugs pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:7324: sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams kyi tshogs la rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK027(sha)002:7325: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi chos kyi
NK027(sha)002:7326: 'khor lo bskor bar mi mdzad pa rnams la 'khor
NK027(sha)002:7327: lo bskor bar bya ba'i phyir bskul bar bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:7328: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams mya ngan
NK027(sha)002:7329: las 'da' bar bzhed pa de dag thams cad mya
NK027(sha)002:7330: ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol bar 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:7331: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la
NK027(sha)002:7332: bdag nyid kyi lus 'bul gyi dus thams cad du
NK027(sha)002:7334: thugs rje dang ldan pa'i mgon po khyed rnams kyi
NK027(sha)002:7335: dam tshig chen po'i dngos grub bdag la stsal du
NK027(sha)002:7336: gsol / bdag gi dge ba'i las rnams 'di dag gi //
NK027(sha)002:7337: 'jig rten 'di nas myur du sangs rgyas shog /
NK027(sha)002:7338: 'gro la phan phyir chos rnams ston byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:7339: sems can sdug bsngal mang pos gzer las grol //
NK027(sha)002:7340: zhes pas bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags /
NK027(sha)002:7341: de nas de dag mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:7345: ma lus sems can kun gyi /
NK027(sha)002:7347: bcom ldan 'di ni byon pa legs //
NK027(sha)002:7348: bdag cag bdag gi byin gyis brlabs par mdzad du gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7349: ga ga na sa ma ye h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7350: ci ltar bltams pa tsam gyi ni /
NK027(sha)002:7352: pra b+ha ra sad ka ra pra ti dza hoh bdag dang 'gro la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7353: zhes pas bzhugs su gsol bar /
NK027(sha)002:7356: lha sogs bdag gi ma byas pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7357: me tog chu skyes thang skyes rnams //
NK027(sha)002:7358: thub pa dbang phyug rnams la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:7360: gang dag spos kyi shing bzang po //
NK027(sha)002:7361: lha dang mi'i spos mchog rnams //
NK027(sha)002:7362: thub pa dbang phyug rnams la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:7364: rin chen sgron me nyi zla'i 'od //
NK027(sha)002:7365: phyogs dus kun nas rab spros te //
NK027(sha)002:7366: thub pa dbang phyug rnams la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:7368: zhal zas ro mchog brgya ldan pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7369: thams cad sbyar ba'i bshos 'di dag /
NK027(sha)002:7370: thub pa dbang phyug nee wi t+ye p+auts+tsha +aahmh'u /
NK027(sha)002:7371: dri med yid du 'ong ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:7372: sil snyan dam pa 'di dag ni //
NK027(sha)002:7373: thub pa dbang phyug rnams la 'bul //
NK027(sha)002:7376: gzhan yang rgyal srid sna bdun dang /
NK027(sha)002:7378: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK027(sha)002:7380: phyag 'tshal don yod grub pa la'o //
NK027(sha)002:7382: 'di nas bdag 'jug slob ma gnyis ka yin par sems /
NK027(sha)002:7383: bar de nas rigs lnga'i sdom pa bzung la rang nyid dal la bzhugs /
NK027(sha)002:7385: 'jig rten du ni kun mkhyen dag /
NK027(sha)002:7387: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du gyur //
NK027(sha)002:7388: bar zhes pa'o don bshad do //
NK027(sha)002:7390: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
NK027(sha)002:7391: sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags //
NK027(sha)002:7393: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:7395: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:7397: dus 'di nas ni bzung nas su //
NK027(sha)002:7398: ci srid byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK027(sha)002:7399: ci ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK027(sha)002:7401: sems can mya ngan 'das la 'god kyi bar /
NK027(sha)002:7402: zhes lan gsum gyis dam tshig 'bog /
NK027(sha)002:7405: bcom ldan nam mkha'i snying po kun //
NK027(sha)002:7406: theg pa chen po'i mthu ldan legs //
NK027(sha)002:7407: bdag gi rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7408: rang bzhin ting 'dzin gzugs med lhas //
NK027(sha)002:7409: bdag la dbang mchog 'di stsol cig /
NK027(sha)002:7410: sangs rgyas bka' yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK027(sha)002:7411: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK027(sha)002:7412: dkyil 'khor bcas pa'i lha tshogs kyis //
NK027(sha)002:7413: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7414: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK027(sha)002:7415: bsod nams can du bdag gnyid 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:7416: sngon las bzang po 'brel ba legs //
NK027(sha)002:7417: thugs rjes sras su dgongs par mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:7419: de nas ngan song gsum gyis sdig pa sbyangs ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:7420: da ha da ha sarba na ra ga te he dun h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:7422: ma tha ma tha gnyis kyang brjod /
NK027(sha)002:7423: a sa me tri sa me ma h+aa sa ma ye h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7424: zhes pas dam tshig bskyed la shar sgo nas lcags kyu'i phyag rgya /
NK027(sha)002:7425: rab gnas sgo 'di zhe sdang gi //
NK027(sha)002:7426: thog med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK027(sha)002:7427: snying rje'i sbyin pa rdo rje'i rigs //
NK027(sha)002:7428: thugs rjes thabs mkhas sprul pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:7429: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya mchog 'di yi //
NK027(sha)002:7430: de ring thar pa'i sgo dbye gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7431: badz+ra kro ta ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ye
NK027(sha)002:7432: ta th+aa pra si shi skram s+pha ra na sa
NK027(sha)002:7435: de nas zhags pa'i phyag rgyas lho sgor /
NK027(sha)002:7436: rab gnas sgo 'di nga rgyal gyi //
NK027(sha)002:7437: thog med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK027(sha)002:7438: byams pa'i rigs mthun rin chen rigs //
NK027(sha)002:7439: thugs rjes thabs mkhas sprul pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:7440: zhags pa'i phyag rgya mchog 'di yi //
NK027(sha)002:7441: de ring thar pa'i sgo dbye gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7442: rat+na kro ta ta th+aa ga ta zhes rin chen 'gros kyi 'jug /
NK027(sha)002:7443: de nas lcags sgrog gi phyag rgyas nub sgo nas /
NK027(sha)002:7445: thogs med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK027(sha)002:7446: dga' ba don spyod pad+ma'i rigs //
NK027(sha)002:7447: thugs rje thabs mkhas sprul pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:7448: lcags sgrog phyag rgya mchog 'di yi //
NK027(sha)002:7449: de ring thar pa'i sgo dbye gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7450: pad+ma kro ta ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ye
NK027(sha)002:7451: ta th+aa pra se shi kram sma rat+na sa ma
NK027(sha)002:7452: ya h'u phata / zhes pad+ma'i 'gros kyis 'jug /
NK027(sha)002:7453: de nas dril bu'i phyag rgyas byang sgor /
NK027(sha)002:7454: rab gnas sgo 'di phrag dog gi //
NK027(sha)002:7455: thog med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK027(sha)002:7456: btang snyoms snyan smra las kyi rigs //
NK027(sha)002:7457: thugs rje thabs mkhas sprul pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:7458: dril bu phyag rgya mchog 'di yi //
NK027(sha)002:7459: de ring thar pa'i sgo dbye gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7460: karma kro ta ta th+aa ga ta /
NK027(sha)002:7461: sa ma ye ta th+aa pra si shi kram sma ra na sa ma ya h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:7463: de nas bla ma rigs lnga dbyer med la phyag byas te /
NK027(sha)002:7464: bcom ldan snying po'i pho brang 'dir //
NK027(sha)002:7465: rgyal ba rigs lnga 'khor bcas la //
NK027(sha)002:7466: skal ldan rgyal sras dag pa zhig /
NK027(sha)002:7467: rab tu gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK027(sha)002:7468: bdag ni dam tshig 'khor lo ste //
NK027(sha)002:7469: rigs lnga'i dam tshig yin pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7471: de ring bdag la dbab tu gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7474: nga ni dam tshig 'khor lo ste //
NK027(sha)002:7475: rgyal ba rigs lnga yin par grags //
NK027(sha)002:7476: 'khor lo ye shes bla med pa //
NK027(sha)002:7477: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)002:7480: snying po pho brang dam tshig 'dir //
NK027(sha)002:7481: bla med byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK027(sha)002:7482: dngos grub dam pa thob pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7483: bdag gi dad pas 'jug tu gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7487: byang chub rin chen sems bskyed do //
NK027(sha)002:7488: 'khor ba'i gnas nas rab drangs te //
NK027(sha)002:7489: bder gshegs sras su bskyed pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:7490: bla med 'bras bu smin bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7491: bdag gi slob ma bzhugs par bgyi //
NK027(sha)002:7495: byang gi bum pas rim pa bzhin dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7496: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis chus //
NK027(sha)002:7497: gti mug sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7498: zhe sdang 'dod chags nga rgyal phrag dog sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7501: de nas me tog phreng ba bzung /
NK027(sha)002:7503: sngon gyi tshe rabs grangs med nas //
NK027(sha)002:7504: dge ba'i las kyis bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:7505: lhag pa'i lha ni gang yin pa //
NK027(sha)002:7506: da ltar nyid du dbab par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7507: a sa me tri sa ma ma h+aa sa ma ye h'u gi ye shes dbab /
NK027(sha)002:7508: rdo rje spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK027(sha)002:7509: badz+ra a d+hi tish+tha h'u gi brtan par bya /
NK027(sha)002:7511: sangs rgyas dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7512: bdag la 'gro la sman bar pra tits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes pas dkyil 'khor du me tog gtor /
NK027(sha)002:7513: pra ti grih+na swa mi mam gyis spyi bor bzhag la gang babs pa'i lha bsam /
NK027(sha)002:7515: shin tu ma rig rmongs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:7516: bdag gi 'dod par gyur pa nas //
NK027(sha)002:7517: de yi thugs rje chen po yi //
NK027(sha)002:7518: bdag gi ming 'di dbye bar gsol //
NK027(sha)002:7521: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag nyid de //
NK027(sha)002:7522: khyod kyis mig ni rab 'bar yin //
NK027(sha)002:7523: thams cad rdo rje 'bar bar mig /
NK027(sha)002:7524: phye bas thams cad mthong bar 'gyur //
NK027(sha)002:7525: badz+ra ha sa ud ga ta ya h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7529: da ni dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK027(sha)002:7530: gsang sngags chen po'i snod du gyur //
NK027(sha)002:7531: rnyed pa mnyam med de ring rnyed //
NK027(sha)002:7532: dam tshig gang yang 'da' mi byed //
NK027(sha)002:7533: bla med byang chub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7535: byang chub sems kyi chu sbyin zhing /
NK027(sha)002:7536: 'di ni khyod kyis dam tshig chu /
NK027(sha)002:7538: sngags sogs de bzhin no'i bar brjod /
NK027(sha)002:7539: badz+ra sa ma ye h'u phata /
NK027(sha)002:7542: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dgongs su gsol /
NK027(sha)002:7543: bcom ldan rdo rje dbyings kyis dkyil 'khor du bdag la dbang bskur du gsol /
NK027(sha)002:7546: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7547: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK027(sha)002:7548: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrub phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7549: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis long //
NK027(sha)002:7550: zhes slob ma la rdo rje 'dzin du gzhugs la
NK027(sha)002:7551: dbang steg gi khrir 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i 'dug steng
NK027(sha)002:7552: du bzhag la / dkyil 'khor gyi lha mkhyen par gsol ba ni /
NK027(sha)002:7553: bdag rdo rje slob dpon 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK027(sha)002:7554: slob ma 'di zhes bgyi bas thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang thob par bya ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:7555: sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa bsgrub cing /
NK027(sha)002:7556: sems can gyi don yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK027(sha)002:7557: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bar 'tshal gyi /
NK027(sha)002:7558: bcom ldan 'das ye shes gtso bor thugs rje'i mnga'
NK027(sha)002:7559: bdag rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i che ba'i yon
NK027(sha)002:7560: tan gyi dbang rnams rim pa bzhin du bskur zhing
NK027(sha)002:7562: dngos gzhi de nas thog mar bum dbang ni /
NK027(sha)002:7564: slob ma khyod la bum pas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7565: las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK027(sha)002:7566: byang chub kyi sems dang byin rlabs ldan pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK027(sha)002:7568: rin chen mdzes pa'i bkra shis bum pa 'dis //
NK027(sha)002:7569: skal ldan skyes bu khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7570: las dang nyon mongs sgrib pa kun dag ste //
NK027(sha)002:7571: byang chub sems mchog rlan gyi rlon par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7572: badz+ra b+hud+d+ha rat+na pad+ma karma ka la k+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7574: de nas bum pa lnga gcig tu bsdus pa'i tshul ni /
NK027(sha)002:7576: slob ma khyod la mi bskyod bum pa chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7577: rnam shes kyi phung po smin zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK027(sha)002:7578: me long lta bu'i ye shes rgyud la skyes pa'i mos pa gyis shig /
NK027(sha)002:7580: sgrib pa dag byed bdud rtsi dri med chu //
NK027(sha)002:7581: bkra shis mdzes pa'i bum pa rab bskang ste //
NK027(sha)002:7582: rigs kyi sangs rgyas kun tu bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7583: bum pa chu'i khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:7584: badz+ra ka la k+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7585: b+hud+d+ha k+aa la k+sha a b+hi shiny+tsara /
NK027(sha)002:7586: rat+na ka la a b+hi pad+ma ka la karma ka la k+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah ye d+harma'o /
NK027(sha)002:7589: slob ma khyod la dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7590: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK027(sha)002:7591: pa rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas myur du thob
NK027(sha)002:7593: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK027(sha)002:7594: mkhyen pa'i ye shes rab brgyan pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7595: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas 'grub pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7596: dbu rgyan dbang 'di khyod kyis longs //
NK027(sha)002:7598: badz+ra a rat+na a b+hi pad+ma a karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah rdo rje slob dpon ngas /
NK027(sha)002:7600: rin po che'i phreng ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7601: bsam pa mya ngan las 'das kyang /
NK027(sha)002:7602: sbyor ba khams gsum na 'gro don byed pa la
NK027(sha)002:7603: mdzes pa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan
NK027(sha)002:7604: par mos shig / rin chen mdzes pa'i me tog phreng ba 'dis //
NK027(sha)002:7605: skal ldan skyes bu khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7606: bsam pa myang 'das sbyor ba phun sum tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:7607: mdzes pa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7608: rat+na ma le a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram tram /
NK027(sha)002:7611: slob ma khyod la dar gyi cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7612: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa dang /
NK027(sha)002:7613: sems can gyi don byed pa la mthu thogs pa med pa'i dbang dang ldan par mos shig /
NK027(sha)002:7614: mdzes shing yid 'ong dar gyi cod pan 'dis //
NK027(sha)002:7615: skal ldan skyes bu khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7616: shes bya kun la thogs pa med pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:7617: 'gro ba'i don la mthu dbang thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7618: badz+ra pa tra a wa lam ba a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7620: de nas snang ba mtha' yas rdo rje'i dbang la /
NK027(sha)002:7622: slob ma khyod la rigs lnga'i phyag rgyas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7623: ye shes lnga'i dbang dang dngos grub thams cad thob par mos shig /
NK027(sha)002:7624: rigs lnga'i phyag rgya lag tu gtad nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:7625: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7626: sku gsung thugs kyis yon tan rab rdzogs te //
NK027(sha)002:7627: ye shes lnga ni myur du rtogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7628: badz+ra mu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7630: rat+na a b+hi pad+ma karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah des 'od dpag med rdo rje'i dbang gi don du'o //
NK027(sha)002:7631: de nas rnam par snang mdzad ming gi dbang ni /
NK027(sha)002:7635: ma 'ongs ba'i dus su sangs rgyas kyi mtshan nges
NK027(sha)002:7636: pa can rtogs shing thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK027(sha)002:7637: mos shig / kun rdzob mtshan ma ming gi dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7638: skal ldan skyes bu khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7639: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas 'jig rten zhing khams su //
NK027(sha)002:7640: de bzhin gshegs pa mtshan gyi dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:7641: badz+ra na mah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7643: rat+na pad+ma karma na mah a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah kyee
NK027(sha)002:7644: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba'i de bzhin
NK027(sha)002:7645: gshegs pa'o // de nas don yod grub pa dril bu'i dbang ni /
NK027(sha)002:7647: slob ma khyod rnams la dril bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7648: phrin las rnam bzhis bdag gzhan gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par mos shig /
NK027(sha)002:7649: rdo rje rgya gram lag tu gtad nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:7650: skal ldan skyes bu khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7651: phrin las rnam bzhis 'gro don mthar phyin nas //
NK027(sha)002:7652: las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7653: badz+ra karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah de rnams ni thun mong rigs pa'i dbang lnga'o //
NK027(sha)002:7654: de nas bdag po'i dbang ni g.yas su dung /
NK027(sha)002:7657: slob ma khyod la rigs thams cad kyi bdag po
NK027(sha)002:7658: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi byed pa pos dbang bskur
NK027(sha)002:7659: bas / 'gro ba'i shes rgyud la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing /
NK027(sha)002:7660: nye ring med par thos pa'i chos sgra sgrogs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon thob par mos shig /
NK027(sha)002:7661: chos la dbang bsgyur bdag po dang //
NK027(sha)002:7662: dkyil 'khor kun gyi gtso byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7663: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrub phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7664: bdag po'i dbang 'di khyod la sbyin //
NK027(sha)002:7665: badz+ra tsakra a ti pa ti s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:7666: a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u h'u h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7667: b+hud+d+ha tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah rat+na a b+hi pad+ma
NK027(sha)002:7668: a b+hi karma tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa a a +aah
NK027(sha)002:7671: dbus phyogs snying po rnam snang mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:7672: sku mdog dkar po gangs ri 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:7673: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:7674: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7675: bee ro tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa //
NK027(sha)002:7676: shar phyogs mngon dag'i mi bskyod pa //
NK027(sha)002:7677: sku mdog sngon po bee d+aur 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:7678: sa non chen po'i phyag rgya mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:7679: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7680: a k+sho b+hee a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah lho phyogs dpal ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK027(sha)002:7681: sku mdog ser po gser ri 'dra //
NK027(sha)002:7682: mchod sbyin chen po phyag rgya mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:7683: de'i dbang rat+na swa b+h+aa wa a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK027(sha)002:7684: nub phyogs bde ldan snang mtha' yas //
NK027(sha)002:7685: sku mdog dmar po byu ru'i mdog /
NK027(sha)002:7686: bsam gtan chen po phyag rgya mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:7687: de'i dbang mchog pad+ma a mi d+he wa a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7688: byang phyogs rnam dag gdod mi za //
NK027(sha)002:7689: sku mdog ljang gu in+d+ra'i mdog /
NK027(sha)002:7690: skyabs sbyin chen po phyag rgya mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:7691: de'i dbang mchog karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a b+hi shiny+tsa shar lho yum chen sangs rgyas spyan //
NK027(sha)002:7693: dam tshig phyag rgya rdo rje bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:7694: de'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7695: b+hud+d+ha lo tsa ni a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7696: lho nub yum chen ma m+aa ki //
NK027(sha)002:7698: dam tshig phyag rgya rdo rje bsnams //
NK027(sha)002:7699: de'i dbang mchog ma m+aa ki tram a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7700: nub byang yum chen na bza' dkar //
NK027(sha)002:7703: de'i dbang mchog badz+ra ba ri d+hi ti a b+hi byang shar yum chen dam tshig sgrol //
NK027(sha)002:7705: dam tshig phyag rgya ting 'dzin ni //
NK027(sha)002:7706: de'i dbang t+aa re tu re a b+hi shiny+tsa sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7707: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7708: mtha' yi 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7709: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis long //
NK027(sha)002:7710: badz+ra sat+wa a b+hi tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:7711: sangs rgyas kun gyi lcags kyu'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7712: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7713: thams cad gnas nas 'gugs pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7714: lcags kyu 'di ni khyod kyis long //
NK027(sha)002:7715: badz+ra sa t+wa a b+hi tish+thi badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:7716: sangs rgyas kun gyi mda' gzhu'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7717: de yi dbang mchog 'big cing thams cad rgyud bskul phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7718: mda' gzhu 'di ni khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7719: badz+ra sat+wa a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:7720: sangs rgyas kun gyi se gol dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7721: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7722: tshogs gnyis dga' ba'i gzing bstod phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7723: se gol 'di ni khyod kyis long //
NK027(sha)002:7724: badz+ra sat+wa a b+hi tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:7725: sangs rgyas kun gyi rin chen dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7726: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7727: chos kyis rgyal por dbang bsgyur phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7728: rin chen 'di ni khyod kyis long //
NK027(sha)002:7729: badz+ra sat+wa a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah tish+tha badz+ra sa sangs rgyas kun gyi gzi brjid dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7730: de ring gti mug mun pa bsal ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7731: nyi ma 'di ni khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7732: badz+ra sat+wa tish+thi badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK027(sha)002:7733: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal mtshan dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7734: de ring sbyin pas dbul ba sel ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7735: rgyal mtshan 'di ni khyod kyi badz+ra sat+wa a b+hi tish+thi badz+ra sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhad pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7736: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7737: skyes bu 'dzum gyi lung bstan phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7738: so phreng 'di ni khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7739: badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi pad+ma'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7740: de ring khyod thams cad chags med gzigs pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7741: pad+ma 'di ni badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi ral gri'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7742: de ring shes rab dam pas gcod pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7743: ral gri 'di ni khyod kyis badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyu yi dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7744: de ring chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7745: 'khor lo badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha badz+ra sangs rgyas kun gyi smra ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7746: de ring khyod la gdul bya'i bsam par chos ston phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7747: rdo rje ljags 'di khyod kyis long //
NK027(sha)002:7748: badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi rgya gram dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7749: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7750: phrin las thams cad lhun grub phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7751: rgya gram 'di ni khyod badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi go cha'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7752: de ring khyod la 'jigs pa gnyis las thar ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7753: go cha 'di ni badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha badz+ra sangs rgyas kun gyi mche ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7754: de ring khyod la gdugs pa thams cad tshar bcad nas //
NK027(sha)002:7755: mche ba 'di ni badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi khu tshur dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7756: de ring thams cad gcig tu 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7757: rdo rje khu tshur badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi sgeg mo'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7758: de ring me long lta bu ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)002:7759: rdo rje sgegs mo khyod kyis long //
NK027(sha)002:7760: badz+ra sat+wa tish+tha sangs rgyas kun gyi phreng ba'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7761: de ring mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)002:7762: rdo rje phreng ba khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7763: sangs rgyas kun gyi glu ma'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7764: de ring khyod la so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)002:7765: rdo rje'i dbang mchog khyod kyis sangs rgyas kun gyi gar mkhan dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7766: de ring bya ba nan tan ye shes kyi //
NK027(sha)002:7767: rdo rje gar mkhan khyod sangs rgyas kun gyi bdug pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7768: de ring khyod la snying rje tshad med ldan pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7769: rdo rje bdug pa sangs rgyas kun gyi me tog dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7770: de ring khyod la bskur byams pa tshad med ldan pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7771: rdo rje me tog sangs rgyas kun gyi mar me'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7772: de ring dga' ba tshad med ldan bya'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7773: rdo rje snang ba khyod kyis sangs rgyas kun gyi dri yi dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7774: de ring btang snyoms tshad med ldan pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7775: rdo rje dri chab khyod sangs rgyas kun gyi lcags kyu'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7776: de ring sbyin pa'i lcags kyus 'gugs pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7777: rdo rje lcags kyu khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7778: sangs rgyas kun gyi zhags pa'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7779: de ring khyod snyan pa'i zhags pas bcing ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7780: rdo rje zhags pa khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7781: sangs rgyas kun gyi lcags sgrog dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7782: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK027(sha)002:7783: don dang mthun par bsdams pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7784: rdo rje lcags sgrog khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7785: sangs rgyas kun gyi dril bu'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7786: de ring don spyod gnas la dbab pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7787: rdo rje 'bebs ma khyod kyi long //
NK027(sha)002:7788: bskal pa bzang po'i rgyal sras mchog /
NK027(sha)002:7789: byams pa mthong ba don yod dang //
NK027(sha)002:7791: shar na bzhugs pas dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:7792: bskal pa bzang po'i rgyal sras mchog /
NK027(sha)002:7793: spos kyi glang po dpal bar 'gro //
NK027(sha)002:7794: nam mkha' mdzod dang ye shes rtogs //
NK027(sha)002:7795: lho na bzhugs pas dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:7796: bskal pa bzang po'i rgya 'od dpag med dang zla 'od dang //
NK027(sha)002:7797: bzang skyong d+r+wa ba can gyi 'od //
NK027(sha)002:7798: nub na bzhugs pas dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:7799: bskal pa bzang po'i rdo rje snying po blo mi bzad //
