NK027(sha)002:7800: spobs pa brtsegs dang kun tu bzang //
NK027(sha)002:7801: byang na bzhugs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:7802: zhes lha dbang rdzogs par bskur nas /
NK027(sha)002:7803: de nas rdzas dbang rim pa bzhin thogs te /
NK027(sha)002:7804: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi rtse /
NK027(sha)002:7806: dpal kun rigs rnam par snang mdzad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:7807: byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad 'grub pa la phyag rgya chen po lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7808: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7809: de bzhin du phyag rgya lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7810: sku lnga ye shes mthar phyin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7812: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon dang //
NK027(sha)002:7813: mchod sbyin mnyam bzhag skyabs sbyin te //
NK027(sha)002:7814: rgyal ba rigs lnga sku'i phyag rgya //
NK027(sha)002:7815: phyag rgya chen po'i mchog thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:7816: rgyal po mchog gi phyag rgya ni //
NK027(sha)002:7817: phyag rgya'i dbang mchog mi 'da' ba //
NK027(sha)002:7818: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK027(sha)002:7819: dbang gi bkra shis dang po'o //
NK027(sha)002:7821: sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7822: snying po sngags kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7823: rtogs pa ye shes phung por gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7824: de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi thugs ye shes kyi byin rlabs snying po sngags kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7825: rtogs pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7826: thugs kyi sa bon yig 'bru mchog /
NK027(sha)002:7827: sngags kyi byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)002:7828: ye shes thugs kyi sa bon mchog /
NK027(sha)002:7829: 'bras bu sngags kyi bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:7830: snying po rigs lnga sangs rgyas kun gyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:7831: gsung mchog sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK027(sha)002:7832: byin rlabs chen po bla na med pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:7833: sngags mchog dbang gi bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7834: h'u tram h+r+aih+aah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:7835: sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par
NK027(sha)002:7836: snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la gser gyi thur mas
NK027(sha)002:7837: dbang bskur bas / ma rig pa'i ling tog byang nas shes rab kyi mig gsal bar gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7838: de bzhin du gser gyi thur mas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7839: ma rig pa'i ling tog bsal nas shes rab kyi
NK027(sha)002:7840: mig gsal ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:7841: / gser gyi thur ma thogs nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:7842: mig mkhan rgyal pos dbang bskur bzhin //
NK027(sha)002:7843: bu khyod ma rig mi shes pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7844: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK027(sha)002:7845: rin chen gser gyi thur ma yi //
NK027(sha)002:7846: 'bar ba'i ye shes gsal phyes nas //
NK027(sha)002:7847: nges par logs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK027(sha)002:7848: shes rab ye shes spyan ldan pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7849: dbang gi bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7852: sngon ri rab kyi rtse mor bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi /
NK027(sha)002:7853: 'khor rnams la me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7854: chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par rtog par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7855: de bzhin du me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7856: chos thams cad gzugs brnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma tsam
NK027(sha)002:7857: du rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:7858: / chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK027(sha)002:7859: rten 'brel mthu la snang ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7860: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa'i don //
NK027(sha)002:7861: chos nyid sgyu ma gsal bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:7862: snang sems dri ma med pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:7863: mngon shes dbang po gsal ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:7864: ye shes gsal ba'i me long gi //
NK027(sha)002:7865: dbang gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7867: sngon ri rab kyis rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7869: 'gro don thogs pa med par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7870: de bzhin du 'khor lo bzhis dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7871: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan zhing khams
NK027(sha)002:7872: gsum du 'gro don thogs pa med pa'i dbang dam
NK027(sha)002:7875: brjod pa med pa'i 'bru bkod nas //
NK027(sha)002:7876: gzhan gyi don la phan pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:7877: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:7878: nyon mongs ma lus gzhom pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:7879: legs pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:7881: dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7883: sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7885: tshangs pa'i dbyangs sgrogs pas dbang thob par gyur ro //
NK027(sha)002:7886: de bzhin du dung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7887: tshangs pa'i dbyangs sgrogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7888: chos dung rgyal bas bos nas ni //
NK027(sha)002:7889: 'jig rten sems can skal ldan la //
NK027(sha)002:7890: rnam gsal sdig sbyangs chos thos pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7891: tshangs pa'i sgra skad thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7892: skyobs pa'i mgon po tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK027(sha)002:7893: tshangs pa'i gsung mchog 'gro ba sgrol //
NK027(sha)002:7894: 'jig rten gsum du gsal ba'i sgra //
NK027(sha)002:7895: dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7897: sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7898: me tog phreng bas dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7899: tshul khrims yongs su rdzogs par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7900: de bzhin du me tog phreng bas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7901: tshul khrims yongs su rdzogs par gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:7902: ngan song las thar pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7903: sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog brgyan //
NK027(sha)002:7904: dgos pa'i don rnams myur bar 'byin //
NK027(sha)002:7905: thams cad kun gyi yid du 'ong //
NK027(sha)002:7906: 'byor ba'i longs spyod rgyan du shog /
NK027(sha)002:7907: kha dog dbyibs legs rin chen me tog 'di //
NK027(sha)002:7908: nam mkha' gang zhing sa gzhi kheb byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:7909: mchod pa'i sprin dpung dus gsum char 'beb pa //
NK027(sha)002:7910: mdzes pa'i dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7911: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7913: thugs rdo rje'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7914: de bzhin du rdo rjes dbang bskur bas thugs ye
NK027(sha)002:7915: shes rdo rje lta bu'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:7916: / sku yi phyag rgya rab rten dang //
NK027(sha)002:7917: ye shes rdo rje lta bu ste //
NK027(sha)002:7918: rdo rje thugs kyis rang bzhin ni //
NK027(sha)002:7919: me long ye shes thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7920: rdo rje'i rigs mchog rdor sems te //
NK027(sha)002:7921: dkar la dag pa shar phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK027(sha)002:7922: bde ba chen po kun la khyab pa'i bdag /
NK027(sha)002:7923: 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7925: sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7926: rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7927: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7928: de bzhin du rin po che'i dbang bskur bas yon
NK027(sha)002:7929: tan rin po che'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK027(sha)002:7930: cig / sku yi phyag rgya rtag brtan pa //
NK027(sha)002:7931: 'gro ba kun gyi re ba bskangs //
NK027(sha)002:7932: yon tan rin chen rang bzhin te //
NK027(sha)002:7933: mnyam nyid ye shes thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7934: rin chen mchog gi yon tan sems dpa' ste //
NK027(sha)002:7935: ser la dag pa lho phyogs rin chen sangs rgyas zhing //
NK027(sha)002:7936: bde ba chen po kun la khyab pa'i bdag /
NK027(sha)002:7937: 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7938: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7940: gsung pad+ma'i rigs kyi dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7941: de bzhin du pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7942: 'gro don byed pa la nyes pa'i skyon gyi ma gos pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7943: sku yi phyag rgya rtag brten pa //
NK027(sha)002:7944: pad+ma dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK027(sha)002:7945: gsung gi rang bzhin 'byung ba'i mdzod //
NK027(sha)002:7946: kun rtogs ye shes thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7947: pad+ma'i rigs mchog chos kyi sems dpa' ste //
NK027(sha)002:7948: dmar la dag pa phung pos sangs rgyas zhing //
NK027(sha)002:7949: bde ba chen po kun la khyab pa'i bdag /
NK027(sha)002:7950: 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7951: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7952: sna tshogs rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:7953: phrin las bzhi'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7954: de bzhin du rgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7955: phrin las bzhi'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7956: sku yi phyag rgya stag brtan pas //
NK027(sha)002:7957: las rnams ma lus rdzogs pa'i mchog /
NK027(sha)002:7958: phrin las 'gro don grub pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:7959: bya grub ye shes thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7960: bya ba'i rigs mchog las kyis sems dpal ste //
NK027(sha)002:7961: ljang gu dag pas byang phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK027(sha)002:7962: bde ba chen po kun la khyab pa'i bdag /
NK027(sha)002:7963: 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7964: ab+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7965: bdud rtsi bum pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7966: rnam par dag pa sil bar gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7967: de bzhin du thugs bdud rtsi bum pas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7968: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma byang ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:7969: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK027(sha)002:7970: bum pa bzang po yum gyi gter //
NK027(sha)002:7971: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin te //
NK027(sha)002:7972: 'gro ba'i nad rnams sel bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:7973: bum pa bzang po spros med chos kyi dbyings //
NK027(sha)002:7974: thugs rje chen po phan mdzad yum gyi tshul //
NK027(sha)002:7975: 'khor ba'i gnas skyob dri ma dag mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:7976: sgrib sel dbang gi bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7977: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:7979: log pa'i phyogs zil gyi gnon pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:7980: de bzhin du seng ge'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7981: gsung rab rgya mtsho'i sgras thams cad zil gyi gnon
NK027(sha)002:7982: nas stong spyi phud kyi sems can thams cad skad
NK027(sha)002:7983: cig la sangs rgyas par byed pa bcom ldan 'das
NK027(sha)002:7984: kun tu bzang po'i dbang dam pa thob par shog
NK027(sha)002:7985: / gzugs bzang sems can kun gyi gtso bo ste //
NK027(sha)002:7986: zil gnon sgra 'byin sder chags skrag par byed //
NK027(sha)002:7987: phyogs mthun kun skyob seng ge'i dpal dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:7988: thams cad zil gnon dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:7989: seng ge'i nga ro sgra chen thogs med pa //
NK027(sha)002:7990: 'jigs med 'joms pa'i sgra rnams bsgrag nas kyang /
NK027(sha)002:7991: bdud dpung ma lus zil gyi gnon mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:7992: che mchog dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:7993: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das nyi mas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7994: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:7995: de bzhin du nyi mas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:7996: skye 'gro rnams kyi rgyud la ye shes 'char ba'i
NK027(sha)002:7997: dbang dam pa nyi mas mun sel shes rab sgron
NK027(sha)002:7998: // kun la gsal ba'i rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:7999: thams cad kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK027(sha)002:8000: ma rig sel ba'i sgron mer shog /
NK027(sha)002:8001: ye shes gsal ba phyogs bcur khyab par bdal //
NK027(sha)002:8002: thugs rje mchog gyur mun pa tha dag gsal //
NK027(sha)002:8003: rang bzhin 'od gsal 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:8004: shes rab dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8005: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das zla bas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8006: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8007: de bzhin du zla bas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8008: sems can thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba
NK027(sha)002:8009: thams cad sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK027(sha)002:8010: cig / thams cad kun gsal chu shel lta bu ste //
NK027(sha)002:8011: dgos pa'i don 'byin dkar la dag pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:8012: tshad med thabs mchog zla ba rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8013: ma rig mun sel ye shes sgron mar shog /
NK027(sha)002:8014: dkar la dag pa'i zla ba dri ma med //
NK027(sha)002:8015: thabs kyi mtshan nyid skyon gyi ma gos te //
NK027(sha)002:8016: yongs su dag pa mun pa sel ba'i sman //
NK027(sha)002:8017: thabs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bac+wo lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8018: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8019: sngon gyi 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po tshul ci lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK027(sha)002:8020: rgyal po'i rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8021: gso sbyong gi nyi ma la khrus byas pas pho brang steng skor dbus gnas pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:8022: shar phyogs kyi nam mkha' la 'khor lo rtsib stong
NK027(sha)002:8023: yod pa lte ba mu khyud gser las grub pa
NK027(sha)002:8024: / gzo bos ma byas pa rang byung rgyal po'i lag pa g.yas su bab pabo //
NK027(sha)002:8025: de'i tshe rgyal po'i bsam pa la rtag 'di dang sbyar nas /
NK027(sha)002:8026: bdag ni 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po yin nges snyams nas /
NK027(sha)002:8028: zhing nam mkha' la 'gro zhing dpung gi tshogs dang
NK027(sha)002:8029: bcas pa la gling bzhi'i rgyal po thams cad kyi
NK027(sha)002:8030: mdun du bsus shing gnas pa'i tshe /
NK027(sha)002:8031: thams cad dge ba bcu'i nam mkha' la 'gro zhing /
NK027(sha)002:8032: 'god pa'i dpal dang ldan par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8033: de bzhin du 'khor lo rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8034: 'jig rten gyi 'gro ba ma lus pa smin grol
NK027(sha)002:8035: gyi lam la 'god pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK027(sha)002:8036: gyur cig / dus gsum rgyal bas bskor ba'i 'khor lo 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8037: mi khoms rgyun gcod rgyu dang 'bras bur ston //
NK027(sha)002:8038: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dbang phyug rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8039: bla med 'khor lo dam pa bskor gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8040: stong nyid ye shes gsal ba'i 'khor lo la //
NK027(sha)002:8041: chos nyid dbyings las phrin las cir yang ston //
NK027(sha)002:8042: sems can kha lo gyen du bsgyur mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:8043: chos 'khor dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8045: sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8046: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i glang po ni kha dog dkar po yan lag bdun dang ldan pa /
NK027(sha)002:8047: lha ma yin dang g.yul 'gyed pas g.yul las rgyal
NK027(sha)002:8048: bar byed pa'i mthu dang ldan pa'i dbang bskur bas
NK027(sha)002:8049: / rgol ba thams cad zil gyi gnon pa'i dbang dam pa de bzhin du 'gres so //
NK027(sha)002:8050: theg pa'i don dam bla med ston pa'i mchog /
NK027(sha)002:8051: yan lag bdun mdzes ku mu ta yi mdog /
NK027(sha)002:8052: 'dul dka' stobs chen glang po rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8053: khyu mchog brlab chen stobs lnga rdzogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8054: stobs mchog pha rol gnon pa'i mthu mnga' ba //
NK027(sha)002:8055: gdul ba stobs ldan gzhan gyi mi bardzi bas //
NK027(sha)002:8056: pha rol rdzu 'phrul mthu stobs gnas mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8057: mthu stobs dbang gi bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8058: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8059: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rta mchog rin po che ni /
NK027(sha)002:8060: sngon po rngog ma dmar pos gling bzhi yud kyis
NK027(sha)002:8061: bskor nas rdzu 'phrul dang ldan zhing thugs rje la
NK027(sha)002:8062: thogs pa med pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8063: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal chu bo bzhi las grol //
NK027(sha)002:8064: brtson 'grus myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul shugs kyi spyod //
NK027(sha)002:8065: cang shes sprin gyi shugs 'chang rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8066: mi gnas ye shes yid bzhin spyod par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8067: rdzu 'phrul thogs med kun tu myur ba'i shugs //
NK027(sha)002:8068: kun tu bsgrod pa'i don la myur ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:8069: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs kun tu ston mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8070: thogs med dbang gi bkra shis bac+wo brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8071: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser sogs /
NK027(sha)002:8072: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i nor bu rin po che ni /
NK027(sha)002:8073: bee d+aur+ya'i rang bzhin can zur brgyad la mun pa sel ba'i gang 'dod mthong ba /
NK027(sha)002:8074: ci tsam 'byung ba dang dpag tshad 'od kyi khyab pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8075: nyon mongs pa'i mun pa bsal te /
NK027(sha)002:8076: lhag mthong gi ye shes rtogs pa'i dbang dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8077: 'khor ba'i mun sel bde ba'i snying po 'byung //
NK027(sha)002:8078: dgos pa'i mchod sbyin longs spyod phun sum tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:8079: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen spyod par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8080: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i nor bu rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8081: thams cad kun gyi yid dang mthun pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8082: che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8083: yid bzhin dbang gi bkra shis bcu dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8084: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK027(sha)002:8085: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i blon po rin po che ni
NK027(sha)002:8086: / mkhas pa gsal ba'i yid gzhungs pa dpag tshad
NK027(sha)002:8087: tshun chad kyi gter mthong ba rgyal po'i dgongs pa
NK027(sha)002:8088: thams cad 'grub pa de'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8089: lha'i mig rnam par dag pa thob cing 'phags pa'i
NK027(sha)002:8090: nor bdun dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa gang la
NK027(sha)002:8091: ci 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //
NK027(sha)002:8092: 'gro la snying brtse tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8093: dbang phyug btsun pa'i blon po rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8094: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal mtshan thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8095: 'tshang pa 'phrul 'byin blon po rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8096: legs nyes kun byed gcod pa'i don la mkhas //
NK027(sha)002:8098: blon po'i dbang gi bkra shis nyi shu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8099: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i btsun mo rin po che ni /
NK027(sha)002:8100: rgyal rigs su skyes pa gzugs mdzes blta na sdug pa /
NK027(sha)002:8102: ba spu'i khung nas tsan+dana gyi dri 'byung ba /
NK027(sha)002:8103: lus la reg pa tsam gyi bde ba de'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8104: ting nge 'dzin zhi ba'i chos la dbang 'byor te
NK027(sha)002:8105: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i spyod yul yongs su dag
NK027(sha)002:8106: pa'i dbang dam pa pha rol phyin bcu sems can
NK027(sha)002:8107: skyab pa'i phyir // shes rab gzugs mdzes btsun mo rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8108: bsdu ba rnam bzhi tshad med bzhi po yi //
NK027(sha)002:8109: tshe dang longs spyod gter la spyod par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8110: shes rab dbyings la grub pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:8111: dgos pa'i don grub btsun mo ste //
NK027(sha)002:8112: smon lam mthu stobs 'brel ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:8113: dbang gi bkra shis nyer gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8114: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK027(sha)002:8115: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dmag dpon rin po che ni
NK027(sha)002:8116: / mkhas pa dpa' ba pha rol gyi dpung 'joms pa'i dgra thabs kyi sbyor ba la mkhas pa /
NK027(sha)002:8117: bsdo ba 'joms pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8118: 'jigs tshogs kyi ri bo nyi shu 'joms pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:8119: dam pa phan pa'i go bsag gnod pa'i dpung 'joms
NK027(sha)002:8120: shing // 'jigs pa'i skyab byed 'gro la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK027(sha)002:8121: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i dmag dpon 'dis //
NK027(sha)002:8122: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul dpung gi bsrung bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:8123: drag shul dreg pa'i pha rol 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:8124: nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo sel byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:8125: rnam par rtog pa'i tshogs kyi mi tshugs pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8126: 'dul thabs dbang gi bkra shis nyer gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8127: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi ral gri'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8128: nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8129: de bzhin du ral gri'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8130: 'khrul ba'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8131: sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba kun bcad de //
NK027(sha)002:8132: mi shes d+r+wa ba gcod tshul du //
NK027(sha)002:8133: gnon pos bag chags gcod pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8134: thams cad kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:8135: sgrib gnyis d+r+wa ba gral byed pa //
NK027(sha)002:8136: ye shes rnam pa thogs pa med //
NK027(sha)002:8137: mi shes bag chags gcod byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8138: dbang gi bkra shis nyer gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8139: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi mda' gzhu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8140: thabs shes rab 'brel ba'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8141: de bzhin du mda' gzhu'i dbang bskur bas thabs shes
NK027(sha)002:8142: rab bzung 'jug rnam par rgyal mtsho'i dbang dam pa
NK027(sha)002:8143: rgol ba'i tshogs 'joms myur ba'i shugs 'chang ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:8144: thabs kyis 'dul la nyes pas ma gos te //
NK027(sha)002:8145: dngos po kun 'joms pha rol 'big byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8146: thabs kyi 'dul ba'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8147: thabs shes dbyer med rang bzhin ro gcig pa //
NK027(sha)002:8148: thugs rje myur mgyog thabs mchog 'gro la 'byung //
NK027(sha)002:8149: yang rab rtsal mchog blo gros rnam par non //
NK027(sha)002:8150: thabs shes dbang gi bkra shis nyer bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8151: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das gnam ral gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8152: bar chad kyi bdud 'joms par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8153: de bzhin du gnam ral gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8154: bdud dpung tha dag 'joms pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8155: stobs ldan dbang phyug mthu stobs che ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:8156: bdud dpung phas kyi bsdo ba kun btul nas //
NK027(sha)002:8157: che btsan drag po kun la rgyal ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:8158: thams cad mthu stobs dag gi dbang byed shog /
NK027(sha)002:8159: rin chen rgyan mdzes gnam ral rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8160: log pa'i phyogs kun tshar gcod zil gyi gnon //
NK027(sha)002:8161: thabs la mkhas pa'i sde dpung chen po ste //
NK027(sha)002:8162: rgyal thabs dbang gi bkra shis nyer lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8163: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8164: shan nye ba'i ral gri rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8165: 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8166: de bzhin du shan nye ba rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8167: 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang dam pa //
NK027(sha)002:8168: nyon mongs sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8169: dngos po mtshan ma ma lus gzhon pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8170: mi shes rnam par rtog pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8171: gdug pa 'joms pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8172: rin chen mdzes pa'i shan mchog rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8173: rnam gcod rnam pas pha rol nyes pa gcod //
NK027(sha)002:8174: ye shes rnon mchog kun gyi yid du 'ong //
NK027(sha)002:8175: nyes gcod dbang gi bkra shis nyer drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8176: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser zhwa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8177: bgegs dang log 'dren med pa tshe'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8178: de bzhin du zhwa nye ba'i rin po che'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:8179: bskur bas bgegs dang bar chad gang gis kyang mi
NK027(sha)002:8180: tshug pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8182: gdung ba sel ba'i nyes mkho ste //
NK027(sha)002:8183: 'bras bu thar pa thob pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8184: 'jigs pa bzhi yi skyabs su shog /
NK027(sha)002:8185: rin chen rgyan mchog dbu zhwa rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8186: 'jigs pa bzhi skyobs log pa'i skyon las grol //
NK027(sha)002:8187: mi 'gyur g.yung drung tshe'i dbang thob pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8188: g.yung drung dbang gi bkra shes nyer bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8189: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das tshangs pa'i khab skud kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8190: legs pa'i yon tan 'grub pa'i dbang dam thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8191: de bzhin du nye ba'i rin chen khab skud kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8192: legs pa'i yon tan 'grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8193: tshangs pa'i khab skud nye ba'i bkra shis te //
NK027(sha)002:8194: legs pa'i yon tan tshang pa rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:8195: nyes pa kun grol legs pa'i rang bzhin can //
NK027(sha)002:8196: phun sum tshogs pa dpal gyi 'byor bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:8197: tshangs pa'i khab skud legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK027(sha)002:8198: gang la yid dang 'tsham pa 'tshem byed nas //
NK027(sha)002:8199: don gyi thugs rje chen pos mtshams sbyor ba //
NK027(sha)002:8200: tshangs skud dbang gi bkra shis nyer brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8201: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das na bza' rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8202: grang ba'i sdug bsngal las skyobs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8203: de bzhin du gos rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8204: 'di phyir grang ba'i nyes pa zhi ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8205: nyes pa kun skyobs na bza' rin po che //
NK027(sha)002:8206: bde ba'i yid bzhin zad pa med pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8207: yon tan tshang ba'i na bza' dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8208: 'di dang pha rol gnyis su gon bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:8209: rin chen na bza' ci ltar blta na sdug /
NK027(sha)002:8210: che chung 'tsham la 'gro la dbyibs legs mdzes //
NK027(sha)002:8211: yon tan bla med 'phags pa'i sku dang mtshungs //
NK027(sha)002:8212: chos rtags dbang gi bkra shis nyer dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8213: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das chags nye ba rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8214: thugs rje 'gro ba la chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8215: de bzhin du chags nye ba rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8216: thugs rje 'gro ba la chags pa'i dbang dam pa rin chen chags kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:8217: kun la snyoms pa'i thugs rje yi //
NK027(sha)002:8218: sems can don la thogs med de //
NK027(sha)002:8220: rin chen mdzes pa'i chags mchog dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8221: gar yang thogs med phyogs bcu bsgrod nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:8222: don rnams ma lus yongs su rdzogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8223: yongs grub dbang gi bkra shis sum cu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8224: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8225: khri stan pags pa rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8226: snying rjes sems can 'dren pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8227: de bzhin du khri stan pag pa rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8228: thugs rjes sems can 'dren pa'i dbang dam pa khri stan sa le'i pag pa mchog tu shes //
NK027(sha)002:8229: sems can kun la snyams pa'i snying rje can //
NK027(sha)002:8230: yon tan mtha' dag tshangs ba'i byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)002:8231: snying rjes 'gro don dgongs pa 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8232: snying rje tshad med sems can kun la dgongs //
NK027(sha)002:8233: nyams thag 'phongs pa mgon med rnams kyi skyabs //
NK027(sha)002:8234: sems can 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8235: 'gro don dbang gi bkra shis so gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8236: a b+hi shiny+tsa sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8237: yungs dkar bgegs kyi gnyen por byin gyis brlab pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8239: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cus mi tshugs shing /
NK027(sha)002:8240: mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8241: yungs dkar rdo rje'i rigs mchog chen po ste //
NK027(sha)002:8242: rtogs bral mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje yis //
NK027(sha)002:8243: rtog pa'i bgegs rnams rab tu 'joms mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:8244: phyogs dus kun tu bgegs rnams zhi bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:8245: yungs dkar rdo rje'i bgegs tshogs 'joms //
NK027(sha)002:8246: bdud dpung 'dul byed thugs rje can //
NK027(sha)002:8247: dgra bgegs kun la rab rgyal ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:8248: dbang gi bkra shis so gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8249: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK027(sha)002:8250: rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi byang chub sems dpa' don
NK027(sha)002:8252: mngon shes lnga'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:8253: 'bras bu ri rab rtser rin po'i khang pa rnam
NK027(sha)002:8254: par snang mdzad rdo rje dbyings su mngon par byang
NK027(sha)002:8256: de bzhin du rigs kyi bu la 'bras bu ri
NK027(sha)002:8257: rab kyi rtser mngon par byang chub par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:8258: / mngon shes lnga ldan 'bras bu sa bcur 'das //
NK027(sha)002:8259: 'bras bu dam pa mngon par sangs rgyas te //
NK027(sha)002:8260: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8261: dbang mchog dam pa yongs su rdzogs pa yis //
NK027(sha)002:8262: chos rnams ma lus thob pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8263: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang mchog yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8264: phyi'i dbang gi bkra shis so gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8272: h'u tram h+r+aih+aah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:8274: khyim bdag bzang skyong gi zho phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:8275: bza' ba'i mdangs dang ldan pa'i rdzas su byin gyis brlab pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8276: ting nge 'dzin gyi gzi brjid dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8277: ba zho kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8278: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs te //
NK027(sha)002:8279: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8280: bkra shis des ni snying po thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8281: zho ni bcud ldan bkra shis rdzas kyi mchog /
NK027(sha)002:8283: nyon mongs 'phongs pa ngom zhing tshim byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8284: bcud ldan dbang gi bkra shis so bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8285: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8289: 'bras bu mang po byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8290: dge ba chung ngu la bsod nams phun sum tshogs
NK027(sha)002:8291: pa'i dbang dam dur was tshe ni 'phel bar byed
NK027(sha)002:8292: pa ste // rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe ni rab 'grub pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8293: skye shi gnyis kyi sdug bsngal rgyun chad de //
NK027(sha)002:8294: 'chi ba med pa tshe yi rig 'dzin shog /
NK027(sha)002:8295: dur was rtsa mchog bsod nams mang po 'phel //
NK027(sha)002:8296: bkra shis bde legs 'bras bu yon tan rgyas //
NK027(sha)002:8297: yid la gang bsam 'phral du 'grub byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8298: 'dod 'byung dbang gi bkra shis so lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8299: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8300: sa'i lha mo'i li khri phul bas dbang gi rang
NK027(sha)002:8301: bzhin du byin gyis brlab pa de bzhin du thugs
NK027(sha)002:8302: rje chen pos / sems can la rjes su 'dzin
NK027(sha)002:8303: pa'i dbang dam pa li khri dmar po dbang gi
NK027(sha)002:8304: rje chen pos / rang bzhin la // chos rnams ma lus dbang du gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8305: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa //
NK027(sha)002:8306: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rab tu brtan gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8307: kha dog dmar po nub phyogs pad+ma'i rigs //
NK027(sha)002:8308: chags pa gnyis ldan bdag gzhan don gnyis 'grub //
NK027(sha)002:8309: gsung gi bdag nyid don ston bkra shis rdzas //
NK027(sha)002:8310: sku tshe dbang gi bkra shis so drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8311: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi kun gzhi'i rnam shes gsum du gnas gyur pas /
NK027(sha)002:8312: me long lta bu'i ye shes brnyes nas /
NK027(sha)002:8313: mngon par sangs rgyas pa de bzhin du me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8314: bag la nyal gyi dri ma phra mo yang rdo
NK027(sha)002:8315: rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bcom nas mngon
NK027(sha)002:8316: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8317: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK027(sha)002:8318: ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du bdag gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:8319: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8320: bkra shis des ni sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8321: me long gdong bstan bzhin gyi dri ma sel //
NK027(sha)002:8322: de bzhin nyon mongs shes bya'i dri ma dag /
NK027(sha)002:8323: gsal las rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK027(sha)002:8324: gsal ba'i dbang gi bkra shis so bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8327: brgya byin gyi dung g.yas 'khyil phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:8328: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cus chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8329: dung tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs pas chos
NK027(sha)002:8330: kyi 'khor lo'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK027(sha)002:8331: / dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:8332: yon tan rgya mtsho bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:8333: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8334: bkra shis des ni tshe la dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:8335: chos sgra chen po phyogs bcur grags pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8336: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog dung gi sgra bus te //
NK027(sha)002:8337: ma lus 'gro ba kun gyi rgyud grol ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:8338: gsung mchog dbang gi bkra shis so gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8339: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8340: glang po che sa skyong gi g+hi wang phul nas /
NK027(sha)002:8341: bdud bzhi las grol bar byin gyis brlab pa bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8342: nyon mongs pa'i nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi las thar
NK027(sha)002:8343: pa'i dbang g+hi wang dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi
NK027(sha)002:8344: sman // sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur nas //
NK027(sha)002:8345: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8346: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal zhi byed shog /
NK027(sha)002:8347: yon tan phun tshogs bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams sel //
NK027(sha)002:8348: sman mchog skye 'gro ma lus kun gyi gsos //
NK027(sha)002:8349: byin gyis brlab pas bkra shis tshe yi rgyu //
NK027(sha)002:8350: nad med dbang gi bkra shis so dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8351: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8352: shing gi lha mo'i 'od 'chang mas bil ba'i 'bras bu phul bas /
NK027(sha)002:8353: 'bras bu rnams yongs su rdzogs pa de bzhin du
NK027(sha)002:8354: sku dang ye shes stobs dang mi 'jigs pa sogs
NK027(sha)002:8355: pa'i 'bras bu'i chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:8356: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8357: bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK027(sha)002:8358: 'jig rten 'jig rten gnas pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK027(sha)002:8359: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8360: bkra shis des ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8361: yal ga lo 'dab me tog g.yu lor 'khyil //
NK027(sha)002:8362: 'bras bu yid bzhin 'byor ba'i longs spyod ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8363: 'dod dgu kun dang mthun pa'i longs spyod pa //
NK027(sha)002:8364: phun tshogs dbang gi bkra shis bzhi bcu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8365: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das byang chub shing drung
NK027(sha)002:8366: du bzhugs pa la bdud kyi rgol ba'i dus su
NK027(sha)002:8367: / thugs dpal wer bkra shis pa de bzhin du
NK027(sha)002:8368: thugs la dpal wer 'bar zhing bkra shis pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:8369: dam pa dpal wer thugs kyis bkra shis te //
NK027(sha)002:8370: 'dren pa rnams kyi thugs lags pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8371: bla med thar lam drangs ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8372: thugs la dpa' wer bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:8373: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtag dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8374: bsngo ba'i chos rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:8375: thugs ka nyid la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:8376: dpal wer dbang gi bkra shis zhe gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8377: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8378: bdud kyi rgol ba'i dus su phyag zhabs 'khor lo bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8380: phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8381: 'khor lo'i bkra shis phyag zhabs mthil //
NK027(sha)002:8382: skyob pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa'i lha //
NK027(sha)002:8383: nyon mongs sems can dmyal ba'i gsos //
NK027(sha)002:8384: phyag zhabs 'khor los bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:8385: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtag dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8386: bsngo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:8387: phyag zhabs mthil la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:8388: 'khor lo dbang gi bkra shis zhe gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8389: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8390: bdud rnams kyi rgol ba'i dus su ljags pad+mara bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8392: ljags pad+mas mtshan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8393: gsung mchog pad+ma chos kyi rgyal //
NK027(sha)002:8394: nyon mongs ma gos pad+ma'i thugs //
NK027(sha)002:8395: thams cad sgrol ba'i gsung lags te //
NK027(sha)002:8396: ljags mchog pad+ma'i bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:8397: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8398: bsngo ba'i chos rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:8399: ljags kyi mchog las mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:8400: pad+ma dbang gi bkra shis zhe gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8401: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8402: bdud kyi rgol ba'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:8403: sku rgyal mtshan bkra shis pa de bzhin du rgyal mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8404: rgyal mtshan gyi mtshan pa'i dbang dam pa mi nub rgyal mtshan 'dren pa'i sku //
NK027(sha)002:8405: thams cad bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK027(sha)002:8406: dpung 'jom sangs rgyas sku bstod de //
NK027(sha)002:8407: sku mchog sangs rgyas bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:8408: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtag dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8409: bsngo ba'i chos rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:8410: sku yi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:8411: rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis zhe bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8412: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8413: bdud kyi rgol ba'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:8414: mgur la bum pas bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8416: mgur bum pas mtshan pa'i dbang dam pa bkra shis bum pa dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8417: bcom ldan 'das kyi mgul lags te //
NK027(sha)002:8418: mgul mchog bkra shis 'di byin pas //
NK027(sha)002:8419: bum pa'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8420: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8421: bsngo ba'i chos rnams mgul gyi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:8422: bum pa'i dbang gi bkra shis zhe lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8423: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyi rgol ba'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:8424: dbu la gdugs kyi bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8426: dbu gdugs kyi mtshan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8427: gdugs kyi tsha ba'i sdug bsngal kun bsal te //
NK027(sha)002:8428: nyon mongs ma lus kun la bsil ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:8429: che ba'i yon tan ma lus rgyas pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8430: log pa'i phyogs rnams zil gyi gnon par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8431: gzhan gyi mi thub bsngo ba'i chos rnams dbu skra'i
NK027(sha)002:8432: machogala gdugs mchog dbang gi bkra shis zhe drug pa'o
NK027(sha)002:8433: // a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8434: bdud kyi rgol ba'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:8435: tshems la dung gi bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK027(sha)002:8436: tshems dung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8437: tshems dung gi mtshan pa'i dbang dam pa snyan pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur sgrogs pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8438: mu stegs logs pa'i phyogs rnams skrag byed cing //
NK027(sha)002:8439: sems can kun gyi shes pa grol ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8440: gsung mchog dung gi rgyal po'i bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:8441: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8442: bsngo ba'i chos rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK027(sha)002:8443: gsung gi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK027(sha)002:8444: dung dkar dbang gi bkra shis zhe bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8445: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la /
NK027(sha)002:8446: bdud kyi rgol ba'i dus su /
NK027(sha)002:8447: nya bzhi nyar bkra shis pa de bzhin du nya'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8448: spyan dang nya bzhi mtshan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8449: phyag zhabs nya shar byin rlabs te //
NK027(sha)002:8451: nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8452: nya ltar nya'i bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:8453: gzhan gyi bsngo ba'i nya bzhi mchog la nya bzhi dbang gi bkra shis zhe brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8454: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8455: sna tshogs rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8456: phrin las bzhi 'grub par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8457: de bzhin du rgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8458: rig sngags 'chang ba rnams kyi bsrung zhing phrin las
NK027(sha)002:8459: bzhi thog pa med par 'grub pa'i dbang dam pa
NK027(sha)002:8460: dog dang lam gnyis med pa la //
NK027(sha)002:8461: gtsug tu rgya gram dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:8462: rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyi kyang //
NK027(sha)002:8463: bsrung zhing rtag tu skyobs par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8464: 'phrin las thogs pa med pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8465: bya ba nan tan ye shes la //
NK027(sha)002:8466: dgos pa'i don rnams kun 'grub pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8467: dbang gi bkra shis zhe dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8468: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8469: cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8470: rdul gyi bag chags dang bral bar gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8471: de bzhin du cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:8472: sbyor ba khams gsum na gnas kyang rdul gyi bag chags dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8473: bkra shis rtag ldan dar gyi cod pan 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8474: dbang gi rang bzhin dmar po 'bar ba ste //
NK027(sha)002:8475: dbang bskur spyi bor btags pa'i yon tan gyi //
NK027(sha)002:8476: dbang gi bkra shis dam pa thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8477: chos nyid dar dang 'dra bar mtshungs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8478: don dam nyid du rtogs pa mngon byung ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:8479: 'di ni legs pa'i don nyid mngon ston pa //
NK027(sha)002:8480: cod pan dbang gi bkra shis lnga bcu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8481: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8482: mchod pa rnam lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8483: rdo rje rgyal thabs kyi dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8484: de bzhin du mchod pa'i rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8485: rdo rje rgyal theb mtha' dag byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8486: thabs chen stobs ldan mchod 'os rnam pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8487: dmigs pa lnga dang ting 'dzin cha dbye ste //
NK027(sha)002:8488: rkyen dang 'tsham pa'i mchod pa dam pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8489: thams cad phul ba'i stobs mchog bkra shis shog /
NK027(sha)002:8490: dri chab dri bsrung me tog mdzes par bkram //
NK027(sha)002:8491: bdug spos yid tshim ar+g+ham bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK027(sha)002:8492: lha bshos ro ldan 'od gsal mar me ste //
NK027(sha)002:8493: mchod rdzas dbang gi bkra shis nga gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8494: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8495: chos la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:8496: gsang sngags kyi rgyud mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8497: de bzhin du ka p+aa li'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8498: sngags rgyud mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang dam pa gdung bas sems bskyed dad pa'i shugs phyung nas //
NK027(sha)002:8499: brtson 'grus dbus kyi thams cad thob pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8500: dad pa'i shugs kyi kun tu nyan pa dang //
NK027(sha)002:8501: shes rab stobs kyi thams cad shes par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8502: shes rab rgya chen nyan pa phyogs med byed //
NK027(sha)002:8503: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' zhes rjes su slob //
NK027(sha)002:8504: sems dang chos nyid gnyis su med pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8505: nyan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis nga gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8506: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8507: chags shing gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8508: theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8509: de bzhin du chags shing gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8510: theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8511: rin chen chags shing 'khor ba'i kha lo 'dren //
NK027(sha)002:8512: 'gro ba ma lus thar pa'i gnas su skyel //
NK027(sha)002:8513: skyes mchog dus gsum sman pa'i rgyal po ste //
NK027(sha)002:8514: ma rig rmongs pa'i 'gro ba 'dren par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8515: gti mug rmongs pa'i shes pa bkrol nas kyang //
NK027(sha)002:8516: ma rig log par rtog pa grol mdzad pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8517: thugs rje che bas shes rgyud bkrol ba yi //
NK027(sha)002:8518: chos 'chad dbang gi bkra shis nga gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8519: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser /
NK027(sha)002:8520: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad glegs bam gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8521: chos kyi sgo mo thams cad la mkhas pa'i dbang
NK027(sha)002:8522: dam pa gsung rab glegs bam chos kyi gzugs brnyan
NK027(sha)002:8523: te // legs pa'i yon tan ma lus bskyed mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:8524: thams cad kun gyi dbang po sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8525: chos rnams thams cad 'chad pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:8526: gsung rab chos 'chad gzhung mchog glegs bam ste //
NK027(sha)002:8527: chos kyi sgra sgrogs yi ge'i phreng bas bskor //
NK027(sha)002:8528: blo la rab 'bring ci ltar 'tsham par ston //
NK027(sha)002:8529: glegs bam dbang gi bkra shis nga bzhi pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8530: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dril bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8531: ye shes thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8532: de bzhin du rdo rje dril bus dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8533: ye shes rtogs nas 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med chos kyi sku //
NK027(sha)002:8534: 'du 'bral med pa chos kyi dbyings mchog ste //
NK027(sha)002:8535: 'bras bu stobs ldan phyag rgya chen po nyid //
NK027(sha)002:8536: rdo rje dril bu 'chang ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:8537: rig pa'i ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NK027(sha)002:8538: ye shes lnga yi rtags kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK027(sha)002:8539: g.yon pas dril bus gsung rab rgya mtsho sgrogs //
NK027(sha)002:8540: thabs shes rab dbang gi bkra shis nga lnga pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8541: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8542: dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8543: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po la mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8544: de bzhin du rin po che'i dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8545: chos kyi rgyal srid 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8546: mya ngan 'das pa thugs rje'i dpal //
NK027(sha)002:8547: rin chen dbu rgyan chos kyi rgyal //
NK027(sha)002:8548: dbang gi byin rlabs sbyin pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8549: chos kyi rgyal srid byed par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8550: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa'i dbu rgyan can //
NK027(sha)002:8551: legs par kun skyob chos kyi rgyal srid byed //
NK027(sha)002:8552: phyag rgya rigs lnga mthu dang ldan byed pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8553: dbu rgyan dbang gi bkra shis nga drug pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8554: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser dpung rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8555: mi 'jigs pa bzhi la mnga' brnyes par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8556: de bzhin du dpung rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8557: mi 'jigs pa bzhi'i dbang dam pa mi 'jigs phas kyi rgol ba thul ba dang //
NK027(sha)002:8558: mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog bkra shis thub pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8559: mnga' mdzes phung po rtags kyis dam pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8560: rgyan mchog dam pa ston pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK027(sha)002:8561: rin chen dpung rgyan sha ri ra'i rgyan //
NK027(sha)002:8562: chos nyid don rtogs rtag dang mthun pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8563: dgongs pa ting 'dzin legs par dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:8564: dpung rgyan dbang gi bkra shis nga bdun pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8565: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser do shal phreng ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:8566: che ba'i yon tan rgyas shing mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8567: de bzhin du do shal gyi dbang bskur bas che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i dbang dam pa //
NK027(sha)002:8568: rin chen phreng bas 'gro ba'i re ba bskangs //
NK027(sha)002:8569: phreng ba do shal 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:8570: sku yi rgyan mchog yon tan sku la rdzogs //
NK027(sha)002:8571: phreng thag bzang pos phrin las rgyun mi 'chad //
NK027(sha)002:8572: rtag tu yon tan zla ltar 'phel bar shog /
NK027(sha)002:8573: rin chen dbang po rgyas pa'i yon tan tshogs //
NK027(sha)002:8574: sku tshe zhing khams mdzad pa bsam mi khyab //
NK027(sha)002:8575: 'gro ba'i dbul sel bde legs kun 'byung ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:8576: phreng ba'i dbang gi bkra shis nga brgyad pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8577: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par phyag gdub kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8578: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8579: de bzhin du gdu bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8580: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang dam pa sil snyan mdzes pa'i rgyan legs te //
NK027(sha)002:8582: 'bras bu thob pa'i dbang mchog go //
NK027(sha)002:8584: rin chen phyag gdub dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8585: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan gyi //
NK027(sha)002:8586: nges legs yon tan kun 'byung ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:8587: dbang gi bkra shis nga dgu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8588: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser zhabs gdub kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8589: stobs bcu la mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8590: de bzhin du zhabs gdub kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8591: stobs bcu la mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8592: rgyan gyi bye brag rgyal po'i tshul //
NK027(sha)002:8593: rdo rje zhabs kyis chas rab 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8594: khyod kyis zhabs la dbang bskur bas //
NK027(sha)002:8595: 'gro ba'i don la chags par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8596: rin chen zhabs gdub dam pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8597: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan gyi //
NK027(sha)002:8598: nges par mdzes pa'i yon tan 'grub //
NK027(sha)002:8599: dbang gi bkra shis drug cu pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8600: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la /
NK027(sha)002:8601: dar phyang gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8602: 'khor 'das kyi chos la dbang thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8603: de dang rjes su mthun par dar phyang gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8604: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa dar phyang gyen du 'phur ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:8605: chos kyi sku dang gnyis su med //
NK027(sha)002:8607: longs sprul sku gnyis thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8608: dmar po g.yas phul chos nyid gyen du rtogs //
NK027(sha)002:8609: sngon po 'phred 'phul phrin las rnam bzhi mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:8610: mthing ka mar 'phyang klu gdon zil gnon pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8611: dar 'phyang dbang gi bkra shis re gcig pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8612: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8613: rigs nges pa'i rdzas su gyur te /
NK027(sha)002:8614: rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur to //
NK027(sha)002:8615: de bzhin du rdo rje ming gi dbang gi bskur bas /
NK027(sha)002:8616: nges pa'i sras kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8617: rdo rje'i ming mchog dam pa'i dpe la drangs //
NK027(sha)002:8618: thugs las gsung du byung nas gtad pa 'di //
NK027(sha)002:8619: dag cing tshul bzhin yod la dbang bskur ba'i //
NK027(sha)002:8620: thams cad ston pa'i ming mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8621: ston pa'i thugs rje nges pa'i ming btags pas //
NK027(sha)002:8622: thugs kyi ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK027(sha)002:8623: rdo rje 'chang gi mtshan gyi dbang thob nas //
NK027(sha)002:8624: mtshan mchog dbang gi bkra shis re gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8625: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyis rtser rigs bzhi'i sangs
NK027(sha)002:8626: rgyas kyi byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad 'grub
NK027(sha)002:8627: pa la me long lnga'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK027(sha)002:8628: 'bras bu ri rab kyis rtser rin po che'i khang
NK027(sha)002:8629: par rnam par snang mdzad kyi rdo rje dbyings su
NK027(sha)002:8630: mngon par byang chub pa lngas dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:8631: de bzhin du 'bras bu ri rab kyi rtser mngon par byang chub par gyur cig /
NK027(sha)002:8632: mngon shes lnga ldan 'bras bu sa bcu nas //
NK027(sha)002:8633: yi ge 'khor lo rdzogs pa che la gnas //
NK027(sha)002:8634: 'bras bus dam pa mngon par sangs rgyas te //
NK027(sha)002:8635: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK027(sha)002:8636: dbang mchog dam pa yongs su rdzogs pa yi //
NK027(sha)002:8637: chos rnams thams cad ma lus thob pa ste //
NK027(sha)002:8638: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang mchog yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8639: phyi'i dbang gi bkra shis re gsum pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8644: h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK027(sha)002:8645: bum chu sgrib pa dag byed bdud rtsi dri med chu /
NK027(sha)002:8646: bkra shis mdzes pa'i bum par rab bkang ste //
NK027(sha)002:8647: rigs kyis sangs rgyas kun du bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK027(sha)002:8648: bum pa mchog gi khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:8649: badz+ra ka la k+sha a b+hi zhes yo ga'i dbang drug cu rtsa gsum po rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK027(sha)002:8650: de nas bum pa'i dbang yang bskur 'byung khrus bya'o //
NK027(sha)002:8652: lha rigs lngas gtso byas rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs /
NK027(sha)002:8655: badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma a mo ga sid+d+hi +aah yo ga'i dbang drug cu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8656: theg pa yo ga'i theg pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8657: 'jug sgo ting nge 'dzin gtso che ste mtshan bcas lha'i dam dang /
NK027(sha)002:8658: mtshan med chos nyid gnyis so //
NK027(sha)002:8659: de'ang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK027(sha)002:8660: dka' thub bsnyung gnas 'dir mi dgos //
NK027(sha)002:8661: khrus dang gtsang sgra 'dir mi dgos //
NK027(sha)002:8662: sangs rgyas thams cad sems dpa' che //
NK027(sha)002:8665: lta ba don dam pa'i bden pa mtshan nyid med
NK027(sha)002:8666: pa spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba rtog pa'i
NK027(sha)002:8667: byin rlabs lha'i dal du 'dod te /
NK027(sha)002:8669: rigs lnga gsal ba grogs po'i tshul dam pa rnam snang chen por rtogs /
NK027(sha)002:8672: rang byung gi bslab pa gsum ldan du bsrung /
NK027(sha)002:8673: khyim pas rigs lnga'i dam tshig bsrung ste /
NK027(sha)002:8675: sdom pa gsum la gnas par bya //
NK027(sha)002:8676: gal te rab tu byung ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:8677: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK027(sha)002:8679: khyim pa'i tshul du bya ba ni //
NK027(sha)002:8680: rigs lnga rgyal po rtag tu bsrung //
NK027(sha)002:8683: yig 'bru lha sku dam tshig pa //
NK027(sha)002:8684: ye shes sems dpa' grogs po'i tshul du dmigs nas mngon par byang chub bsgom mo //
NK027(sha)002:8691: lha'i ting nge 'dzin dang ma bral bas phrin las
NK027(sha)002:8692: bzhi'i sgo nas rang gzhan gyi don gtsor byed pa
NK027(sha)002:8694: lha'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas te /
NK027(sha)002:8695: sems can thams cad yongs mi gtong //
NK027(sha)002:8696: rtag tu sangs rgyas yid la byed //
NK027(sha)002:8697: rtag tu sangs rgyas mchod pa mchog /
NK027(sha)002:8699: gsang rdzas kyang skabs su spyod de /
NK027(sha)002:8700: mgo bo thod pa'i dum bu dag /
NK027(sha)002:8701: ma mo brtan pa'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK027(sha)002:8702: bum pa khrag gi bkang ba yang //
NK027(sha)002:8703: dkyil 'khor grwa bzhir bzhag par bya //
NK027(sha)002:8705: don dam pa'i ye shes rtogs pa chos sku /
NK027(sha)002:8707: de las shar ba sprul sku'o //
NK027(sha)002:8709: rigs lnga shar ba grogs pos tshul //
NK027(sha)002:8710: dam pa rnam snang chen por rtogs //
NK027(sha)002:8711: yan lag dgu ldan stug po bkod //
NK027(sha)002:8714: gnas lha bya skad snyan ljon shing gi tshal /
NK027(sha)002:8715: rdo rje dbyings kyis dkyil 'khor du'o //
NK027(sha)002:8719: rdo rje khyung drag rtsal la sogs pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8721: yo ga'i drug cu rtsa gsum mo //
NK027(sha)002:8723: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku che ba'i yon tan brjod pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8725: dbang thob pas bkra shis shing yon tan rgyud la skye ba'o //
NK027(sha)002:8726: de nas dbang de mi nyams shing /
NK027(sha)002:8727: gdams ngag gsal gdab pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:8728: rang gi snying gi dkyil du dwangs ma chen po lnga gnas pa ni /
NK027(sha)002:8729: rang bzhin gyi rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gdod nas gnas pa'o //
NK027(sha)002:8730: de yang spyi bor thig le dkar po ril ma tsam gcig bsam /
NK027(sha)002:8731: de gsal ba dang nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig le shar /
NK027(sha)002:8732: zhes pas thig le dkar po de yar mar babs
NK027(sha)002:8733: pas snying gi dkyil 'khor du dwangs ma rigs lngar
NK027(sha)002:8734: gnas gnyis med du 'dres par bsam /
NK027(sha)002:8735: de don dam mtshan nyid med pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK027(sha)002:8736: rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi lha //
NK027(sha)002:8737: snang ba kun rdzob ye shes kyi snang ba de
NK027(sha)002:8738: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i ngang las blos ma
NK027(sha)002:8739: bcos par gnas pa dbyings chos nyid yin te /
NK027(sha)002:8740: de nas dkyil 'khor la mchod bstod /
NK027(sha)002:8746: me tog bkram la rom mo dang bcas pas /
NK027(sha)002:8748: rnam par snang mdzad ye shes dam pa mtsho chen ldan //
NK027(sha)002:8749: zla ba nya 'dra'i sku mnga' srid pa mthar phyin pa //
NK027(sha)002:8750: dgongs pa mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK027(sha)002:8751: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi byed bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:8752: mi 'khrugs rgyal po srid dang gti mug rnam sbyangs pa //
NK027(sha)002:8753: dge ba mnyam med sems can don rdzogs rab ldan pa //
NK027(sha)002:8754: mgon po yon tan mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK027(sha)002:8755: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi byed bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:8756: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan rnams kyis rgyan gnas shing //
NK027(sha)002:8757: yang dag 'byor ba'i sbyin pa sbyin mdzad mi bslu ba //
NK027(sha)002:8758: rin chen 'byung ldan zhes bya'i bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK027(sha)002:8759: bkra shis bsam gtan dang ni ting 'dzin pha rol phyin gnas shing //
NK027(sha)002:8760: ye shes pad+ma'i steng gzhis dpag med tshe ldan pa'i //
NK027(sha)002:8761: 'od dpag med pa'i byin rlabs bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK027(sha)002:8762: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi byed bde legs shog /
NK027(sha)002:8763: sems can don phyir las la thugs ni sbyor mdzad cing //
NK027(sha)002:8764: 'gro ba thams cad 'ching ba'i bcing las sgrol mdzad pa //
NK027(sha)002:8765: thugs mchog don yod grub pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK027(sha)002:8766: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi byed bde legs shog //
NK027(sha)002:8767: ces brjod la me tog gtor /
NK027(sha)002:8768: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo bar bya'o //
